LONG_HELP: dict[str, dict[str, str]] = {
    "bg": {
        'Size of waypoint symbols on the map as a percentage of the built-in artwork (list dialogs keep a fixed row icon size).': 'Размер на символите на точки на картата като процент от вградената илюстрация (списъчните диалогови прозорци поддържат фиксиран размер на иконата на реда).',
        'Home waypoint name, arrival altitude difference relative to the safety arrival height, and distance. Click to change the home waypoint.': 'Име на домашна точка, разлика във височината на пристигане спрямо височината на безопасно пристигане и разстояние. Щракнете, за да промените началната точка.',
        'Current QNH pressure setting used for barometric altitude calculation. Tap the infobox to open the setup panel and adjust QNH manually.': 'Текущата настройка на налягането QNH, използвана за изчисляване на барометрична надморска височина. Докоснете информационното поле, за да отворите панела за настройка и да настроите QNH ръчно.',
        'This page shows WiFi status when NetworkManager or ConnMan is on D-Bus (e.g. Linux with Wayland or KMS). Open WiFi list to scan and connect when a service is available.': 'Тази страница показва състоянието на WiFi, когато NetworkManager или ConnMan са на D-Bus (напр. Linux с Wayland или KMS). Отворете WiFi списъка, за да сканирате и да се свържете, когато е налична услуга.',
        'The terrain can be shaded among slopes to indicate either wind direction, sun position, a geographically fixed shading from North-West, or a screen-relative fixed shading from top left.': 'Теренът може да бъде засенчен между склоновете, за да посочи посоката на вятъра, позицията на слънцето, географски фиксирано засенчване от северозапад или фиксирано засенчване спрямо екрана от горния ляв ъгъл.',
        "Synchronize the glide polar between XCSoar and the device (LXNAV varios). 'Receive' adopts the polar from the device (e.g. for club gliders). 'Send' pushes XCSoar's polar to the device.": 'Синхронизирайте полюса на плъзгане между XCSoar и устройството (LXNAV varios). „Получаване“ приема полюса от устройството (напр. за клубни планери). „Изпращане“ избутва полярника на XCSoar към устройството.',
        'List of active airspace files. Use the Add and Remove buttons to activate or deactivate airspace files respectively. Supported file types are: Openair (.openair /.txt /.air), and Tim Newport-Pearce (.sua).': 'Списък на активните файлове на въздушното пространство. Използвайте бутоните Добавяне и Премахване, за да активирате или деактивирате съответно файлове за въздушно пространство. Поддържаните типове файлове са: Openair (.openair /.txt /.air) и Tim Newport-Pearce (.sua).',
        'Signed countdown until the start gate opens or closes (now). Value colour and secondary line reflect gate state at the current time: Waiting (blue), Open (green), Closed (red). PEV window overrides task gate when set.': 'Подписано обратно броене до отварянето или затварянето на стартовата врата (сега). Цветът на стойността и вторичната линия отразяват състоянието на вратата в текущия момент: чакане (синьо), отворено (зелено), затворено (червено). Прозорецът PEV отменя вратата на задачата, когато е зададен.',
        'Tells XCSoar to send its current GPS position to the device as $GPGGA and $GPRMC sentences. Turn off when another GPS source is already feeding the device on the same line. Changes take effect after reconnecting the device.': 'Казва на XCSoar да изпрати текущата си GPS позиция на устройството като $GPGGA и $GPRMC изречения. Изключете, когато друг GPS източник вече захранва устройството на същата линия. Промените влизат в сила след повторно свързване на устройството.',
        'Logger pressure altitude when the device provides it (igc_pressure_altitude), otherwise ISA pressure altitude only (1013.25 hPa; not QNH-corrected). Does not show barometric AMSL or GPS height — use other InfoBoxes for navigation.': 'Регистрирайте барометричната височина, когато устройството я предоставя (igc_pressure_altitude), в противен случай само барометричната височина по ISA (1013,25 hPa; не е коригирана с QNH). Не показва барометрична AMSL или GPS височина — използвайте други информационни полета за навигация.',
        'Same gate as Start open. Main value is estimated time to reach the start line (MacCready leg when available, else distance / ground speed). Value colour and secondary line reflect gate state at that ETA: Too early (blue), Can start (green), Too late (red).': 'Същата врата като Start отворена. Основната стойност е очакваното време за достигане на стартовата линия (крак MacCready, когато е наличен, в противен случай разстояние / земна скорост). Цветът на стойността и вторичната линия отразяват състоянието на вратата при това ETA: твърде рано (синьо), може да започне (зелено), твърде късно (червено).',
        'Active waypoint: shows the next task waypoint when an ordered task is loaded, otherwise the Goto waypoint. Displays the waypoint name, arrival altitude difference relative to the safety arrival height, and distance. Click to choose a different waypoint (a task waypoint to skip to that leg, or any waypoint to set as Goto when no task is loaded).': 'Активна междинна точка: показва следващата междинна точка на задача, когато е заредена поръчана задача, в противен случай междинната точка Goto. Показва името на точката, разликата във височината на пристигане спрямо безопасното пристигане и разстоянието. Щракнете, за да изберете друга междинна точка (пътна точка на задача, която да прескочите до този етап, или всяка точка, която да зададете като Goto, когато няма заредена задача).',
        'FFVP Federal Cup (NetCoupe) on WeGlide. The scored path has at most three turnpoints between start and finish and at least 25 km total. Points are proportional to credited distance, 100 divided by the glider handicap (DAeC-style index), and a success factor of 1.0 for a free flight or 1.2 for a task declared electronically before takeoff. XCSoar live scoring uses a success factor of 1.0 only, not the 1.2 multiplier for declared tasks.': 'Федерална купа на FFVP (NetCoupe) на WeGlide. Оценената пътека има най-много три обратни точки между старта и финала и поне 25 км общо. Точките са пропорционални на кредитираната дистанция, 100 разделени на хендикапа на планера (индекс в стил DAeC) и коефициент на успех 1,0 за свободен полет или 1,2 за задача, декларирана електронно преди излитане. Точкуването на живо в XCSoar използва само коефициент на успех 1,0, а не множител 1,2 за декларирани задачи.',
        'Previous waypoint: when an ordered task is loaded, automatically tracks the task waypoint before the active leg (the start waypoint when on the first leg). Displays the waypoint name, arrival altitude difference relative to the safety arrival height, and distance. Click to choose a different waypoint to display (task waypoints when a task is loaded, otherwise the full waypoint list); selection is informational only and never advances the task or sets a Goto. With a task loaded, choose "Resume auto tracking" at the top of the list to revert to automatic tracking.': 'Предишна междинна точка: когато се зареди поръчана задача, автоматично проследява междинната точка на задачата преди активния етап (началната междинна точка, когато е на първия етап). Показва името на точката, разликата във височината на пристигане спрямо безопасното пристигане и разстоянието. Щракнете, за да изберете друга точка за показване (точки на задачата, когато задача е заредена, в противен случай пълния списък с точки); изборът е само информативен и никога не напредва задачата или задава Goto. При заредена задача изберете "Възобновете автоматичното проследяване" в горната част на списъка, за да се върнете към автоматично проследяване.',
        'This parameter estimates the height%s at which the average dry updraft strength drops below 225 fpm and is expected to give better quantitative numbers for the maximum cloudless thermalling height than the BL Top height, especially when mixing results from vertical wind shear rather than thermals. (Note: the present assumptions tend to underpredict the max. thermalling height for dry conditions.) In the presence of clouds the maximum thermalling height may instead be limited by the cloud base. Being for "dry" thermals, this parameter omits the effect of "cloudsuck".': 'Този параметър оценява височината %s, при която средната сила на сухото възходящо течение пада под 225 fpm и се очаква да даде по-добри количествени стойности за максималната безоблачна термична височина от височината BL Top, особено когато смесването е резултат от вертикално срязване на вятъра, а не от термики. (Забележка: настоящите предположения са склонни да предскажат по-малко от максималната височина на загряване за сухи условия.) При наличие на облаци максималната височина на загряване може вместо това да бъде ограничена от основата на облака. Тъй като е за "суха" термика, този параметър пропуска ефекта на "всмукване на облак".',
        '![](resource:IDB_WARNING_TRIANGLE)\n\n!!! warning\n# Important Safety Notice\n\nBy using XCSoar, you acknowledge and accept the following:\n\n## Limitations\n\n- XCSoar is for **situational awareness only**\n- XCSoar is **not** a FLARM display\n- XCSoar is **not** aviation certified in any way\n- The artificial horizon is **not** fit for any purpose\n- Databanks (airspace, waypoints) may contain errors, be incomplete, or **not** up to date\n- NOTAM display does **not** replace proper pre-flight NOTAM briefing\n- NOTAM data may be incomplete, delayed, filtered, or unavailable\n- XCSoar is **not** guaranteed to be error free\n\n## Pilot Responsibility\n\nThe **Pilot in Command** is always responsible for the safe operation of the aircraft. Never rely solely on XCSoar for navigation or situational awareness.\n\n': '![](resource:IDB_WARNING_TRIANGLE)\n\n!!! warning\n# Важна бележка за безопасност\n\nИзползвайки XCSoar, вие потвърждавате и приемате следното:\n\n## Ограничения\n\n- XCSoar е за **само ситуационна осведоменост**\n- XCSoar е **не** FLARM дисплей\n- XCSoar е **не** авиационен сертифициран по всякакъв начин\n- Изкуственият хоризонт е **не** подходящ за всякакви цели\n- Банките данни (въздушно пространство, пътни точки) може да съдържат грешки, да са непълни или **не** актуални\n- Дисплеят на NOTAM замества ли **не** правилния NOTAM брифинг преди полета\n- NOTAM данните може да са непълни, със закъснение, филтрирани или недостъпни\n- XCSoar е **не** гарантирано без грешки\n\n## Отговорност на пилота\n\n**Командващ пилот** винаги е отговорен за безопасната експлоатация на самолета. Никога не разчитайте единствено на XCSoar за навигация или ситуационна осведоменост.\n\n',
        '# Getting Started\n\nTo use XCSoar effectively, configure the following:\n\n- [Restore from backup](xcsoar://dialog/backup) - Restore previous XCSoar data from a USB or SD card (optional)\n\n- [%s] [Map and data](xcsoar://config/site-files) - Download maps, waypoints, and airspace files for your region\n\n- [%s] [Aircraft polar](xcsoar://config/planes) - Set up your aircraft with the correct polar curve\n\n- [%s] [Pilot info](xcsoar://config/logger) - Enter your name and weight\n\n- [%s] [Devices](xcsoar://config/devices) - Connect your flight instruments\n\n- [%s] [WeGlide](xcsoar://config/weglide) - Upload flights automatically to WeGlide\n\n- [%s] [Thermal Information Map](xcsoar://config/weather) - Show thermal locations from thermalmap.info on the map\n\n- [%s] [Safety factors](xcsoar://config/safety) - Set arrival height, terrain clearance and polar degradation\n\n- [%s] [Terrain Display](xcsoar://config/terrain) - Choose terrain colors, shading and contour lines\n\n- [ ] [Live tracking](xcsoar://config/tracking) *(optional)* - Share your position via SkyLines or LiveTrack24\n\nThe easiest way to explore XCSoar is to [replay an existing IGC flight](xcsoar://dialog/replay).': '# Първи стъпки\n\nЗа да използвате ефективно XCSoar, конфигурирайте следното:\n\n- [Възстановяване от резервно копие](xcsoar://dialog/backup) - Възстановете предишни XCSoar данни от USB или SD карта (по избор)\n\n- [%s] [Карта и данни](xcsoar://config/site-files) - Изтеглете карти, точки и файлове с въздушно пространство за вашия регион\n\n- [%s] [Самолет полярен](xcsoar://config/planes) - Настройте вашия самолет с правилната полярна крива\n\n- [%s] [Информация за пилота](xcsoar://config/logger) - Въведете вашето име и тегло\n\n- [%s] [устройства](xcsoar://config/devices) - Свържете вашите летателни инструменти\n\n- [%s] [WeGlide](xcsoar://config/weglide) - Качвайте полети автоматично в WeGlide\n\n- [%s] [Термична информационна карта](xcsoar://config/weather) - Показване на термални местоположения от termalmap.info на картата\n\n- [%s] [Фактори на безопасност](xcsoar://config/safety) - Задайте височина на пристигане, разстояние от терена и полярна деградация\n\n- [%s] [Показване на терена](xcsoar://config/terrain) - Изберете цветове на терена, засенчване и контурни линии\n\n- [ ] [Проследяване на живо](xcsoar://config/tracking) *(optional)* - Споделете вашата позиция чрез SkyLines или LiveTrack24\n\nНай-лесният начин да изследвате XCSoar е да [повторете съществуващ полет на IGC](xcsoar://dialog/replay).',
        '# Gesture Navigation\n\nXCSoar supports touch gestures on the map:\n\n- ![U](resource:IDB_GESTURE_UP) **Swipe Up** (U): Zoom in\n- ![D](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DOWN) **Swipe Down** (D): Zoom out\n- ![R](resource:IDB_GESTURE_RIGHT) **Swipe Right** (R): Previous screen mode\n- ![L](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LEFT) **Swipe Left** (L): Next screen mode\n- ![UD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_UD) **Up-Down** (UD): Auto zoom\n- ![DU](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DU) **Down-Up** (DU): Menu\n- ![DR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DR) **Down-Right** (DR): Waypoint details\n- ![DL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DL) **Down-Left** (DL): Alternates\n- ![LU](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LU) **Left-Up** (LU): Recently used waypoints\n- ![RD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_RD) **Right-Down** (RD): Task manager\n- ![URD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_URD) **Up-Right-Down** (URD): Analysis\n- ![LDR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LDR) **Left-Down-Right** (LDR): Checklist\n- ![URDL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_URDL) **Up-Right-Down-Left** (URDL): Pan mode\n- ![LDRDL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LDRDL) **Left-Down-Right-Down-Left** (LDRDL): Status\n- ![ULDR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_ULDR) **Up-Left-Down-Right** (ULDR): Quick menu\n\nLong-press on the map to enter Pan mode. Tap while in Pan mode to see nearby waypoints.': '# Навигация с жестове\n\nXCSoar поддържа жестове с докосване на картата:\n\n- ![U](resource:IDB_GESTURE_UP) **Плъзнете нагоре** (U): Увеличете мащаба\n- ![D](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DOWN) **Плъзнете надолу** (D): Намаляване\n- ![R](resource:IDB_GESTURE_RIGHT) **Плъзнете надясно** (R): Режим на предишен екран\n- ![L](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LEFT) **Плъзнете наляво** (L): Следващ екранен режим\n- ![UD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_UD) **Нагоре-Надолу** (UD): Автоматично увеличение\n- ![DU](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DU) **Надолу-Нагоре** (DU): Меню\n- ![DR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DR) **Надолу-надясно** (DR): Подробности за точката\n- ![DL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DL) **Долу-ляво** (DL): Заместници\n- ![LU](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LU) **Ляво-Нагоре** (LU): Наскоро използвани точки\n- ![RD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_RD) **Надясно-Надолу** (RD): Мениджър на задачи\n- ![URD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_URD) **Нагоре-надясно-надолу** (URD): Анализ\n- ![LDR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LDR) **Ляво-Надолу-Дясно** (LDR): Контролен списък\n- ![URDL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_URDL) **Нагоре-надясно-надолу-наляво** (URDL): Пан режим\n- ![LDRDL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LDRDL) **Наляво-Надолу-Надясно-Надолу-Наляво** (LDRDL): Статус\n- ![ULDR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_ULDR) **Нагоре-наляво-надолу-надясно** (ULDR): Бързо меню\n\nНатиснете дълго върху картата, за да влезете в режим Pan. Докоснете, докато сте в режим Pan, за да видите точки наблизо.',
    },
    "ca": {
        'Size of waypoint symbols on the map as a percentage of the built-in artwork (list dialogs keep a fixed row icon size).': "Mida dels símbols de waypoint al mapa com a percentatge de l'il·lustració integrada (els diàlegs de llista mantenen una mida fixa d'icona de fila).",
        'Home waypoint name, arrival altitude difference relative to the safety arrival height, and distance. Click to change the home waypoint.': "Nom del punt d'inici, diferència d'altitud d'arribada en relació amb l'alçada d'arribada de seguretat i distància. Feu clic per canviar el waypoint d'inici.",
        'Current QNH pressure setting used for barometric altitude calculation. Tap the infobox to open the setup panel and adjust QNH manually.': "Configuració actual de pressió QNH utilitzada per al càlcul d'altitud baromètrica. Toqueu el quadre d'informació per obrir el tauler de configuració i ajustar QNH manualment.",
        'This page shows WiFi status when NetworkManager or ConnMan is on D-Bus (e.g. Linux with Wayland or KMS). Open WiFi list to scan and connect when a service is available.': "Aquesta pàgina mostra l'estat de WiFi quan NetworkManager o ConnMan estan a D-Bus (p. ex., Linux amb Wayland o KMS). Obriu la llista de WiFi per escanejar i connectar-vos quan hi hagi un servei disponible.",
        'The terrain can be shaded among slopes to indicate either wind direction, sun position, a geographically fixed shading from North-West, or a screen-relative fixed shading from top left.': 'El terreny es pot ombrejar entre els vessants per indicar la direcció del vent, la posició del sol, un ombreig fixat geogràficament des del nord-oest o un ombrejat fix relatiu a la pantalla des de la part superior esquerra.',
        "Synchronize the glide polar between XCSoar and the device (LXNAV varios). 'Receive' adopts the polar from the device (e.g. for club gliders). 'Send' pushes XCSoar's polar to the device.": 'Sincronitza el polar de lliscament entre XCSoar i el dispositiu (LXNAV diversos). "Rebre" adopta el polar del dispositiu (per exemple, per a planadors de club). "Envia" empeny el polar de XCSoar al dispositiu.',
        'List of active airspace files. Use the Add and Remove buttons to activate or deactivate airspace files respectively. Supported file types are: Openair (.openair /.txt /.air), and Tim Newport-Pearce (.sua).': "Llista de fitxers d'espai aeri actius. Utilitzeu els botons Afegeix i Elimina per activar o desactivar fitxers d'espai aeri respectivament. Els tipus de fitxers admesos són: Openair (.openair /.txt /.air) i Tim Newport-Pearce (.sua).",
        'Signed countdown until the start gate opens or closes (now). Value colour and secondary line reflect gate state at the current time: Waiting (blue), Open (green), Closed (red). PEV window overrides task gate when set.': "Compte enrere signat fins que s'obri o es tanqui la porta d'inici (ara). El color del valor i la línia secundària reflecteixen l'estat de la porta en el moment actual: En espera (blau), Obert (verd), Tancat (vermell). La finestra PEV anul·la la porta de tasques quan s'estableix.",
        'Tells XCSoar to send its current GPS position to the device as $GPGGA and $GPRMC sentences. Turn off when another GPS source is already feeding the device on the same line. Changes take effect after reconnecting the device.': 'Indica a XCSoar que enviï la seva posició GPS actual al dispositiu com a frases $GPGGA i $GPRMC. Apagueu quan una altra font GPS ja estigui alimentant el dispositiu a la mateixa línia. Els canvis tenen efecte després de tornar a connectar el dispositiu.',
        'Logger pressure altitude when the device provides it (igc_pressure_altitude), otherwise ISA pressure altitude only (1013.25 hPa; not QNH-corrected). Does not show barometric AMSL or GPS height — use other InfoBoxes for navigation.': "Registra l'altitud de pressió quan el dispositiu la proporciona (igc_pressure_altitude), en cas contrari només l'altitud de pressió ISA (1013,25 hPa; no corregit per QNH). No mostra l'alçada baromètrica de l'AMSL ni del GPS; utilitzeu altres InfoBoxes per a la navegació.",
        'Same gate as Start open. Main value is estimated time to reach the start line (MacCready leg when available, else distance / ground speed). Value colour and secondary line reflect gate state at that ETA: Too early (blue), Can start (green), Too late (red).': "La mateixa porta que Inici oberta. El valor principal és el temps estimat per arribar a la línia de sortida (cama MacCready quan estigui disponible, en cas contrari la distància / velocitat de terra). El color del valor i la línia secundària reflecteixen l'estat de la porta en aquesta ETA: Massa aviat (blau), Pot començar (verd), Massa tard (vermell).",
        'Active waypoint: shows the next task waypoint when an ordered task is loaded, otherwise the Goto waypoint. Displays the waypoint name, arrival altitude difference relative to the safety arrival height, and distance. Click to choose a different waypoint (a task waypoint to skip to that leg, or any waypoint to set as Goto when no task is loaded).': "Punt de ruta actiu: mostra el punt de ruta següent de la tasca quan es carrega una tasca ordenada, en cas contrari, el punt de ruta Anar a. Mostra el nom del waypoint, la diferència d'altitud d'arribada en relació amb l'alçada d'arribada de seguretat i la distància. Feu clic per triar un waypoint diferent (un waypoint de la tasca per saltar a aquest tram, o qualsevol waypoint per establir com Goto quan no es carregui cap tasca).",
        'FFVP Federal Cup (NetCoupe) on WeGlide. The scored path has at most three turnpoints between start and finish and at least 25 km total. Points are proportional to credited distance, 100 divided by the glider handicap (DAeC-style index), and a success factor of 1.0 for a free flight or 1.2 for a task declared electronically before takeoff. XCSoar live scoring uses a success factor of 1.0 only, not the 1.2 multiplier for declared tasks.': "Copa Federal FFVP (NetCoupe) a WeGlide. El camí puntuat té com a màxim tres trencalls entre la sortida i l'arribada i un mínim de 25 km en total. Els punts són proporcionals a la distància acreditada, 100 dividits pel handicap del planador (índex d'estil DAeC) i un factor d'èxit d'1,0 per a un vol lliure o 1,2 per a una tasca declarada electrònicament abans de l'enlairament. La puntuació en directe de XCSoar només utilitza un factor d'èxit d'1,0, no el multiplicador d'1,2 per a les tasques declarades.",
        'Previous waypoint: when an ordered task is loaded, automatically tracks the task waypoint before the active leg (the start waypoint when on the first leg). Displays the waypoint name, arrival altitude difference relative to the safety arrival height, and distance. Click to choose a different waypoint to display (task waypoints when a task is loaded, otherwise the full waypoint list); selection is informational only and never advances the task or sets a Goto. With a task loaded, choose "Resume auto tracking" at the top of the list to revert to automatic tracking.': 'Punt de ruta anterior: quan es carrega una tasca ordenada, fa un seguiment automàtic del punt de ruta de la tasca abans del tram actiu (el punt de ruta inicial quan es troba al primer tram). Mostra el nom del waypoint, la diferència d\'altitud d\'arribada en relació amb l\'alçada d\'arribada de seguretat i la distància. Feu clic per triar un waypoint diferent per mostrar (punts de ruta de la tasca quan es carrega una tasca, en cas contrari, la llista completa de waypoints); la selecció només és informativa i mai avança la tasca ni estableix un Goto. Amb una tasca carregada, trieu "Reprèn el seguiment automàtic" a la part superior de la llista per tornar al seguiment automàtic.',
        'This parameter estimates the height%s at which the average dry updraft strength drops below 225 fpm and is expected to give better quantitative numbers for the maximum cloudless thermalling height than the BL Top height, especially when mixing results from vertical wind shear rather than thermals. (Note: the present assumptions tend to underpredict the max. thermalling height for dry conditions.) In the presence of clouds the maximum thermalling height may instead be limited by the cloud base. Being for "dry" thermals, this parameter omits the effect of "cloudsuck".': 'Aquest paràmetre estima l\'alçada %s a la qual la força de corrent ascendent seca mitjana baixa per sota de 225 fpm i s\'espera que doni millors números quantitatius per a l\'alçada tèrmica màxima sense núvols que l\'alçada BL Top, especialment quan es barregen els resultats de la cisalla vertical del vent en lloc de les tèrmiques. (Nota: les suposicions actuals tendeixen a subestimar l\'alçada tèrmica màxima per a condicions seques.) En presència de núvols, l\'alçada tèrmica màxima pot estar limitada per la base del núvol. En tractar-se de tèrmiques "seques", aquest paràmetre omet l\'efecte de "suc de núvols".',
        '![](resource:IDB_WARNING_TRIANGLE)\n\n!!! warning\n# Important Safety Notice\n\nBy using XCSoar, you acknowledge and accept the following:\n\n## Limitations\n\n- XCSoar is for **situational awareness only**\n- XCSoar is **not** a FLARM display\n- XCSoar is **not** aviation certified in any way\n- The artificial horizon is **not** fit for any purpose\n- Databanks (airspace, waypoints) may contain errors, be incomplete, or **not** up to date\n- NOTAM display does **not** replace proper pre-flight NOTAM briefing\n- NOTAM data may be incomplete, delayed, filtered, or unavailable\n- XCSoar is **not** guaranteed to be error free\n\n## Pilot Responsibility\n\nThe **Pilot in Command** is always responsible for the safe operation of the aircraft. Never rely solely on XCSoar for navigation or situational awareness.\n\n': "![](resource:IDB_WARNING_TRIANGLE)\n\n!!! warning\n# Avís de seguretat important\n\nEn utilitzar XCSoar, reconeixeu i accepteu el següent:\n\n## Limitacions\n\n- XCSoar és per a **només consciència de la situació**\n- XCSoar és **no** una pantalla FLARM\n- XCSoar té la certificació d'aviació **no** de qualsevol manera\n- L'horitzó artificial és **no** apte per a qualsevol propòsit\n- Els bancs de dades (espai aeri, waypoints) poden contenir errors, estar incomplets o **no** actualitzats\n- La visualització de NOTAM fa que **no** substitueix la sessió informativa de NOTAM prèvia al vol\n- Les dades NOTAM poden estar incompletes, retardades, filtrades o no disponibles\n- XCSoar té la garantia de **no** sense errors\n\n## Responsabilitat del pilot\n\nEl **Pilot al comandament** sempre és responsable de l'operació segura de l'aeronau. No confieu mai únicament en XCSoar per a la navegació o la consciència de la situació.\n\n",
        '# Getting Started\n\nTo use XCSoar effectively, configure the following:\n\n- [Restore from backup](xcsoar://dialog/backup) - Restore previous XCSoar data from a USB or SD card (optional)\n\n- [%s] [Map and data](xcsoar://config/site-files) - Download maps, waypoints, and airspace files for your region\n\n- [%s] [Aircraft polar](xcsoar://config/planes) - Set up your aircraft with the correct polar curve\n\n- [%s] [Pilot info](xcsoar://config/logger) - Enter your name and weight\n\n- [%s] [Devices](xcsoar://config/devices) - Connect your flight instruments\n\n- [%s] [WeGlide](xcsoar://config/weglide) - Upload flights automatically to WeGlide\n\n- [%s] [Thermal Information Map](xcsoar://config/weather) - Show thermal locations from thermalmap.info on the map\n\n- [%s] [Safety factors](xcsoar://config/safety) - Set arrival height, terrain clearance and polar degradation\n\n- [%s] [Terrain Display](xcsoar://config/terrain) - Choose terrain colors, shading and contour lines\n\n- [ ] [Live tracking](xcsoar://config/tracking) *(optional)* - Share your position via SkyLines or LiveTrack24\n\nThe easiest way to explore XCSoar is to [replay an existing IGC flight](xcsoar://dialog/replay).': "# Primers passos\n\nPer utilitzar XCSoar de manera eficaç, configureu el següent:\n\n- [Restaura des de la còpia de seguretat](xcsoar://dialog/backup) - Restaura les dades anteriors de XCSoar des d'una targeta USB o SD (opcional)\n\n- [%s] [Mapa i dades](xcsoar://config/site-files) - Baixeu mapes, waypoints i fitxers d'espai aeri per a la vostra regió\n\n- [%s] [Aeronau polar](xcsoar://config/planes) - Configureu el vostre avió amb la corba polar correcta\n\n- [%s] [Informació del pilot](xcsoar://config/logger) - Introduïu el vostre nom i pes\n\n- [%s] [Dispositius](xcsoar://config/devices) - Connecteu els vostres instruments de vol\n\n- [%s] [WeGlide](xcsoar://config/weglide) - Carregueu vols automàticament a WeGlide\n\n- [%s] [Mapa d'informació tèrmica](xcsoar://config/weather) - Mostra les ubicacions tèrmiques de thermalmap.info al mapa\n\n- [%s] [Factors de seguretat](xcsoar://config/safety) - Estableix l'alçada d'arribada, l'espai lliure del terreny i la degradació polar\n\n- [%s] [Visualització del terreny](xcsoar://config/terrain) - Trieu els colors del terreny, l'ombrejat i les corbes de nivell\n\n- [ ] [Seguiment en directe](xcsoar://config/tracking) *(optional)* - Comparteix la teva posició mitjançant SkyLines o LiveTrack24\n\nLa manera més fàcil d'explorar XCSoar és [reproduir un vol IGC existent](xcsoar://dialog/replay).",
        '# Gesture Navigation\n\nXCSoar supports touch gestures on the map:\n\n- ![U](resource:IDB_GESTURE_UP) **Swipe Up** (U): Zoom in\n- ![D](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DOWN) **Swipe Down** (D): Zoom out\n- ![R](resource:IDB_GESTURE_RIGHT) **Swipe Right** (R): Previous screen mode\n- ![L](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LEFT) **Swipe Left** (L): Next screen mode\n- ![UD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_UD) **Up-Down** (UD): Auto zoom\n- ![DU](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DU) **Down-Up** (DU): Menu\n- ![DR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DR) **Down-Right** (DR): Waypoint details\n- ![DL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DL) **Down-Left** (DL): Alternates\n- ![LU](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LU) **Left-Up** (LU): Recently used waypoints\n- ![RD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_RD) **Right-Down** (RD): Task manager\n- ![URD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_URD) **Up-Right-Down** (URD): Analysis\n- ![LDR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LDR) **Left-Down-Right** (LDR): Checklist\n- ![URDL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_URDL) **Up-Right-Down-Left** (URDL): Pan mode\n- ![LDRDL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LDRDL) **Left-Down-Right-Down-Left** (LDRDL): Status\n- ![ULDR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_ULDR) **Up-Left-Down-Right** (ULDR): Quick menu\n\nLong-press on the map to enter Pan mode. Tap while in Pan mode to see nearby waypoints.': "# Navegació gestual\n\nXCSoar admet gestos tàctils al mapa:\n\n- ![U](resource:IDB_GESTURE_UP) **Llisca cap amunt** (U): Apropa\n- ![D](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DOWN) **Feu lliscar cap avall** (D): Allunya el zoom\n- ![R](resource:IDB_GESTURE_RIGHT) **Llisca cap a la dreta** (R): Mode de pantalla anterior\n- ![L](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LEFT) **Llisca cap a l'esquerra** (L): Següent mode de pantalla\n- ![UD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_UD) **Amunt-Avall** (UD): Zoom automàtic\n- ![DU](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DU) **Avall-Amunt** (DU): Menú\n- ![DR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DR) **Abaix-Dreta** (DR): Detalls del waypoint\n- ![DL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DL) **Abaix-Esquerra** (DL): Suplents\n- ![LU](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LU) **Esquerra amunt** (LU): Waypoints utilitzats recentment\n- ![RD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_RD) **Dreta-Avall** (RD): Gestor de tasques\n- ![URD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_URD) **Amunt-Dreta-Avall** (URD): Anàlisi\n- ![LDR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LDR) **Esquerra-Abaix-Dreta** (LDR): Llista de verificació\n- ![URDL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_URDL) **Amunt-Dreta-Abaix-Esquerra** (URDL): Mode panoràmica\n- ![LDRDL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LDRDL) **Esquerra-Abaix-Dreta-Avall-Esquerra** (LDRDL): Estat\n- ![ULDR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_ULDR) **Amunt-Esquerra-Abaix-Dreta** (ULDR): Menú ràpid\n\nPremeu llargament el mapa per entrar al mode Panorama. Toqueu mentre esteu en el mode Panorama per veure punts de referència propers.",
    },
    "cs": {
        'Size of waypoint symbols on the map as a percentage of the built-in artwork (list dialogs keep a fixed row icon size).': 'Velikost symbolů navigačních bodů na mapě jako procento vestavěné kresby (dialogová okna seznamu mají pevnou velikost ikony řádku).',
        'Home waypoint name, arrival altitude difference relative to the safety arrival height, and distance. Click to change the home waypoint.': 'Název trasového bodu domů, rozdíl nadmořské výšky příjezdu vzhledem k výšce bezpečného příjezdu a vzdálenost. Kliknutím změníte domovský trasový bod.',
        'Current QNH pressure setting used for barometric altitude calculation. Tap the infobox to open the setup panel and adjust QNH manually.': 'Aktuální nastavení tlaku QNH používané pro výpočet barometrické výšky. Klepnutím na informační pole otevřete panel nastavení a ručně upravte QNH.',
        'This page shows WiFi status when NetworkManager or ConnMan is on D-Bus (e.g. Linux with Wayland or KMS). Open WiFi list to scan and connect when a service is available.': 'Tato stránka zobrazuje stav WiFi, když je NetworkManager nebo ConnMan na D-Bus (např. Linux s Wayland nebo KMS). Otevřete seznam WiFi a vyhledejte a připojte se, když je služba dostupná.',
        'The terrain can be shaded among slopes to indicate either wind direction, sun position, a geographically fixed shading from North-West, or a screen-relative fixed shading from top left.': 'Terén může být zastíněn mezi svahy, aby bylo možné indikovat buď směr větru, polohu slunce, geograficky pevné zastínění ze severozápadu nebo pevné stínění relativní k obrazovce zleva nahoře.',
        "Synchronize the glide polar between XCSoar and the device (LXNAV varios). 'Receive' adopts the polar from the device (e.g. for club gliders). 'Send' pushes XCSoar's polar to the device.": "Synchronizujte klouzavou poláru mezi XCSoarem a zařízením (LXNAV varios). „Příjem“ přebírá poláru ze zařízení (např. pro klubové kluzáky). 'Odeslat' posune poláru XCSoar do zařízení.",
        'List of active airspace files. Use the Add and Remove buttons to activate or deactivate airspace files respectively. Supported file types are: Openair (.openair /.txt /.air), and Tim Newport-Pearce (.sua).': 'Seznam souborů aktivního vzdušného prostoru. Pomocí tlačítek Přidat a Odebrat můžete soubory vzdušného prostoru aktivovat nebo deaktivovat. Podporované typy souborů jsou: Openair (.openair /.txt /.air) a Tim Newport-Pearce (.sua).',
        'Signed countdown until the start gate opens or closes (now). Value colour and secondary line reflect gate state at the current time: Waiting (blue), Open (green), Closed (red). PEV window overrides task gate when set.': 'Podepsané odpočítávání do otevření nebo zavření startovací brány (nyní). Barva hodnoty a sekundární čára odrážejí stav brány v aktuálním čase: Čeká (modrá), Otevřeno (zelená), Zavřeno (červená). Okno PEV přepíše bránu úlohy, když je nastaveno.',
        'Tells XCSoar to send its current GPS position to the device as $GPGGA and $GPRMC sentences. Turn off when another GPS source is already feeding the device on the same line. Changes take effect after reconnecting the device.': 'Řekne XCSoar, aby poslal svou aktuální GPS pozici do zařízení jako $GPGGA a $GPRMC věty. Vypněte, když jiný zdroj GPS již napájí zařízení na stejné lince. Změny se projeví po opětovném připojení zařízení.',
        'Logger pressure altitude when the device provides it (igc_pressure_altitude), otherwise ISA pressure altitude only (1013.25 hPa; not QNH-corrected). Does not show barometric AMSL or GPS height — use other InfoBoxes for navigation.': 'Zaznamenat tlakovou výšku, když ji zařízení poskytuje (igc_pressure_altitude), jinak pouze tlakovou výšku ISA (1013,25 hPa; bez korekce QNH). Nezobrazuje barometrickou výšku AMSL ani GPS – pro navigaci použijte jiné InfoBoxy.',
        'Same gate as Start open. Main value is estimated time to reach the start line (MacCready leg when available, else distance / ground speed). Value colour and secondary line reflect gate state at that ETA: Too early (blue), Can start (green), Too late (red).': 'Stejná brána jako Start otevřena. Hlavní hodnota je odhadovaný čas na dosažení startovní čáry (MacCready noha, pokud je k dispozici, jinak vzdálenost / rychlost vůči zemi). Barva hodnoty a sekundární čára odrážejí stav brány v daném ETA: Příliš brzy (modrá), Může začít (zelená), Příliš pozdě (červená).',
        'Active waypoint: shows the next task waypoint when an ordered task is loaded, otherwise the Goto waypoint. Displays the waypoint name, arrival altitude difference relative to the safety arrival height, and distance. Click to choose a different waypoint (a task waypoint to skip to that leg, or any waypoint to set as Goto when no task is loaded).': 'Aktivní trasový bod: zobrazuje trasový bod další úlohy, když je načten objednaný úkol, jinak trasový bod Přejít. Zobrazuje název navigačního bodu, rozdíl nadmořské výšky příjezdu vzhledem k výšce bezpečného příjezdu a vzdálenost. Kliknutím vyberte jiný trasový bod (traťový bod úkolu, který chcete přeskočit na tuto nohu, nebo jakýkoli trasový bod, který chcete nastavit jako Goto, když není načten žádný úkol).',
        'FFVP Federal Cup (NetCoupe) on WeGlide. The scored path has at most three turnpoints between start and finish and at least 25 km total. Points are proportional to credited distance, 100 divided by the glider handicap (DAeC-style index), and a success factor of 1.0 for a free flight or 1.2 for a task declared electronically before takeoff. XCSoar live scoring uses a success factor of 1.0 only, not the 1.2 multiplier for declared tasks.': 'Federální pohár FFVP (NetCoupe) na WeGlide. Bodovaná dráha má nejvýše tři otočné body mezi startem a cílem a celkem nejméně 25 km. Body jsou úměrné započítané vzdálenosti, 100 děleno handicapem kluzáku (index ve stylu DAeC) a faktorem úspěšnosti 1,0 za volný let nebo 1,2 za úkol deklarovaný elektronicky před vzletem. XCSoar live scoring používá faktor úspěchu pouze 1,0, nikoli multiplikátor 1,2 pro deklarované úkoly.',
        'Previous waypoint: when an ordered task is loaded, automatically tracks the task waypoint before the active leg (the start waypoint when on the first leg). Displays the waypoint name, arrival altitude difference relative to the safety arrival height, and distance. Click to choose a different waypoint to display (task waypoints when a task is loaded, otherwise the full waypoint list); selection is informational only and never advances the task or sets a Goto. With a task loaded, choose "Resume auto tracking" at the top of the list to revert to automatic tracking.': 'Předchozí trasový bod: když je načten objednaný úkol, automaticky sleduje trasový bod úkolu před aktivním úsekem (počáteční bod na prvním úseku). Zobrazuje název navigačního bodu, rozdíl nadmořské výšky příjezdu vzhledem k výšce bezpečného příjezdu a vzdálenost. Kliknutím vyberte jiný trasový bod, který se má zobrazit (traťové body úlohy, když je úloha načtena, jinak úplný seznam trasových bodů); výběr je pouze informativní a nikdy neposune úlohu ani nenastaví Goto. Po načtení úlohy vyberte "Obnovit automatické sledování" v horní části seznamu, abyste se vrátili k automatickému sledování.',
        'This parameter estimates the height%s at which the average dry updraft strength drops below 225 fpm and is expected to give better quantitative numbers for the maximum cloudless thermalling height than the BL Top height, especially when mixing results from vertical wind shear rather than thermals. (Note: the present assumptions tend to underpredict the max. thermalling height for dry conditions.) In the presence of clouds the maximum thermalling height may instead be limited by the cloud base. Being for "dry" thermals, this parameter omits the effect of "cloudsuck".': 'Tento parametr odhaduje výšku%s, při které průměrná síla vzestupného tahu za sucha klesne pod 225 fpm a očekává se, že poskytne lepší kvantitativní čísla pro maximální bezoblačnou výšku stoupání než výška BL Top, zejména pokud jsou výsledky smíchání z vertikálního střihu větru spíše než z termiky. (Poznámka: současné předpoklady mají tendenci podhodnocovat maximální výšku stoupání pro suché podmínky.) V přítomnosti oblačnosti může být maximální výška stoupání omezena základnou oblačnosti. Vzhledem k tomu, že jde o "suchou" termiku, tento parametr vynechává efekt "cloudsuck".',
        '![](resource:IDB_WARNING_TRIANGLE)\n\n!!! warning\n# Important Safety Notice\n\nBy using XCSoar, you acknowledge and accept the following:\n\n## Limitations\n\n- XCSoar is for **situational awareness only**\n- XCSoar is **not** a FLARM display\n- XCSoar is **not** aviation certified in any way\n- The artificial horizon is **not** fit for any purpose\n- Databanks (airspace, waypoints) may contain errors, be incomplete, or **not** up to date\n- NOTAM display does **not** replace proper pre-flight NOTAM briefing\n- NOTAM data may be incomplete, delayed, filtered, or unavailable\n- XCSoar is **not** guaranteed to be error free\n\n## Pilot Responsibility\n\nThe **Pilot in Command** is always responsible for the safe operation of the aircraft. Never rely solely on XCSoar for navigation or situational awareness.\n\n': '![](resource:IDB_WARNING_TRIANGLE)\n\n!!! warning\n# Důležité bezpečnostní upozornění\n\nPoužíváním XCSoar berete na vědomí a přijímáte následující:\n\n## Omezení\n\n- XCSoar je pro **pouze situační povědomí**\n- XCSoar je **ne** a FLARM displej\n- XCSoar je jakýmkoli způsobem certifikován pro letectví **ne**\n- Umělý horizont je **ne** vhodný pro jakýkoli účel\n- Databanky (vzdušný prostor, navigační body) mohou obsahovat chyby, být neúplné nebo **ne** aktuální\n- Zobrazení NOTAM nahrazuje **ne** řádnou předletovou instruktáž NOTAM\n- Data NOTAM mohou být neúplná, zpožděná, filtrovaná nebo nedostupná\n- XCSoar je **ne** zaručeně bez chyb\n\n## Odpovědnost pilota\n\nZa bezpečný provoz letadla vždy odpovídá **Pilot ve velení**. Nikdy se nespoléhejte pouze na XCSoar pro navigaci nebo situační povědomí.\n\n',
        '# Getting Started\n\nTo use XCSoar effectively, configure the following:\n\n- [Restore from backup](xcsoar://dialog/backup) - Restore previous XCSoar data from a USB or SD card (optional)\n\n- [%s] [Map and data](xcsoar://config/site-files) - Download maps, waypoints, and airspace files for your region\n\n- [%s] [Aircraft polar](xcsoar://config/planes) - Set up your aircraft with the correct polar curve\n\n- [%s] [Pilot info](xcsoar://config/logger) - Enter your name and weight\n\n- [%s] [Devices](xcsoar://config/devices) - Connect your flight instruments\n\n- [%s] [WeGlide](xcsoar://config/weglide) - Upload flights automatically to WeGlide\n\n- [%s] [Thermal Information Map](xcsoar://config/weather) - Show thermal locations from thermalmap.info on the map\n\n- [%s] [Safety factors](xcsoar://config/safety) - Set arrival height, terrain clearance and polar degradation\n\n- [%s] [Terrain Display](xcsoar://config/terrain) - Choose terrain colors, shading and contour lines\n\n- [ ] [Live tracking](xcsoar://config/tracking) *(optional)* - Share your position via SkyLines or LiveTrack24\n\nThe easiest way to explore XCSoar is to [replay an existing IGC flight](xcsoar://dialog/replay).': '# Začínáme\n\nChcete-li efektivně používat XCSoar, nakonfigurujte následující:\n\n- [Obnovit ze zálohy](xcsoar://dialog/backup) - Obnovte předchozí data XCSoar z USB nebo SD karty (volitelné)\n\n- [%s] [Mapa a data](xcsoar://config/site-files) - Stáhněte si mapy, navigační body a soubory vzdušného prostoru pro váš region\n\n- [%s] [Polární letadla](xcsoar://config/planes) - Nastavte své letadlo se správnou polární křivkou\n\n- [%s] [Informace o pilotovi](xcsoar://config/logger) - Zadejte své jméno a váhu\n\n- [%s] [Zařízení](xcsoar://config/devices) - Připojte své letové přístroje\n\n- [%s] [WeGlide](xcsoar://config/weglide) - Nahrajte lety automaticky do WeGlide\n\n- [%s] [Termální informační mapa](xcsoar://config/weather) - Zobrazit na mapě termální umístění z thermalmap.info\n\n- [%s] [Bezpečnostní faktory](xcsoar://config/safety) - Nastavte výšku příjezdu, světlou výšku terénu a polární degradaci\n\n- [%s] [Zobrazení terénu](xcsoar://config/terrain) - Vyberte barvy terénu, stínování a vrstevnice\n\n- [ ] [Živé sledování](xcsoar://config/tracking) *(optional)* - Sdílejte svou pozici prostřednictvím SkyLines nebo LiveTrack24\n\nNejjednodušší způsob, jak prozkoumat XCSoar, je [přehrát existující let IGC](xcsoar://dialog/replay).',
        '# Gesture Navigation\n\nXCSoar supports touch gestures on the map:\n\n- ![U](resource:IDB_GESTURE_UP) **Swipe Up** (U): Zoom in\n- ![D](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DOWN) **Swipe Down** (D): Zoom out\n- ![R](resource:IDB_GESTURE_RIGHT) **Swipe Right** (R): Previous screen mode\n- ![L](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LEFT) **Swipe Left** (L): Next screen mode\n- ![UD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_UD) **Up-Down** (UD): Auto zoom\n- ![DU](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DU) **Down-Up** (DU): Menu\n- ![DR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DR) **Down-Right** (DR): Waypoint details\n- ![DL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DL) **Down-Left** (DL): Alternates\n- ![LU](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LU) **Left-Up** (LU): Recently used waypoints\n- ![RD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_RD) **Right-Down** (RD): Task manager\n- ![URD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_URD) **Up-Right-Down** (URD): Analysis\n- ![LDR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LDR) **Left-Down-Right** (LDR): Checklist\n- ![URDL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_URDL) **Up-Right-Down-Left** (URDL): Pan mode\n- ![LDRDL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LDRDL) **Left-Down-Right-Down-Left** (LDRDL): Status\n- ![ULDR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_ULDR) **Up-Left-Down-Right** (ULDR): Quick menu\n\nLong-press on the map to enter Pan mode. Tap while in Pan mode to see nearby waypoints.': '# Navigace gesty\n\nXCSoar podporuje dotyková gesta na mapě:\n\n- ![U](resource:IDB_GESTURE_UP) **Přejeďte nahoru** (U): Přiblížit\n- ![D](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DOWN) **Přejeďte dolů** (D): Oddálit\n- ![R](resource:IDB_GESTURE_RIGHT) **Přejeďte doprava** (R): Předchozí režim obrazovky\n- ![L](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LEFT) **Přejeďte doleva** (L): Režim další obrazovky\n- ![UD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_UD) **Nahoru-dolů** (UD): Automatický zoom\n- ![DU](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DU) **Down-Up** (DU): Menu\n- ![DR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DR) **Dolů-vpravo** (DR): Podrobnosti trasového bodu\n- ![DL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DL) **Dolů-vlevo** (DL): Náhradníci\n- ![LU](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LU) **Zleva nahoru** (LU): Nedávno použité průjezdní body\n- ![RD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_RD) **Zprava-dolů** (RD): Správce úloh\n- ![URD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_URD) **Nahoru-vpravo-dolů** (URD): Analýza\n- ![LDR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LDR) **Vlevo-dolů-vpravo** (LDR): Kontrolní seznam\n- ![URDL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_URDL) **Nahoru-vpravo-dolů-vlevo** (URDL): Režim Pan\n- ![LDRDL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LDRDL) **Vlevo-dolů-vpravo-dolů-vlevo** (LDRDL): Postavení\n- ![ULDR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_ULDR) **Nahoru-vlevo-dolů-vpravo** (ULDR): Rychlé menu\n\nDlouhým stisknutím na mapě vstoupíte do režimu Pan. Klepnutím v režimu Posouvání zobrazíte blízké trasové body.',
    },
    "da": {
        'Size of waypoint symbols on the map as a percentage of the built-in artwork (list dialogs keep a fixed row icon size).': 'Størrelse af waypoint-symboler på kortet som en procentdel af den indbyggede illustration (listedialoger beholder en fast rækkeikonstørrelse).',
        'Home waypoint name, arrival altitude difference relative to the safety arrival height, and distance. Click to change the home waypoint.': 'Hjemmewaypointnavn, ankomsthøjdeforskel i forhold til sikkerhedsankomsthøjden og afstand. Klik for at ændre hjemmewaypointet.',
        'Current QNH pressure setting used for barometric altitude calculation. Tap the infobox to open the setup panel and adjust QNH manually.': 'Aktuel QNH-trykindstilling, der bruges til barometrisk højdeberegning. Tryk på infoboksen for at åbne opsætningspanelet og justere QNH manuelt.',
        'This page shows WiFi status when NetworkManager or ConnMan is on D-Bus (e.g. Linux with Wayland or KMS). Open WiFi list to scan and connect when a service is available.': 'Denne side viser WiFi-status, når NetworkManager eller ConnMan er på D-Bus (f.eks. Linux med Wayland eller KMS). Åbn WiFi-listen for at scanne og oprette forbindelse, når en tjeneste er tilgængelig.',
        'The terrain can be shaded among slopes to indicate either wind direction, sun position, a geographically fixed shading from North-West, or a screen-relative fixed shading from top left.': 'Terrænet kan skygges blandt skråninger for at angive enten vindretning, solposition, en geografisk fast skygge fra Nord-Vest eller en skærmrelativ fast skygge fra øverst til venstre.',
        "Synchronize the glide polar between XCSoar and the device (LXNAV varios). 'Receive' adopts the polar from the device (e.g. for club gliders). 'Send' pushes XCSoar's polar to the device.": "Synkroniser glidepolaren mellem XCSoar og enheden (LXNAV varios). 'Receive' adopterer polaren fra enheden (f.eks. til klubsvævefly). 'Send' skubber XCSoars polar til enheden.",
        'List of active airspace files. Use the Add and Remove buttons to activate or deactivate airspace files respectively. Supported file types are: Openair (.openair /.txt /.air), and Tim Newport-Pearce (.sua).': 'Liste over aktive luftrumsfiler. Brug knapperne Tilføj og Fjern til henholdsvis at aktivere eller deaktivere luftrumsfiler. Understøttede filtyper er: Openair (.openair /.txt /.air) og Tim Newport-Pearce (.sua).',
        'Signed countdown until the start gate opens or closes (now). Value colour and secondary line reflect gate state at the current time: Waiting (blue), Open (green), Closed (red). PEV window overrides task gate when set.': 'Underskrevet nedtælling indtil startporten åbner eller lukker (nu). Værdifarve og sekundær linje afspejler portens tilstand på det aktuelle tidspunkt: Venter (blå), Åben (grøn), Lukket (rød). PEV-vinduet tilsidesætter opgaveporten, når den er indstillet.',
        'Tells XCSoar to send its current GPS position to the device as $GPGGA and $GPRMC sentences. Turn off when another GPS source is already feeding the device on the same line. Changes take effect after reconnecting the device.': 'Beder XCSoar om at sende sin aktuelle GPS-position til enheden som $GPGGA- og $GPRMC-sætninger. Sluk, når en anden GPS-kilde allerede fodrer enheden på samme linje. Ændringer træder i kraft efter gentilslutning af enheden.',
        'Logger pressure altitude when the device provides it (igc_pressure_altitude), otherwise ISA pressure altitude only (1013.25 hPa; not QNH-corrected). Does not show barometric AMSL or GPS height — use other InfoBoxes for navigation.': 'Loggertrykhøjde, når enheden giver det (igc_pressure_altitude), ellers kun ISA-trykhøjde (1013,25 hPa; ikke QNH-korrigeret). Viser ikke barometrisk AMSL- eller GPS-højde — brug andre infobokse til navigation.',
        'Same gate as Start open. Main value is estimated time to reach the start line (MacCready leg when available, else distance / ground speed). Value colour and secondary line reflect gate state at that ETA: Too early (blue), Can start (green), Too late (red).': 'Samme port som Start åben. Hovedværdien er estimeret tid til at nå startlinjen (MacCready-benet, når det er tilgængeligt, ellers distance / hastighed). Værdifarve og sekundær linje afspejler gatetilstanden ved denne ETA: For tidligt (blå), Kan starte (grøn), For sent (rød).',
        'Active waypoint: shows the next task waypoint when an ordered task is loaded, otherwise the Goto waypoint. Displays the waypoint name, arrival altitude difference relative to the safety arrival height, and distance. Click to choose a different waypoint (a task waypoint to skip to that leg, or any waypoint to set as Goto when no task is loaded).': 'Aktivt waypoint: viser det næste opgave-waypoint, når en bestilt opgave er indlæst, ellers Goto-waypointet. Viser waypointnavnet, ankomsthøjdeforskellen i forhold til sikkerhedsankomsthøjden og afstanden. Klik for at vælge et andet waypoint (et opgave-waypoint for at springe til dette ben, eller et hvilket som helst waypoint, der skal indstilles som Goto, når ingen opgave er indlæst).',
        'FFVP Federal Cup (NetCoupe) on WeGlide. The scored path has at most three turnpoints between start and finish and at least 25 km total. Points are proportional to credited distance, 100 divided by the glider handicap (DAeC-style index), and a success factor of 1.0 for a free flight or 1.2 for a task declared electronically before takeoff. XCSoar live scoring uses a success factor of 1.0 only, not the 1.2 multiplier for declared tasks.': 'FFVP Federal Cup (NetCoupe) på WeGlide. Den scorede sti har højst tre vendepunkter mellem start og mål og mindst 25 km i alt. Point er proportional med krediteret distance, 100 divideret med svæveflyhandicap (DAeC-stil indeks) og en succesfaktor på 1,0 for en fri flyvning eller 1,2 for en opgave, der erklæres elektronisk før start. XCSoar live scoring bruger kun en succesfaktor på 1,0, ikke multiplikatoren på 1,2 for erklærede opgaver.',
        'Previous waypoint: when an ordered task is loaded, automatically tracks the task waypoint before the active leg (the start waypoint when on the first leg). Displays the waypoint name, arrival altitude difference relative to the safety arrival height, and distance. Click to choose a different waypoint to display (task waypoints when a task is loaded, otherwise the full waypoint list); selection is informational only and never advances the task or sets a Goto. With a task loaded, choose "Resume auto tracking" at the top of the list to revert to automatic tracking.': 'Forrige waypoint: når en bestilt opgave er indlæst, sporer automatisk opgavens waypoint før det aktive ben (startwaypointet, når det er på det første ben). Viser waypointnavnet, ankomsthøjdeforskellen i forhold til sikkerhedsankomsthøjden og afstanden. Klik for at vælge et andet waypoint, der skal vises (opgave-waypoints, når en opgave er indlæst, ellers den fulde waypoint-liste); Valget er kun informativt og fremmer aldrig opgaven eller angiver en Goto. Med en opgave indlæst skal du vælge "Genoptag automatisk sporing" øverst på listen for at vende tilbage til automatisk sporing.',
        'This parameter estimates the height%s at which the average dry updraft strength drops below 225 fpm and is expected to give better quantitative numbers for the maximum cloudless thermalling height than the BL Top height, especially when mixing results from vertical wind shear rather than thermals. (Note: the present assumptions tend to underpredict the max. thermalling height for dry conditions.) In the presence of clouds the maximum thermalling height may instead be limited by the cloud base. Being for "dry" thermals, this parameter omits the effect of "cloudsuck".': 'Denne parameter estimerer højden%s, ved hvilken den gennemsnitlige tørstrømsstyrke falder til under 225 fpm og forventes at give bedre kvantitative tal for den maksimale skyfri termiske højde end BL Top-højden, især ved blandingsresultater fra lodret vindforskydning frem for termik. (Bemærk: de nuværende antagelser har en tendens til at underforudsige den maksimale termiske højde for tørre forhold.) I nærvær af skyer kan den maksimale termiske højde i stedet være begrænset af skybasen. Da denne parameter er til "tør" termik, udelades effekten af \u200b\u200b"skysug".',
        '![](resource:IDB_WARNING_TRIANGLE)\n\n!!! warning\n# Important Safety Notice\n\nBy using XCSoar, you acknowledge and accept the following:\n\n## Limitations\n\n- XCSoar is for **situational awareness only**\n- XCSoar is **not** a FLARM display\n- XCSoar is **not** aviation certified in any way\n- The artificial horizon is **not** fit for any purpose\n- Databanks (airspace, waypoints) may contain errors, be incomplete, or **not** up to date\n- NOTAM display does **not** replace proper pre-flight NOTAM briefing\n- NOTAM data may be incomplete, delayed, filtered, or unavailable\n- XCSoar is **not** guaranteed to be error free\n\n## Pilot Responsibility\n\nThe **Pilot in Command** is always responsible for the safe operation of the aircraft. Never rely solely on XCSoar for navigation or situational awareness.\n\n': '![](resource:IDB_WARNING_TRIANGLE)\n\n!!! warning\n# Vigtig sikkerhedsmeddelelse\n\nVed at bruge XCSoar, anerkender og accepterer du følgende:\n\n## Begrænsninger\n\n- XCSoar er for **Kun situationsbevidsthed**\n- XCSoar er **ikke** en FLARM-skærm\n- XCSoar er **ikke** luftfartscertificeret på nogen måde\n- Den kunstige horisont er **ikke** egnet til ethvert formål\n- Databanker (luftrum, waypoints) kan indeholde fejl, være ufuldstændige eller **ikke** opdaterede\n- NOTAM-displayet erstatter korrekt NOTAM-briefing før flyvning\n- NOTAM-data kan være ufuldstændige, forsinkede, filtrerede eller utilgængelige\n- XCSoar er **ikke** garanteret at være fejlfri\n\n## Pilotansvar\n\n**Pilot i kommando** er altid ansvarlig for sikker drift af flyet. Stol aldrig udelukkende på XCSoar til navigation eller situationsbevidsthed.\n\n',
        '# Getting Started\n\nTo use XCSoar effectively, configure the following:\n\n- [Restore from backup](xcsoar://dialog/backup) - Restore previous XCSoar data from a USB or SD card (optional)\n\n- [%s] [Map and data](xcsoar://config/site-files) - Download maps, waypoints, and airspace files for your region\n\n- [%s] [Aircraft polar](xcsoar://config/planes) - Set up your aircraft with the correct polar curve\n\n- [%s] [Pilot info](xcsoar://config/logger) - Enter your name and weight\n\n- [%s] [Devices](xcsoar://config/devices) - Connect your flight instruments\n\n- [%s] [WeGlide](xcsoar://config/weglide) - Upload flights automatically to WeGlide\n\n- [%s] [Thermal Information Map](xcsoar://config/weather) - Show thermal locations from thermalmap.info on the map\n\n- [%s] [Safety factors](xcsoar://config/safety) - Set arrival height, terrain clearance and polar degradation\n\n- [%s] [Terrain Display](xcsoar://config/terrain) - Choose terrain colors, shading and contour lines\n\n- [ ] [Live tracking](xcsoar://config/tracking) *(optional)* - Share your position via SkyLines or LiveTrack24\n\nThe easiest way to explore XCSoar is to [replay an existing IGC flight](xcsoar://dialog/replay).': '# Kom godt i gang\n\nFor at bruge XCSoar effektivt skal du konfigurere følgende:\n\n- [Gendan fra backup](xcsoar://dialog/backup) - Gendan tidligere XCSoar-data fra et USB- eller SD-kort (valgfrit)\n\n- [%s] [Kort og data](xcsoar://config/site-files) - Download kort, waypoints og luftrumsfiler for din region\n\n- [%s] [Fly polar](xcsoar://config/planes) - Indstil dit fly med den korrekte polære kurve\n\n- [%s] [Pilot info](xcsoar://config/logger) - Indtast dit navn og vægt\n\n- [%s] [Enheder](xcsoar://config/devices) - Tilslut dine flyinstrumenter\n\n- [%s] [WeGlide](xcsoar://config/weglide) - Upload flyafgange automatisk til WeGlide\n\n- [%s] [Termisk informationskort](xcsoar://config/weather) - Vis termiske steder fra thermalmap.info på kortet\n\n- [%s] [Sikkerhedsfaktorer](xcsoar://config/safety) - Indstil ankomsthøjde, terrænfrihøjde og polar nedbrydning\n\n- [%s] [Terræn display](xcsoar://config/terrain) - Vælg terrænfarver, skygge og konturlinjer\n\n- [ ] [Live tracking](xcsoar://config/tracking) *(optional)* - Del din position via SkyLines eller LiveTrack24\n\nDen nemmeste måde at udforske XCSoar er at [afspille en eksisterende IGC-flyvning](xcsoar://dialog/replay).',
        '# Gesture Navigation\n\nXCSoar supports touch gestures on the map:\n\n- ![U](resource:IDB_GESTURE_UP) **Swipe Up** (U): Zoom in\n- ![D](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DOWN) **Swipe Down** (D): Zoom out\n- ![R](resource:IDB_GESTURE_RIGHT) **Swipe Right** (R): Previous screen mode\n- ![L](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LEFT) **Swipe Left** (L): Next screen mode\n- ![UD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_UD) **Up-Down** (UD): Auto zoom\n- ![DU](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DU) **Down-Up** (DU): Menu\n- ![DR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DR) **Down-Right** (DR): Waypoint details\n- ![DL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DL) **Down-Left** (DL): Alternates\n- ![LU](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LU) **Left-Up** (LU): Recently used waypoints\n- ![RD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_RD) **Right-Down** (RD): Task manager\n- ![URD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_URD) **Up-Right-Down** (URD): Analysis\n- ![LDR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LDR) **Left-Down-Right** (LDR): Checklist\n- ![URDL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_URDL) **Up-Right-Down-Left** (URDL): Pan mode\n- ![LDRDL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LDRDL) **Left-Down-Right-Down-Left** (LDRDL): Status\n- ![ULDR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_ULDR) **Up-Left-Down-Right** (ULDR): Quick menu\n\nLong-press on the map to enter Pan mode. Tap while in Pan mode to see nearby waypoints.': '# Gestik navigation\n\nXCSoar understøtter berøringsbevægelser på kortet:\n\n- ![U](resource:IDB_GESTURE_UP) **Swipe op** (U): Zoom ind\n- ![D](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DOWN) **Stryg ned** (D): Zoom ud\n- ![R](resource:IDB_GESTURE_RIGHT) **Stryg til højre** (R): Forrige skærmtilstand\n- ![L](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LEFT) **Stryg til venstre** (L): Næste skærmtilstand\n- ![UD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_UD) **Op-Ned** (UD): Auto zoom\n- ![DU](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DU) **Ned-Op** (DU): Menu\n- ![DR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DR) **Ned til højre** (DR): Waypoint detaljer\n- ![DL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DL) **Ned-venstre** (DL): Supplerende\n- ![LU](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LU) **Venstre-Op** (LU): Nyligt brugte waypoints\n- ![RD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_RD) **Højre ned** (RD): Task manager\n- ![URD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_URD) **Op-Højre-Ned** (URD): Analyse\n- ![LDR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LDR) **Venstre-Ned-Højre** (LDR): Tjekliste\n- ![URDL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_URDL) **Op-Højre-Ned-Venstre** (URDL): Panoreringstilstand\n- ![LDRDL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LDRDL) **Venstre-Ned-Højre-Ned-Venstre** (LDRDL): Status\n- ![ULDR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_ULDR) **Op-Venstre-Ned-Højre** (ULDR): Hurtig menu\n\nTryk længe på kortet for at gå ind i panoreringstilstand. Tryk på, mens du er i panoreringstilstand for at se nærliggende waypoints.',
    },
    "de": {
        'Size of waypoint symbols on the map as a percentage of the built-in artwork (list dialogs keep a fixed row icon size).': 'Größe der Wegpunktsymbole auf der Karte in Prozent der eingebauten Grafik (Listendialoge behalten eine feste Symbolgröße in der Zeile).',
        'Home waypoint name, arrival altitude difference relative to the safety arrival height, and distance. Click to change the home waypoint.': 'Name des Heimat-Wegpunkts, Ankunftshöhendifferenz relativ zur Sicherheitsankunftshöhe und Entfernung. Tippen, um den Heimat-Wegpunkt zu ändern.',
        'Current QNH pressure setting used for barometric altitude calculation. Tap the infobox to open the setup panel and adjust QNH manually.': 'Aktuelle QNH-Druckeinstellung für die barometrische Höhenberechnung. Tippen Sie auf die InfoBox, um das Einstellungsfeld zu öffnen und QNH manuell anzupassen.',
        'This page shows WiFi status when NetworkManager or ConnMan is on D-Bus (e.g. Linux with Wayland or KMS). Open WiFi list to scan and connect when a service is available.': 'Diese Seite zeigt den WLAN-Status, wenn NetworkManager oder ConnMan auf D-Bus verfügbar ist (z. B. Linux mit Wayland oder KMS). Öffnen Sie die WLAN-Liste zum Suchen und Verbinden, wenn ein Dienst verfügbar ist.',
        'The terrain can be shaded among slopes to indicate either wind direction, sun position, a geographically fixed shading from North-West, or a screen-relative fixed shading from top left.': 'Das Gelände kann an Hängen schattiert werden, um Windrichtung, Sonnenstand, eine geografisch feste Schattierung von Nordwest oder eine bildschirmrelative feste Schattierung von oben links anzuzeigen.',
        "Synchronize the glide polar between XCSoar and the device (LXNAV varios). 'Receive' adopts the polar from the device (e.g. for club gliders). 'Send' pushes XCSoar's polar to the device.": 'Gleitpolare zwischen XCSoar und dem Gerät synchronisieren (LXNAV-Varios). „Empfangen“ übernimmt die Polare vom Gerät (z. B. für Vereinssegler). „Senden“ überträgt die XCSoar-Polare an das Gerät.',
        'List of active airspace files. Use the Add and Remove buttons to activate or deactivate airspace files respectively. Supported file types are: Openair (.openair /.txt /.air), and Tim Newport-Pearce (.sua).': 'Liste aktiver Luftraumdateien. Mit den Schaltflächen Hinzufügen und Entfernen können Luftraumdateien aktiviert bzw. deaktiviert werden. Unterstützte Dateitypen: Openair (.openair /.txt /.air) und Tim Newport-Pearce (.sua).',
        'Signed countdown until the start gate opens or closes (now). Value colour and secondary line reflect gate state at the current time: Waiting (blue), Open (green), Closed (red). PEV window overrides task gate when set.': 'Vorzeichenbehafteter Countdown bis zum Öffnen oder Schließen des Startgates (jetzt). Wertfarbe und zweite Zeile zeigen den Gate-Status zum aktuellen Zeitpunkt: Warten (blau), Offen (grün), Geschlossen (rot). PEV-Fenster überschreibt das Aufgaben-Gate, wenn gesetzt.',
        'Tells XCSoar to send its current GPS position to the device as $GPGGA and $GPRMC sentences. Turn off when another GPS source is already feeding the device on the same line. Changes take effect after reconnecting the device.': 'Veranlasst XCSoar, die aktuelle GPS-Position als $GPGGA- und $GPRMC-Sätze an das Gerät zu senden. Deaktivieren, wenn bereits eine andere GPS-Quelle das Gerät über dieselbe Leitung versorgt. Änderungen werden nach erneutem Verbinden wirksam.',
        'Logger pressure altitude when the device provides it (igc_pressure_altitude), otherwise ISA pressure altitude only (1013.25 hPa; not QNH-corrected). Does not show barometric AMSL or GPS height — use other InfoBoxes for navigation.': 'Logger-Druckhöhe, wenn das Gerät sie liefert (igc_pressure_altitude), andernfalls nur ISA-Druckhöhe (1013,25 hPa; nicht QNH-korrigiert). Zeigt keine barometrische AMSL oder GPS-Höhe — verwenden Sie andere InfoBoxen für die Navigation.',
        'Same gate as Start open. Main value is estimated time to reach the start line (MacCready leg when available, else distance / ground speed). Value colour and secondary line reflect gate state at that ETA: Too early (blue), Can start (green), Too late (red).': 'Dasselbe Gate wie Start offen. Hauptwert ist die geschätzte Zeit bis zur Startlinie (MacCready-Strecke falls verfügbar, sonst Entfernung / Bodengeschwindigkeit). Wertfarbe und zweite Zeile zeigen den Gate-Status zu dieser ETA: Zu früh (blau), Start möglich (grün), Zu spät (rot).',
        'Active waypoint: shows the next task waypoint when an ordered task is loaded, otherwise the Goto waypoint. Displays the waypoint name, arrival altitude difference relative to the safety arrival height, and distance. Click to choose a different waypoint (a task waypoint to skip to that leg, or any waypoint to set as Goto when no task is loaded).': 'Aktiver Wegpunkt: zeigt den nächsten Aufgaben-Wegpunkt bei geladener geordneter Aufgabe, andernfalls den Goto-Wegpunkt. Zeigt Wegpunktname, Ankunftshöhendifferenz relativ zur Sicherheitsankunftshöhe und Entfernung. Tippen, um einen anderen Wegpunkt zu wählen (Aufgaben-Wegpunkt zum Überspringen auf dieses Segment oder beliebigen Wegpunkt als Goto, wenn keine Aufgabe geladen ist).',
        'FFVP Federal Cup (NetCoupe) on WeGlide. The scored path has at most three turnpoints between start and finish and at least 25 km total. Points are proportional to credited distance, 100 divided by the glider handicap (DAeC-style index), and a success factor of 1.0 for a free flight or 1.2 for a task declared electronically before takeoff. XCSoar live scoring uses a success factor of 1.0 only, not the 1.2 multiplier for declared tasks.': 'FFVP Federal Cup (NetCoupe) auf WeGlide. Der gewertete Pfad hat höchstens drei Wendepunkte zwischen Start und Ziel und mindestens 25 km Gesamtstrecke. Punkte sind proportional zur anerkannten Distanz, 100 geteilt durch den Segler-Handicap (DAeC-Index), und einem Erfolgsfaktor von 1,0 für einen freien Flug oder 1,2 für vor dem Start elektronisch deklarierte Aufgabe. XCSoar-Live-Wertung verwendet nur einen Erfolgsfaktor von 1,0, nicht den 1,2-Multiplikator für deklarierte Aufgaben.',
        'Previous waypoint: when an ordered task is loaded, automatically tracks the task waypoint before the active leg (the start waypoint when on the first leg). Displays the waypoint name, arrival altitude difference relative to the safety arrival height, and distance. Click to choose a different waypoint to display (task waypoints when a task is loaded, otherwise the full waypoint list); selection is informational only and never advances the task or sets a Goto. With a task loaded, choose "Resume auto tracking" at the top of the list to revert to automatic tracking.': 'Vorheriger Wegpunkt: bei geladener geordneter Aufgabe wird automatisch der Aufgaben-Wegpunkt vor dem aktiven Segment verfolgt (Start-Wegpunkt im ersten Segment). Zeigt Wegpunktname, Ankunftshöhendifferenz relativ zur Sicherheitsankunftshöhe und Entfernung. Tippen, um einen anderen anzuzeigenden Wegpunkt zu wählen (Aufgaben-Wegpunkte bei geladener Aufgabe, sonst die vollständige Wegpunktliste); die Auswahl dient nur der Information und setzt weder die Aufgabe fort noch einen Goto. Bei geladener Aufgabe „Automatische Verfolgung fortsetzen“ oben in der Liste wählen, um zur automatischen Verfolgung zurückzukehren.',
        'This parameter estimates the height%s at which the average dry updraft strength drops below 225 fpm and is expected to give better quantitative numbers for the maximum cloudless thermalling height than the BL Top height, especially when mixing results from vertical wind shear rather than thermals. (Note: the present assumptions tend to underpredict the max. thermalling height for dry conditions.) In the presence of clouds the maximum thermalling height may instead be limited by the cloud base. Being for "dry" thermals, this parameter omits the effect of "cloudsuck".': 'Dieser Parameter schätzt die Höhe%s, bei der die durchschnittliche trockene Aufwindstärke unter 225 fpm fällt, und soll genauere quantitative Werte für die maximale wolkenlose Thermikhöhe liefern als die BL-Top-Höhe, besonders bei Vermischung von Ergebnissen aus vertikaler Windscherung statt Thermik. (Hinweis: die gegenwärtigen Annahmen neigen dazu, die max. Thermikhöhe bei trockenen Bedingungen zu unterschätzen.) Bei Wolken kann die maximale Thermikhöhe stattdessen durch die Wolkenbasis begrenzt sein. Da dieser Parameter für „trockene“ Thermik gilt, lässt er den Effekt von „Cloudsuck“ außer Acht.',
        '![](resource:IDB_WARNING_TRIANGLE)\n\n!!! warning\n# Important Safety Notice\n\nBy using XCSoar, you acknowledge and accept the following:\n\n## Limitations\n\n- XCSoar is for **situational awareness only**\n- XCSoar is **not** a FLARM display\n- XCSoar is **not** aviation certified in any way\n- The artificial horizon is **not** fit for any purpose\n- Databanks (airspace, waypoints) may contain errors, be incomplete, or **not** up to date\n- NOTAM display does **not** replace proper pre-flight NOTAM briefing\n- NOTAM data may be incomplete, delayed, filtered, or unavailable\n- XCSoar is **not** guaranteed to be error free\n\n## Pilot Responsibility\n\nThe **Pilot in Command** is always responsible for the safe operation of the aircraft. Never rely solely on XCSoar for navigation or situational awareness.\n\n': '![](resource:IDB_WARNING_TRIANGLE)\n\n!!! warning\n# Wichtiger Sicherheitshinweis\n\nDurch die Nutzung von XCSoar erkennen Sie Folgendes an und akzeptieren es:\n\n## Einschränkungen\n\n- XCSoar dient **nur der Lagesinformation**\n- XCSoar ist **kein** FLARM-Display\n- XCSoar ist in keiner Weise **luftfahrtzertifiziert**\n- Der künstliche Horizont ist **für keinen Zweck geeignet**\n- Datenbanken (Luftraum, Wegpunkte) können Fehler enthalten, unvollständig oder **nicht** aktuell sein\n- Die NOTAM-Anzeige **ersetzt keine** ordnungsgemäße NOTAM-Briefing vor dem Flug\n- NOTAM-Daten können unvollständig, verzögert, gefiltert oder nicht verfügbar sein\n- XCSoar ist **nicht** garantiert fehlerfrei\n\n## Verantwortung des Piloten\n\nDer **verantwortliche Pilot** trägt stets die Verantwortung für den sicheren Betrieb des Luftfahrzeugs. Verlassen Sie sich niemals ausschließlich auf XCSoar für Navigation oder Lageinformation.\n\n',
        '# Getting Started\n\nTo use XCSoar effectively, configure the following:\n\n- [Restore from backup](xcsoar://dialog/backup) - Restore previous XCSoar data from a USB or SD card (optional)\n\n- [%s] [Map and data](xcsoar://config/site-files) - Download maps, waypoints, and airspace files for your region\n\n- [%s] [Aircraft polar](xcsoar://config/planes) - Set up your aircraft with the correct polar curve\n\n- [%s] [Pilot info](xcsoar://config/logger) - Enter your name and weight\n\n- [%s] [Devices](xcsoar://config/devices) - Connect your flight instruments\n\n- [%s] [WeGlide](xcsoar://config/weglide) - Upload flights automatically to WeGlide\n\n- [%s] [Thermal Information Map](xcsoar://config/weather) - Show thermal locations from thermalmap.info on the map\n\n- [%s] [Safety factors](xcsoar://config/safety) - Set arrival height, terrain clearance and polar degradation\n\n- [%s] [Terrain Display](xcsoar://config/terrain) - Choose terrain colors, shading and contour lines\n\n- [ ] [Live tracking](xcsoar://config/tracking) *(optional)* - Share your position via SkyLines or LiveTrack24\n\nThe easiest way to explore XCSoar is to [replay an existing IGC flight](xcsoar://dialog/replay).': '# Erste Schritte\n\nUm XCSoar effektiv zu nutzen, konfigurieren Sie Folgendes:\n\n- [Aus Sicherung wiederherstellen](xcsoar://dialog/backup) - Vorherige XCSoar-Daten von USB- oder SD-Karte wiederherstellen (optional)\n\n- [%s] [Karte und Daten](xcsoar://config/site-files) - Karten, Wegpunkte und Luftraumdateien für Ihre Region herunterladen\n\n- [%s] [Flugzeugpolare](xcsoar://config/planes) - Ihr Flugzeug mit der richtigen Polare einrichten\n\n- [%s] [Piloteninfo](xcsoar://config/logger) - Ihren Namen und Ihr Gewicht eingeben\n\n- [%s] [Geräte](xcsoar://config/devices) - Ihre Fluginstrumente verbinden\n\n- [%s] [WeGlide](xcsoar://config/weglide) - Flüge automatisch zu WeGlide hochladen\n\n- [%s] [Thermik-Informationskarte](xcsoar://config/weather) - Thermikstandorte von thermalmap.info auf der Karte anzeigen\n\n- [%s] [Sicherheitsfaktoren](xcsoar://config/safety) - Ankunftshöhe, Geländeabstand und Polarenverschlechterung festlegen\n\n- [%s] [Geländedarstellung](xcsoar://config/terrain) - Geländefarben, Schattierung und Höhenlinien wählen\n\n- [ ] [Live-Tracking](xcsoar://config/tracking) *(optional)* - Ihre Position über SkyLines oder LiveTrack24 teilen\n\nAm einfachsten erkunden Sie XCSoar, indem Sie [einen vorhandenen IGC-Flug wiedergeben](xcsoar://dialog/replay).',
        '# Gesture Navigation\n\nXCSoar supports touch gestures on the map:\n\n- ![U](resource:IDB_GESTURE_UP) **Swipe Up** (U): Zoom in\n- ![D](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DOWN) **Swipe Down** (D): Zoom out\n- ![R](resource:IDB_GESTURE_RIGHT) **Swipe Right** (R): Previous screen mode\n- ![L](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LEFT) **Swipe Left** (L): Next screen mode\n- ![UD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_UD) **Up-Down** (UD): Auto zoom\n- ![DU](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DU) **Down-Up** (DU): Menu\n- ![DR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DR) **Down-Right** (DR): Waypoint details\n- ![DL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DL) **Down-Left** (DL): Alternates\n- ![LU](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LU) **Left-Up** (LU): Recently used waypoints\n- ![RD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_RD) **Right-Down** (RD): Task manager\n- ![URD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_URD) **Up-Right-Down** (URD): Analysis\n- ![LDR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LDR) **Left-Down-Right** (LDR): Checklist\n- ![URDL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_URDL) **Up-Right-Down-Left** (URDL): Pan mode\n- ![LDRDL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LDRDL) **Left-Down-Right-Down-Left** (LDRDL): Status\n- ![ULDR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_ULDR) **Up-Left-Down-Right** (ULDR): Quick menu\n\nLong-press on the map to enter Pan mode. Tap while in Pan mode to see nearby waypoints.': '# Gestensteuerung\n\nXCSoar unterstützt Touch-Gesten auf der Karte:\n\n- ![U](resource:IDB_GESTURE_UP) **Nach oben wischen** (U): Hineinzoomen\n- ![D](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DOWN) **Nach unten wischen** (D): Herauszoomen\n- ![R](resource:IDB_GESTURE_RIGHT) **Nach rechts wischen** (R): Vorheriger Bildschirmmodus\n- ![L](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LEFT) **Nach links wischen** (L): Nächster Bildschirmmodus\n- ![UD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_UD) **Oben-Unten** (UD): Auto-Zoom\n- ![DU](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DU) **Unten-Oben** (DU): Menü\n- ![DR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DR) **Unten-Rechts** (DR): Wegpunkt-Details\n- ![DL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DL) **Unten-Links** (DL): Alternativen\n- ![LU](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LU) **Links-Oben** (LU): Zuletzt verwendete Wegpunkte\n- ![RD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_RD) **Rechts-Unten** (RD): Aufgabenmanager\n- ![URD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_URD) **Oben-Rechts-Unten** (URD): Analyse\n- ![LDR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LDR) **Links-Unten-Rechts** (LDR): Checkliste\n- ![URDL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_URDL) **Oben-Rechts-Unten-Links** (URDL): Schwenkmodus\n- ![LDRDL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LDRDL) **Links-Unten-Rechts-Unten-Links** (LDRDL): Status\n- ![ULDR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_ULDR) **Oben-Links-Unten-Rechts** (ULDR): Schnellmenü\n\nLange auf die Karte drücken, um in den Schwenkmodus zu wechseln. Im Schwenkmodus tippen, um nahegelegene Wegpunkte anzuzeigen.',
    },
    "el": {
        'Size of waypoint symbols on the map as a percentage of the built-in artwork (list dialogs keep a fixed row icon size).': 'Το μέγεθος των συμβόλων σημείων διαδρομής στο χάρτη ως ποσοστό του ενσωματωμένου έργου τέχνης (οι διάλογοι λίστας διατηρούν ένα σταθερό μέγεθος εικονιδίου σειράς).',
        'Home waypoint name, arrival altitude difference relative to the safety arrival height, and distance. Click to change the home waypoint.': 'Όνομα σημείου οικίας, διαφορά υψομέτρου άφιξης σε σχέση με το ύψος άφιξης ασφαλείας και απόσταση. Κάντε κλικ για να αλλάξετε το σημείο αναφοράς.',
        'Current QNH pressure setting used for barometric altitude calculation. Tap the infobox to open the setup panel and adjust QNH manually.': 'Τρέχουσα ρύθμιση πίεσης QNH που χρησιμοποιείται για τον βαρομετρικό υπολογισμό του υψομέτρου. Πατήστε το πλαίσιο πληροφοριών για να ανοίξετε τον πίνακα ρυθμίσεων και να ρυθμίσετε το QNH με μη αυτόματο τρόπο.',
        'This page shows WiFi status when NetworkManager or ConnMan is on D-Bus (e.g. Linux with Wayland or KMS). Open WiFi list to scan and connect when a service is available.': 'Αυτή η σελίδα εμφανίζει την κατάσταση WiFi όταν το NetworkManager ή το ConnMan είναι σε D-Bus (π.χ. Linux με Wayland ή KMS). Ανοίξτε τη λίστα WiFi για σάρωση και σύνδεση όταν μια υπηρεσία είναι διαθέσιμη.',
        'The terrain can be shaded among slopes to indicate either wind direction, sun position, a geographically fixed shading from North-West, or a screen-relative fixed shading from top left.': 'Το έδαφος μπορεί να σκιάζεται μεταξύ των πλαγιών για να υποδεικνύει είτε την κατεύθυνση του ανέμου, τη θέση του ήλιου, μια γεωγραφικά σταθερή σκίαση από Βορειοδυτικά ή μια σταθερή σκίαση σχετική με την οθόνη από πάνω αριστερά.',
        "Synchronize the glide polar between XCSoar and the device (LXNAV varios). 'Receive' adopts the polar from the device (e.g. for club gliders). 'Send' pushes XCSoar's polar to the device.": "Συγχρονίστε την πολική ολίσθηση μεταξύ του XCSoar και της συσκευής (LXNAV varios). Το «Receive» υιοθετεί το πολικό από τη συσκευή (π.χ. για ανεμόπτερα κλαμπ). Το 'Send' ωθεί το polar του XCSoar στη συσκευή.",
        'List of active airspace files. Use the Add and Remove buttons to activate or deactivate airspace files respectively. Supported file types are: Openair (.openair /.txt /.air), and Tim Newport-Pearce (.sua).': 'Λίστα ενεργών αρχείων εναέριου χώρου. Χρησιμοποιήστε τα κουμπιά Προσθήκη και Αφαίρεση για να ενεργοποιήσετε ή να απενεργοποιήσετε τα αρχεία εναέριου χώρου αντίστοιχα. Οι τύποι αρχείων που υποστηρίζονται είναι: Openair (.openair /.txt /.air) και Tim Newport-Pearce (.sua).',
        'Signed countdown until the start gate opens or closes (now). Value colour and secondary line reflect gate state at the current time: Waiting (blue), Open (green), Closed (red). PEV window overrides task gate when set.': 'Υπογεγραμμένη αντίστροφη μέτρηση μέχρι να ανοίξει ή να κλείσει η πύλη εκκίνησης (τώρα). Το χρώμα της τιμής και η δευτερεύουσα γραμμή αντικατοπτρίζουν την κατάσταση της πύλης την τρέχουσα ώρα: Αναμονή (μπλε), Ανοιχτό (πράσινο), Κλειστό (κόκκινο). Το παράθυρο PEV παρακάμπτει την πύλη εργασιών όταν έχει οριστεί.',
        'Tells XCSoar to send its current GPS position to the device as $GPGGA and $GPRMC sentences. Turn off when another GPS source is already feeding the device on the same line. Changes take effect after reconnecting the device.': 'Λέει στο XCSoar να στείλει την τρέχουσα θέση του GPS στη συσκευή ως προτάσεις $GPGGA και $GPRMC. Απενεργοποιήστε όταν μια άλλη πηγή GPS τροφοδοτεί ήδη τη συσκευή στην ίδια γραμμή. Οι αλλαγές τίθενται σε ισχύ μετά την επανασύνδεση της συσκευής.',
        'Logger pressure altitude when the device provides it (igc_pressure_altitude), otherwise ISA pressure altitude only (1013.25 hPa; not QNH-corrected). Does not show barometric AMSL or GPS height — use other InfoBoxes for navigation.': 'Καταγράψτε το υψόμετρο πίεσης όταν το παρέχει η συσκευή (igc_pressure_altitude), διαφορετικά μόνο υψόμετρο πίεσης ISA (1013,25 hPa, χωρίς διόρθωση QNH). Δεν εμφανίζει βαρομετρικό ύψος AMSL ή GPS — χρησιμοποιήστε άλλα Πλαίσια πληροφοριών για πλοήγηση.',
        'Same gate as Start open. Main value is estimated time to reach the start line (MacCready leg when available, else distance / ground speed). Value colour and secondary line reflect gate state at that ETA: Too early (blue), Can start (green), Too late (red).': 'Ίδια πύλη με το Start ανοιχτό. Η κύρια τιμή είναι ο εκτιμώμενος χρόνος για να φτάσετε στη γραμμή εκκίνησης (πόδι MacCready όταν είναι διαθέσιμο, διαφορετικά απόσταση / ταχύτητα εδάφους). Το χρώμα της τιμής και η δευτερεύουσα γραμμή αντικατοπτρίζουν την κατάσταση της πύλης σε αυτό το ETA: Πολύ νωρίς (μπλε), Μπορεί να ξεκινήσει (πράσινο), Πολύ αργά (κόκκινο).',
        'Active waypoint: shows the next task waypoint when an ordered task is loaded, otherwise the Goto waypoint. Displays the waypoint name, arrival altitude difference relative to the safety arrival height, and distance. Click to choose a different waypoint (a task waypoint to skip to that leg, or any waypoint to set as Goto when no task is loaded).': 'Ενεργό σημείο διαδρομής: εμφανίζει το επόμενο σημείο διαδρομής εργασίας όταν φορτώνεται μια διατεταγμένη εργασία, διαφορετικά το σημείο διαδρομής Goto. Εμφανίζει το όνομα του σημείου διαδρομής, τη διαφορά υψομέτρου άφιξης σε σχέση με το ύψος άφιξης ασφαλείας και την απόσταση. Κάντε κλικ για να επιλέξετε ένα διαφορετικό σημείο διαδρομής (ένα σημείο διαδρομής εργασίας για να μεταβείτε σε αυτό το σκέλος ή οποιοδήποτε σημείο για να ορίσετε ως Μετάβαση όταν δεν φορτώνεται καμία εργασία).',
        'FFVP Federal Cup (NetCoupe) on WeGlide. The scored path has at most three turnpoints between start and finish and at least 25 km total. Points are proportional to credited distance, 100 divided by the glider handicap (DAeC-style index), and a success factor of 1.0 for a free flight or 1.2 for a task declared electronically before takeoff. XCSoar live scoring uses a success factor of 1.0 only, not the 1.2 multiplier for declared tasks.': 'Ομοσπονδιακό Κύπελλο FFVP (NetCoupe) στο WeGlide. Το μονοπάτι που έχει σημειωθεί έχει το πολύ τρεις στροφές μεταξύ εκκίνησης και τερματισμού και τουλάχιστον 25 km συνολικά. Οι πόντοι είναι ανάλογοι της απόστασης που πιστώθηκε, 100 διαιρούμενοι με το μειονέκτημα του ανεμόπτερου (δείκτης τύπου DAeC) και συντελεστής επιτυχίας 1,0 για μια ελεύθερη πτήση ή 1,2 για μια εργασία που δηλώθηκε ηλεκτρονικά πριν από την απογείωση. Η ζωντανή βαθμολογία XCSoar χρησιμοποιεί συντελεστή επιτυχίας 1,0 μόνο, όχι τον πολλαπλασιαστή 1,2 για δηλωμένες εργασίες.',
        'Previous waypoint: when an ordered task is loaded, automatically tracks the task waypoint before the active leg (the start waypoint when on the first leg). Displays the waypoint name, arrival altitude difference relative to the safety arrival height, and distance. Click to choose a different waypoint to display (task waypoints when a task is loaded, otherwise the full waypoint list); selection is informational only and never advances the task or sets a Goto. With a task loaded, choose "Resume auto tracking" at the top of the list to revert to automatic tracking.': 'Προηγούμενο σημείο διαδρομής: όταν φορτώνεται μια διατεταγμένη εργασία, παρακολουθεί αυτόματα το σημείο διαδρομής εργασίας πριν από το ενεργό σκέλος (το σημείο έναρξης όταν βρίσκεται στο πρώτο σκέλος). Εμφανίζει το όνομα του σημείου διαδρομής, τη διαφορά υψομέτρου άφιξης σε σχέση με το ύψος άφιξης ασφαλείας και την απόσταση. Κάντε κλικ για να επιλέξετε ένα διαφορετικό σημείο προς εμφάνιση (σημεία διαδρομής κατά τη φόρτωση μιας εργασίας, διαφορετικά η πλήρης λίστα σημείων διαδρομής). Η επιλογή είναι μόνο ενημερωτική και ποτέ δεν προωθεί την εργασία ή δεν ορίζει Goto. Με μια εργασία φορτωμένη, επιλέξτε "Συνέχιση της αυτόματης παρακολούθησης" στην κορυφή της λίστας για να επιστρέψετε στην αυτόματη παρακολούθηση.',
        'This parameter estimates the height%s at which the average dry updraft strength drops below 225 fpm and is expected to give better quantitative numbers for the maximum cloudless thermalling height than the BL Top height, especially when mixing results from vertical wind shear rather than thermals. (Note: the present assumptions tend to underpredict the max. thermalling height for dry conditions.) In the presence of clouds the maximum thermalling height may instead be limited by the cloud base. Being for "dry" thermals, this parameter omits the effect of "cloudsuck".': 'Αυτή η παράμετρος εκτιμά το ύψος%s στο οποίο η μέση αντοχή ξηρού ανοδικού ρεύματος πέφτει κάτω από 225 fpm και αναμένεται να δώσει καλύτερους ποσοτικούς αριθμούς για το μέγιστο ύψος θερμότητας χωρίς νέφη από το ύψος κορυφής BL, ειδικά όταν η ανάμειξη είναι αποτέλεσμα κατακόρυφης διάτμησης ανέμου και όχι θερμικών. (Σημείωση: οι παρούσες παραδοχές τείνουν να υπονομεύουν το μέγιστο ύψος θερμότητας για ξηρές συνθήκες.) Παρουσία νεφών, το μέγιστο ύψος θερμότητας μπορεί να περιοριστεί από τη βάση του νέφους. Όντας για "dry" thermals, αυτή η παράμετρος παραλείπει την επίδραση του "cloudsuck".',
        '![](resource:IDB_WARNING_TRIANGLE)\n\n!!! warning\n# Important Safety Notice\n\nBy using XCSoar, you acknowledge and accept the following:\n\n## Limitations\n\n- XCSoar is for **situational awareness only**\n- XCSoar is **not** a FLARM display\n- XCSoar is **not** aviation certified in any way\n- The artificial horizon is **not** fit for any purpose\n- Databanks (airspace, waypoints) may contain errors, be incomplete, or **not** up to date\n- NOTAM display does **not** replace proper pre-flight NOTAM briefing\n- NOTAM data may be incomplete, delayed, filtered, or unavailable\n- XCSoar is **not** guaranteed to be error free\n\n## Pilot Responsibility\n\nThe **Pilot in Command** is always responsible for the safe operation of the aircraft. Never rely solely on XCSoar for navigation or situational awareness.\n\n': '![](resource:IDB_WARNING_TRIANGLE)\n\n!!! warning\n# Σημαντική Σημείωση Ασφαλείας\n\nΧρησιμοποιώντας το XCSoar, αναγνωρίζετε και αποδέχεστε τα ακόλουθα:\n\n## Περιορισμοί\n\n- Το XCSoar είναι για το **μόνο επίγνωση της κατάστασης**\n- Το XCSoar είναι **δεν** μια οθόνη FLARM\n- Το XCSoar είναι πιστοποιημένο με οποιονδήποτε τρόπο αεροπορίας **δεν**\n- Ο τεχνητός ορίζοντας είναι **δεν** κατάλληλος για οποιονδήποτε σκοπό\n- Οι τράπεζες δεδομένων (εναέριος χώρος, σημεία διαδρομής) μπορεί να περιέχουν σφάλματα, να είναι ελλιπείς ή **δεν** ενημερωμένες\n- Η οθόνη NOTAM αντικαθιστά το **δεν** την κατάλληλη ενημέρωση NOTAM πριν από την πτήση\n- Τα δεδομένα NOTAM μπορεί να είναι ελλιπή, καθυστερημένα, φιλτραρισμένα ή μη διαθέσιμα\n- Το XCSoar είναι **δεν** εγγυημένο ότι είναι χωρίς σφάλματα\n\n## Ευθύνη πιλότου\n\nΤο **Πιλότος στην Διοίκηση** είναι πάντα υπεύθυνο για την ασφαλή λειτουργία του αεροσκάφους. Ποτέ μην βασίζεστε αποκλειστικά στο XCSoar για πλοήγηση ή επίγνωση της κατάστασης.\n\n',
        '# Getting Started\n\nTo use XCSoar effectively, configure the following:\n\n- [Restore from backup](xcsoar://dialog/backup) - Restore previous XCSoar data from a USB or SD card (optional)\n\n- [%s] [Map and data](xcsoar://config/site-files) - Download maps, waypoints, and airspace files for your region\n\n- [%s] [Aircraft polar](xcsoar://config/planes) - Set up your aircraft with the correct polar curve\n\n- [%s] [Pilot info](xcsoar://config/logger) - Enter your name and weight\n\n- [%s] [Devices](xcsoar://config/devices) - Connect your flight instruments\n\n- [%s] [WeGlide](xcsoar://config/weglide) - Upload flights automatically to WeGlide\n\n- [%s] [Thermal Information Map](xcsoar://config/weather) - Show thermal locations from thermalmap.info on the map\n\n- [%s] [Safety factors](xcsoar://config/safety) - Set arrival height, terrain clearance and polar degradation\n\n- [%s] [Terrain Display](xcsoar://config/terrain) - Choose terrain colors, shading and contour lines\n\n- [ ] [Live tracking](xcsoar://config/tracking) *(optional)* - Share your position via SkyLines or LiveTrack24\n\nThe easiest way to explore XCSoar is to [replay an existing IGC flight](xcsoar://dialog/replay).': '# Ξεκινώντας\n\nΓια να χρησιμοποιήσετε αποτελεσματικά το XCSoar, διαμορφώστε τα εξής:\n\n- [Επαναφορά από αντίγραφο ασφαλείας](xcsoar://dialog/backup) - Επαναφορά προηγούμενων δεδομένων XCSoar από κάρτα USB ή SD (προαιρετικό)\n\n- [%s] [Χάρτης και δεδομένα](xcsoar://config/site-files) - Λήψη χαρτών, σημείων διαδρομής και αρχείων εναέριου χώρου για την περιοχή σας\n\n- [%s] [Πολικό αεροσκάφος](xcsoar://config/planes) - Ρυθμίστε το αεροσκάφος σας με τη σωστή πολική καμπύλη\n\n- [%s] [Πληροφορίες πιλότου](xcsoar://config/logger) - Εισαγάγετε το όνομα και το βάρος σας\n\n- [%s] [Συσκευές](xcsoar://config/devices) - Συνδέστε τα όργανα πτήσης σας\n\n- [%s] [WeGlide](xcsoar://config/weglide) - Ανεβάστε αυτόματα πτήσεις στο WeGlide\n\n- [%s] [Θερμικός χάρτης πληροφοριών](xcsoar://config/weather) - Εμφάνιση θερμικών τοποθεσιών από το thermalmap.info στον χάρτη\n\n- [%s] [Παράγοντες ασφάλειας](xcsoar://config/safety) - Ρυθμίστε το ύψος άφιξης, την απόσταση του εδάφους και την πολική υποβάθμιση\n\n- [%s] [Εμφάνιση εδάφους](xcsoar://config/terrain) - Επιλέξτε χρώματα εδάφους, σκίαση και γραμμές περιγράμματος\n\n- [ ] [Ζωντανή παρακολούθηση](xcsoar://config/tracking) *(optional)* - Μοιραστείτε τη θέση σας μέσω SkyLines ή LiveTrack24\n\nΟ ευκολότερος τρόπος για να εξερευνήσετε το XCSoar είναι να [επαναλάβετε μια υπάρχουσα πτήση IGC](xcsoar://dialog/replay).',
        '# Gesture Navigation\n\nXCSoar supports touch gestures on the map:\n\n- ![U](resource:IDB_GESTURE_UP) **Swipe Up** (U): Zoom in\n- ![D](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DOWN) **Swipe Down** (D): Zoom out\n- ![R](resource:IDB_GESTURE_RIGHT) **Swipe Right** (R): Previous screen mode\n- ![L](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LEFT) **Swipe Left** (L): Next screen mode\n- ![UD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_UD) **Up-Down** (UD): Auto zoom\n- ![DU](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DU) **Down-Up** (DU): Menu\n- ![DR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DR) **Down-Right** (DR): Waypoint details\n- ![DL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DL) **Down-Left** (DL): Alternates\n- ![LU](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LU) **Left-Up** (LU): Recently used waypoints\n- ![RD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_RD) **Right-Down** (RD): Task manager\n- ![URD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_URD) **Up-Right-Down** (URD): Analysis\n- ![LDR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LDR) **Left-Down-Right** (LDR): Checklist\n- ![URDL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_URDL) **Up-Right-Down-Left** (URDL): Pan mode\n- ![LDRDL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LDRDL) **Left-Down-Right-Down-Left** (LDRDL): Status\n- ![ULDR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_ULDR) **Up-Left-Down-Right** (ULDR): Quick menu\n\nLong-press on the map to enter Pan mode. Tap while in Pan mode to see nearby waypoints.': '# Πλοήγηση με χειρονομίες\n\nΤο XCSoar υποστηρίζει χειρονομίες αφής στον χάρτη:\n\n- ![U](resource:IDB_GESTURE_UP) **Σύρετε προς τα επάνω** (U): Μεγέθυνση\n- ![D](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DOWN) **Σύρετε προς τα κάτω** (D): Σμίκρυνση\n- ![R](resource:IDB_GESTURE_RIGHT) **Σύρετε προς τα δεξιά** (R): Προηγούμενη λειτουργία οθόνης\n- ![L](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LEFT) **Σύρετε προς τα αριστερά** (L): Επόμενη λειτουργία οθόνης\n- ![UD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_UD) **Πάνω-Κάτω** (UD): Αυτόματο ζουμ\n- ![DU](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DU) **Κάτω-Πάνω** (DU): Μενού\n- ![DR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DR) **Ευθύς** (DR): Λεπτομέρειες σημείου διαδρομής\n- ![DL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DL) **Κάτω-Αριστερά** (DL): Αναπληρωματικοί\n- ![LU](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LU) **Αριστερά Επάνω** (LU): Σημεία διαδρομής που χρησιμοποιήθηκαν πρόσφατα\n- ![RD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_RD) **Δεξιά-Κάτω** (RD): Task manager\n- ![URD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_URD) **Πάνω-Δεξιά-Κάτω** (URD): Ανάλυση\n- ![LDR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LDR) **Αριστερά-Κάτω-Δεξιά** (LDR): Λίστα ελέγχου\n- ![URDL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_URDL) **Πάνω-Δεξιά-Κάτω-Αριστερά** (URDL): Λειτουργία πανοραμικής λήψης\n- ![LDRDL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LDRDL) **Αριστερά-Κάτω-Δεξιά-Κάτω-Αριστερά** (LDRDL): Κατάσταση\n- ![ULDR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_ULDR) **Πάνω-Αριστερά-Κάτω-Δεξιά** (ULDR): Γρήγορο μενού\n\nΠατήστε παρατεταμένα στο χάρτη για να μεταβείτε στη λειτουργία Pan. Πατήστε ενώ βρίσκεστε σε λειτουργία Pan για να δείτε κοντινά σημεία.',
    },
    "es": {
        'Size of waypoint symbols on the map as a percentage of the built-in artwork (list dialogs keep a fixed row icon size).': 'Tamaño de los símbolos de waypoint en el mapa como porcentaje de la ilustración incorporada (los cuadros de diálogo de lista mantienen un tamaño de icono de fila fijo).',
        'Home waypoint name, arrival altitude difference relative to the safety arrival height, and distance. Click to change the home waypoint.': 'Nombre del punto de referencia de origen, diferencia de altitud de llegada en relación con la altura de llegada de seguridad y distancia. Haga clic para cambiar el punto de ruta de inicio.',
        'Current QNH pressure setting used for barometric altitude calculation. Tap the infobox to open the setup panel and adjust QNH manually.': 'Configuración de presión QNH actual utilizada para el cálculo de la altitud barométrica. Toque el cuadro de información para abrir el panel de configuración y ajustar QNH manualmente.',
        'This page shows WiFi status when NetworkManager or ConnMan is on D-Bus (e.g. Linux with Wayland or KMS). Open WiFi list to scan and connect when a service is available.': 'Esta página muestra el estado de WiFi cuando NetworkManager o ConnMan está en D-Bus (por ejemplo, Linux con Wayland o KMS). Abra la lista de WiFi para escanear y conectarse cuando haya un servicio disponible.',
        'The terrain can be shaded among slopes to indicate either wind direction, sun position, a geographically fixed shading from North-West, or a screen-relative fixed shading from top left.': 'El terreno se puede sombrear entre pendientes para indicar la dirección del viento, la posición del sol, un sombreado fijo geográficamente desde el noroeste o un sombreado fijo relativo a la pantalla desde la parte superior izquierda.',
        "Synchronize the glide polar between XCSoar and the device (LXNAV varios). 'Receive' adopts the polar from the device (e.g. for club gliders). 'Send' pushes XCSoar's polar to the device.": "Sincroniza el planeo polar entre XCSoar y el dispositivo (LXNAV varios). 'Recibir' adopta la polaridad del dispositivo (por ejemplo, para planeadores de club). 'Enviar' empuja el polar de XCSoar al dispositivo.",
        'List of active airspace files. Use the Add and Remove buttons to activate or deactivate airspace files respectively. Supported file types are: Openair (.openair /.txt /.air), and Tim Newport-Pearce (.sua).': 'Lista de archivos de espacio aéreo activos. Utilice los botones Agregar y Quitar para activar o desactivar archivos de espacio aéreo respectivamente. Los tipos de archivos admitidos son: Openair (.openair /.txt /.air) y Tim Newport-Pearce (.sua).',
        'Signed countdown until the start gate opens or closes (now). Value colour and secondary line reflect gate state at the current time: Waiting (blue), Open (green), Closed (red). PEV window overrides task gate when set.': 'Cuenta atrás firmada hasta que se abra o cierre la puerta de salida (ahora). El color del valor y la línea secundaria reflejan el estado de la puerta en el momento actual: en espera (azul), abierta (verde), cerrada (rojo). La ventana PEV anula la puerta de tareas cuando se configura.',
        'Tells XCSoar to send its current GPS position to the device as $GPGGA and $GPRMC sentences. Turn off when another GPS source is already feeding the device on the same line. Changes take effect after reconnecting the device.': 'Le dice a XCSoar que envíe su posición GPS actual al dispositivo como oraciones $GPGGA y $GPRMC. Apague cuando otra fuente de GPS ya esté alimentando el dispositivo en la misma línea. Los cambios entran en vigor después de volver a conectar el dispositivo.',
        'Logger pressure altitude when the device provides it (igc_pressure_altitude), otherwise ISA pressure altitude only (1013.25 hPa; not QNH-corrected). Does not show barometric AMSL or GPS height — use other InfoBoxes for navigation.': 'Registra la altitud de presión cuando el dispositivo la proporciona (igc_pression_altitude); de lo contrario, solo la altitud de presión ISA (1013,25 hPa; no corregida por QNH). No muestra AMSL barométrico ni la altura GPS; utilice otros cuadros de información para la navegación.',
        'Same gate as Start open. Main value is estimated time to reach the start line (MacCready leg when available, else distance / ground speed). Value colour and secondary line reflect gate state at that ETA: Too early (blue), Can start (green), Too late (red).': 'La misma puerta que Start abierta. El valor principal es el tiempo estimado para llegar a la línea de salida (tramo MacCready cuando esté disponible; en caso contrario, distancia/velocidad sobre el terreno). El color del valor y la línea secundaria reflejan el estado de la puerta en esa ETA: Demasiado temprano (azul), Puede comenzar (verde), Demasiado tarde (rojo).',
        'Active waypoint: shows the next task waypoint when an ordered task is loaded, otherwise the Goto waypoint. Displays the waypoint name, arrival altitude difference relative to the safety arrival height, and distance. Click to choose a different waypoint (a task waypoint to skip to that leg, or any waypoint to set as Goto when no task is loaded).': 'Punto de ruta activo: muestra el siguiente punto de ruta de la tarea cuando se carga una tarea ordenada; de lo contrario, el punto de ruta Ir a. Muestra el nombre del punto de ruta, la diferencia de altitud de llegada en relación con la altura de llegada segura y la distancia. Haga clic para elegir un punto de ruta diferente (un punto de ruta de tarea para saltar a ese tramo, o cualquier punto de ruta para configurar como Ir a cuando no hay ninguna tarea cargada).',
        'FFVP Federal Cup (NetCoupe) on WeGlide. The scored path has at most three turnpoints between start and finish and at least 25 km total. Points are proportional to credited distance, 100 divided by the glider handicap (DAeC-style index), and a success factor of 1.0 for a free flight or 1.2 for a task declared electronically before takeoff. XCSoar live scoring uses a success factor of 1.0 only, not the 1.2 multiplier for declared tasks.': 'Copa Federal FFVP (NetCoupe) en WeGlide. El camino puntuado tiene como máximo tres puntos de giro entre la salida y la meta y al menos 25 km en total. Los puntos son proporcionales a la distancia acreditada, 100 divididos por el handicap del planeador (índice estilo DAeC) y un factor de éxito de 1,0 para un vuelo libre o 1,2 para una tarea declarada electrónicamente antes del despegue. La puntuación en vivo de XCSoar utiliza un factor de éxito de 1,0 únicamente, no el multiplicador de 1,2 para las tareas declaradas.',
        'Previous waypoint: when an ordered task is loaded, automatically tracks the task waypoint before the active leg (the start waypoint when on the first leg). Displays the waypoint name, arrival altitude difference relative to the safety arrival height, and distance. Click to choose a different waypoint to display (task waypoints when a task is loaded, otherwise the full waypoint list); selection is informational only and never advances the task or sets a Goto. With a task loaded, choose "Resume auto tracking" at the top of the list to revert to automatic tracking.': 'Punto de ruta anterior: cuando se carga una tarea ordenada, rastrea automáticamente el punto de ruta de la tarea antes del tramo activo (el punto de ruta inicial cuando está en el primer tramo). Muestra el nombre del punto de ruta, la diferencia de altitud de llegada en relación con la altura de llegada segura y la distancia. Haga clic para elegir un punto de ruta diferente para mostrar (puntos de ruta de la tarea cuando se carga una tarea; de lo contrario, la lista completa de puntos de ruta); La selección es sólo informativa y nunca avanza la tarea ni establece un Ir a. Con una tarea cargada, elija "Reanudar seguimiento automático" en la parte superior de la lista para volver al seguimiento automático.',
        'This parameter estimates the height%s at which the average dry updraft strength drops below 225 fpm and is expected to give better quantitative numbers for the maximum cloudless thermalling height than the BL Top height, especially when mixing results from vertical wind shear rather than thermals. (Note: the present assumptions tend to underpredict the max. thermalling height for dry conditions.) In the presence of clouds the maximum thermalling height may instead be limited by the cloud base. Being for "dry" thermals, this parameter omits the effect of "cloudsuck".': 'Este parámetro estima la altura %s a la cual la fuerza promedio de la corriente ascendente seca cae por debajo de 225 fpm y se espera que proporcione mejores números cuantitativos para la altura máxima de térmica sin nubes que la altura BL Top, especialmente cuando se mezclan resultados de cizalladura vertical del viento en lugar de térmicas. (Nota: los supuestos actuales tienden a subestimar la altura máxima de térmica para condiciones secas.) En presencia de nubes, la altura máxima de térmica puede estar limitada por la base de la nube. Al ser para térmicas "secas", este parámetro omite el efecto de "chupa de nubes".',
        '![](resource:IDB_WARNING_TRIANGLE)\n\n!!! warning\n# Important Safety Notice\n\nBy using XCSoar, you acknowledge and accept the following:\n\n## Limitations\n\n- XCSoar is for **situational awareness only**\n- XCSoar is **not** a FLARM display\n- XCSoar is **not** aviation certified in any way\n- The artificial horizon is **not** fit for any purpose\n- Databanks (airspace, waypoints) may contain errors, be incomplete, or **not** up to date\n- NOTAM display does **not** replace proper pre-flight NOTAM briefing\n- NOTAM data may be incomplete, delayed, filtered, or unavailable\n- XCSoar is **not** guaranteed to be error free\n\n## Pilot Responsibility\n\nThe **Pilot in Command** is always responsible for the safe operation of the aircraft. Never rely solely on XCSoar for navigation or situational awareness.\n\n': '![](resource:IDB_WARNING_TRIANGLE)\n\n!!! warning\n# Aviso de seguridad importante\n\nAl utilizar XCSoar, usted reconoce y acepta lo siguiente:\n\n## Limitaciones\n\n- XCSoar es para **Sólo conciencia situacional**\n- XCSoar es **no** una pantalla FLARM\n- XCSoar tiene certificación de aviación **no** de cualquier forma\n- El horizonte artificial es **no** apto para cualquier propósito.\n- Los bancos de datos (espacio aéreo, waypoints) pueden contener errores, estar incompletos o estar actualizados.\n- La visualización de NOTAM reemplaza **no** la información informativa NOTAM previa al vuelo adecuada\n- Los datos NOTAM pueden estar incompletos, retrasados, filtrados o no disponibles\n- XCSoar tiene la garantía **no** de estar libre de errores\n\n## Responsabilidad del piloto\n\nEl **Piloto al mando** siempre es responsable de la operación segura de la aeronave. Nunca confíe únicamente en XCSoar para la navegación o el conocimiento de la situación.\n\n',
        '# Getting Started\n\nTo use XCSoar effectively, configure the following:\n\n- [Restore from backup](xcsoar://dialog/backup) - Restore previous XCSoar data from a USB or SD card (optional)\n\n- [%s] [Map and data](xcsoar://config/site-files) - Download maps, waypoints, and airspace files for your region\n\n- [%s] [Aircraft polar](xcsoar://config/planes) - Set up your aircraft with the correct polar curve\n\n- [%s] [Pilot info](xcsoar://config/logger) - Enter your name and weight\n\n- [%s] [Devices](xcsoar://config/devices) - Connect your flight instruments\n\n- [%s] [WeGlide](xcsoar://config/weglide) - Upload flights automatically to WeGlide\n\n- [%s] [Thermal Information Map](xcsoar://config/weather) - Show thermal locations from thermalmap.info on the map\n\n- [%s] [Safety factors](xcsoar://config/safety) - Set arrival height, terrain clearance and polar degradation\n\n- [%s] [Terrain Display](xcsoar://config/terrain) - Choose terrain colors, shading and contour lines\n\n- [ ] [Live tracking](xcsoar://config/tracking) *(optional)* - Share your position via SkyLines or LiveTrack24\n\nThe easiest way to explore XCSoar is to [replay an existing IGC flight](xcsoar://dialog/replay).': '# Empezando\n\nPara utilizar XCSoar de forma eficaz, configure lo siguiente:\n\n- [Restaurar desde copia de seguridad](xcsoar://dialog/backup) - Restaurar datos anteriores de XCSoar desde una tarjeta USB o SD (opcional)\n\n- [%s] [Mapa y datos](xcsoar://config/site-files) - Descargue mapas, puntos de ruta y archivos de espacio aéreo para su región\n\n- [%s] [Aviones polares](xcsoar://config/planes) - Configura tu avión con la curva polar correcta\n\n- [%s] [Información piloto](xcsoar://config/logger) - Introduce tu nombre y peso\n\n- [%s] [Dispositivos](xcsoar://config/devices) - Conecte sus instrumentos de vuelo\n\n- [%s] [NosotrosGlide](xcsoar://config/weglide) - Sube vuelos automáticamente a WeGlide\n\n- [%s] [Mapa de información térmica](xcsoar://config/weather) - Mostrar ubicaciones térmicas de Thermalmap.info en el mapa\n\n- [%s] [Factores de seguridad](xcsoar://config/safety) - Establecer la altura de llegada, el espacio libre del terreno y la degradación polar.\n\n- [%s] [Visualización del terreno](xcsoar://config/terrain) - Elija colores del terreno, sombreado y líneas de contorno.\n\n- [ ] [Seguimiento en vivo](xcsoar://config/tracking) *(optional)* - Comparte tu posición a través de SkyLines o LiveTrack24\n\nLa forma más sencilla de explorar XCSoar es [reproducir un vuelo IGC existente](xcsoar://dialog/replay).',
        '# Gesture Navigation\n\nXCSoar supports touch gestures on the map:\n\n- ![U](resource:IDB_GESTURE_UP) **Swipe Up** (U): Zoom in\n- ![D](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DOWN) **Swipe Down** (D): Zoom out\n- ![R](resource:IDB_GESTURE_RIGHT) **Swipe Right** (R): Previous screen mode\n- ![L](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LEFT) **Swipe Left** (L): Next screen mode\n- ![UD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_UD) **Up-Down** (UD): Auto zoom\n- ![DU](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DU) **Down-Up** (DU): Menu\n- ![DR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DR) **Down-Right** (DR): Waypoint details\n- ![DL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DL) **Down-Left** (DL): Alternates\n- ![LU](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LU) **Left-Up** (LU): Recently used waypoints\n- ![RD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_RD) **Right-Down** (RD): Task manager\n- ![URD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_URD) **Up-Right-Down** (URD): Analysis\n- ![LDR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LDR) **Left-Down-Right** (LDR): Checklist\n- ![URDL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_URDL) **Up-Right-Down-Left** (URDL): Pan mode\n- ![LDRDL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LDRDL) **Left-Down-Right-Down-Left** (LDRDL): Status\n- ![ULDR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_ULDR) **Up-Left-Down-Right** (ULDR): Quick menu\n\nLong-press on the map to enter Pan mode. Tap while in Pan mode to see nearby waypoints.': '# Navegación por gestos\n\nXCSoar admite gestos táctiles en el mapa:\n\n- ![U](resource:IDB_GESTURE_UP) **Deslizar hacia arriba** (U): Dar un golpe de zoom\n- ![D](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DOWN) **Deslizar hacia abajo** (D): alejar\n- ![R](resource:IDB_GESTURE_RIGHT) **Deslizar hacia la derecha** (R): Modo de pantalla anterior\n- ![L](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LEFT) **Deslizar hacia la izquierda** (L): Modo de pantalla siguiente\n- ![UD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_UD) **arriba-abajo** (UD): Zoom automático\n- ![DU](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DU) **Abajo-arriba** (DU): Menú\n- ![DR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DR) **Completamente** (DR): Detalles del punto de referencia\n- ![DL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DL) **Abajo-izquierda** (DL): Suplentes\n- ![LU](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LU) **Izquierda arriba** (LU): Puntos de referencia utilizados recientemente\n- ![RD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_RD) **Consumado** (RD): administrador de tareas\n- ![URD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_URD) **Arriba-Derecha-Abajo** (URD): Análisis\n- ![LDR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LDR) **Izquierda-abajo-derecha** (LDR): Lista de verificación\n- ![URDL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_URDL) **Arriba-Derecha-Abajo-Izquierda** (URDL): Modo panorámico\n- ![LDRDL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LDRDL) **Izquierda-Abajo-Derecha-Abajo-Izquierda** (LDRDL): Estado\n- ![ULDR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_ULDR) **Arriba-Izquierda-Abajo-Derecha** (ULDR): Menú rápido\n\nMantenga presionado el mapa para ingresar al modo Pan. Toque mientras está en modo Panorámico para ver puntos de ruta cercanos.',
    },
    "fi": {
        'Size of waypoint symbols on the map as a percentage of the built-in artwork (list dialogs keep a fixed row icon size).': 'Reittipistesymbolien koko kartalla prosentteina sisäänrakennetusta kuvamateriaalista (luetteloikkunat pitävät kiinteän rivikuvakkeen koon).',
        'Home waypoint name, arrival altitude difference relative to the safety arrival height, and distance. Click to change the home waypoint.': 'Kotireittipisteen nimi, saapumiskorkeusero suhteessa turvalliseen saapumiskorkeuteen ja etäisyys. Napsauta muuttaaksesi kotireittipistettä.',
        'Current QNH pressure setting used for barometric altitude calculation. Tap the infobox to open the setup panel and adjust QNH manually.': 'Nykyinen QNH-paineasetus, jota käytetään barometrisen korkeuden laskennassa. Napauta tietolaatikkoa avataksesi asetuspaneelin ja säädäksesi QNH:ta manuaalisesti.',
        'This page shows WiFi status when NetworkManager or ConnMan is on D-Bus (e.g. Linux with Wayland or KMS). Open WiFi list to scan and connect when a service is available.': 'Tämä sivu näyttää WiFi-tilan, kun NetworkManager tai ConnMan on D-Busissa (esim. Linux ja Wayland tai KMS). Avaa WiFi-luettelo skannataksesi ja muodostaaksesi yhteyden, kun palvelu on saatavilla.',
        'The terrain can be shaded among slopes to indicate either wind direction, sun position, a geographically fixed shading from North-West, or a screen-relative fixed shading from top left.': 'Maasto voidaan varjostaa rinteiden kesken osoittamaan joko tuulen suuntaa, auringon sijaintia, maantieteellisesti kiinteää varjostusta luoteesta tai näytön suhteen kiinteää varjostusta ylhäältä vasemmalta.',
        "Synchronize the glide polar between XCSoar and the device (LXNAV varios). 'Receive' adopts the polar from the device (e.g. for club gliders). 'Send' pushes XCSoar's polar to the device.": "Synkronoi liukunapa XCSoarin ja laitteen välillä (LXNAV varios). 'Receive' ottaa napaisuuden laitteesta (esim. mailapurjelentokoneissa). 'Lähetä' työntää XCSoarin polaarin laitteeseen.",
        'List of active airspace files. Use the Add and Remove buttons to activate or deactivate airspace files respectively. Supported file types are: Openair (.openair /.txt /.air), and Tim Newport-Pearce (.sua).': 'Luettelo aktiivisista ilmatilan tiedostoista. Käytä Lisää- ja Poista-painikkeita aktivoidaksesi tai deaktivoidaksesi vastaavasti ilmatilatiedostoja. Tuetut tiedostotyypit ovat: Openair (.openair /.txt /.air) ja Tim Newport-Pearce (.sua).',
        'Signed countdown until the start gate opens or closes (now). Value colour and secondary line reflect gate state at the current time: Waiting (blue), Open (green), Closed (red). PEV window overrides task gate when set.': 'Allekirjoitettu lähtölaskenta, kunnes lähtöportti avautuu tai sulkeutuu (nyt). Arvon väri ja toissijainen rivi heijastavat portin tilaa tällä hetkellä: Odottaa (sininen), Avoin (vihreä), Kiinni (punainen). PEV-ikkuna ohittaa tehtäväportin, kun se on asetettu.',
        'Tells XCSoar to send its current GPS position to the device as $GPGGA and $GPRMC sentences. Turn off when another GPS source is already feeding the device on the same line. Changes take effect after reconnecting the device.': 'Käskee XCSoaria lähettämään nykyisen GPS-sijaintinsa laitteeseen $GPGGA- ja $GPRMC-lauseina. Sammuta, kun toinen GPS-lähde syöttää jo laitetta samalla linjalla. Muutokset tulevat voimaan, kun laite on yhdistetty uudelleen.',
        'Logger pressure altitude when the device provides it (igc_pressure_altitude), otherwise ISA pressure altitude only (1013.25 hPa; not QNH-corrected). Does not show barometric AMSL or GPS height — use other InfoBoxes for navigation.': 'Kirjaa painekorkeus, kun laite antaa sen (igc_pressure_altitude), muuten vain ISA-painekorkeus (1013,25 hPa; ei QNH-korjattu). Ei näytä barometrista AMSL- tai GPS-korkeutta – käytä muita tietolaatikoita navigointiin.',
        'Same gate as Start open. Main value is estimated time to reach the start line (MacCready leg when available, else distance / ground speed). Value colour and secondary line reflect gate state at that ETA: Too early (blue), Can start (green), Too late (red).': 'Sama portti kuin Start auki. Pääarvo on arvioitu aika lähtöviivalle saavuttamiseen (MacCready-osuus, jos saatavilla, muuten matka / maanopeus). Arvon väri ja toissijainen viiva heijastavat portin tilaa kyseisessä saapumisajankohdassa: Liian aikaisin (sininen), Voi alkaa (vihreä), Liian myöhään (punainen).',
        'Active waypoint: shows the next task waypoint when an ordered task is loaded, otherwise the Goto waypoint. Displays the waypoint name, arrival altitude difference relative to the safety arrival height, and distance. Click to choose a different waypoint (a task waypoint to skip to that leg, or any waypoint to set as Goto when no task is loaded).': 'Aktiivinen reittipiste: näyttää seuraavan tehtävän reittipisteen, kun tilattu tehtävä ladataan, muussa tapauksessa Goto-reittipiste. Näyttää reittipisteen nimen, saapumiskorkeuseron suhteessa turvatulokorkeuteen ja etäisyyden. Napsauta valitaksesi eri reittipisteen (tehtävän reittipisteen, jolla voit hypätä kyseiselle osuudelle, tai mikä tahansa reittipiste, joka asetetaan Gotoksi, kun tehtävää ei ole ladattu).',
        'FFVP Federal Cup (NetCoupe) on WeGlide. The scored path has at most three turnpoints between start and finish and at least 25 km total. Points are proportional to credited distance, 100 divided by the glider handicap (DAeC-style index), and a success factor of 1.0 for a free flight or 1.2 for a task declared electronically before takeoff. XCSoar live scoring uses a success factor of 1.0 only, not the 1.2 multiplier for declared tasks.': 'FFVP Federal Cup (NetCoupe) WeGlidessa. Arvostetulla polulla on enintään kolme käännekohtaa lähdön ja maalin välillä ja yhteensä vähintään 25 km. Pisteet ovat verrannollisia hyvitettyyn matkaan, 100 jaettuna purjelentokoneen tasoituksella (DAeC-tyylinen indeksi) ja onnistumiskerroin 1,0 vapaalle lennolle tai 1,2 tehtävästä, joka on ilmoitettu sähköisesti ennen lentoonlähtöä. XCSoarin live-pisteytys käyttää ilmoitettujen tehtävien onnistumiskerrointa vain 1,0, ei kerrointa 1,2.',
        'Previous waypoint: when an ordered task is loaded, automatically tracks the task waypoint before the active leg (the start waypoint when on the first leg). Displays the waypoint name, arrival altitude difference relative to the safety arrival height, and distance. Click to choose a different waypoint to display (task waypoints when a task is loaded, otherwise the full waypoint list); selection is informational only and never advances the task or sets a Goto. With a task loaded, choose "Resume auto tracking" at the top of the list to revert to automatic tracking.': 'Edellinen reittipiste: kun tilattu tehtävä ladataan, seuraa automaattisesti tehtävän reittipistettä ennen aktiivista osuutta (aloitusreittipiste ensimmäisellä osuudella). Näyttää reittipisteen nimen, saapumiskorkeuseron suhteessa turvatulokorkeuteen ja etäisyyden. Napsauta valitaksesi eri reittipisteen näytettäväksi (tehtävän reittipisteet, kun tehtävä on ladattu, muuten koko reittipisteluettelo); valinta on vain informatiivinen, eikä se koskaan edistä tehtävää tai aseta Goto-asetusta. Kun tehtävä on ladattu, palaa automaattiseen seurantaan valitsemalla luettelon yläreunasta "Jatka automaattista seurantaa".',
        'This parameter estimates the height%s at which the average dry updraft strength drops below 225 fpm and is expected to give better quantitative numbers for the maximum cloudless thermalling height than the BL Top height, especially when mixing results from vertical wind shear rather than thermals. (Note: the present assumptions tend to underpredict the max. thermalling height for dry conditions.) In the presence of clouds the maximum thermalling height may instead be limited by the cloud base. Being for "dry" thermals, this parameter omits the effect of "cloudsuck".': 'Tämä parametri arvioi korkeuden%s, jossa keskimääräinen kuivan ylävirran voimakkuus laskee alle 225 fpm, ja sen odotetaan antavan paremmat kvantitatiiviset luvut maksimaaliselle pilvettömälle lämpökorkeudelle kuin BL-yläkorkeudelle, erityisesti kun sekoitustulokset ovat peräisin pystysuuntaisesta tuulenleikkauksesta termien sijaan. (Huomaa: nykyiset oletukset yleensä aliarvioivat kuivien olosuhteiden maksimilämpökorkeuden.) Pilvien läsnä ollessa pilvipohja voi sen sijaan rajoittaa maksimilämpenemiskorkeutta. Koska kyseessä on "kuiva" lämpö, \u200b\u200btämä parametri jättää huomiotta "pilviimun" vaikutuksen.',
        '![](resource:IDB_WARNING_TRIANGLE)\n\n!!! warning\n# Important Safety Notice\n\nBy using XCSoar, you acknowledge and accept the following:\n\n## Limitations\n\n- XCSoar is for **situational awareness only**\n- XCSoar is **not** a FLARM display\n- XCSoar is **not** aviation certified in any way\n- The artificial horizon is **not** fit for any purpose\n- Databanks (airspace, waypoints) may contain errors, be incomplete, or **not** up to date\n- NOTAM display does **not** replace proper pre-flight NOTAM briefing\n- NOTAM data may be incomplete, delayed, filtered, or unavailable\n- XCSoar is **not** guaranteed to be error free\n\n## Pilot Responsibility\n\nThe **Pilot in Command** is always responsible for the safe operation of the aircraft. Never rely solely on XCSoar for navigation or situational awareness.\n\n': '![](resource:IDB_WARNING_TRIANGLE)\n\n!!! warning\n# Tärkeä turvallisuushuomautus\n\nKäyttämällä XCSoaria hyväksyt seuraavat asiat:\n\n## Rajoitukset\n\n- XCSoar on **vain tilannetietoisuus**ille\n- XCSoar on **ei** FLARM-näyttö\n- XCSoar on **ei**-ilmailusertifioitu millään tavalla\n- Keinotekoinen horisontti sopii **ei** mihin tahansa tarkoitukseen\n- Tietopankit (ilmatila, reittipisteet) voivat sisältää virheitä, olla epätäydellisiä tai **ei** ajan tasalla\n- NOTAM-näyttö **ei** korvaa asianmukaisen lentoa edeltävän NOTAM-tiedotuksen\n- NOTAM-tiedot voivat olla epätäydellisiä, viivästyneitä, suodatettuja tai poissa käytöstä\n- XCSoar on **ei** taatusti virheetön\n\n## Lentäjän vastuu\n\n**Pilotti komennossa** on aina vastuussa lentokoneen turvallisesta käytöstä. Älä koskaan luota pelkästään XCSoariin navigoinnissa tai tilannetietoisuudessa.\n\n',
        '# Getting Started\n\nTo use XCSoar effectively, configure the following:\n\n- [Restore from backup](xcsoar://dialog/backup) - Restore previous XCSoar data from a USB or SD card (optional)\n\n- [%s] [Map and data](xcsoar://config/site-files) - Download maps, waypoints, and airspace files for your region\n\n- [%s] [Aircraft polar](xcsoar://config/planes) - Set up your aircraft with the correct polar curve\n\n- [%s] [Pilot info](xcsoar://config/logger) - Enter your name and weight\n\n- [%s] [Devices](xcsoar://config/devices) - Connect your flight instruments\n\n- [%s] [WeGlide](xcsoar://config/weglide) - Upload flights automatically to WeGlide\n\n- [%s] [Thermal Information Map](xcsoar://config/weather) - Show thermal locations from thermalmap.info on the map\n\n- [%s] [Safety factors](xcsoar://config/safety) - Set arrival height, terrain clearance and polar degradation\n\n- [%s] [Terrain Display](xcsoar://config/terrain) - Choose terrain colors, shading and contour lines\n\n- [ ] [Live tracking](xcsoar://config/tracking) *(optional)* - Share your position via SkyLines or LiveTrack24\n\nThe easiest way to explore XCSoar is to [replay an existing IGC flight](xcsoar://dialog/replay).': '# Aloitus\n\nKäytä XCSoaria tehokkaasti määrittämällä seuraavat:\n\n- [Palauta varmuuskopiosta](xcsoar://dialog/backup) - Palauta aiemmat XCSoar-tiedot USB- tai SD-kortilta (valinnainen)\n\n- [%s] [Kartta ja tiedot](xcsoar://config/site-files) - Lataa alueesi karttoja, reittipisteitä ja ilmatilatiedostoja\n\n- [%s] [Lentokone polaarinen](xcsoar://config/planes) - Aseta lentokoneesi oikeaan napakäyrään\n\n- [%s] [Lentäjän tiedot](xcsoar://config/logger) - Kirjoita nimesi ja painosi\n\n- [%s] [Laitteet](xcsoar://config/devices) - Yhdistä lentomittarisi\n\n- [%s] [WeGlide](xcsoar://config/weglide) - Lataa lennot automaattisesti WeGlideen\n\n- [%s] [Lämpötietokartta](xcsoar://config/weather) - Näytä lämpöpaikat kartalla osoitteesta thermomap.info\n\n- [%s] [Turvallisuustekijät](xcsoar://config/safety) - Aseta saapumiskorkeus, maastovara ja napatilan heikkeneminen\n\n- [%s] [Maaston näyttö](xcsoar://config/terrain) - Valitse maaston värit, varjostukset ja ääriviivat\n\n- [ ] [Live-seuranta](xcsoar://config/tracking) *(optional)* - Jaa sijaintisi SkyLinesin tai LiveTrack24:n kautta\n\nHelpoin tapa tutustua XCSoariin on [toista olemassa oleva IGC-lento](xcsoar://dialog/replay).',
        '# Gesture Navigation\n\nXCSoar supports touch gestures on the map:\n\n- ![U](resource:IDB_GESTURE_UP) **Swipe Up** (U): Zoom in\n- ![D](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DOWN) **Swipe Down** (D): Zoom out\n- ![R](resource:IDB_GESTURE_RIGHT) **Swipe Right** (R): Previous screen mode\n- ![L](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LEFT) **Swipe Left** (L): Next screen mode\n- ![UD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_UD) **Up-Down** (UD): Auto zoom\n- ![DU](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DU) **Down-Up** (DU): Menu\n- ![DR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DR) **Down-Right** (DR): Waypoint details\n- ![DL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DL) **Down-Left** (DL): Alternates\n- ![LU](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LU) **Left-Up** (LU): Recently used waypoints\n- ![RD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_RD) **Right-Down** (RD): Task manager\n- ![URD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_URD) **Up-Right-Down** (URD): Analysis\n- ![LDR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LDR) **Left-Down-Right** (LDR): Checklist\n- ![URDL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_URDL) **Up-Right-Down-Left** (URDL): Pan mode\n- ![LDRDL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LDRDL) **Left-Down-Right-Down-Left** (LDRDL): Status\n- ![ULDR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_ULDR) **Up-Left-Down-Right** (ULDR): Quick menu\n\nLong-press on the map to enter Pan mode. Tap while in Pan mode to see nearby waypoints.': '# Elenavigointi\n\nXCSoar tukee kosketuseleitä kartalla:\n\n- ![U](resource:IDB_GESTURE_UP) **Pyyhkäise ylös** (U): Lähennä\n- ![D](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DOWN) **Pyyhkäise alas** (D): Loitonna\n- ![R](resource:IDB_GESTURE_RIGHT) **Pyyhkäise oikealle** (R): Edellinen näyttötila\n- ![L](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LEFT) **Pyyhkäise vasemmalle** (L): Seuraavan näytön tila\n- ![UD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_UD) **Ylös-alas** (UD): Automaattinen zoomaus\n- ![DU](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DU) **Alas-ylös** (DU): Valikko\n- ![DR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DR) **Suorastaan** (DR): Reittipisteen tiedot\n- ![DL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DL) **Alas-vasen** (DL): Vaihtoehtoiset\n- ![LU](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LU) **Vasen ylös** (LU): Äskettäin käytetyt reittipisteet\n- ![RD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_RD) **Oikea alas** (RD): Tehtävienhallinta\n- ![URD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_URD) **Ylös-oikea-alas** (URD): Analyysi\n- ![LDR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LDR) **Vasen-Alas-Oikea** (LDR): Tarkistuslista\n- ![URDL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_URDL) **Ylös-oikea-alas-vasen** (URDL): Pan-tila\n- ![LDRDL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LDRDL) **Vasen-Alas-Oikea-Alas-Vasen** (LDRDL): Status\n- ![ULDR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_ULDR) **Ylös-vasen-alas-oikea** (ULDR): Pikavalikko\n\nSiirry Pan-tilaan painamalla karttaa pitkään. Napauta Pan-tilassa nähdäksesi lähellä olevat reittipisteet.',
    },
    "fr": {
        'Size of waypoint symbols on the map as a percentage of the built-in artwork (list dialogs keep a fixed row icon size).': "Taille des symboles de points de cheminement sur la carte en pourcentage de l'illustration intégrée (les boîtes de dialogue de liste conservent une taille d'icône de ligne fixe).",
        'Home waypoint name, arrival altitude difference relative to the safety arrival height, and distance. Click to change the home waypoint.': "Nom du point de cheminement d'origine, différence d'altitude d'arrivée par rapport à la hauteur d'arrivée de sécurité et distance. Cliquez pour modifier le waypoint d'origine.",
        'Current QNH pressure setting used for barometric altitude calculation. Tap the infobox to open the setup panel and adjust QNH manually.': "Réglage actuel de la pression QNH utilisé pour le calcul de l’altitude barométrique. Appuyez sur la boîte d'informations pour ouvrir le panneau de configuration et régler le QNH manuellement.",
        'This page shows WiFi status when NetworkManager or ConnMan is on D-Bus (e.g. Linux with Wayland or KMS). Open WiFi list to scan and connect when a service is available.': "Cette page affiche l'état du WiFi lorsque NetworkManager ou ConnMan est sur D-Bus (par exemple Linux avec Wayland ou KMS). Ouvrez la liste WiFi pour scanner et vous connecter lorsqu'un service est disponible.",
        'The terrain can be shaded among slopes to indicate either wind direction, sun position, a geographically fixed shading from North-West, or a screen-relative fixed shading from top left.': "Le terrain peut être ombré entre les pentes pour indiquer soit la direction du vent, la position du soleil, un ombrage géographiquement fixe du nord-ouest ou un ombrage fixe relatif à l'écran depuis le coin supérieur gauche.",
        "Synchronize the glide polar between XCSoar and the device (LXNAV varios). 'Receive' adopts the polar from the device (e.g. for club gliders). 'Send' pushes XCSoar's polar to the device.": "Synchronisez la polaire de glisse entre XCSoar et l'appareil (varios LXNAV). «\xa0Recevoir\xa0» reprend la polaire de l'appareil (par exemple pour les planeurs de club). «\xa0Envoyer\xa0» pousse la polaire de XCSoar vers l'appareil.",
        'List of active airspace files. Use the Add and Remove buttons to activate or deactivate airspace files respectively. Supported file types are: Openair (.openair /.txt /.air), and Tim Newport-Pearce (.sua).': "Liste des fichiers d'espace aérien actifs. Utilisez les boutons Ajouter et Supprimer pour activer ou désactiver respectivement les fichiers d'espace aérien. Les types de fichiers pris en charge sont\xa0: Openair (.openair /.txt /.air) et Tim Newport-Pearce (.sua).",
        'Signed countdown until the start gate opens or closes (now). Value colour and secondary line reflect gate state at the current time: Waiting (blue), Open (green), Closed (red). PEV window overrides task gate when set.': "Compte à rebours signé jusqu'à l'ouverture ou la fermeture de la porte de départ (maintenant). La couleur de la valeur et la ligne secondaire reflètent l'état de la porte à l'heure actuelle\xa0: en attente (bleu), ouverte (vert), fermée (rouge). La fenêtre PEV remplace la porte de tâche lorsqu'elle est définie.",
        'Tells XCSoar to send its current GPS position to the device as $GPGGA and $GPRMC sentences. Turn off when another GPS source is already feeding the device on the same line. Changes take effect after reconnecting the device.': "Indique à XCSoar d'envoyer sa position GPS actuelle à l'appareil sous forme de phrases $GPGGA et $GPRMC. Éteignez-le lorsqu'une autre source GPS alimente déjà l'appareil sur la même ligne. Les modifications prennent effet après la reconnexion de l'appareil.",
        'Logger pressure altitude when the device provides it (igc_pressure_altitude), otherwise ISA pressure altitude only (1013.25 hPa; not QNH-corrected). Does not show barometric AMSL or GPS height — use other InfoBoxes for navigation.': "Enregistreur d'altitude-pression lorsque l'appareil la fournit (igc_pression_altitude), sinon altitude-pression ISA uniquement (1013,25 hPa\xa0; non corrigé par QNH). N'affiche pas la hauteur barométrique AMSL ou GPS — utilisez d'autres InfoBox pour la navigation.",
        'Same gate as Start open. Main value is estimated time to reach the start line (MacCready leg when available, else distance / ground speed). Value colour and secondary line reflect gate state at that ETA: Too early (blue), Can start (green), Too late (red).': "Même portail que Start ouvert. La valeur principale est le temps estimé pour atteindre la ligne de départ (étape MacCready si disponible, sinon distance / vitesse sol). La couleur de la valeur et la ligne secondaire reflètent l'état de la porte à cet ETA\xa0: trop tôt (bleu), peut démarrer (vert), trop tard (rouge).",
        'Active waypoint: shows the next task waypoint when an ordered task is loaded, otherwise the Goto waypoint. Displays the waypoint name, arrival altitude difference relative to the safety arrival height, and distance. Click to choose a different waypoint (a task waypoint to skip to that leg, or any waypoint to set as Goto when no task is loaded).': "Waypoint actif\xa0: affiche le waypoint de tâche suivant lorsqu'une tâche ordonnée est chargée, sinon le waypoint Goto. Affiche le nom du point de cheminement, la différence d'altitude d'arrivée par rapport à la hauteur d'arrivée de sécurité et la distance. Cliquez pour choisir un waypoint différent (un waypoint de tâche pour passer à cette étape, ou n'importe quel waypoint à définir comme Goto lorsqu'aucune tâche n'est chargée).",
        'FFVP Federal Cup (NetCoupe) on WeGlide. The scored path has at most three turnpoints between start and finish and at least 25 km total. Points are proportional to credited distance, 100 divided by the glider handicap (DAeC-style index), and a success factor of 1.0 for a free flight or 1.2 for a task declared electronically before takeoff. XCSoar live scoring uses a success factor of 1.0 only, not the 1.2 multiplier for declared tasks.': "Coupe Fédérale FFVP (NetCoupe) sur WeGlide. Le parcours balisé comporte au maximum trois points de virage entre le départ et l'arrivée et au moins 25 km au total. Les points sont proportionnels à la distance créditée, 100 divisé par le handicap du planeur (indice de type DAeC), et un facteur de réussite de 1,0 pour un vol libre ou de 1,2 pour une tâche déclarée électroniquement avant le décollage. La notation en direct XCSoar utilise un facteur de réussite de 1,0 uniquement, et non le multiplicateur de 1,2 pour les tâches déclarées.",
        'Previous waypoint: when an ordered task is loaded, automatically tracks the task waypoint before the active leg (the start waypoint when on the first leg). Displays the waypoint name, arrival altitude difference relative to the safety arrival height, and distance. Click to choose a different waypoint to display (task waypoints when a task is loaded, otherwise the full waypoint list); selection is informational only and never advances the task or sets a Goto. With a task loaded, choose "Resume auto tracking" at the top of the list to revert to automatic tracking.': 'Waypoint précédent\xa0: lorsqu\'une tâche ordonnée est chargée, suit automatiquement le waypoint de la tâche avant l\'étape active (le waypoint de départ lors de la première étape). Affiche le nom du point de cheminement, la différence d\'altitude d\'arrivée par rapport à la hauteur d\'arrivée de sécurité et la distance. Cliquez pour choisir un waypoint différent à afficher (les waypoints de la tâche lorsqu\'une tâche est chargée, sinon la liste complète des waypoints)\xa0; la sélection est uniquement informative et ne fait jamais avancer la tâche ni ne définit un Goto. Une fois une tâche chargée, choisissez "Reprendre le suivi automatique" en haut de la liste pour revenir au suivi automatique.',
        'This parameter estimates the height%s at which the average dry updraft strength drops below 225 fpm and is expected to give better quantitative numbers for the maximum cloudless thermalling height than the BL Top height, especially when mixing results from vertical wind shear rather than thermals. (Note: the present assumptions tend to underpredict the max. thermalling height for dry conditions.) In the presence of clouds the maximum thermalling height may instead be limited by the cloud base. Being for "dry" thermals, this parameter omits the effect of "cloudsuck".': 'Ce paramètre estime la hauteur%s à laquelle la force moyenne du courant ascendant sec tombe en dessous de 225 fpm et devrait donner de meilleurs chiffres quantitatifs pour la hauteur maximale de thermique sans nuages \u200b\u200bque la hauteur BL Top, en particulier lors du mélange des résultats du cisaillement vertical du vent plutôt que des thermiques. (Remarque\xa0: les hypothèses actuelles ont tendance à sous-estimer la hauteur thermique maximale dans des conditions sèches.) En présence de nuages, la hauteur thermique maximale peut plutôt être limitée par la base des nuages. S\'agissant des thermiques "secs", ce paramètre omet l\'effet de "cloudsuck".',
        '![](resource:IDB_WARNING_TRIANGLE)\n\n!!! warning\n# Important Safety Notice\n\nBy using XCSoar, you acknowledge and accept the following:\n\n## Limitations\n\n- XCSoar is for **situational awareness only**\n- XCSoar is **not** a FLARM display\n- XCSoar is **not** aviation certified in any way\n- The artificial horizon is **not** fit for any purpose\n- Databanks (airspace, waypoints) may contain errors, be incomplete, or **not** up to date\n- NOTAM display does **not** replace proper pre-flight NOTAM briefing\n- NOTAM data may be incomplete, delayed, filtered, or unavailable\n- XCSoar is **not** guaranteed to be error free\n\n## Pilot Responsibility\n\nThe **Pilot in Command** is always responsible for the safe operation of the aircraft. Never rely solely on XCSoar for navigation or situational awareness.\n\n': "![](resource:IDB_WARNING_TRIANGLE)\n\n!!! warning\n# Avis de sécurité important\n\nEn utilisant XCSoar, vous reconnaissez et acceptez ce qui suit\xa0:\n\n## Limites\n\n- XCSoar est pour **connaissance de la situation uniquement**\n- XCSoar est **pas** un écran FLARM\n- XCSoar est certifié **pas** aviation de quelque manière que ce soit\n- L'horizon artificiel est **pas** adapté à tous les usages\n- Les banques de données (espace aérien, waypoints) peuvent contenir des erreurs, être incomplètes ou **pas** à jour\n- L'affichage NOTAM est-il que **pas** remplace le briefing NOTAM approprié avant le vol\n- Les données NOTAM peuvent être incomplètes, retardées, filtrées ou indisponibles\n- XCSoar est **pas** garanti sans erreur\n\n## Responsabilité du pilote\n\nLe **Pilote aux commandes** est toujours responsable de l’exploitation sûre de l’avion. Ne comptez jamais uniquement sur XCSoar pour la navigation ou la connaissance de la situation.\n\n",
        '# Getting Started\n\nTo use XCSoar effectively, configure the following:\n\n- [Restore from backup](xcsoar://dialog/backup) - Restore previous XCSoar data from a USB or SD card (optional)\n\n- [%s] [Map and data](xcsoar://config/site-files) - Download maps, waypoints, and airspace files for your region\n\n- [%s] [Aircraft polar](xcsoar://config/planes) - Set up your aircraft with the correct polar curve\n\n- [%s] [Pilot info](xcsoar://config/logger) - Enter your name and weight\n\n- [%s] [Devices](xcsoar://config/devices) - Connect your flight instruments\n\n- [%s] [WeGlide](xcsoar://config/weglide) - Upload flights automatically to WeGlide\n\n- [%s] [Thermal Information Map](xcsoar://config/weather) - Show thermal locations from thermalmap.info on the map\n\n- [%s] [Safety factors](xcsoar://config/safety) - Set arrival height, terrain clearance and polar degradation\n\n- [%s] [Terrain Display](xcsoar://config/terrain) - Choose terrain colors, shading and contour lines\n\n- [ ] [Live tracking](xcsoar://config/tracking) *(optional)* - Share your position via SkyLines or LiveTrack24\n\nThe easiest way to explore XCSoar is to [replay an existing IGC flight](xcsoar://dialog/replay).': "# Commencer\n\nPour utiliser XCSoar efficacement, configurez les éléments suivants\xa0:\n\n- [Restaurer à partir d'une sauvegarde](xcsoar://dialog/backup) - Restaurer les données XCSoar précédentes à partir d'une carte USB ou SD (facultatif)\n\n- [%s] [Carte et données](xcsoar://config/site-files) - Téléchargez des cartes, des waypoints et des fichiers d'espace aérien pour votre région\n\n- [%s] [Polaire d'avion](xcsoar://config/planes) - Configurez votre avion avec la bonne courbe polaire\n\n- [%s] [Informations sur le pilote](xcsoar://config/logger) - Entrez votre nom et votre poids\n\n- [%s] [Appareils](xcsoar://config/devices) - Connectez vos instruments de vol\n\n- [%s] [WeGlide](xcsoar://config/weglide) - Télécharger automatiquement les vols sur WeGlide\n\n- [%s] [Carte d'informations thermiques](xcsoar://config/weather) - Afficher les emplacements thermiques de thermalmap.info sur la carte\n\n- [%s] [Facteurs de sécurité](xcsoar://config/safety) - Définir la hauteur d'arrivée, la garde au sol et la dégradation polaire\n\n- [%s] [Affichage du terrain](xcsoar://config/terrain) - Choisissez les couleurs du terrain, les ombres et les courbes de niveau\n\n- [ ] [Suivi en direct](xcsoar://config/tracking) *(optional)* - Partagez votre position via SkyLines ou LiveTrack24\n\nLa façon la plus simple d'explorer XCSoar est de [rejouer un vol IGC existant](xcsoar://dialog/replay).",
        '# Gesture Navigation\n\nXCSoar supports touch gestures on the map:\n\n- ![U](resource:IDB_GESTURE_UP) **Swipe Up** (U): Zoom in\n- ![D](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DOWN) **Swipe Down** (D): Zoom out\n- ![R](resource:IDB_GESTURE_RIGHT) **Swipe Right** (R): Previous screen mode\n- ![L](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LEFT) **Swipe Left** (L): Next screen mode\n- ![UD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_UD) **Up-Down** (UD): Auto zoom\n- ![DU](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DU) **Down-Up** (DU): Menu\n- ![DR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DR) **Down-Right** (DR): Waypoint details\n- ![DL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DL) **Down-Left** (DL): Alternates\n- ![LU](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LU) **Left-Up** (LU): Recently used waypoints\n- ![RD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_RD) **Right-Down** (RD): Task manager\n- ![URD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_URD) **Up-Right-Down** (URD): Analysis\n- ![LDR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LDR) **Left-Down-Right** (LDR): Checklist\n- ![URDL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_URDL) **Up-Right-Down-Left** (URDL): Pan mode\n- ![LDRDL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LDRDL) **Left-Down-Right-Down-Left** (LDRDL): Status\n- ![ULDR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_ULDR) **Up-Left-Down-Right** (ULDR): Quick menu\n\nLong-press on the map to enter Pan mode. Tap while in Pan mode to see nearby waypoints.': '# Navigation gestuelle\n\nXCSoar prend en charge les gestes tactiles sur la carte\xa0:\n\n- ![U](resource:IDB_GESTURE_UP) **Glissez vers le haut** (U): Zoomer\n- ![D](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DOWN) **Faites glisser vers le bas** (D): Zoom arrière\n- ![R](resource:IDB_GESTURE_RIGHT) **Balayez vers la droite** (R): Mode écran précédent\n- ![L](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LEFT) **Balayez vers la gauche** (L): Mode écran suivant\n- ![UD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_UD) **Haut-Bas** (UD): Zoom automatique\n- ![DU](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DU) **Vers le bas** (DU): Menu\n- ![DR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DR) **Carrément** (DR): Détails du point de cheminement\n- ![DL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DL) **En bas à gauche** (DL): Suppléants\n- ![LU](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LU) **Gauche en haut** (LU): Waypoints récemment utilisés\n- ![RD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_RD) **En bas à droite** (RD): Gestionnaire de tâches\n- ![URD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_URD) **Haut-Droite-Bas** (URD): Analyse\n- ![LDR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LDR) **Gauche-Bas-Droite** (LDR): Liste de contrôle\n- ![URDL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_URDL) **Haut-Droite-Bas-Gauche** (URDL): Mode panoramique\n- ![LDRDL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LDRDL) **Gauche-Bas-Droite-Bas-Gauche** (LDRDL): Statut\n- ![ULDR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_ULDR) **Haut-Gauche-Bas-Droite** (ULDR): Menu rapide\n\nAppuyez longuement sur la carte pour passer en mode Panoramique. Appuyez en mode Panoramique pour voir les waypoints à proximité.',
    },
    "he": {
        'Size of waypoint symbols on the map as a percentage of the built-in artwork (list dialogs keep a fixed row icon size).': 'גודל סמלי נקודות ציון במפה כאחוז מהגרפיקה המובנית (תיבת דו-שיח של רשימה שומרת על גודל סמל שורה קבוע).',
        'Home waypoint name, arrival altitude difference relative to the safety arrival height, and distance. Click to change the home waypoint.': 'שם נקודת ציון ביתית, הפרש גובה הגעה ביחס לגובה ההגעה הבטיחותי והמרחק. לחץ כדי לשנות את נקודת הציון הביתית.',
        'Current QNH pressure setting used for barometric altitude calculation. Tap the infobox to open the setup panel and adjust QNH manually.': 'הגדרת לחץ QNH נוכחית המשמשת לחישוב גובה ברומטרי. הקש על תיבת המידע כדי לפתוח את לוח ההגדרות ולהתאים את QNH באופן ידני.',
        'This page shows WiFi status when NetworkManager or ConnMan is on D-Bus (e.g. Linux with Wayland or KMS). Open WiFi list to scan and connect when a service is available.': 'דף זה מציג את מצב ה-WiFi כאשר NetworkManager או ConnMan נמצאים ב-D-Bus (לדוגמה, Linux עם Wayland או KMS). פתח את רשימת ה-WiFi כדי לסרוק ולהתחבר כאשר שירות זמין.',
        'The terrain can be shaded among slopes to indicate either wind direction, sun position, a geographically fixed shading from North-West, or a screen-relative fixed shading from top left.': 'השטח יכול להיות מוצל בין מדרונות כדי לציין כיוון רוח, מיקום שמש, הצללה קבועה גיאוגרפית מצפון-מערב, או הצללה קבועה יחסית למסך משמאל למעלה.',
        "Synchronize the glide polar between XCSoar and the device (LXNAV varios). 'Receive' adopts the polar from the device (e.g. for club gliders). 'Send' pushes XCSoar's polar to the device.": "סנכרן את קוטבי הגלישה בין XCSoar והמכשיר (LXNAV varios). 'קבל' מאמצת את הקוטב מהמכשיר (למשל עבור רחפני מועדונים). 'שלח' דוחף את הקוטב של XCSoar למכשיר.",
        'List of active airspace files. Use the Add and Remove buttons to activate or deactivate airspace files respectively. Supported file types are: Openair (.openair /.txt /.air), and Tim Newport-Pearce (.sua).': 'רשימת קבצי המרחב האווירי הפעילים. השתמש בלחצנים הוסף והסר כדי להפעיל או לבטל קבצי מרחב אווירי בהתאמה. סוגי הקבצים הנתמכים הם: Openair (.openair /.txt /.air), ו-Tim Newport-Pearce (.sua).',
        'Signed countdown until the start gate opens or closes (now). Value colour and secondary line reflect gate state at the current time: Waiting (blue), Open (green), Closed (red). PEV window overrides task gate when set.': 'ספירה לאחור חתומה עד ששער ההתחלה נפתח או נסגר (עכשיו). צבע הערך והקו המשני משקפים את מצב השער בזמן הנוכחי: המתנה (כחול), פתוח (ירוק), סגור (אדום). חלון PEV עוקף את שער המשימות כאשר הוא מוגדר.',
        'Tells XCSoar to send its current GPS position to the device as $GPGGA and $GPRMC sentences. Turn off when another GPS source is already feeding the device on the same line. Changes take effect after reconnecting the device.': 'אומר ל-XCSoar לשלוח את מיקום ה-GPS הנוכחי שלה למכשיר כמשפטים של $GPGGA ו-$GPRMC. כבה כאשר מקור GPS אחר כבר מזין את המכשיר באותו קו. השינויים נכנסים לתוקף לאחר חיבור המכשיר מחדש.',
        'Logger pressure altitude when the device provides it (igc_pressure_altitude), otherwise ISA pressure altitude only (1013.25 hPa; not QNH-corrected). Does not show barometric AMSL or GPS height — use other InfoBoxes for navigation.': 'גובה לחץ לוגר כאשר המכשיר מספק זאת (igc_pressure_altitude), אחרת גובה לחץ ISA בלבד (1013.25 hPa; לא מתוקן QNH). לא מציג גובה AMSL או GPS ברומטרי - השתמש בתיבות מידע אחרות לניווט.',
        'Same gate as Start open. Main value is estimated time to reach the start line (MacCready leg when available, else distance / ground speed). Value colour and secondary line reflect gate state at that ETA: Too early (blue), Can start (green), Too late (red).': 'אותו שער כמו Start open. הערך העיקרי הוא זמן הגעה משוער לקו הזינוק (רגל MacCready כאשר זמין, אחרת מרחק / מהירות קרקע). צבע הערך והקו המשני משקפים את מצב השער ב-ETA זה: מוקדם מדי (כחול), יכול להתחיל (ירוק), מאוחר מדי (אדום).',
        'Active waypoint: shows the next task waypoint when an ordered task is loaded, otherwise the Goto waypoint. Displays the waypoint name, arrival altitude difference relative to the safety arrival height, and distance. Click to choose a different waypoint (a task waypoint to skip to that leg, or any waypoint to set as Goto when no task is loaded).': 'נקודת ציון פעילה: מציג את נקודת הציון של המשימה הבאה כאשר משימה מסודרת נטענת, אחרת את נקודת הציון עבור אל. מציג את שם נקודת הציון, הפרש גובה הגעה ביחס לגובה ההגעה הבטיחותי והמרחק. לחץ כדי לבחור נקודת ציון אחרת (נקודת ציון של משימה כדי לדלג לאותה שלב, או כל נקודת ציון להגדיר כ- Goto כאשר אף משימה אינה נטענת).',
        'FFVP Federal Cup (NetCoupe) on WeGlide. The scored path has at most three turnpoints between start and finish and at least 25 km total. Points are proportional to credited distance, 100 divided by the glider handicap (DAeC-style index), and a success factor of 1.0 for a free flight or 1.2 for a task declared electronically before takeoff. XCSoar live scoring uses a success factor of 1.0 only, not the 1.2 multiplier for declared tasks.': 'גביע פדרלי FFVP (NetCoupe) ב-WeGlide. בשביל הניקוד יש לכל היותר שלוש נקודות סיבוב בין התחלה לסיום ולפחות 25 ק"מ בסך הכל. הנקודות הן פרופורציונליות למרחק הנזקף, 100 חלקי נכות הרחפן (מדד בסגנון DAeC), ומקדם הצלחה של 1.0 לטיסה חופשית או 1.2 עבור משימה שהוכרזה אלקטרונית לפני ההמראה. ציון חי של XCSoar משתמש במקדם הצלחה של 1.0 בלבד, לא במכפיל 1.2 עבור משימות מוצהרות.',
        'Previous waypoint: when an ordered task is loaded, automatically tracks the task waypoint before the active leg (the start waypoint when on the first leg). Displays the waypoint name, arrival altitude difference relative to the safety arrival height, and distance. Click to choose a different waypoint to display (task waypoints when a task is loaded, otherwise the full waypoint list); selection is informational only and never advances the task or sets a Goto. With a task loaded, choose "Resume auto tracking" at the top of the list to revert to automatic tracking.': 'נקודת ציון קודמת: כאשר משימה מסודרת נטענת, עוקב אוטומטית אחר נקודת הציון של המשימה לפני הרגל הפעילה (נקודת ההתחלה כאשר נמצאת ברגל הראשונה). מציג את שם נקודת הציון, הפרש גובה הגעה ביחס לגובה ההגעה הבטיחותי והמרחק. לחץ כדי לבחור נקודת ציון אחרת להצגה (נקודות ציון למשימה כאשר משימה נטענת, אחרת רשימת נקודות הציון המלאה); הבחירה היא אינפורמטיבית בלבד ולעולם אינה מקדמת את המשימה או מגדירה Goto. עם משימה נטענת, בחר "המשך מעקב אוטומטי" בראש הרשימה כדי לחזור למעקב אוטומטי.',
        'This parameter estimates the height%s at which the average dry updraft strength drops below 225 fpm and is expected to give better quantitative numbers for the maximum cloudless thermalling height than the BL Top height, especially when mixing results from vertical wind shear rather than thermals. (Note: the present assumptions tend to underpredict the max. thermalling height for dry conditions.) In the presence of clouds the maximum thermalling height may instead be limited by the cloud base. Being for "dry" thermals, this parameter omits the effect of "cloudsuck".': 'פרמטר זה מעריך את הגובה %s שבו חוזק הנסיגה היבש הממוצע יורד מתחת ל-225 fpm וצפוי לתת מספרים כמותיים טובים יותר עבור גובה התרמיל המקסימלי ללא עננים מאשר גובה ה-BL Top, במיוחד כאשר ערבוב תוצאות של גזירת רוח אנכית ולא תרמיות. (הערה: ההנחות הנוכחיות נוטות לא לחזות את גובה התרמיל המקסימלי עבור תנאים יבשים.) בנוכחות עננים גובה התרמיל המרבי עשוי להיות מוגבל במקום זאת על ידי בסיס הענן. בהיותו עבור תרמיות "יבשות", פרמטר זה משמיט את ההשפעה של "סאק ענן".',
        '![](resource:IDB_WARNING_TRIANGLE)\n\n!!! warning\n# Important Safety Notice\n\nBy using XCSoar, you acknowledge and accept the following:\n\n## Limitations\n\n- XCSoar is for **situational awareness only**\n- XCSoar is **not** a FLARM display\n- XCSoar is **not** aviation certified in any way\n- The artificial horizon is **not** fit for any purpose\n- Databanks (airspace, waypoints) may contain errors, be incomplete, or **not** up to date\n- NOTAM display does **not** replace proper pre-flight NOTAM briefing\n- NOTAM data may be incomplete, delayed, filtered, or unavailable\n- XCSoar is **not** guaranteed to be error free\n\n## Pilot Responsibility\n\nThe **Pilot in Command** is always responsible for the safe operation of the aircraft. Never rely solely on XCSoar for navigation or situational awareness.\n\n': '![](resource:IDB_WARNING_TRIANGLE)\n\n!!! warning\n# הודעת בטיחות חשובה\n\nעל ידי שימוש ב-XCSoar, אתה מאשר ומקבל את הדברים הבאים:\n\n## מגבלות\n\n- XCSoar הוא עבור **מודעות למצב בלבד**\n- XCSoar היא צג FLARM של **לֹא**\n- XCSoar הוא הסמכה לתעופה **לֹא** בכל דרך שהיא\n- האופק המלאכותי הוא **לֹא** מתאים לכל מטרה\n- מאגרי מידע (מרחב אווירי, נקודות ציון) עשויים להכיל שגיאות, להיות חלקיים או **לֹא** מעודכנים\n- תצוגת NOTAM האם **לֹא** מחליפה את תדרוך NOTAM תקין לפני הטיסה\n- נתוני NOTAM עשויים להיות חלקיים, מושהים, מסוננים או לא זמינים\n- XCSoar הוא **לֹא** מובטח ללא שגיאות\n\n## אחריות טייס\n\nה-**טייס בפיקוד** תמיד אחראי לתפעול בטוח של המטוס. לעולם אל תסתמך רק על XCSoar עבור ניווט או מודעות למצב.\n\n',
        '# Getting Started\n\nTo use XCSoar effectively, configure the following:\n\n- [Restore from backup](xcsoar://dialog/backup) - Restore previous XCSoar data from a USB or SD card (optional)\n\n- [%s] [Map and data](xcsoar://config/site-files) - Download maps, waypoints, and airspace files for your region\n\n- [%s] [Aircraft polar](xcsoar://config/planes) - Set up your aircraft with the correct polar curve\n\n- [%s] [Pilot info](xcsoar://config/logger) - Enter your name and weight\n\n- [%s] [Devices](xcsoar://config/devices) - Connect your flight instruments\n\n- [%s] [WeGlide](xcsoar://config/weglide) - Upload flights automatically to WeGlide\n\n- [%s] [Thermal Information Map](xcsoar://config/weather) - Show thermal locations from thermalmap.info on the map\n\n- [%s] [Safety factors](xcsoar://config/safety) - Set arrival height, terrain clearance and polar degradation\n\n- [%s] [Terrain Display](xcsoar://config/terrain) - Choose terrain colors, shading and contour lines\n\n- [ ] [Live tracking](xcsoar://config/tracking) *(optional)* - Share your position via SkyLines or LiveTrack24\n\nThe easiest way to explore XCSoar is to [replay an existing IGC flight](xcsoar://dialog/replay).': '# תחילת העבודה\n\nכדי להשתמש ב-XCSoar בצורה יעילה, הגדר את הדברים הבאים:\n\n- [שחזר מגיבוי](xcsoar://dialog/backup) - שחזור נתוני XCSoar קודמים מכרטיס USB או SD (אופציונלי)\n\n- [%s] [מפה ונתונים](xcsoar://config/site-files) - הורד מפות, נקודות ציון וקבצי מרחב אווירי עבור האזור שלך\n\n- [%s] [מטוס קוטבי](xcsoar://config/planes) - הגדר את המטוס שלך עם העקומה הקוטבית הנכונה\n\n- [%s] [מידע על הטייס](xcsoar://config/logger) - הכנס את שמך ומשקלך\n\n- [%s] [התקנים](xcsoar://config/devices) - חבר את מכשירי הטיסה שלך\n\n- [%s] [WeGlide](xcsoar://config/weglide) - העלה טיסות אוטומטית ל-WeGlide\n\n- [%s] [מפת מידע תרמי](xcsoar://config/weather) - הצג מיקומים תרמיים מ-thermalmap.info על המפה\n\n- [%s] [גורמי בטיחות](xcsoar://config/safety) - הגדר את גובה ההגעה, מרווח השטח והשפלה הקוטבית\n\n- [%s] [תצוגת שטח](xcsoar://config/terrain) - בחר צבעי שטח, הצללה וקווי מתאר\n\n- [ ] [מעקב חי](xcsoar://config/tracking) *(optional)* - שתף את העמדה שלך באמצעות SkyLines או LiveTrack24\n\nהדרך הקלה ביותר לחקור את XCSoar היא לעשות זאת [השמעת טיסת IGC קיימת מחדש](xcsoar://dialog/replay).',
        '# Gesture Navigation\n\nXCSoar supports touch gestures on the map:\n\n- ![U](resource:IDB_GESTURE_UP) **Swipe Up** (U): Zoom in\n- ![D](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DOWN) **Swipe Down** (D): Zoom out\n- ![R](resource:IDB_GESTURE_RIGHT) **Swipe Right** (R): Previous screen mode\n- ![L](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LEFT) **Swipe Left** (L): Next screen mode\n- ![UD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_UD) **Up-Down** (UD): Auto zoom\n- ![DU](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DU) **Down-Up** (DU): Menu\n- ![DR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DR) **Down-Right** (DR): Waypoint details\n- ![DL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DL) **Down-Left** (DL): Alternates\n- ![LU](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LU) **Left-Up** (LU): Recently used waypoints\n- ![RD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_RD) **Right-Down** (RD): Task manager\n- ![URD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_URD) **Up-Right-Down** (URD): Analysis\n- ![LDR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LDR) **Left-Down-Right** (LDR): Checklist\n- ![URDL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_URDL) **Up-Right-Down-Left** (URDL): Pan mode\n- ![LDRDL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LDRDL) **Left-Down-Right-Down-Left** (LDRDL): Status\n- ![ULDR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_ULDR) **Up-Left-Down-Right** (ULDR): Quick menu\n\nLong-press on the map to enter Pan mode. Tap while in Pan mode to see nearby waypoints.': '# ניווט מחוות\n\nXCSoar תומך במחוות מגע במפה:\n\n- ![U](resource:IDB_GESTURE_UP) **החלק למעלה** (U): לְהִתְמַקֵד\n- ![D](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DOWN) **החלק למטה** (D): זום החוצה\n- ![R](resource:IDB_GESTURE_RIGHT) **החלק ימינה** (R): מצב מסך קודם\n- ![L](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LEFT) **החלק שמאלה** (L): מצב המסך הבא\n- ![UD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_UD) **למעלה-למטה** (UD): זום אוטומטי\n- ![DU](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DU) **למטה-מעלה** (DU): תַפרִיט\n- ![DR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DR) **לְגַמרֵי** (DR): פרטי נקודת ציון\n- ![DL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DL) **למטה-שמאל** (DL): מחליפים\n- ![LU](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LU) **שמאלה למעלה** (LU): נקודות ציון בשימוש לאחרונה\n- ![RD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_RD) **ימינה-למטה** (RD): מנהל משימות\n- ![URD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_URD) **למעלה-ימינה-למטה** (URD): אָנָלִיזָה\n- ![LDR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LDR) **שמאל-מטה-ימין** (LDR): רשימת תיוג\n- ![URDL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_URDL) **למעלה-ימין למטה-שמאל** (URDL): מצב פאן\n- ![LDRDL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LDRDL) **שמאל-מטה-ימין-למטה-שמאל** (LDRDL): סטָטוּס\n- ![ULDR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_ULDR) **למעלה-שמאל למטה-ימין** (ULDR): תפריט מהיר\n\nלחץ לחיצה ארוכה על המפה כדי להיכנס למצב Pan. הקש במצב Pan כדי לראות נקודות ציון קרובות.',
    },
    "hr": {
        'Size of waypoint symbols on the map as a percentage of the built-in artwork (list dialogs keep a fixed row icon size).': 'Veličina simbola putnih točaka na karti kao postotak ugrađenog ilustracije (dijalozi s popisom zadržavaju fiksnu veličinu ikone retka).',
        'Home waypoint name, arrival altitude difference relative to the safety arrival height, and distance. Click to change the home waypoint.': 'Naziv početne putne točke, razlika visine dolaska u odnosu na sigurnosnu visinu dolaska i udaljenost. Kliknite za promjenu početne međutočke.',
        'Current QNH pressure setting used for barometric altitude calculation. Tap the infobox to open the setup panel and adjust QNH manually.': 'Trenutna postavka QNH tlaka koja se koristi za izračun barometrijske visine. Dodirnite okvir za informacije kako biste otvorili ploču za postavljanje i ručno prilagodili QNH.',
        'This page shows WiFi status when NetworkManager or ConnMan is on D-Bus (e.g. Linux with Wayland or KMS). Open WiFi list to scan and connect when a service is available.': 'Ova stranica prikazuje WiFi status kada su NetworkManager ili ConnMan na D-Busu (npr. Linux s Waylandom ili KMS-om). Otvorite WiFi popis za skeniranje i povezivanje kada usluga bude dostupna.',
        'The terrain can be shaded among slopes to indicate either wind direction, sun position, a geographically fixed shading from North-West, or a screen-relative fixed shading from top left.': 'Teren se može zasjeniti među padinama kako bi se označio smjer vjetra, položaj sunca, geografski fiksno sjenčanje sa sjeverozapada ili fiksno sjenčanje u odnosu na zaslon s gornjeg lijevog dijela.',
        "Synchronize the glide polar between XCSoar and the device (LXNAV varios). 'Receive' adopts the polar from the device (e.g. for club gliders). 'Send' pushes XCSoar's polar to the device.": "Sinkronizirajte klizni pol između XCSoara i uređaja (različiti LXNAV). 'Primanje' preuzima polare s uređaja (npr. za klupske jedrilice). 'Pošalji' gura XCSoarov polar na uređaj.",
        'List of active airspace files. Use the Add and Remove buttons to activate or deactivate airspace files respectively. Supported file types are: Openair (.openair /.txt /.air), and Tim Newport-Pearce (.sua).': 'Popis aktivnih datoteka zračnog prostora. Koristite gumbe Dodaj i Ukloni za aktiviranje ili deaktiviranje datoteka zračnog prostora. Podržane vrste datoteka su: Openair (.openair /.txt /.air) i Tim Newport-Pearce (.sua).',
        'Signed countdown until the start gate opens or closes (now). Value colour and secondary line reflect gate state at the current time: Waiting (blue), Open (green), Closed (red). PEV window overrides task gate when set.': 'Odbrojavanje s potpisom do otvaranja ili zatvaranja startnih vrata (sada). Boja vrijednosti i sekundarna linija odražavaju stanje vrata u trenutnom trenutku: čekanje (plavo), otvoreno (zeleno), zatvoreno (crveno). Prozor PEV nadjačava vrata zadatka kada je postavljen.',
        'Tells XCSoar to send its current GPS position to the device as $GPGGA and $GPRMC sentences. Turn off when another GPS source is already feeding the device on the same line. Changes take effect after reconnecting the device.': 'Kaže XCSoaru da pošalje svoj trenutni GPS položaj uređaju kao $GPGGA i $GPRMC rečenice. Isključite kada drugi GPS izvor već napaja uređaj na istoj liniji. Promjene stupaju na snagu nakon ponovnog povezivanja uređaja.',
        'Logger pressure altitude when the device provides it (igc_pressure_altitude), otherwise ISA pressure altitude only (1013.25 hPa; not QNH-corrected). Does not show barometric AMSL or GPS height — use other InfoBoxes for navigation.': 'Zabilježite visinu po tlaku kada je uređaj pruži (igc_pressure_altitude), inače samo visinu po tlaku ISA (1013,25 hPa; nije ispravljeno QNH). Ne prikazuje barometarsku AMSL ili GPS visinu — koristite druge InfoBoxove za navigaciju.',
        'Same gate as Start open. Main value is estimated time to reach the start line (MacCready leg when available, else distance / ground speed). Value colour and secondary line reflect gate state at that ETA: Too early (blue), Can start (green), Too late (red).': 'Ista vrata kao Start otvorena. Glavna vrijednost je procijenjeno vrijeme za postizanje startne crte (MacCready etapa kada je dostupna, inače udaljenost / brzina kretanja). Boja vrijednosti i sekundarna linija odražavaju stanje vrata u tom ETA: Prerano (plavo), Može početi (zeleno), Prekasno (crveno).',
        'Active waypoint: shows the next task waypoint when an ordered task is loaded, otherwise the Goto waypoint. Displays the waypoint name, arrival altitude difference relative to the safety arrival height, and distance. Click to choose a different waypoint (a task waypoint to skip to that leg, or any waypoint to set as Goto when no task is loaded).': 'Aktivna međutočka: prikazuje sljedeću međutočku zadatka kada se učita naručeni zadatak, inače Goto međutočku. Prikazuje naziv putne točke, razliku nadmorske visine dolaska u odnosu na sigurnosnu visinu dolaska i udaljenost. Kliknite da biste odabrali drugu međutočku (međutočku zadatka koju želite preskočiti na tu dionicu ili bilo koju međutočku koju želite postaviti kao Goto kada nema učitanog zadatka).',
        'FFVP Federal Cup (NetCoupe) on WeGlide. The scored path has at most three turnpoints between start and finish and at least 25 km total. Points are proportional to credited distance, 100 divided by the glider handicap (DAeC-style index), and a success factor of 1.0 for a free flight or 1.2 for a task declared electronically before takeoff. XCSoar live scoring uses a success factor of 1.0 only, not the 1.2 multiplier for declared tasks.': 'FFVP savezni kup (NetCoupe) na WeGlideu. Bodovana staza ima najviše tri okretišta između starta i cilja i ukupno najmanje 25 km. Bodovi su proporcionalni dodijeljenoj udaljenosti, 100 podijeljeno s hendikepom jedrilice (indeks u stilu DAeC) i faktorom uspjeha 1,0 za slobodni let ili 1,2 za zadatak objavljen elektronički prije polijetanja. XCSoar live bodovanje koristi samo faktor uspjeha 1,0, a ne množitelj 1,2 za deklarirane zadatke.',
        'Previous waypoint: when an ordered task is loaded, automatically tracks the task waypoint before the active leg (the start waypoint when on the first leg). Displays the waypoint name, arrival altitude difference relative to the safety arrival height, and distance. Click to choose a different waypoint to display (task waypoints when a task is loaded, otherwise the full waypoint list); selection is informational only and never advances the task or sets a Goto. With a task loaded, choose "Resume auto tracking" at the top of the list to revert to automatic tracking.': 'Prethodna međutočka: kada se učita naručeni zadatak, automatski prati međutočku zadatka prije aktivne dionice (početna međutočka kada je na prvoj dionici). Prikazuje naziv putne točke, razliku nadmorske visine dolaska u odnosu na sigurnosnu visinu dolaska i udaljenost. Kliknite za odabir druge međutočke za prikaz (međutočke zadatka kada se zadatak učita, inače cijeli popis međutočaka); odabir je samo informativan i nikada ne napreduje u zadatku niti postavlja Goto. S učitanim zadatkom odaberite "Nastavi automatsko praćenje" na vrhu popisa za povratak na automatsko praćenje.',
        'This parameter estimates the height%s at which the average dry updraft strength drops below 225 fpm and is expected to give better quantitative numbers for the maximum cloudless thermalling height than the BL Top height, especially when mixing results from vertical wind shear rather than thermals. (Note: the present assumptions tend to underpredict the max. thermalling height for dry conditions.) In the presence of clouds the maximum thermalling height may instead be limited by the cloud base. Being for "dry" thermals, this parameter omits the effect of "cloudsuck".': 'Ovaj parametar procjenjuje visinu %s na kojoj prosječna jakost suhog uzlaznog strujanja pada ispod 225 fpm i očekuje se da će dati bolje kvantitativne brojeve za maksimalnu visinu topline bez oblaka od visine BL Top, posebno kada miješanje proizlazi iz vertikalnog smicanja vjetra, a ne termike. (Napomena: sadašnje pretpostavke imaju tendenciju premalo predviđati maksimalnu visinu zagrijavanja za suhe uvjete.) U prisutnosti oblaka maksimalna visina zagrijavanja može umjesto toga biti ograničena bazom oblaka. Budući da se radi o "suhoj" termici, ovaj parametar izostavlja učinak "usisavanja oblaka".',
        '![](resource:IDB_WARNING_TRIANGLE)\n\n!!! warning\n# Important Safety Notice\n\nBy using XCSoar, you acknowledge and accept the following:\n\n## Limitations\n\n- XCSoar is for **situational awareness only**\n- XCSoar is **not** a FLARM display\n- XCSoar is **not** aviation certified in any way\n- The artificial horizon is **not** fit for any purpose\n- Databanks (airspace, waypoints) may contain errors, be incomplete, or **not** up to date\n- NOTAM display does **not** replace proper pre-flight NOTAM briefing\n- NOTAM data may be incomplete, delayed, filtered, or unavailable\n- XCSoar is **not** guaranteed to be error free\n\n## Pilot Responsibility\n\nThe **Pilot in Command** is always responsible for the safe operation of the aircraft. Never rely solely on XCSoar for navigation or situational awareness.\n\n': '![](resource:IDB_WARNING_TRIANGLE)\n\n!!! warning\n# Važna obavijest o sigurnosti\n\nKorištenjem XCSoar-a potvrđujete i prihvaćate sljedeće:\n\n## Ograničenja\n\n- XCSoar je za **samo situacijska svijest**\n- XCSoar je **ne** FLARM zaslon\n- XCSoar ima **ne** zračni certifikat na bilo koji način\n- Umjetni horizont je **ne** pogodan za svaku namjenu\n- Banke podataka (zračni prostor, međutočke) mogu sadržavati pogreške, biti nepotpune ili **ne** ažurne\n- Zaslon NOTAM zamjenjuje li **ne** odgovarajući NOTAM brifing prije leta\n- NOTAM podaci mogu biti nepotpuni, kasniti, filtrirani ili nedostupni\n- XCSoar je **ne** zajamčeno bez grešaka\n\n## Odgovornost pilota\n\n**Pilot u zapovjedništvu** je uvijek odgovoran za siguran rad zrakoplova. Nikada se nemojte oslanjati isključivo na XCSoar za navigaciju ili svijest o situaciji.\n\n',
        '# Getting Started\n\nTo use XCSoar effectively, configure the following:\n\n- [Restore from backup](xcsoar://dialog/backup) - Restore previous XCSoar data from a USB or SD card (optional)\n\n- [%s] [Map and data](xcsoar://config/site-files) - Download maps, waypoints, and airspace files for your region\n\n- [%s] [Aircraft polar](xcsoar://config/planes) - Set up your aircraft with the correct polar curve\n\n- [%s] [Pilot info](xcsoar://config/logger) - Enter your name and weight\n\n- [%s] [Devices](xcsoar://config/devices) - Connect your flight instruments\n\n- [%s] [WeGlide](xcsoar://config/weglide) - Upload flights automatically to WeGlide\n\n- [%s] [Thermal Information Map](xcsoar://config/weather) - Show thermal locations from thermalmap.info on the map\n\n- [%s] [Safety factors](xcsoar://config/safety) - Set arrival height, terrain clearance and polar degradation\n\n- [%s] [Terrain Display](xcsoar://config/terrain) - Choose terrain colors, shading and contour lines\n\n- [ ] [Live tracking](xcsoar://config/tracking) *(optional)* - Share your position via SkyLines or LiveTrack24\n\nThe easiest way to explore XCSoar is to [replay an existing IGC flight](xcsoar://dialog/replay).': '# Početak rada\n\nDa biste učinkovito koristili XCSoar, konfigurirajte sljedeće:\n\n- [Vrati iz sigurnosne kopije](xcsoar://dialog/backup) - Vratite prethodne XCSoar podatke s USB-a ili SD kartice (opcionalno)\n\n- [%s] [Karta i podaci](xcsoar://config/site-files) - Preuzmite karte, putne točke i datoteke zračnog prostora za svoju regiju\n\n- [%s] [Zrakoplov polarni](xcsoar://config/planes) - Postavite svoj zrakoplov s ispravnom polarnom krivuljom\n\n- [%s] [Informacije o pilotu](xcsoar://config/logger) - Unesite svoje ime i težinu\n\n- [%s] [Uređaji](xcsoar://config/devices) - Povežite instrumente za let\n\n- [%s] [WeGlide](xcsoar://config/weglide) - Automatski prenesite letove na WeGlide\n\n- [%s] [Karta toplinskih informacija](xcsoar://config/weather) - Prikažite termalne lokacije s termalmap.info na karti\n\n- [%s] [Sigurnosni faktori](xcsoar://config/safety) - Postavite visinu dolaska, udaljenost od terena i polarnu degradaciju\n\n- [%s] [Prikaz terena](xcsoar://config/terrain) - Odaberite boje terena, sjenčanje i obrise\n\n- [ ] [Praćenje uživo](xcsoar://config/tracking) *(optional)* - Podijelite svoju poziciju putem SkyLines ili LiveTrack24\n\nNajlakši način da istražite XCSoar je da [reproducirati postojeći IGC let](xcsoar://dialog/replay).',
        '# Gesture Navigation\n\nXCSoar supports touch gestures on the map:\n\n- ![U](resource:IDB_GESTURE_UP) **Swipe Up** (U): Zoom in\n- ![D](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DOWN) **Swipe Down** (D): Zoom out\n- ![R](resource:IDB_GESTURE_RIGHT) **Swipe Right** (R): Previous screen mode\n- ![L](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LEFT) **Swipe Left** (L): Next screen mode\n- ![UD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_UD) **Up-Down** (UD): Auto zoom\n- ![DU](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DU) **Down-Up** (DU): Menu\n- ![DR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DR) **Down-Right** (DR): Waypoint details\n- ![DL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DL) **Down-Left** (DL): Alternates\n- ![LU](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LU) **Left-Up** (LU): Recently used waypoints\n- ![RD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_RD) **Right-Down** (RD): Task manager\n- ![URD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_URD) **Up-Right-Down** (URD): Analysis\n- ![LDR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LDR) **Left-Down-Right** (LDR): Checklist\n- ![URDL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_URDL) **Up-Right-Down-Left** (URDL): Pan mode\n- ![LDRDL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LDRDL) **Left-Down-Right-Down-Left** (LDRDL): Status\n- ![ULDR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_ULDR) **Up-Left-Down-Right** (ULDR): Quick menu\n\nLong-press on the map to enter Pan mode. Tap while in Pan mode to see nearby waypoints.': '# Navigacija gestama\n\nXCSoar podržava pokrete dodirom na karti:\n\n- ![U](resource:IDB_GESTURE_UP) **Povucite prema gore** (U): Povećaj\n- ![D](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DOWN) **Prijeđite prstom prema dolje** (D): Smanji\n- ![R](resource:IDB_GESTURE_RIGHT) **Prijeđite prstom udesno** (R): Prethodni način rada zaslona\n- ![L](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LEFT) **Prijeđite prstom ulijevo** (L): Sljedeći način rada zaslona\n- ![UD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_UD) **Gore-dolje** (UD): Automatski zum\n- ![DU](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DU) **Dolje-gore** (DU): Jelovnik \n- ![DR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DR) **Stvarno** (DR): Pojedinosti međutočke\n- ![DL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DL) **Dolje-lijevo** (DL): Zamjenici\n- ![LU](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LU) **Lijevo-gore** (LU): Nedavno korištene međutočke\n- ![RD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_RD) **Desno-Dolje** (RD): Upravitelj zadataka\n- ![URD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_URD) **Gore-desno-dolje** (URD): Analiza\n- ![LDR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LDR) **Lijevo-Dolje-Desno** (LDR): Kontrolni popis\n- ![URDL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_URDL) **Gore-desno-dolje-lijevo** (URDL): Način pomicanja\n- ![LDRDL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LDRDL) **Lijevo-dolje-desno-dolje-lijevo** (LDRDL): Status\n- ![ULDR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_ULDR) **Gore-lijevo-dolje-desno** (ULDR): Brzi izbornik\n\nDugo pritisnite kartu za ulazak u način rada Pan. Dodirnite dok ste u načinu Pan da vidite obližnje međutočke.',
    },
    "hu": {
        'Size of waypoint symbols on the map as a percentage of the built-in artwork (list dialogs keep a fixed row icon size).': 'Az útvonalpont szimbólumok mérete a térképen a beépített grafika százalékában (a lista párbeszédpanelek rögzített sorikonméretet tartanak fenn).',
        'Home waypoint name, arrival altitude difference relative to the safety arrival height, and distance. Click to change the home waypoint.': 'Otthoni útpont neve, érkezési magasságkülönbség a biztonsági érkezési magassághoz képest és távolság. Kattintson az otthoni fordulópont módosításához.',
        'Current QNH pressure setting used for barometric altitude calculation. Tap the infobox to open the setup panel and adjust QNH manually.': 'A barometrikus magasság kiszámításához használt aktuális QNH nyomásbeállítás. Érintse meg az infoboxot a beállítási panel megnyitásához és a QNH manuális beállításához.',
        'This page shows WiFi status when NetworkManager or ConnMan is on D-Bus (e.g. Linux with Wayland or KMS). Open WiFi list to scan and connect when a service is available.': 'Ez az oldal a WiFi állapotát mutatja, amikor a NetworkManager vagy a ConnMan D-buszon van (pl. Linux Wayland vagy KMS rendszerrel). Nyissa meg a WiFi listát a kereséshez és a csatlakozáshoz, amikor egy szolgáltatás elérhető.',
        'The terrain can be shaded among slopes to indicate either wind direction, sun position, a geographically fixed shading from North-West, or a screen-relative fixed shading from top left.': 'A terep árnyékolható lejtők között, jelezve a szél irányát, a nap helyzetét, a földrajzilag rögzített északnyugati árnyékolást, vagy a képernyőhöz képest rögzített árnyékolást a bal felső felől.',
        "Synchronize the glide polar between XCSoar and the device (LXNAV varios). 'Receive' adopts the polar from the device (e.g. for club gliders). 'Send' pushes XCSoar's polar to the device.": "Szinkronizálja a siklási polárt az XCSoar és az eszköz között (LXNAV varios). A „Receive” átveszi a polárist az eszközről (pl. klubvitorlázóknál). A 'Küldés' az XCSoar polaritását az eszközre tolja.",
        'List of active airspace files. Use the Add and Remove buttons to activate or deactivate airspace files respectively. Supported file types are: Openair (.openair /.txt /.air), and Tim Newport-Pearce (.sua).': 'Az aktív légtérfájlok listája. Használja a Hozzáadás és Eltávolítás gombokat a légtérfájlok aktiválásához vagy deaktiválásához. A támogatott fájltípusok: Openair (.openair /.txt /.air) és Tim Newport-Pearce (.sua).',
        'Signed countdown until the start gate opens or closes (now). Value colour and secondary line reflect gate state at the current time: Waiting (blue), Open (green), Closed (red). PEV window overrides task gate when set.': 'Aláírt visszaszámlálás a rajtkapu nyitásáig vagy záródásáig (most). Az érték színe és a másodlagos vonal a kapu aktuális állapotát tükrözi: Várakozás (kék), Nyitva (zöld), Zárva (piros). A PEV ablak felülírja a feladatkaput, ha be van állítva.',
        'Tells XCSoar to send its current GPS position to the device as $GPGGA and $GPRMC sentences. Turn off when another GPS source is already feeding the device on the same line. Changes take effect after reconnecting the device.': 'Megmondja az XCSoar-nak, hogy $GPGGA és $GPRMC mondatként küldje el az aktuális GPS-pozíciót az eszközre. Kapcsolja ki, ha egy másik GPS-forrás már táplálja az eszközt ugyanazon a vonalon. A változtatások az eszköz újracsatlakoztatása után lépnek életbe.',
        'Logger pressure altitude when the device provides it (igc_pressure_altitude), otherwise ISA pressure altitude only (1013.25 hPa; not QNH-corrected). Does not show barometric AMSL or GPS height — use other InfoBoxes for navigation.': 'A nyomásmagasság naplózása, amikor az eszköz biztosítja (igc_pressure_altitude), egyébként csak az ISA nyomásmagasság (1013,25 hPa; nem QNH-korrigált). Nem mutatja a barometrikus AMSL vagy GPS magasságot – használjon más InfoBoxokat a navigációhoz.',
        'Same gate as Start open. Main value is estimated time to reach the start line (MacCready leg when available, else distance / ground speed). Value colour and secondary line reflect gate state at that ETA: Too early (blue), Can start (green), Too late (red).': 'Ugyanaz a kapu, mint a Start nyitva. A fő érték a rajtvonal eléréséhez szükséges becsült idő (MacCready szakasz, ha elérhető, különben távolság / talajsebesség). Az érték színe és a másodlagos vonal tükrözi a kapu állapotát az adott érkezési időpontban: Túl korai (kék), Indulhat (zöld), Túl későn (piros).',
        'Active waypoint: shows the next task waypoint when an ordered task is loaded, otherwise the Goto waypoint. Displays the waypoint name, arrival altitude difference relative to the safety arrival height, and distance. Click to choose a different waypoint (a task waypoint to skip to that leg, or any waypoint to set as Goto when no task is loaded).': 'Aktív útpont: a következő feladat fordulópontját mutatja, amikor egy rendezett feladatot betöltenek, ellenkező esetben a Goto útpontot. Megjeleníti az útpont nevét, a biztonságos érkezési magassághoz viszonyított érkezési magasságkülönbséget és a távolságot. Kattintson egy másik útpont kiválasztásához (egy feladat útpontja az adott szakaszhoz való ugráshoz, vagy bármely útpont, amelyet Goto-nak állíthat be, ha nincs betöltve feladat).',
        'FFVP Federal Cup (NetCoupe) on WeGlide. The scored path has at most three turnpoints between start and finish and at least 25 km total. Points are proportional to credited distance, 100 divided by the glider handicap (DAeC-style index), and a success factor of 1.0 for a free flight or 1.2 for a task declared electronically before takeoff. XCSoar live scoring uses a success factor of 1.0 only, not the 1.2 multiplier for declared tasks.': 'FFVP Szövetségi Kupa (NetCoupe) a WeGlide-on. A pontozott útvonalnak legfeljebb három fordulópontja van a rajt és a cél között, és összesen legalább 25 km. A pontok arányosak a jóváírt távolsággal, 100 osztva a vitorlázó hendikeppel (DAeC-stílusú index), és a sikertényező 1,0 egy szabad repülés vagy 1,2 a felszállás előtt elektronikusan bejelentett feladat esetén. Az XCSoar élő pontozása csak 1,0-s sikertényezőt használ, a deklarált feladatok 1,2-es szorzóját nem.',
        'Previous waypoint: when an ordered task is loaded, automatically tracks the task waypoint before the active leg (the start waypoint when on the first leg). Displays the waypoint name, arrival altitude difference relative to the safety arrival height, and distance. Click to choose a different waypoint to display (task waypoints when a task is loaded, otherwise the full waypoint list); selection is informational only and never advances the task or sets a Goto. With a task loaded, choose "Resume auto tracking" at the top of the list to revert to automatic tracking.': 'Előző útpont: amikor egy megrendelt feladat betöltődik, automatikusan követi a feladat útpontját az aktív szakasz előtt (az első szakaszon a kezdő útpont). Megjeleníti az útpont nevét, a biztonságos érkezési magassághoz viszonyított érkezési magasságkülönbséget és a távolságot. Kattintson ide egy másik megjelenítési útpont kiválasztásához (feladat-útpontok a feladat betöltésekor, ellenkező esetben a teljes útpontlista); A kiválasztás csak tájékoztató jellegű, és soha nem viszi előre a feladatot, és nem állít be Goto-t. Ha egy feladat betöltődött, válassza a "Az automatikus követés folytatása" lehetőséget a lista tetején az automatikus követéshez való visszatéréshez.',
        'This parameter estimates the height%s at which the average dry updraft strength drops below 225 fpm and is expected to give better quantitative numbers for the maximum cloudless thermalling height than the BL Top height, especially when mixing results from vertical wind shear rather than thermals. (Note: the present assumptions tend to underpredict the max. thermalling height for dry conditions.) In the presence of clouds the maximum thermalling height may instead be limited by the cloud base. Being for "dry" thermals, this parameter omits the effect of "cloudsuck".': 'Ez a paraméter azt a %s magasságot becsüli meg, amelynél az átlagos száraz feláramlási szilárdság 225 fpm alá esik, és várhatóan jobb mennyiségi számokat ad a maximális felhőmentes termikus magasságra, mint a BL felső magasságra, különösen akkor, ha a függőleges szélnyírásból származó eredményeket keverik, nem pedig a hőhatásokat. (Megjegyzés: a jelenlegi feltételezések hajlamosak alábecsülni a maximális hőkezelési magasságot száraz körülmények között.) Felhők jelenlétében a maximális hőkezelési magasságot a felhőalap korlátozhatja. Mivel a "száraz" termik, ez a paraméter kihagyja a "felhőszívás" hatását.',
        '![](resource:IDB_WARNING_TRIANGLE)\n\n!!! warning\n# Important Safety Notice\n\nBy using XCSoar, you acknowledge and accept the following:\n\n## Limitations\n\n- XCSoar is for **situational awareness only**\n- XCSoar is **not** a FLARM display\n- XCSoar is **not** aviation certified in any way\n- The artificial horizon is **not** fit for any purpose\n- Databanks (airspace, waypoints) may contain errors, be incomplete, or **not** up to date\n- NOTAM display does **not** replace proper pre-flight NOTAM briefing\n- NOTAM data may be incomplete, delayed, filtered, or unavailable\n- XCSoar is **not** guaranteed to be error free\n\n## Pilot Responsibility\n\nThe **Pilot in Command** is always responsible for the safe operation of the aircraft. Never rely solely on XCSoar for navigation or situational awareness.\n\n': '![](resource:IDB_WARNING_TRIANGLE)\n\n!!! warning\n# Fontos biztonsági megjegyzés\n\nAz XCSoar használatával Ön tudomásul veszi és elfogadja a következőket:\n\n## Korlátozások\n\n- Az XCSoar a **csak helyzetfelismerés** számára készült\n- Az XCSoar egy FLARM kijelző\n- Az XCSoar bármilyen módon **nem** repülési tanúsítvánnyal rendelkezik\n- A mesterséges horizont **nem** bármilyen célra alkalmas\n- Az adatbankok (légtér, útpontok) hibákat tartalmazhatnak, hiányosak vagy **nem** naprakészek\n- A NOTAM kijelző a **nem** helyettesíti a megfelelő repülés előtti NOTAM eligazítást\n- A NOTAM-adatok hiányosak, késleltettek, szűrtek vagy nem érhetők el\n- Az XCSoar a **nem** garantáltan hibamentes\n\n## Pilóta felelőssége\n\nA **Pilóta a parancsnokságban** mindig felelős a repülőgép biztonságos üzemeltetéséért. Soha ne hagyatkozzon kizárólag az XCSoarra a navigáció vagy a helyzetfelismerés terén.\n\n',
        '# Getting Started\n\nTo use XCSoar effectively, configure the following:\n\n- [Restore from backup](xcsoar://dialog/backup) - Restore previous XCSoar data from a USB or SD card (optional)\n\n- [%s] [Map and data](xcsoar://config/site-files) - Download maps, waypoints, and airspace files for your region\n\n- [%s] [Aircraft polar](xcsoar://config/planes) - Set up your aircraft with the correct polar curve\n\n- [%s] [Pilot info](xcsoar://config/logger) - Enter your name and weight\n\n- [%s] [Devices](xcsoar://config/devices) - Connect your flight instruments\n\n- [%s] [WeGlide](xcsoar://config/weglide) - Upload flights automatically to WeGlide\n\n- [%s] [Thermal Information Map](xcsoar://config/weather) - Show thermal locations from thermalmap.info on the map\n\n- [%s] [Safety factors](xcsoar://config/safety) - Set arrival height, terrain clearance and polar degradation\n\n- [%s] [Terrain Display](xcsoar://config/terrain) - Choose terrain colors, shading and contour lines\n\n- [ ] [Live tracking](xcsoar://config/tracking) *(optional)* - Share your position via SkyLines or LiveTrack24\n\nThe easiest way to explore XCSoar is to [replay an existing IGC flight](xcsoar://dialog/replay).': '# Kezdő lépések\n\nAz XCSoar hatékony használatához konfigurálja a következőket:\n\n- [Visszaállítás biztonsági másolatból](xcsoar://dialog/backup) - Korábbi XCSoar adatok visszaállítása USB-ről vagy SD-kártyáról (opcionális)\n\n- [%s] [Térkép és adatok](xcsoar://config/site-files) - Töltsön le térképeket, útpontokat és légtérfájlokat a régiójában\n\n- [%s] [Repülőgép sarki](xcsoar://config/planes) - Állítsa be repülőgépét a megfelelő poláris görbével\n\n- [%s] [Pilóta információ](xcsoar://config/logger) - Adja meg nevét és súlyát\n\n- [%s] [Eszközök](xcsoar://config/devices) - Csatlakoztassa a repülési műszereket\n\n- [%s] [WeGlide](xcsoar://config/weglide) - Járatok automatikus feltöltése a WeGlide-ba\n\n- [%s] [Termál információs térkép](xcsoar://config/weather) - Mutassa meg a termikus helyeket a thermomap.info webhelyről a térképen\n\n- [%s] [Biztonsági tényezők](xcsoar://config/safety) - Állítsa be az érkezési magasságot, a tereptávolságot és a poláris degradációt\n\n- [%s] [Terep megjelenítése](xcsoar://config/terrain) - Válasszon terepszíneket, árnyékolást és kontúrvonalakat\n\n- [ ] [Élő követés](xcsoar://config/tracking) *(optional)* - Ossza meg pozícióját a SkyLines vagy a LiveTrack24 segítségével\n\nAz XCSoar felfedezésének legegyszerűbb módja az, hogy [egy meglévő IGC repülés újrajátszása](xcsoar://dialog/replay).',
        '# Gesture Navigation\n\nXCSoar supports touch gestures on the map:\n\n- ![U](resource:IDB_GESTURE_UP) **Swipe Up** (U): Zoom in\n- ![D](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DOWN) **Swipe Down** (D): Zoom out\n- ![R](resource:IDB_GESTURE_RIGHT) **Swipe Right** (R): Previous screen mode\n- ![L](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LEFT) **Swipe Left** (L): Next screen mode\n- ![UD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_UD) **Up-Down** (UD): Auto zoom\n- ![DU](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DU) **Down-Up** (DU): Menu\n- ![DR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DR) **Down-Right** (DR): Waypoint details\n- ![DL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DL) **Down-Left** (DL): Alternates\n- ![LU](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LU) **Left-Up** (LU): Recently used waypoints\n- ![RD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_RD) **Right-Down** (RD): Task manager\n- ![URD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_URD) **Up-Right-Down** (URD): Analysis\n- ![LDR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LDR) **Left-Down-Right** (LDR): Checklist\n- ![URDL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_URDL) **Up-Right-Down-Left** (URDL): Pan mode\n- ![LDRDL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LDRDL) **Left-Down-Right-Down-Left** (LDRDL): Status\n- ![ULDR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_ULDR) **Up-Left-Down-Right** (ULDR): Quick menu\n\nLong-press on the map to enter Pan mode. Tap while in Pan mode to see nearby waypoints.': '# Gesztus-navigáció\n\nAz XCSoar támogatja az érintési gesztusokat a térképen:\n\n- ![U](resource:IDB_GESTURE_UP) **Csúsztassa felfelé az ujját** (U): Nagyítás\n- ![D](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DOWN) **Csúsztassa lefelé az ujját** (D): Kicsinyítés\n- ![R](resource:IDB_GESTURE_RIGHT) **Csúsztasson jobbra** (R): Előző képernyő mód\n- ![L](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LEFT) **Csúsztasson balra** (L): Következő képernyő mód\n- ![UD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_UD) **Fel-Le** (UD): Automatikus zoom\n- ![DU](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DU) **Le-Fel** (DU): Menü\n- ![DR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DR) **Le-jobbra** (DR): Útpont részletei\n- ![DL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DL) **Le-balra** (DL): Alternatívák\n- ![LU](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LU) **Balra felfelé** (LU): Nemrég használt útpontok\n- ![RD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_RD) **Jobbra-Le** (RD): Feladatkezelő\n- ![URD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_URD) **Fel-Jobbra-Le** (URD): Elemzés\n- ![LDR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LDR) **Bal-Le-Jobbra** (LDR): Ellenőrző lista\n- ![URDL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_URDL) **Fel-jobbra-le-balra** (URDL): Pan mód\n- ![LDRDL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LDRDL) **Balra-Le-Jobbra-Le-Balra** (LDRDL): Állapot\n- ![ULDR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_ULDR) **Fel-Bal-Le-Jobbra** (ULDR): Gyors menü\n\nNyomja meg hosszan a térképet a Pásztázás módba lépéshez. Érintse meg Pan módban a közeli útpontok megtekintéséhez.',
    },
    "it": {
        'Size of waypoint symbols on the map as a percentage of the built-in artwork (list dialogs keep a fixed row icon size).': "Dimensioni dei simboli dei waypoint sulla mappa come percentuale della grafica incorporata (le finestre di dialogo dell'elenco mantengono una dimensione fissa dell'icona della riga).",
        'Home waypoint name, arrival altitude difference relative to the safety arrival height, and distance. Click to change the home waypoint.': "Nome del waypoint di casa, differenza di altitudine di arrivo rispetto all'altezza di arrivo di sicurezza e distanza. Fare clic per modificare il waypoint di casa.",
        'Current QNH pressure setting used for barometric altitude calculation. Tap the infobox to open the setup panel and adjust QNH manually.': "Impostazione attuale della pressione QNH utilizzata per il calcolo dell'altitudine barometrica. Tocca la casella delle informazioni per aprire il pannello di configurazione e regolare manualmente il QNH.",
        'This page shows WiFi status when NetworkManager or ConnMan is on D-Bus (e.g. Linux with Wayland or KMS). Open WiFi list to scan and connect when a service is available.': "Questa pagina mostra lo stato del WiFi quando NetworkManager o ConnMan è su D-Bus (ad esempio Linux con Wayland o KMS). Apri l'elenco WiFi per scansionare e connetterti quando un servizio è disponibile.",
        'The terrain can be shaded among slopes to indicate either wind direction, sun position, a geographically fixed shading from North-West, or a screen-relative fixed shading from top left.': "Il terreno può essere ombreggiato tra i pendii per indicare la direzione del vento, la posizione del sole, un'ombreggiatura geograficamente fissa da nord-ovest o un'ombreggiatura fissa relativa allo schermo dall'alto a sinistra.",
        "Synchronize the glide polar between XCSoar and the device (LXNAV varios). 'Receive' adopts the polar from the device (e.g. for club gliders). 'Send' pushes XCSoar's polar to the device.": "Sincronizza la planata polare tra XCSoar e il dispositivo (vari LXNAV). 'Ricevi' adotta la polare dal dispositivo (ad esempio per gli alianti del club). 'Invia' invia la polare di XCSoar al dispositivo.",
        'List of active airspace files. Use the Add and Remove buttons to activate or deactivate airspace files respectively. Supported file types are: Openair (.openair /.txt /.air), and Tim Newport-Pearce (.sua).': 'Elenco dei file di spazio aereo attivi. Utilizzare i pulsanti Aggiungi e Rimuovi rispettivamente per attivare o disattivare i file dello spazio aereo. I tipi di file supportati sono: Openair (.openair /.txt /.air) e Tim Newport-Pearce (.sua).',
        'Signed countdown until the start gate opens or closes (now). Value colour and secondary line reflect gate state at the current time: Waiting (blue), Open (green), Closed (red). PEV window overrides task gate when set.': "Conto alla rovescia firmato fino all'apertura o chiusura del cancello di partenza (ora). Il colore del valore e la linea secondaria riflettono lo stato del gate al momento corrente: In attesa (blu), Aperto (verde), Chiuso (rosso). La finestra PEV sovrascrive il gate delle attività quando impostata.",
        'Tells XCSoar to send its current GPS position to the device as $GPGGA and $GPRMC sentences. Turn off when another GPS source is already feeding the device on the same line. Changes take effect after reconnecting the device.': "Indica a XCSoar di inviare la sua posizione GPS corrente al dispositivo come frasi $GPGGA e $GPRMC. Spegnere quando un'altra sorgente GPS sta già alimentando il dispositivo sulla stessa linea. Le modifiche diventano effettive dopo aver ricollegato il dispositivo.",
        'Logger pressure altitude when the device provides it (igc_pressure_altitude), otherwise ISA pressure altitude only (1013.25 hPa; not QNH-corrected). Does not show barometric AMSL or GPS height — use other InfoBoxes for navigation.': "Altitudine pressione del registratore quando fornita dal dispositivo (igc_pression_altitude), altrimenti solo altitudine pressione ISA (1013,25 hPa; non corretta QNH). Non mostra l'AMSL barometrico o l'altezza GPS: utilizza altri InfoBox per la navigazione.",
        'Same gate as Start open. Main value is estimated time to reach the start line (MacCready leg when available, else distance / ground speed). Value colour and secondary line reflect gate state at that ETA: Too early (blue), Can start (green), Too late (red).': "Stesso cancello di Start aperto. Il valore principale è il tempo stimato per raggiungere la linea di partenza (tappa MacCready quando disponibile, altrimenti distanza/velocità al suolo). Il colore del valore e la linea secondaria riflettono lo stato del cancello a quell'ETA: Troppo presto (blu), Può iniziare (verde), Troppo tardi (rosso).",
        'Active waypoint: shows the next task waypoint when an ordered task is loaded, otherwise the Goto waypoint. Displays the waypoint name, arrival altitude difference relative to the safety arrival height, and distance. Click to choose a different waypoint (a task waypoint to skip to that leg, or any waypoint to set as Goto when no task is loaded).': "Waypoint attivo: mostra il waypoint dell'attività successiva quando viene caricata un'attività ordinata, altrimenti il \u200b\u200bwaypoint Vai a. Visualizza il nome del waypoint, la differenza di altitudine di arrivo rispetto all'altezza di arrivo di sicurezza e la distanza. Fare clic per scegliere un punto di passaggio diverso (un punto di passaggio di un'attività da saltare a quella tratta o qualsiasi punto di passaggio da impostare come Vai a quando non è caricata alcuna attività).",
        'FFVP Federal Cup (NetCoupe) on WeGlide. The scored path has at most three turnpoints between start and finish and at least 25 km total. Points are proportional to credited distance, 100 divided by the glider handicap (DAeC-style index), and a success factor of 1.0 for a free flight or 1.2 for a task declared electronically before takeoff. XCSoar live scoring uses a success factor of 1.0 only, not the 1.2 multiplier for declared tasks.': "Coppa federale FFVP (NetCoupe) su WeGlide. Il percorso segnato prevede al massimo tre punti di svolta tra partenza e arrivo e almeno 25 km totali. I punti sono proporzionali alla distanza accreditata, 100 diviso per l'handicap dell'aliante (indice stile DAeC) e un fattore di successo pari a 1,0 per un volo libero o 1,2 per una task dichiarata elettronicamente prima del decollo. Il punteggio in tempo reale di XCSoar utilizza solo un fattore di successo pari a 1,0, non il moltiplicatore 1,2 per le attività dichiarate.",
        'Previous waypoint: when an ordered task is loaded, automatically tracks the task waypoint before the active leg (the start waypoint when on the first leg). Displays the waypoint name, arrival altitude difference relative to the safety arrival height, and distance. Click to choose a different waypoint to display (task waypoints when a task is loaded, otherwise the full waypoint list); selection is informational only and never advances the task or sets a Goto. With a task loaded, choose "Resume auto tracking" at the top of the list to revert to automatic tracking.': 'Waypoint precedente: quando viene caricata un\'attività ordinata, traccia automaticamente il waypoint dell\'attività prima della tratta attiva (il waypoint iniziale quando si è sulla prima tratta). Visualizza il nome del waypoint, la differenza di altitudine di arrivo rispetto all\'altezza di arrivo di sicurezza e la distanza. Fare clic per scegliere un punto di passaggio diverso da visualizzare (i punti di passaggio dell\'attività quando viene caricata un\'attività, altrimenti l\'elenco completo dei punti di passaggio); la selezione è solo informativa e non fa mai avanzare l\'attività né imposta un Vai a. Con un\'attività caricata, scegli "Riprendi il monitoraggio automatico" nella parte superiore dell\'elenco per ripristinare il monitoraggio automatico.',
        'This parameter estimates the height%s at which the average dry updraft strength drops below 225 fpm and is expected to give better quantitative numbers for the maximum cloudless thermalling height than the BL Top height, especially when mixing results from vertical wind shear rather than thermals. (Note: the present assumptions tend to underpredict the max. thermalling height for dry conditions.) In the presence of clouds the maximum thermalling height may instead be limited by the cloud base. Being for "dry" thermals, this parameter omits the effect of "cloudsuck".': 'Questo parametro stima l\'altezza%s alla quale la forza media della corrente ascensionale asciutta scende al di sotto di 225 fpm e si prevede che dia numeri quantitativi migliori per l\'altezza massima di termica senza nuvole rispetto all\'altezza BL Top, specialmente quando si mescolano i risultati del wind shear verticale piuttosto che delle termiche. (Nota: le presenti ipotesi tendono a sottostimare l\'altezza massima per la termica in condizioni asciutte.) In presenza di nuvole l\'altezza massima per la termica può invece essere limitata dalla base delle nuvole. Essendo per le termiche "asciutte", questo parametro omette l\'effetto del "risucchio delle nuvole".',
        '![](resource:IDB_WARNING_TRIANGLE)\n\n!!! warning\n# Important Safety Notice\n\nBy using XCSoar, you acknowledge and accept the following:\n\n## Limitations\n\n- XCSoar is for **situational awareness only**\n- XCSoar is **not** a FLARM display\n- XCSoar is **not** aviation certified in any way\n- The artificial horizon is **not** fit for any purpose\n- Databanks (airspace, waypoints) may contain errors, be incomplete, or **not** up to date\n- NOTAM display does **not** replace proper pre-flight NOTAM briefing\n- NOTAM data may be incomplete, delayed, filtered, or unavailable\n- XCSoar is **not** guaranteed to be error free\n\n## Pilot Responsibility\n\nThe **Pilot in Command** is always responsible for the safe operation of the aircraft. Never rely solely on XCSoar for navigation or situational awareness.\n\n': "![](resource:IDB_WARNING_TRIANGLE)\n\n!!! warning\n# Avviso importante sulla sicurezza\n\nUtilizzando XCSoar, riconosci e accetti quanto segue:\n\n## Limitazioni\n\n- XCSoar è per **solo consapevolezza situazionale**\n- XCSoar è **non** un display FLARM\n- XCSoar è in alcun modo certificato per l'aviazione **non**\n- L'orizzonte artificiale è **non** adatto a qualsiasi scopo\n- Le banche dati (spazio aereo, waypoint) possono contenere errori, essere incomplete o **non** aggiornate\n- La visualizzazione NOTAM **non** sostituisce il corretto briefing NOTAM pre-volo\n- I dati NOTAM potrebbero essere incompleti, ritardati, filtrati o non disponibili\n- XCSoar garantisce che **non** sia privo di errori\n\n## Responsabilità del pilota\n\nLo **Pilota al comando** è sempre responsabile del funzionamento sicuro dell'aeromobile. Non fare mai affidamento esclusivamente su XCSoar per la navigazione o la consapevolezza della situazione.\n\n",
        '# Getting Started\n\nTo use XCSoar effectively, configure the following:\n\n- [Restore from backup](xcsoar://dialog/backup) - Restore previous XCSoar data from a USB or SD card (optional)\n\n- [%s] [Map and data](xcsoar://config/site-files) - Download maps, waypoints, and airspace files for your region\n\n- [%s] [Aircraft polar](xcsoar://config/planes) - Set up your aircraft with the correct polar curve\n\n- [%s] [Pilot info](xcsoar://config/logger) - Enter your name and weight\n\n- [%s] [Devices](xcsoar://config/devices) - Connect your flight instruments\n\n- [%s] [WeGlide](xcsoar://config/weglide) - Upload flights automatically to WeGlide\n\n- [%s] [Thermal Information Map](xcsoar://config/weather) - Show thermal locations from thermalmap.info on the map\n\n- [%s] [Safety factors](xcsoar://config/safety) - Set arrival height, terrain clearance and polar degradation\n\n- [%s] [Terrain Display](xcsoar://config/terrain) - Choose terrain colors, shading and contour lines\n\n- [ ] [Live tracking](xcsoar://config/tracking) *(optional)* - Share your position via SkyLines or LiveTrack24\n\nThe easiest way to explore XCSoar is to [replay an existing IGC flight](xcsoar://dialog/replay).': "# Iniziare\n\nPer utilizzare XCSoar in modo efficace, configura quanto segue:\n\n- [Ripristina dal backup](xcsoar://dialog/backup) - Ripristina i dati XCSoar precedenti da una scheda USB o SD (opzionale)\n\n- [%s] [Mappa e dati](xcsoar://config/site-files) - Scarica mappe, waypoint e file di spazio aereo per la tua regione\n\n- [%s] [Polare dell'aereo](xcsoar://config/planes) - Imposta il tuo aereo con la curva polare corretta\n\n- [%s] [Informazioni sul pilota](xcsoar://config/logger) - Inserisci il tuo nome e peso\n\n- [%s] [Dispositivi](xcsoar://config/devices) - Collega i tuoi strumenti di volo\n\n- [%s] [WeGlide](xcsoar://config/weglide) - Carica automaticamente i voli su WeGlide\n\n- [%s] [Mappa delle informazioni termiche](xcsoar://config/weather) - Mostra le posizioni termiche da Thermalmap.info sulla mappa\n\n- [%s] [Fattori di sicurezza](xcsoar://config/safety) - Imposta l'altezza di arrivo, la distanza dal terreno e il degrado polare\n\n- [%s] [Visualizzazione del terreno](xcsoar://config/terrain) - Scegli i colori del terreno, l'ombreggiatura e le linee di contorno\n\n- [ ] [Monitoraggio in tempo reale](xcsoar://config/tracking) *(optional)* - Condividi la tua posizione tramite SkyLines o LiveTrack24\n\nIl modo più semplice per esplorare XCSoar è farlo [riprodurre un volo IGC esistente](xcsoar://dialog/replay).",
        '# Gesture Navigation\n\nXCSoar supports touch gestures on the map:\n\n- ![U](resource:IDB_GESTURE_UP) **Swipe Up** (U): Zoom in\n- ![D](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DOWN) **Swipe Down** (D): Zoom out\n- ![R](resource:IDB_GESTURE_RIGHT) **Swipe Right** (R): Previous screen mode\n- ![L](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LEFT) **Swipe Left** (L): Next screen mode\n- ![UD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_UD) **Up-Down** (UD): Auto zoom\n- ![DU](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DU) **Down-Up** (DU): Menu\n- ![DR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DR) **Down-Right** (DR): Waypoint details\n- ![DL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DL) **Down-Left** (DL): Alternates\n- ![LU](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LU) **Left-Up** (LU): Recently used waypoints\n- ![RD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_RD) **Right-Down** (RD): Task manager\n- ![URD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_URD) **Up-Right-Down** (URD): Analysis\n- ![LDR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LDR) **Left-Down-Right** (LDR): Checklist\n- ![URDL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_URDL) **Up-Right-Down-Left** (URDL): Pan mode\n- ![LDRDL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LDRDL) **Left-Down-Right-Down-Left** (LDRDL): Status\n- ![ULDR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_ULDR) **Up-Left-Down-Right** (ULDR): Quick menu\n\nLong-press on the map to enter Pan mode. Tap while in Pan mode to see nearby waypoints.': "# Navigazione gestuale\n\nXCSoar supporta i gesti tattili sulla mappa:\n\n- ![U](resource:IDB_GESTURE_UP) **Scorri verso l'alto** (U): Ingrandisci\n- ![D](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DOWN) **Scorri verso il basso** (D): Rimpicciolisci\n- ![R](resource:IDB_GESTURE_RIGHT) **Scorri verso destra** (R): Modalità schermata precedente\n- ![L](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LEFT) **Scorri verso sinistra** (L): Modalità schermata successiva\n- ![UD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_UD) **Su-Giù** (UD): Zoom automatico\n- ![DU](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DU) **Giù-su** (DU): Menu\n- ![DR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DR) **In basso a destra** (DR): Dettagli del punto di passaggio\n- ![DL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DL) **In basso a sinistra** (DL): Supplenti\n- ![LU](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LU) **A sinistra in alto** (LU): Waypoint utilizzati di recente\n- ![RD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_RD) **Giù a destra** (RD): Responsabile attività\n- ![URD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_URD) **Su-Destra-Giù** (URD): Analisi\n- ![LDR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LDR) **Sinistra-Giù-Destra** (LDR): Lista di controllo\n- ![URDL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_URDL) **Su-Destra-Giù-Sinistra** (URDL): Modalità panoramica\n- ![LDRDL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LDRDL) **Sinistra-Giù-Destra-Giù-Sinistra** (LDRDL): Stato\n- ![ULDR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_ULDR) **Su-Sinistra-Giù-Destra** (ULDR): Menù veloce\n\nPremi a lungo sulla mappa per accedere alla modalità Pan. Tocca in modalità Panoramica per visualizzare i punti di passaggio nelle vicinanze.",
    },
    "ja": {
        'Size of waypoint symbols on the map as a percentage of the built-in artwork (list dialogs keep a fixed row icon size).': 'マップ上のウェイポイント シンボルのサイズ (組み込みアートワークのパーセンテージとして) (リスト ダイアログでは行アイコンのサイズが固定されます)。',
        'Home waypoint name, arrival altitude difference relative to the safety arrival height, and distance. Click to change the home waypoint.': 'ホームウェイポイント名、安全到着高度に対する到着高度差、および距離。クリックしてホームウェイポイントを変更します。',
        'Current QNH pressure setting used for barometric altitude calculation. Tap the infobox to open the setup panel and adjust QNH manually.': '気圧高度の計算に使用される現在の QNH 圧力設定。情報ボックスをタップしてセットアップ パネルを開き、QNH を手動で調整します。',
        'This page shows WiFi status when NetworkManager or ConnMan is on D-Bus (e.g. Linux with Wayland or KMS). Open WiFi list to scan and connect when a service is available.': 'このページには、NetworkManager または ConnMan が D-Bus 上にある場合 (例: Wayland または KMS を備えた Linux) の WiFi ステータスが表示されます。 WiFi リストを開いて、サービスが利用可能な場合にスキャンして接続します。',
        'The terrain can be shaded among slopes to indicate either wind direction, sun position, a geographically fixed shading from North-West, or a screen-relative fixed shading from top left.': '斜面間で地形をシェーディングして、風向き、太陽の位置、北西からの地理的に固定されたシェーディング、または左上からの画面相対の固定シェーディングのいずれかを示すことができます。',
        "Synchronize the glide polar between XCSoar and the device (LXNAV varios). 'Receive' adopts the polar from the device (e.g. for club gliders). 'Send' pushes XCSoar's polar to the device.": 'XCSoar とデバイス (LXNAV varios) の間でグライド極を同期します。 「受信」はデバイスからの極を採用します（クラブグライダーなど）。 「送信」は、XCSoar の極性をデバイスにプッシュします。',
        'List of active airspace files. Use the Add and Remove buttons to activate or deactivate airspace files respectively. Supported file types are: Openair (.openair /.txt /.air), and Tim Newport-Pearce (.sua).': 'アクティブな空域ファイルのリスト。 [追加] ボタンと [削除] ボタンを使用して、空域ファイルをそれぞれアクティブまたは非アクティブにします。サポートされているファイルの種類は、Openair (.openair /.txt /.air)、および Tim Newport-Pearce (.sua) です。',
        'Signed countdown until the start gate opens or closes (now). Value colour and secondary line reflect gate state at the current time: Waiting (blue), Open (green), Closed (red). PEV window overrides task gate when set.': 'スタートゲートが開閉するまでのサイン入りカウントダウン（現在）。値の色と二次線は、現時点でのゲートの状態を反映します: 待機中 (青)、オープン (緑)、クローズド (赤)。 PEV ウィンドウは、設定されている場合にタスク ゲートをオーバーライドします。',
        'Tells XCSoar to send its current GPS position to the device as $GPGGA and $GPRMC sentences. Turn off when another GPS source is already feeding the device on the same line. Changes take effect after reconnecting the device.': '現在の GPS 位置を $GPGGA および $GPRMC センテンスとしてデバイスに送信するように XCSoar に指示します。別の GPS ソースが同じ回線ですでにデバイスに信号を供給している場合はオフにします。変更はデバイスを再接続した後に有効になります。',
        'Logger pressure altitude when the device provides it (igc_pressure_altitude), otherwise ISA pressure altitude only (1013.25 hPa; not QNH-corrected). Does not show barometric AMSL or GPS height — use other InfoBoxes for navigation.': 'デバイスが提供する場合はロガー気圧高度 (igc_pressure_altitude)、それ以外の場合は ISA 気圧高度のみ (1013.25 hPa、QNH 補正なし)。 AMSL または GPS の気圧高度は表示されません。ナビゲーションには他の InfoBox を使用してください。',
        'Same gate as Start open. Main value is estimated time to reach the start line (MacCready leg when available, else distance / ground speed). Value colour and secondary line reflect gate state at that ETA: Too early (blue), Can start (green), Too late (red).': 'スタートと同じゲートが開きます。主な値は、スタートラインに到達するまでの推定時間 (利用可能な場合はマクレディレッグ、それ以外の場合は距離/対地速度) です。値の色とセカンダリ ラインは、ETA でのゲートの状態を反映します。早すぎる (青)、開始可能 (緑)、遅すぎる (赤)。',
        'Active waypoint: shows the next task waypoint when an ordered task is loaded, otherwise the Goto waypoint. Displays the waypoint name, arrival altitude difference relative to the safety arrival height, and distance. Click to choose a different waypoint (a task waypoint to skip to that leg, or any waypoint to set as Goto when no task is loaded).': 'アクティブなウェイポイント: 順序付けされたタスクがロードされると次のタスクのウェイポイントが表示され、それ以外の場合は Goto ウェイポイントが表示されます。ウェイポイント名、安全到着高度に対する到着高度差、距離を表示します。クリックして別のウェイポイント (その区間までスキップするタスク ウェイポイント、またはタスクがロードされていないときにジャンプとして設定する任意のウェイポイント) を選択します。',
        'FFVP Federal Cup (NetCoupe) on WeGlide. The scored path has at most three turnpoints between start and finish and at least 25 km total. Points are proportional to credited distance, 100 divided by the glider handicap (DAeC-style index), and a success factor of 1.0 for a free flight or 1.2 for a task declared electronically before takeoff. XCSoar live scoring uses a success factor of 1.0 only, not the 1.2 multiplier for declared tasks.': 'WeGlide の FFVP フェデラル カップ (NetCoupe)。スコア付きのパスには、スタートとフィニッシュの間に最大 3 つのターンポイントがあり、合計は少なくとも 25 km です。ポイントは、クレジットされた距離に比例し、100 をグライダーのハンディキャップ (DAeC スタイルの指数) で割ったもので、成功係数はフリーフライトの場合は 1.0、離陸前に電子的に宣言されたタスクの場合は 1.2 です。 XCSoar ライブ スコアリングでは、宣言されたタスクの乗数 1.2 ではなく、成功係数 1.0 のみが使用されます。',
        'Previous waypoint: when an ordered task is loaded, automatically tracks the task waypoint before the active leg (the start waypoint when on the first leg). Displays the waypoint name, arrival altitude difference relative to the safety arrival height, and distance. Click to choose a different waypoint to display (task waypoints when a task is loaded, otherwise the full waypoint list); selection is informational only and never advances the task or sets a Goto. With a task loaded, choose "Resume auto tracking" at the top of the list to revert to automatic tracking.': '前のウェイポイント: 順序付けされたタスクがロードされると、アクティブなレグの前のタスク ウェイポイント (最初のレグの場合は開始ウェイポイント) を自動的に追跡します。ウェイポイント名、安全到着高度に対する到着高度差、距離を表示します。クリックして、表示する別のウェイポイントを選択します (タスクがロードされている場合はタスク ウェイポイント、それ以外の場合は完全なウェイポイント リスト)。選択は情報提供のみを目的としており、タスクを進めたり、Goto を設定したりすることはありません。タスクがロードされたら、リストの先頭にある "自動追跡を再開する" を選択して自動追跡に戻します。',
        'This parameter estimates the height%s at which the average dry updraft strength drops below 225 fpm and is expected to give better quantitative numbers for the maximum cloudless thermalling height than the BL Top height, especially when mixing results from vertical wind shear rather than thermals. (Note: the present assumptions tend to underpredict the max. thermalling height for dry conditions.) In the presence of clouds the maximum thermalling height may instead be limited by the cloud base. Being for "dry" thermals, this parameter omits the effect of "cloudsuck".': 'このパラメータは、平均乾燥上昇気流の強さが 225 fpm を下回る高さ %s を推定し、特にサーマルではなく垂直ウィンドシアによる結果を混合する場合、雲のないサーマルの最大高さについて BL Top の高さよりも優れた定量的な数値を与えることが期待されます。 (注: 現在の仮定は、乾燥状態での最大サーマル高さを過小予測する傾向があります。) 雲が存在する場合、最大サーマル高さは代わりに雲底によって制限される可能性があります。 「ドライ」サーマル用であるため、このパラメータは「雲吸い」の影響を省略します。',
        '![](resource:IDB_WARNING_TRIANGLE)\n\n!!! warning\n# Important Safety Notice\n\nBy using XCSoar, you acknowledge and accept the following:\n\n## Limitations\n\n- XCSoar is for **situational awareness only**\n- XCSoar is **not** a FLARM display\n- XCSoar is **not** aviation certified in any way\n- The artificial horizon is **not** fit for any purpose\n- Databanks (airspace, waypoints) may contain errors, be incomplete, or **not** up to date\n- NOTAM display does **not** replace proper pre-flight NOTAM briefing\n- NOTAM data may be incomplete, delayed, filtered, or unavailable\n- XCSoar is **not** guaranteed to be error free\n\n## Pilot Responsibility\n\nThe **Pilot in Command** is always responsible for the safe operation of the aircraft. Never rely solely on XCSoar for navigation or situational awareness.\n\n': '![](resource:IDB_WARNING_TRIANGLE)\n\n!!! warning\n# 安全に関する重要なお知らせ\n\nXCSoar を使用すると、次のことを承認し、受け入れることになります。\n\n## 制限事項\n\n- XCSoar は **状況認識のみ** 用です\n- XCSoar は **ない** FLARM ディスプレイです\n- XCSoar は何らかの形で **ない** 航空認定を受けています\n- 人工地平線はどんな目的にもフィットする**ない**です\n- データバンク (空域、ウェイポイント) にエラーが含まれているか、不完全であるか、**ない** が最新である可能性があります\n- NOTAM 表示 **ない** は適切な飛行前の NOTAM ブリーフィングに代わるものですか\n- NOTAM データは不完全、遅延、フィルタリングされている、または利用できない可能性があります\n- XCSoar はエラーがないことが保証された **ない** です\n\n## パイロットの責任\n\n**パイロットの指揮官** は常に航空機の安全な運航に責任を負います。ナビゲーションや状況認識を XCSoar だけに依存しないでください。\n\n',
        '# Getting Started\n\nTo use XCSoar effectively, configure the following:\n\n- [Restore from backup](xcsoar://dialog/backup) - Restore previous XCSoar data from a USB or SD card (optional)\n\n- [%s] [Map and data](xcsoar://config/site-files) - Download maps, waypoints, and airspace files for your region\n\n- [%s] [Aircraft polar](xcsoar://config/planes) - Set up your aircraft with the correct polar curve\n\n- [%s] [Pilot info](xcsoar://config/logger) - Enter your name and weight\n\n- [%s] [Devices](xcsoar://config/devices) - Connect your flight instruments\n\n- [%s] [WeGlide](xcsoar://config/weglide) - Upload flights automatically to WeGlide\n\n- [%s] [Thermal Information Map](xcsoar://config/weather) - Show thermal locations from thermalmap.info on the map\n\n- [%s] [Safety factors](xcsoar://config/safety) - Set arrival height, terrain clearance and polar degradation\n\n- [%s] [Terrain Display](xcsoar://config/terrain) - Choose terrain colors, shading and contour lines\n\n- [ ] [Live tracking](xcsoar://config/tracking) *(optional)* - Share your position via SkyLines or LiveTrack24\n\nThe easiest way to explore XCSoar is to [replay an existing IGC flight](xcsoar://dialog/replay).': '# はじめる\n\nXCSoar を効果的に使用するには、次のように設定します。\n\n- [バックアップから復元する](xcsoar://dialog/backup) - USB または SD カードから以前の XCSoar データを復元します (オプション)\n\n- [%s] [地図とデータ](xcsoar://config/site-files) - お住まいの地域の地図、ウェイポイント、空域ファイルをダウンロードします\n\n- [%s] [航空機極地](xcsoar://config/planes) - 正しい極曲線を使用して航空機をセットアップします\n\n- [%s] [パイロット情報](xcsoar://config/logger) - 名前と体重を入力してください\n\n- [%s] [デバイス](xcsoar://config/devices) - 飛行計器を接続する\n\n- [%s] [ウィーグライド](xcsoar://config/weglide) - フライトを WeGlide に自動的にアップロードする\n\n- [%s] [熱情報マップ](xcsoar://config/weather) - Thermalmap.info からの熱位置を地図上に表示します\n\n- [%s] [安全係数](xcsoar://config/safety) - 到着高度、地形クリアランス、極地劣化を設定します\n\n- [%s] [地形表示](xcsoar://config/terrain) - 地形の色、陰影、等高線を選択します\n\n- [ ] [ライブトラッキング](xcsoar://config/tracking) *(optional)* - SkyLines または LiveTrack24 経由で自分の位置を共有します\n\nXCSoar を探索する最も簡単な方法は、次のとおりです。 [既存の IGC フライトを再生する](xcsoar://dialog/replay).',
        '# Gesture Navigation\n\nXCSoar supports touch gestures on the map:\n\n- ![U](resource:IDB_GESTURE_UP) **Swipe Up** (U): Zoom in\n- ![D](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DOWN) **Swipe Down** (D): Zoom out\n- ![R](resource:IDB_GESTURE_RIGHT) **Swipe Right** (R): Previous screen mode\n- ![L](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LEFT) **Swipe Left** (L): Next screen mode\n- ![UD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_UD) **Up-Down** (UD): Auto zoom\n- ![DU](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DU) **Down-Up** (DU): Menu\n- ![DR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DR) **Down-Right** (DR): Waypoint details\n- ![DL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DL) **Down-Left** (DL): Alternates\n- ![LU](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LU) **Left-Up** (LU): Recently used waypoints\n- ![RD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_RD) **Right-Down** (RD): Task manager\n- ![URD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_URD) **Up-Right-Down** (URD): Analysis\n- ![LDR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LDR) **Left-Down-Right** (LDR): Checklist\n- ![URDL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_URDL) **Up-Right-Down-Left** (URDL): Pan mode\n- ![LDRDL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LDRDL) **Left-Down-Right-Down-Left** (LDRDL): Status\n- ![ULDR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_ULDR) **Up-Left-Down-Right** (ULDR): Quick menu\n\nLong-press on the map to enter Pan mode. Tap while in Pan mode to see nearby waypoints.': '# ジェスチャーナビゲーション\n\nXCSoar は、地図上でのタッチ ジェスチャをサポートしています。\n\n- ![U](resource:IDB_GESTURE_UP) **上にスワイプ** (U): ズームイン\n- ![D](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DOWN) **下にスワイプ** (D): ズームアウト\n- ![R](resource:IDB_GESTURE_RIGHT) **右にスワイプ** (R): 以前の画面モード\n- ![L](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LEFT) **左にスワイプ** (L): 次の画面モード\n- ![UD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_UD) **アップダウン** (UD): オートズーム\n- ![DU](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DU) **ダウンアップ** (DU): メニュー\n- ![DR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DR) **右下** (DR): ウェイポイントの詳細\n- ![DL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DL) **左下** (DL): 代替品\n- ![LU](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LU) **左上** (LU): 最近使用したウェイポイント\n- ![RD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_RD) **右下** (RD): タスクマネージャー\n- ![URD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_URD) **上下左右** (URD): 分析\n- ![LDR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LDR) **左-下-右** (LDR): チェックリスト\n- ![URDL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_URDL) **上-右-下-左** (URDL): パンモード\n- ![LDRDL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LDRDL) **左-下-右-下-左** (LDRDL): 状態\n- ![ULDR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_ULDR) **上-左-下-右** (ULDR): クイックメニュー\n\nマップを長押ししてパン モードに入ります。パン モード中にタップすると、近くのウェイポイントが表示されます。',
    },
    "ko": {
        'Size of waypoint symbols on the map as a percentage of the built-in artwork (list dialogs keep a fixed row icon size).': '내장 아트워크의 백분율로 표시되는 지도의 웨이포인트 기호 크기(목록 대화 상자는 고정된 행 아이콘 크기를 유지함)',
        'Home waypoint name, arrival altitude difference relative to the safety arrival height, and distance. Click to change the home waypoint.': '홈 웨이포인트 이름, 안전 도착 고도를 기준으로 한 도착 고도 차이 및 거리. 홈 웨이포인트를 변경하려면 클릭하세요.',
        'Current QNH pressure setting used for barometric altitude calculation. Tap the infobox to open the setup panel and adjust QNH manually.': '기압 고도 계산에 사용되는 현재 QNH 압력 설정입니다. 정보 상자를 눌러 설정 패널을 열고 QNH를 수동으로 조정하세요.',
        'This page shows WiFi status when NetworkManager or ConnMan is on D-Bus (e.g. Linux with Wayland or KMS). Open WiFi list to scan and connect when a service is available.': '이 페이지에는 NetworkManager 또는 ConnMan이 D-Bus(예: Wayland 또는 KMS가 포함된 Linux)에 있을 때 WiFi 상태가 표시됩니다. 서비스를 사용할 수 있을 때 WiFi 목록을 열어 검색하고 연결하세요.',
        'The terrain can be shaded among slopes to indicate either wind direction, sun position, a geographically fixed shading from North-West, or a screen-relative fixed shading from top left.': '경사면 사이에 지형을 음영 처리하여 바람 방향, 태양 위치, 북서쪽의 지리적으로 고정된 음영 또는 왼쪽 상단의 화면 기준 고정 음영을 나타낼 수 있습니다.',
        "Synchronize the glide polar between XCSoar and the device (LXNAV varios). 'Receive' adopts the polar from the device (e.g. for club gliders). 'Send' pushes XCSoar's polar to the device.": "XCSoar와 장치(LXNAV varios) 사이의 활공 극성을 동기화합니다. '수신'은 장치의 폴라를 채택합니다(예: 클럽 글라이더의 경우). '보내기'는 XCSoar의 극성을 장치로 푸시합니다.",
        'List of active airspace files. Use the Add and Remove buttons to activate or deactivate airspace files respectively. Supported file types are: Openair (.openair /.txt /.air), and Tim Newport-Pearce (.sua).': '활성 공역 파일 목록. 추가 및 제거 버튼을 사용하여 영공 파일을 각각 활성화하거나 비활성화합니다. 지원되는 파일 형식은 Openair(.openair /.txt /.air) 및 Tim Newport-Pearce(.sua)입니다.',
        'Signed countdown until the start gate opens or closes (now). Value colour and secondary line reflect gate state at the current time: Waiting (blue), Open (green), Closed (red). PEV window overrides task gate when set.': '시작 게이트가 열리거나 닫힐 때까지(현재) 서명된 카운트다운입니다. 값 색상과 보조 라인은 현재 시간의 게이트 상태를 반영합니다: 대기(파란색), 열림(녹색), 닫힘(빨간색). PEV 창이 설정되면 작업 게이트를 재정의합니다.',
        'Tells XCSoar to send its current GPS position to the device as $GPGGA and $GPRMC sentences. Turn off when another GPS source is already feeding the device on the same line. Changes take effect after reconnecting the device.': 'XCSoar에게 현재 GPS 위치를 $GPGGA 및 $GPRMC 문장으로 장치에 보내도록 지시합니다. 다른 GPS 소스가 이미 동일한 회선에서 장치에 신호를 공급하고 있으면 끄십시오. 변경 사항은 장치를 다시 연결한 후에 적용됩니다.',
        'Logger pressure altitude when the device provides it (igc_pressure_altitude), otherwise ISA pressure altitude only (1013.25 hPa; not QNH-corrected). Does not show barometric AMSL or GPS height — use other InfoBoxes for navigation.': '장치가 제공하는 경우 로거 압력 고도(igc_press_altitude), 그렇지 않은 경우 ISA 압력 고도만(1013.25hPa, QNH 보정 아님). 기압계 AMSL 또는 GPS 높이를 표시하지 않습니다. 탐색을 위해 다른 InfoBox를 사용하십시오.',
        'Same gate as Start open. Main value is estimated time to reach the start line (MacCready leg when available, else distance / ground speed). Value colour and secondary line reflect gate state at that ETA: Too early (blue), Can start (green), Too late (red).': 'Start와 동일한 게이트가 열립니다. 주요 값은 출발선에 도달하는 데 걸리는 예상 시간입니다(사용 가능한 경우 MacCready 구간, 그렇지 않은 경우 거리/지상 속도). 값 색상과 보조 선은 해당 ETA의 게이트 상태를 반영합니다. 너무 이르다(파란색), 시작할 수 있음(녹색), 너무 늦음(빨간색).',
        'Active waypoint: shows the next task waypoint when an ordered task is loaded, otherwise the Goto waypoint. Displays the waypoint name, arrival altitude difference relative to the safety arrival height, and distance. Click to choose a different waypoint (a task waypoint to skip to that leg, or any waypoint to set as Goto when no task is loaded).': '활성 경유지: 주문된 작업이 로드되면 다음 작업 경유지를 표시하고, 그렇지 않으면 Goto 경유지를 표시합니다. 웨이포인트 이름, 안전 도착 고도를 기준으로 한 도착 고도 차이, 거리를 표시합니다. 다른 웨이포인트(해당 구간으로 건너뛰기 위한 작업 웨이포인트 또는 작업이 로드되지 않았을 때 Goto로 설정할 웨이포인트)를 선택하려면 클릭하세요.',
        'FFVP Federal Cup (NetCoupe) on WeGlide. The scored path has at most three turnpoints between start and finish and at least 25 km total. Points are proportional to credited distance, 100 divided by the glider handicap (DAeC-style index), and a success factor of 1.0 for a free flight or 1.2 for a task declared electronically before takeoff. XCSoar live scoring uses a success factor of 1.0 only, not the 1.2 multiplier for declared tasks.': 'WeGlide의 FFVP Federal Cup(NetCoupe). 득점 경로에는 시작과 끝 사이에 최대 3개의 전환점이 있으며 총 길이는 최소 25km입니다. 포인트는 100을 글라이더 핸디캡(DAeC 스타일 지수)으로 나눈 거리, 자유 비행의 경우 1.0, 이륙 전에 전자적으로 선언된 작업의 경우 1.2의 성공 요인에 비례합니다. XCSoar 실시간 채점에서는 선언된 작업에 대해 1.2 승수가 아닌 1.0의 성공 요인만 사용합니다.',
        'Previous waypoint: when an ordered task is loaded, automatically tracks the task waypoint before the active leg (the start waypoint when on the first leg). Displays the waypoint name, arrival altitude difference relative to the safety arrival height, and distance. Click to choose a different waypoint to display (task waypoints when a task is loaded, otherwise the full waypoint list); selection is informational only and never advances the task or sets a Goto. With a task loaded, choose "Resume auto tracking" at the top of the list to revert to automatic tracking.': '이전 웨이포인트: 주문된 작업이 로드되면 활성 구간 이전의 작업 웨이포인트(첫 번째 구간의 시작 웨이포인트)를 자동으로 추적합니다. 웨이포인트 이름, 안전 도착 고도를 기준으로 한 도착 고도 차이, 거리를 표시합니다. 표시할 다른 경유지를 선택하려면 클릭합니다(작업이 로드될 때의 작업 경유지, 그렇지 않으면 전체 경유지 목록). 선택은 정보 제공용일 뿐이며 작업을 진행하거나 Goto를 설정하지 않습니다. 작업이 로드된 상태에서 목록 상단의 "자동 추적 재개"를 선택하면 자동 추적으로 되돌아갑니다.',
        'This parameter estimates the height%s at which the average dry updraft strength drops below 225 fpm and is expected to give better quantitative numbers for the maximum cloudless thermalling height than the BL Top height, especially when mixing results from vertical wind shear rather than thermals. (Note: the present assumptions tend to underpredict the max. thermalling height for dry conditions.) In the presence of clouds the maximum thermalling height may instead be limited by the cloud base. Being for "dry" thermals, this parameter omits the effect of "cloudsuck".': '이 매개변수는 평균 건식 상승 기류 강도가 225fpm 아래로 떨어지는 높이%s를 추정하며, 특히 상승기류가 아닌 수직 바람 전단의 혼합 결과인 경우 BL Top 높이보다 최대 구름 없는 온열기 높이에 대해 더 나은 정량적 숫자를 제공할 것으로 예상됩니다. (참고: 현재의 가정은 건조한 조건에 대한 최대 열적 고도를 과소 예측하는 경향이 있습니다.) 구름이 있는 경우 최대 열적 고도는 구름 기저에 의해 대신 제한될 수 있습니다. "건식" 열에 대한 것이므로 이 매개변수는 "구름 흡입" 효과를 생략합니다.',
        '![](resource:IDB_WARNING_TRIANGLE)\n\n!!! warning\n# Important Safety Notice\n\nBy using XCSoar, you acknowledge and accept the following:\n\n## Limitations\n\n- XCSoar is for **situational awareness only**\n- XCSoar is **not** a FLARM display\n- XCSoar is **not** aviation certified in any way\n- The artificial horizon is **not** fit for any purpose\n- Databanks (airspace, waypoints) may contain errors, be incomplete, or **not** up to date\n- NOTAM display does **not** replace proper pre-flight NOTAM briefing\n- NOTAM data may be incomplete, delayed, filtered, or unavailable\n- XCSoar is **not** guaranteed to be error free\n\n## Pilot Responsibility\n\nThe **Pilot in Command** is always responsible for the safe operation of the aircraft. Never rely solely on XCSoar for navigation or situational awareness.\n\n': '![](resource:IDB_WARNING_TRIANGLE)\n\n!!! warning\n# 중요한 안전 공지\n\nXCSoar를 사용함으로써 귀하는 다음 사항을 인정하고 수락합니다.\n\n## 제한사항\n\n- XCSoar는 **상황인식만 가능**를 위한 것입니다.\n- XCSoar는 FLARM 디스플레이인 **~ 아니다**입니다.\n- XCSoar는 어떤 방식으로든 **~ 아니다** 항공 인증을 받았습니다.\n- 인공 지평선은 **~ 아니다** 어떤 목적에도 적합합니다\n- 데이터뱅크(공역, 경유지)에 오류가 있거나, 불완전하거나, **~ 아니다** 최신 상태일 수 있습니다.\n- NOTAM 디스플레이는 **~ 아니다**가 적절한 비행 전 NOTAM 브리핑을 대체합니다.\n- NOTAM 데이터는 불완전하거나 지연되거나 필터링되거나 사용 불가능할 수 있습니다.\n- XCSoar는 **~ 아니다**이며 오류가 없음을 보장합니다.\n\n## 조종사의 책임\n\n**지휘하는 조종사**는 항상 항공기의 안전한 운항을 책임집니다. 탐색이나 상황 인식을 위해 XCSoar에만 의존하지 마십시오.\n\n',
        '# Getting Started\n\nTo use XCSoar effectively, configure the following:\n\n- [Restore from backup](xcsoar://dialog/backup) - Restore previous XCSoar data from a USB or SD card (optional)\n\n- [%s] [Map and data](xcsoar://config/site-files) - Download maps, waypoints, and airspace files for your region\n\n- [%s] [Aircraft polar](xcsoar://config/planes) - Set up your aircraft with the correct polar curve\n\n- [%s] [Pilot info](xcsoar://config/logger) - Enter your name and weight\n\n- [%s] [Devices](xcsoar://config/devices) - Connect your flight instruments\n\n- [%s] [WeGlide](xcsoar://config/weglide) - Upload flights automatically to WeGlide\n\n- [%s] [Thermal Information Map](xcsoar://config/weather) - Show thermal locations from thermalmap.info on the map\n\n- [%s] [Safety factors](xcsoar://config/safety) - Set arrival height, terrain clearance and polar degradation\n\n- [%s] [Terrain Display](xcsoar://config/terrain) - Choose terrain colors, shading and contour lines\n\n- [ ] [Live tracking](xcsoar://config/tracking) *(optional)* - Share your position via SkyLines or LiveTrack24\n\nThe easiest way to explore XCSoar is to [replay an existing IGC flight](xcsoar://dialog/replay).': '# 시작하기\n\nXCSoar를 효과적으로 사용하려면 다음을 구성하십시오.\n\n- [백업에서 복원](xcsoar://dialog/backup) - USB 또는 SD 카드에서 이전 XCSoar 데이터 복원(선택 사항)\n\n- [%s] [지도 및 데이터](xcsoar://config/site-files) - 해당 지역의 지도, 경유지, 영공 파일을 다운로드하세요.\n\n- [%s] [항공기 극지](xcsoar://config/planes) - 올바른 극곡선으로 항공기를 설정하세요.\n\n- [%s] [파일럿 정보](xcsoar://config/logger) - 이름과 몸무게를 입력하세요\n\n- [%s] [장치](xcsoar://config/devices) - 비행 계기 연결\n\n- [%s] [위글라이드](xcsoar://config/weglide) - WeGlide에 자동으로 항공편 업로드\n\n- [%s] [열정보 지도](xcsoar://config/weather) - Thermalmap.info의 열 위치를 지도에 표시\n\n- [%s] [안전 요인](xcsoar://config/safety) - 도착 높이, 지형 간격 및 극지 저하 설정\n\n- [%s] [지형 디스플레이](xcsoar://config/terrain) - 지형 색상, 음영 및 등고선 선택\n\n- [ ] [실시간 추적](xcsoar://config/tracking) *(optional)* - SkyLines 또는 LiveTrack24를 통해 위치를 공유하세요\n\nXCSoar를 탐색하는 가장 쉬운 방법은 다음과 같습니다. [기존 IGC 항공편 재생](xcsoar://dialog/replay).',
        '# Gesture Navigation\n\nXCSoar supports touch gestures on the map:\n\n- ![U](resource:IDB_GESTURE_UP) **Swipe Up** (U): Zoom in\n- ![D](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DOWN) **Swipe Down** (D): Zoom out\n- ![R](resource:IDB_GESTURE_RIGHT) **Swipe Right** (R): Previous screen mode\n- ![L](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LEFT) **Swipe Left** (L): Next screen mode\n- ![UD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_UD) **Up-Down** (UD): Auto zoom\n- ![DU](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DU) **Down-Up** (DU): Menu\n- ![DR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DR) **Down-Right** (DR): Waypoint details\n- ![DL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DL) **Down-Left** (DL): Alternates\n- ![LU](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LU) **Left-Up** (LU): Recently used waypoints\n- ![RD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_RD) **Right-Down** (RD): Task manager\n- ![URD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_URD) **Up-Right-Down** (URD): Analysis\n- ![LDR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LDR) **Left-Down-Right** (LDR): Checklist\n- ![URDL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_URDL) **Up-Right-Down-Left** (URDL): Pan mode\n- ![LDRDL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LDRDL) **Left-Down-Right-Down-Left** (LDRDL): Status\n- ![ULDR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_ULDR) **Up-Left-Down-Right** (ULDR): Quick menu\n\nLong-press on the map to enter Pan mode. Tap while in Pan mode to see nearby waypoints.': '# 제스처 탐색\n\nXCSoar는 지도에서 터치 제스처를 지원합니다.\n\n- ![U](resource:IDB_GESTURE_UP) **위로 스와이프** (U): 확대\n- ![D](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DOWN) **아래로 스와이프** (D): 축소\n- ![R](resource:IDB_GESTURE_RIGHT) **오른쪽으로 스와이프** (R): 이전 화면 모드\n- ![L](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LEFT) **왼쪽으로 스와이프** (L): 다음 화면 모드\n- ![UD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_UD) **업다운** (UD): 자동 줌\n- ![DU](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DU) **다운업** (DU): 메뉴\n- ![DR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DR) **철저한** (DR): 웨이포인트 세부정보\n- ![DL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DL) **아래-왼쪽** (DL): 대체\n- ![LU](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LU) **왼쪽 위로** (LU): 최근 사용된 웨이포인트\n- ![RD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_RD) **오른쪽 아래** (RD): 작업 관리자\n- ![URD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_URD) **위-오른쪽-아래** (URD): 분석\n- ![LDR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LDR) **왼쪽-아래-오른쪽** (LDR): 체크리스트\n- ![URDL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_URDL) **위-오른쪽-아래-왼쪽** (URDL): 팬 모드\n- ![LDRDL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LDRDL) **왼쪽-아래-오른쪽-아래-왼쪽** (LDRDL): 상태\n- ![ULDR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_ULDR) **상-왼쪽-아래-오른쪽** (ULDR): 퀵메뉴\n\n지도를 길게 누르면 팬 모드로 들어갑니다. 근처 웨이포인트를 보려면 팬 모드에서 탭하세요.',
    },
    "lt": {
        'Size of waypoint symbols on the map as a percentage of the built-in artwork (list dialogs keep a fixed row icon size).': 'Kelio taško simbolių dydis žemėlapyje, išreikštas procentais nuo integruoto meno kūrinio (sąrašo dialogo langai išlaiko fiksuotą eilutės piktogramos dydį).',
        'Home waypoint name, arrival altitude difference relative to the safety arrival height, and distance. Click to change the home waypoint.': 'Namo kelio taško pavadinimas, atvykimo aukščio skirtumas, palyginti su saugiu atvykimo aukščiu ir atstumas. Spustelėkite, kad pakeistumėte namų maršruto tašką.',
        'Current QNH pressure setting used for barometric altitude calculation. Tap the infobox to open the setup panel and adjust QNH manually.': 'Dabartinis QNH slėgio nustatymas naudojamas barometriniam aukščiui apskaičiuoti. Bakstelėkite informacijos laukelį, kad atidarytumėte sąrankos skydelį ir rankiniu būdu sureguliuotumėte QNH.',
        'This page shows WiFi status when NetworkManager or ConnMan is on D-Bus (e.g. Linux with Wayland or KMS). Open WiFi list to scan and connect when a service is available.': 'Šiame puslapyje rodoma „WiFi“ būsena, kai „NetworkManager“ arba „ConnMan“ yra D-Bus (pvz., „Linux“ su „Wayland“ arba KMS). Atidarykite „WiFi“ sąrašą, kad nuskaitytumėte ir prisijungtumėte, kai paslauga pasiekiama.',
        'The terrain can be shaded among slopes to indicate either wind direction, sun position, a geographically fixed shading from North-West, or a screen-relative fixed shading from top left.': 'Vietovė gali būti užtamsinta tarp šlaitų, kad būtų nurodyta vėjo kryptis, saulės padėtis, geografiškai pastovus šešėlis iš šiaurės vakarų arba ekrano atžvilgiu fiksuotas šešėlis iš viršaus kairėje.',
        "Synchronize the glide polar between XCSoar and the device (LXNAV varios). 'Receive' adopts the polar from the device (e.g. for club gliders). 'Send' pushes XCSoar's polar to the device.": 'Sinchronizuokite XCSoar ir įrenginio slydimo poliarinį ryšį (LXNAV varios). „Gauti“ perima polius iš įrenginio (pvz., klubo sklandytuvams). „Siųsti“ nustumia XCSoar polinį įtaisą.',
        'List of active airspace files. Use the Add and Remove buttons to activate or deactivate airspace files respectively. Supported file types are: Openair (.openair /.txt /.air), and Tim Newport-Pearce (.sua).': 'Aktyvių oro erdvės failų sąrašas. Norėdami įjungti arba išjungti oro erdvės failus, naudokite mygtukus Pridėti ir šalinti. Palaikomi failų tipai: Openair (.openair /.txt /.air) ir Tim Newport-Pearce (.sua).',
        'Signed countdown until the start gate opens or closes (now). Value colour and secondary line reflect gate state at the current time: Waiting (blue), Open (green), Closed (red). PEV window overrides task gate when set.': 'Pasirašyta atgalinė atskaita iki starto vartų atsidarymo arba uždarymo (dabar). Reikšmės spalva ir antrinė eilutė atspindi vartų būseną šiuo metu: Laukiama (mėlyna), Atidaryta (žalia), Uždaryta (raudona). Kai nustatyta, PEV langas nepaiso užduočių vartų.',
        'Tells XCSoar to send its current GPS position to the device as $GPGGA and $GPRMC sentences. Turn off when another GPS source is already feeding the device on the same line. Changes take effect after reconnecting the device.': 'Nurodo XCSoar siųsti savo dabartinę GPS padėtį į įrenginį kaip $GPGGA ir $GPRMC sakinius. Išjunkite, kai kitas GPS šaltinis jau maitina įrenginį toje pačioje linijoje. Pakeitimai įsigalioja vėl prijungus įrenginį.',
        'Logger pressure altitude when the device provides it (igc_pressure_altitude), otherwise ISA pressure altitude only (1013.25 hPa; not QNH-corrected). Does not show barometric AMSL or GPS height — use other InfoBoxes for navigation.': 'Registruokite barometrinį aukštį, kai prietaisas jį suteikia (igc_pressure_altitude), kitu atveju tik ISA barometrinis aukštis (1013,25 hPa; QNH nepataisytas). Nerodo barometrinio AMSL ar GPS aukščio – navigacijai naudokite kitus informacinius langelius.',
        'Same gate as Start open. Main value is estimated time to reach the start line (MacCready leg when available, else distance / ground speed). Value colour and secondary line reflect gate state at that ETA: Too early (blue), Can start (green), Too late (red).': 'Tie patys vartai kaip ir Startas atidaryti. Pagrindinė reikšmė – tai numatomas laikas, per kurį reikia pasiekti starto liniją (MacCready atstumas, jei įmanoma, atstumas / greitis). Vertės spalva ir antrinė linija atspindi vartų būseną tuo ETA: per anksti (mėlyna), gali prasidėti (žalia), per vėlai (raudona).',
        'Active waypoint: shows the next task waypoint when an ordered task is loaded, otherwise the Goto waypoint. Displays the waypoint name, arrival altitude difference relative to the safety arrival height, and distance. Click to choose a different waypoint (a task waypoint to skip to that leg, or any waypoint to set as Goto when no task is loaded).': 'Aktyvus maršruto taškas: rodo kitą užduoties tašką, kai įkeliama užsakyta užduotis, kitu atveju – Goto maršruto taškas. Rodo maršruto taško pavadinimą, atvykimo aukščio skirtumą, palyginti su saugaus atvykimo aukščiu, ir atstumą. Spustelėkite, kad pasirinktumėte kitą tarpinį tašką (užduoties tašką, kurį norite praleisti į tą etapą, arba bet kurį tarpinį tašką, kurį norite nustatyti kaip Goto, kai neįkeliama jokia užduotis).',
        'FFVP Federal Cup (NetCoupe) on WeGlide. The scored path has at most three turnpoints between start and finish and at least 25 km total. Points are proportional to credited distance, 100 divided by the glider handicap (DAeC-style index), and a success factor of 1.0 for a free flight or 1.2 for a task declared electronically before takeoff. XCSoar live scoring uses a success factor of 1.0 only, not the 1.2 multiplier for declared tasks.': 'FFVP federalinė taurė („NetCoupe“) „WeGlide“. Įskaitytas kelias turi ne daugiau kaip tris posūkius tarp starto ir finišo ir ne mažiau kaip 25 km. Taškai yra proporcingi įskaitytam atstumui, 100 padalyti iš sklandytuvo negalios (DAeC stiliaus indeksas), o sėkmės koeficientas yra 1,0 už nemokamą skrydį arba 1,2 už užduotį, paskelbtą elektroniniu būdu prieš kilimą. „XCSoar“ tiesioginiame įvertinime naudojamas tik sėkmės koeficientas 1,0, o ne deklaruotų užduočių daugiklis 1,2.',
        'Previous waypoint: when an ordered task is loaded, automatically tracks the task waypoint before the active leg (the start waypoint when on the first leg). Displays the waypoint name, arrival altitude difference relative to the safety arrival height, and distance. Click to choose a different waypoint to display (task waypoints when a task is loaded, otherwise the full waypoint list); selection is informational only and never advances the task or sets a Goto. With a task loaded, choose "Resume auto tracking" at the top of the list to revert to automatic tracking.': 'Ankstesnis maršruto taškas: kai įkeliama užsakyta užduotis, automatiškai seka užduoties maršruto tašką prieš aktyvią atkarpą (pradžios tašką, kai vyksta pirmoji atkarpa). Rodo maršruto taško pavadinimą, atvykimo aukščio skirtumą, palyginti su saugaus atvykimo aukščiu, ir atstumą. Spustelėkite, kad pasirinktumėte kitą rodytiną maršruto tašką (užduočių kelio taškai, kai užduotis įkeliama, kitu atveju visas kelio taškų sąrašas); pasirinkimas yra tik informacinis ir niekada nekelia užduoties ar nenustato Goto. Kai užduotis įkelta, sąrašo viršuje pasirinkite "Tęsti automatinį stebėjimą", kad grįžtumėte į automatinį stebėjimą.',
        'This parameter estimates the height%s at which the average dry updraft strength drops below 225 fpm and is expected to give better quantitative numbers for the maximum cloudless thermalling height than the BL Top height, especially when mixing results from vertical wind shear rather than thermals. (Note: the present assumptions tend to underpredict the max. thermalling height for dry conditions.) In the presence of clouds the maximum thermalling height may instead be limited by the cloud base. Being for "dry" thermals, this parameter omits the effect of "cloudsuck".': 'Šis parametras įvertina aukštį%s, kuriam esant vidutinis sausos srovės stiprumas nukrenta žemiau 225 fpm, ir tikimasi, kad jis duos geresnius kiekybinius didžiausio be debesų šiluminio aukščio skaitmenis nei BL viršutinis aukštis, ypač kai maišomi rezultatai dėl vertikalaus vėjo šlyties, o ne dėl šilumos. (Pastaba: dabartinės prielaidos linkusios nepakankamai nuspėti maksimalų šiluminį aukštį esant sausoms sąlygoms.) Esant debesims maksimalų šiluminio aukštį gali riboti debesų bazė. Šis parametras, skirtas „sausiems“ termikams, praleidžia „debesų traukimo“ efektą.',
        '![](resource:IDB_WARNING_TRIANGLE)\n\n!!! warning\n# Important Safety Notice\n\nBy using XCSoar, you acknowledge and accept the following:\n\n## Limitations\n\n- XCSoar is for **situational awareness only**\n- XCSoar is **not** a FLARM display\n- XCSoar is **not** aviation certified in any way\n- The artificial horizon is **not** fit for any purpose\n- Databanks (airspace, waypoints) may contain errors, be incomplete, or **not** up to date\n- NOTAM display does **not** replace proper pre-flight NOTAM briefing\n- NOTAM data may be incomplete, delayed, filtered, or unavailable\n- XCSoar is **not** guaranteed to be error free\n\n## Pilot Responsibility\n\nThe **Pilot in Command** is always responsible for the safe operation of the aircraft. Never rely solely on XCSoar for navigation or situational awareness.\n\n': '![](resource:IDB_WARNING_TRIANGLE)\n\n!!! warning\n# Svarbus saugos pranešimas\n\nNaudodami XCSoar patvirtinate ir sutinkate su šiais dalykais:\n\n## Apribojimai\n\n- XCSoar skirtas **tik situacijos suvokimas**\n- XCSoar yra **ne** FLARM ekranas\n- XCSoar yra **ne** aviacijos sertifikatas bet kokiu būdu\n- Dirbtinis horizontas **ne** tinka bet kokiam tikslui\n- Duomenų bankuose (oro erdvėje, maršruto taškuose) gali būti klaidų, jie gali būti neišsamūs arba **ne** atnaujinti\n- NOTAM ekranas **ne** pakeičia tinkamą NOTAM instruktažą prieš skrydį\n- NOTAM duomenys gali būti neišsamūs, uždelsti, filtruojami arba nepasiekiami\n- „XCSoar“ yra **ne** be klaidų\n\n## Piloto atsakomybė\n\n**Pilotas komandoje** visada atsakingas už saugų orlaivio naudojimą. Niekada nepasikliaukite vien XCSoar navigacija ar situacijos suvokimu.\n\n',
        '# Getting Started\n\nTo use XCSoar effectively, configure the following:\n\n- [Restore from backup](xcsoar://dialog/backup) - Restore previous XCSoar data from a USB or SD card (optional)\n\n- [%s] [Map and data](xcsoar://config/site-files) - Download maps, waypoints, and airspace files for your region\n\n- [%s] [Aircraft polar](xcsoar://config/planes) - Set up your aircraft with the correct polar curve\n\n- [%s] [Pilot info](xcsoar://config/logger) - Enter your name and weight\n\n- [%s] [Devices](xcsoar://config/devices) - Connect your flight instruments\n\n- [%s] [WeGlide](xcsoar://config/weglide) - Upload flights automatically to WeGlide\n\n- [%s] [Thermal Information Map](xcsoar://config/weather) - Show thermal locations from thermalmap.info on the map\n\n- [%s] [Safety factors](xcsoar://config/safety) - Set arrival height, terrain clearance and polar degradation\n\n- [%s] [Terrain Display](xcsoar://config/terrain) - Choose terrain colors, shading and contour lines\n\n- [ ] [Live tracking](xcsoar://config/tracking) *(optional)* - Share your position via SkyLines or LiveTrack24\n\nThe easiest way to explore XCSoar is to [replay an existing IGC flight](xcsoar://dialog/replay).': '# Darbo pradžia\n\nNorėdami efektyviai naudoti XCSoar, sukonfigūruokite:\n\n- [Atkurti iš atsarginės kopijos](xcsoar://dialog/backup) - Atkurti ankstesnius XCSoar duomenis iš USB arba SD kortelės (pasirinktinai)\n\n- [%s] [Žemėlapis ir duomenys](xcsoar://config/site-files) - Atsisiųskite savo regiono žemėlapius, kelio taškus ir oro erdvės failus\n\n- [%s] [Lėktuvas poliarinis](xcsoar://config/planes) - Nustatykite savo orlaivį su teisinga poliarine kreive\n\n- [%s] [Piloto informacija](xcsoar://config/logger) - Įveskite savo vardą ir svorį\n\n- [%s] [Prietaisai](xcsoar://config/devices) - Prijunkite skrydžio prietaisus\n\n- [%s] [WeGlide](xcsoar://config/weglide) - Automatiškai įkelkite skrydžius į WeGlide\n\n- [%s] [Šiluminės informacijos žemėlapis](xcsoar://config/weather) - Žemėlapyje rodyti šilumines vietas iš thermomap.info\n\n- [%s] [Saugos veiksniai](xcsoar://config/safety) - Nustatykite atvykimo aukštį, reljefo prošvaisą ir polių degradaciją\n\n- [%s] [Vietovės ekranas](xcsoar://config/terrain) - Pasirinkite reljefo spalvas, šešėliavimą ir kontūro linijas\n\n- [ ] [Tiesioginis stebėjimas](xcsoar://config/tracking) *(optional)* - Pasidalykite savo pozicija per SkyLines arba LiveTrack24\n\nLengviausias būdas ištirti XCSoar yra [pakartoti esamą IGC skrydį](xcsoar://dialog/replay).',
        '# Gesture Navigation\n\nXCSoar supports touch gestures on the map:\n\n- ![U](resource:IDB_GESTURE_UP) **Swipe Up** (U): Zoom in\n- ![D](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DOWN) **Swipe Down** (D): Zoom out\n- ![R](resource:IDB_GESTURE_RIGHT) **Swipe Right** (R): Previous screen mode\n- ![L](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LEFT) **Swipe Left** (L): Next screen mode\n- ![UD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_UD) **Up-Down** (UD): Auto zoom\n- ![DU](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DU) **Down-Up** (DU): Menu\n- ![DR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DR) **Down-Right** (DR): Waypoint details\n- ![DL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DL) **Down-Left** (DL): Alternates\n- ![LU](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LU) **Left-Up** (LU): Recently used waypoints\n- ![RD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_RD) **Right-Down** (RD): Task manager\n- ![URD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_URD) **Up-Right-Down** (URD): Analysis\n- ![LDR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LDR) **Left-Down-Right** (LDR): Checklist\n- ![URDL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_URDL) **Up-Right-Down-Left** (URDL): Pan mode\n- ![LDRDL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LDRDL) **Left-Down-Right-Down-Left** (LDRDL): Status\n- ![ULDR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_ULDR) **Up-Left-Down-Right** (ULDR): Quick menu\n\nLong-press on the map to enter Pan mode. Tap while in Pan mode to see nearby waypoints.': '# Navigacija gestais\n\nXCSoar palaiko lietimo gestus žemėlapyje:\n\n- ![U](resource:IDB_GESTURE_UP) **Braukite aukštyn** (U): Priartinti\n- ![D](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DOWN) **Braukite žemyn** (D): Nutolinti\n- ![R](resource:IDB_GESTURE_RIGHT) **Braukite dešinėn** (R): Ankstesnis ekrano režimas\n- ![L](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LEFT) **Braukite kairėn** (L): Kitas ekrano režimas\n- ![UD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_UD) **Aukštyn-žemyn** (UD): Automatinis priartinimas\n- ![DU](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DU) **Žemyn-Aukštyn** (DU): Meniu\n- ![DR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DR) **Žemyn-Dešinėn** (DR): Informacija apie kelio tašką\n- ![DL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DL) **Žemyn-kairėn** (DL): Pakaitiniai\n- ![LU](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LU) **Kairėn aukštyn** (LU): Neseniai naudoti kelio taškai\n- ![RD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_RD) **Dešinėn žemyn** (RD): Užduočių tvarkyklė\n- ![URD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_URD) **Aukštyn-Dešinėn-Žemyn** (URD): Analizė\n- ![LDR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LDR) **Kairėn-žemyn-dešinėn** (LDR): Kontrolinis sąrašas\n- ![URDL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_URDL) **Aukštyn-dešinėn-žemyn-kairėn** (URDL): Panelės režimas\n- ![LDRDL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LDRDL) **Kairėn-žemyn-dešinėn-žemyn-kairėn** (LDRDL): Būsena\n- ![ULDR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_ULDR) **Aukštyn-kairėn-žemyn-dešinėn** (ULDR): Greitas meniu\n\nIlgai paspauskite žemėlapį, kad įjungtumėte panoraminį režimą. Norėdami pamatyti netoliese esančius kelio taškus, palieskite, kol veikia panoraminis režimas.',
    },
    "nb": {
        'Size of waypoint symbols on the map as a percentage of the built-in artwork (list dialogs keep a fixed row icon size).': 'Størrelsen på veipunktsymbolene på kartet som en prosentandel av det innebygde kunstverket (listedialoger har en fast radikonstørrelse).',
        'Home waypoint name, arrival altitude difference relative to the safety arrival height, and distance. Click to change the home waypoint.': 'Hjemmeveipunktnavn, ankomsthøydeforskjell i forhold til sikkerhetsankomsthøyden og avstand. Klikk for å endre hjemmeveipunktet.',
        'Current QNH pressure setting used for barometric altitude calculation. Tap the infobox to open the setup panel and adjust QNH manually.': 'Gjeldende QNH-trykkinnstilling brukt for barometrisk høydeberegning. Trykk på infoboksen for å åpne oppsettpanelet og justere QNH manuelt.',
        'This page shows WiFi status when NetworkManager or ConnMan is on D-Bus (e.g. Linux with Wayland or KMS). Open WiFi list to scan and connect when a service is available.': 'Denne siden viser WiFi-status når NetworkManager eller ConnMan er på D-Bus (f.eks. Linux med Wayland eller KMS). Åpne WiFi-listen for å skanne og koble til når en tjeneste er tilgjengelig.',
        'The terrain can be shaded among slopes to indicate either wind direction, sun position, a geographically fixed shading from North-West, or a screen-relative fixed shading from top left.': 'Terrenget kan skyggelegges blant bakker for å indikere enten vindretning, solposisjon, en geografisk fast skyggelegging fra Nord-Vest, eller en skjermrelatert fast skyggelegging fra øverst til venstre.',
        "Synchronize the glide polar between XCSoar and the device (LXNAV varios). 'Receive' adopts the polar from the device (e.g. for club gliders). 'Send' pushes XCSoar's polar to the device.": "Synkroniser glidepolaren mellom XCSoar og enheten (LXNAV varios). 'Motta' adopterer polaren fra enheten (f.eks. for klubbseilfly). 'Send' skyver XCSoars polar til enheten.",
        'List of active airspace files. Use the Add and Remove buttons to activate or deactivate airspace files respectively. Supported file types are: Openair (.openair /.txt /.air), and Tim Newport-Pearce (.sua).': 'Liste over aktive luftromsfiler. Bruk knappene Legg til og Fjern for å aktivere eller deaktivere luftromsfiler. Støttede filtyper er: Openair (.openair /.txt /.air) og Tim Newport-Pearce (.sua).',
        'Signed countdown until the start gate opens or closes (now). Value colour and secondary line reflect gate state at the current time: Waiting (blue), Open (green), Closed (red). PEV window overrides task gate when set.': 'Signert nedtelling til startporten åpnes eller lukkes (nå). Verdifarge og sekundærlinje reflekterer portens tilstand på gjeldende tidspunkt: Venter (blå), Åpen (grønn), Lukket (rød). PEV-vinduet overstyrer oppgaveporten når den er satt.',
        'Tells XCSoar to send its current GPS position to the device as $GPGGA and $GPRMC sentences. Turn off when another GPS source is already feeding the device on the same line. Changes take effect after reconnecting the device.': 'Ber XCSoar sende sin nåværende GPS-posisjon til enheten som $GPGGA- og $GPRMC-setninger. Slå av når en annen GPS-kilde allerede mater enheten på samme linje. Endringer trer i kraft etter at enheten er koblet til igjen.',
        'Logger pressure altitude when the device provides it (igc_pressure_altitude), otherwise ISA pressure altitude only (1013.25 hPa; not QNH-corrected). Does not show barometric AMSL or GPS height — use other InfoBoxes for navigation.': 'Logger trykkhøyde når enheten gir det (igc_pressure_altitude), ellers kun ISA trykkhøyde (1013,25 hPa; ikke QNH-korrigert). Viser ikke barometrisk AMSL- eller GPS-høyde — bruk andre infobokser for navigering.',
        'Same gate as Start open. Main value is estimated time to reach the start line (MacCready leg when available, else distance / ground speed). Value colour and secondary line reflect gate state at that ETA: Too early (blue), Can start (green), Too late (red).': 'Samme port som Start åpen. Hovedverdi er beregnet tid for å nå startlinjen (MacCready etappe når tilgjengelig, ellers distanse / bakkehastighet). Verdifarge og sekundærlinje reflekterer porttilstand ved den ETA: For tidlig (blå), Kan starte (grønn), For sent (rød).',
        'Active waypoint: shows the next task waypoint when an ordered task is loaded, otherwise the Goto waypoint. Displays the waypoint name, arrival altitude difference relative to the safety arrival height, and distance. Click to choose a different waypoint (a task waypoint to skip to that leg, or any waypoint to set as Goto when no task is loaded).': 'Aktivt veipunkt: viser neste oppgaveveipunkt når en bestilt oppgave er lastet, ellers Gå til veipunkt. Viser veipunktnavnet, høydeforskjellen for ankomst i forhold til sikkerhetsankomsthøyden og avstanden. Klikk for å velge et annet veipunkt (et oppgaveveipunkt for å hoppe til det etappen, eller et hvilket som helst veipunkt for å angi som Goto når ingen oppgave er lastet inn).',
        'FFVP Federal Cup (NetCoupe) on WeGlide. The scored path has at most three turnpoints between start and finish and at least 25 km total. Points are proportional to credited distance, 100 divided by the glider handicap (DAeC-style index), and a success factor of 1.0 for a free flight or 1.2 for a task declared electronically before takeoff. XCSoar live scoring uses a success factor of 1.0 only, not the 1.2 multiplier for declared tasks.': 'FFVP Federal Cup (NetCoupe) på WeGlide. Den scorede banen har maksimalt tre vendepunkter mellom start og mål og minst 25 km totalt. Poeng er proporsjonale med kreditert distanse, 100 delt på gliderhandicap (DAeC-stil indeks), og en suksessfaktor på 1,0 for en fri flytur eller 1,2 for en oppgave som er deklarert elektronisk før start. XCSoar live-scoring bruker kun en suksessfaktor på 1,0, ikke multiplikatoren på 1,2 for deklarerte oppgaver.',
        'Previous waypoint: when an ordered task is loaded, automatically tracks the task waypoint before the active leg (the start waypoint when on the first leg). Displays the waypoint name, arrival altitude difference relative to the safety arrival height, and distance. Click to choose a different waypoint to display (task waypoints when a task is loaded, otherwise the full waypoint list); selection is informational only and never advances the task or sets a Goto. With a task loaded, choose "Resume auto tracking" at the top of the list to revert to automatic tracking.': 'Forrige veipunkt: når en bestilt oppgave er lastet inn, sporer automatisk oppgaveveipunktet før den aktive etappen (startveipunktet når du er på den første etappen). Viser veipunktnavnet, høydeforskjellen for ankomst i forhold til sikkerhetsankomsthøyden og avstanden. Klikk for å velge et annet veipunkt å vise (oppgaveveipunkter når en oppgave er lastet, ellers hele veipunktlisten); valget er kun informativt og fremmer aldri oppgaven eller setter en Goto. Med en oppgave lastet, velg "Gjenoppta automatisk sporing" øverst på listen for å gå tilbake til automatisk sporing.',
        'This parameter estimates the height%s at which the average dry updraft strength drops below 225 fpm and is expected to give better quantitative numbers for the maximum cloudless thermalling height than the BL Top height, especially when mixing results from vertical wind shear rather than thermals. (Note: the present assumptions tend to underpredict the max. thermalling height for dry conditions.) In the presence of clouds the maximum thermalling height may instead be limited by the cloud base. Being for "dry" thermals, this parameter omits the effect of "cloudsuck".': 'Denne parameteren estimerer høyden %s der gjennomsnittlig tørr oppstrømsstyrke faller under 225 fpm og forventes å gi bedre kvantitative tall for maksimal skyfri termisk høyde enn BL Top-høyden, spesielt når blandingsresultater fra vertikal vindskjæring i stedet for termikk. (Merk: de nåværende antakelsene har en tendens til å underforutsi maks. termisk høyde for tørre forhold.) I nærvær av skyer kan den maksimale termiske høyden i stedet begrenses av skybasen. For å være for "tørr" termikk, utelater denne parameteren effekten av "cloudsuck".',
        '![](resource:IDB_WARNING_TRIANGLE)\n\n!!! warning\n# Important Safety Notice\n\nBy using XCSoar, you acknowledge and accept the following:\n\n## Limitations\n\n- XCSoar is for **situational awareness only**\n- XCSoar is **not** a FLARM display\n- XCSoar is **not** aviation certified in any way\n- The artificial horizon is **not** fit for any purpose\n- Databanks (airspace, waypoints) may contain errors, be incomplete, or **not** up to date\n- NOTAM display does **not** replace proper pre-flight NOTAM briefing\n- NOTAM data may be incomplete, delayed, filtered, or unavailable\n- XCSoar is **not** guaranteed to be error free\n\n## Pilot Responsibility\n\nThe **Pilot in Command** is always responsible for the safe operation of the aircraft. Never rely solely on XCSoar for navigation or situational awareness.\n\n': '![](resource:IDB_WARNING_TRIANGLE)\n\n!!! warning\n# Viktig sikkerhetsmerknad\n\nVed å bruke XCSoar, erkjenner og godtar du følgende:\n\n## Begrensninger\n\n- XCSoar er for **Kun situasjonsforståelse**\n- XCSoar er **ikke** en FLARM-skjerm\n- XCSoar er **ikke** luftfartssertifisert på noen måte\n- Den kunstige horisonten er **ikke** egnet for ethvert formål\n- Databanker (luftrom, veipunkter) kan inneholde feil, være ufullstendige eller **ikke** oppdatert\n- NOTAM-skjermen erstatter **ikke** riktig NOTAM-briefing før fly\n- NOTAM-data kan være ufullstendige, forsinket, filtrert eller utilgjengelig\n- XCSoar er **ikke** garantert feilfri\n\n## Pilotansvar\n\n**Pilot i kommando** er alltid ansvarlig for sikker drift av flyet. Stol aldri utelukkende på XCSoar for navigasjon eller situasjonsforståelse.\n\n',
        '# Getting Started\n\nTo use XCSoar effectively, configure the following:\n\n- [Restore from backup](xcsoar://dialog/backup) - Restore previous XCSoar data from a USB or SD card (optional)\n\n- [%s] [Map and data](xcsoar://config/site-files) - Download maps, waypoints, and airspace files for your region\n\n- [%s] [Aircraft polar](xcsoar://config/planes) - Set up your aircraft with the correct polar curve\n\n- [%s] [Pilot info](xcsoar://config/logger) - Enter your name and weight\n\n- [%s] [Devices](xcsoar://config/devices) - Connect your flight instruments\n\n- [%s] [WeGlide](xcsoar://config/weglide) - Upload flights automatically to WeGlide\n\n- [%s] [Thermal Information Map](xcsoar://config/weather) - Show thermal locations from thermalmap.info on the map\n\n- [%s] [Safety factors](xcsoar://config/safety) - Set arrival height, terrain clearance and polar degradation\n\n- [%s] [Terrain Display](xcsoar://config/terrain) - Choose terrain colors, shading and contour lines\n\n- [ ] [Live tracking](xcsoar://config/tracking) *(optional)* - Share your position via SkyLines or LiveTrack24\n\nThe easiest way to explore XCSoar is to [replay an existing IGC flight](xcsoar://dialog/replay).': '# Komme i gang\n\nFor å bruke XCSoar effektivt, konfigurer følgende:\n\n- [Gjenopprett fra sikkerhetskopi](xcsoar://dialog/backup) - Gjenopprett tidligere XCSoar-data fra et USB- eller SD-kort (valgfritt)\n\n- [%s] [Kart og data](xcsoar://config/site-files) - Last ned kart, veipunkter og luftromsfiler for din region\n\n- [%s] [Fly polar](xcsoar://config/planes) - Sett opp flyet med riktig polarkurve\n\n- [%s] [Pilotinformasjon](xcsoar://config/logger) - Skriv inn navn og vekt\n\n- [%s] [Enheter](xcsoar://config/devices) - Koble til flyinstrumentene dine\n\n- [%s] [WeGlide](xcsoar://config/weglide) - Last opp flyreiser automatisk til WeGlide\n\n- [%s] [Termisk informasjonskart](xcsoar://config/weather) - Vis termiske steder fra thermalmap.info på kartet\n\n- [%s] [Sikkerhetsfaktorer](xcsoar://config/safety) - Still inn ankomsthøyde, terrengklaring og polar degradering\n\n- [%s] [Terrengvisning](xcsoar://config/terrain) - Velg terrengfarger, skyggelegging og konturlinjer\n\n- [ ] [Live sporing](xcsoar://config/tracking) *(optional)* - Del posisjonen din via SkyLines eller LiveTrack24\n\nDen enkleste måten å utforske XCSoar på er å [spille av en eksisterende IGC-flyvning](xcsoar://dialog/replay).',
        '# Gesture Navigation\n\nXCSoar supports touch gestures on the map:\n\n- ![U](resource:IDB_GESTURE_UP) **Swipe Up** (U): Zoom in\n- ![D](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DOWN) **Swipe Down** (D): Zoom out\n- ![R](resource:IDB_GESTURE_RIGHT) **Swipe Right** (R): Previous screen mode\n- ![L](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LEFT) **Swipe Left** (L): Next screen mode\n- ![UD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_UD) **Up-Down** (UD): Auto zoom\n- ![DU](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DU) **Down-Up** (DU): Menu\n- ![DR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DR) **Down-Right** (DR): Waypoint details\n- ![DL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DL) **Down-Left** (DL): Alternates\n- ![LU](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LU) **Left-Up** (LU): Recently used waypoints\n- ![RD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_RD) **Right-Down** (RD): Task manager\n- ![URD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_URD) **Up-Right-Down** (URD): Analysis\n- ![LDR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LDR) **Left-Down-Right** (LDR): Checklist\n- ![URDL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_URDL) **Up-Right-Down-Left** (URDL): Pan mode\n- ![LDRDL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LDRDL) **Left-Down-Right-Down-Left** (LDRDL): Status\n- ![ULDR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_ULDR) **Up-Left-Down-Right** (ULDR): Quick menu\n\nLong-press on the map to enter Pan mode. Tap while in Pan mode to see nearby waypoints.': '# Bevegelsesnavigering\n\nXCSoar støtter berøringsbevegelser på kartet:\n\n- ![U](resource:IDB_GESTURE_UP) **Sveip opp** (U): Zoom inn\n- ![D](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DOWN) **Sveip ned** (D): Zoom ut\n- ![R](resource:IDB_GESTURE_RIGHT) **Sveip til høyre** (R): Forrige skjermmodus\n- ![L](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LEFT) **Sveip til venstre** (L): Neste skjermmodus\n- ![UD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_UD) **Opp-Ned** (UD): Autozoom\n- ![DU](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DU) **Ned-Opp** (DU): Meny\n- ![DR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DR) **Ned til høyre** (DR): Veipunktdetaljer\n- ![DL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DL) **Ned-venstre** (DL): Alternativer\n- ![LU](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LU) **Venstre-opp** (LU): Nylig brukte veipunkter\n- ![RD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_RD) **Høyre ned** (RD): Oppgaveleder\n- ![URD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_URD) **Opp-Høyre-Ned** (URD): Analyse\n- ![LDR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LDR) **Venstre-Ned-Høyre** (LDR): Sjekkliste\n- ![URDL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_URDL) **Opp-Høyre-Ned-Venstre** (URDL): Panoreringsmodus\n- ![LDRDL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LDRDL) **Venstre-Ned-Høyre-Ned-Venstre** (LDRDL): Status\n- ![ULDR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_ULDR) **Opp-Venstre-Ned-Høyre** (ULDR): Hurtigmeny\n\nTrykk lenge på kartet for å gå inn i panoreringsmodus. Trykk mens du er i panoreringsmodus for å se veipunkter i nærheten.',
    },
    "nl": {
        'Size of waypoint symbols on the map as a percentage of the built-in artwork (list dialogs keep a fixed row icon size).': 'Grootte van waypoint-symbolen op de kaart als percentage van de ingebouwde illustratie (lijstdialoogvensters behouden een vaste pictogramgrootte voor rijen).',
        'Home waypoint name, arrival altitude difference relative to the safety arrival height, and distance. Click to change the home waypoint.': 'Naam thuiswaypoint, verschil in aankomsthoogte ten opzichte van de veiligheidsaankomsthoogte, en afstand. Klik om het thuiswaypoint te wijzigen.',
        'Current QNH pressure setting used for barometric altitude calculation. Tap the infobox to open the setup panel and adjust QNH manually.': 'Huidige QNH-drukinstelling gebruikt voor barometrische hoogteberekening. Tik op de infobox om het installatiepaneel te openen en QNH handmatig aan te passen.',
        'This page shows WiFi status when NetworkManager or ConnMan is on D-Bus (e.g. Linux with Wayland or KMS). Open WiFi list to scan and connect when a service is available.': 'Deze pagina toont de WiFi-status wanneer NetworkManager of ConnMan zich op D-Bus bevindt (bijvoorbeeld Linux met Wayland of KMS). Open de WiFi-lijst om te scannen en verbinding te maken wanneer een dienst beschikbaar is.',
        'The terrain can be shaded among slopes to indicate either wind direction, sun position, a geographically fixed shading from North-West, or a screen-relative fixed shading from top left.': 'Het terrein kan worden gearceerd tussen hellingen om de windrichting, de stand van de zon, een geografisch vaste schaduw vanuit het noordwesten of een scherm-relatieve vaste schaduw van linksboven aan te geven.',
        "Synchronize the glide polar between XCSoar and the device (LXNAV varios). 'Receive' adopts the polar from the device (e.g. for club gliders). 'Send' pushes XCSoar's polar to the device.": "Synchroniseer de glide polar tussen XCSoar en het apparaat (LXNAV varios). 'Ontvangen' neemt de polariteit van het apparaat over (bijvoorbeeld voor clubzweefvliegtuigen). 'Verzenden' duwt de polariteit van XCSoar naar het apparaat.",
        'List of active airspace files. Use the Add and Remove buttons to activate or deactivate airspace files respectively. Supported file types are: Openair (.openair /.txt /.air), and Tim Newport-Pearce (.sua).': 'Lijst met actieve luchtruimbestanden. Gebruik de knoppen Toevoegen en Verwijderen om luchtruimbestanden respectievelijk te activeren of te deactiveren. Ondersteunde bestandstypen zijn: Openair (.openair /.txt /.air) en Tim Newport-Pearce (.sua).',
        'Signed countdown until the start gate opens or closes (now). Value colour and secondary line reflect gate state at the current time: Waiting (blue), Open (green), Closed (red). PEV window overrides task gate when set.': 'Getekend aftellen tot het starthek (nu) open of dicht gaat. Waardekleur en secundaire lijn weerspiegelen de poortstatus op het huidige tijdstip: Wachtend (blauw), Open (groen), Gesloten (rood). Het PEV-venster overschrijft de taakpoort wanneer deze is ingesteld.',
        'Tells XCSoar to send its current GPS position to the device as $GPGGA and $GPRMC sentences. Turn off when another GPS source is already feeding the device on the same line. Changes take effect after reconnecting the device.': 'Vertelt XCSoar om zijn huidige GPS-positie naar het apparaat te sturen als $GPGGA- en $GPRMC-zinnen. Schakel uit wanneer een andere GPS-bron het apparaat al op dezelfde lijn voedt. Wijzigingen worden van kracht nadat het apparaat opnieuw is aangesloten.',
        'Logger pressure altitude when the device provides it (igc_pressure_altitude), otherwise ISA pressure altitude only (1013.25 hPa; not QNH-corrected). Does not show barometric AMSL or GPS height — use other InfoBoxes for navigation.': 'Drukhoogte registreren wanneer het apparaat deze levert (igc_druk_altitude), anders alleen ISA-drukhoogte (1013,25 hPa; niet QNH-gecorrigeerd). Toont geen barometrische AMSL- of GPS-hoogte - gebruik andere InfoBoxen voor navigatie.',
        'Same gate as Start open. Main value is estimated time to reach the start line (MacCready leg when available, else distance / ground speed). Value colour and secondary line reflect gate state at that ETA: Too early (blue), Can start (green), Too late (red).': 'Zelfde poort als Start open. De hoofdwaarde is de geschatte tijd om de startlijn te bereiken (MacCready-been indien beschikbaar, anders afstand/grondsnelheid). Waardekleur en secundaire lijn weerspiegelen de poortstatus op die ETA: te vroeg (blauw), kan starten (groen), te laat (rood).',
        'Active waypoint: shows the next task waypoint when an ordered task is loaded, otherwise the Goto waypoint. Displays the waypoint name, arrival altitude difference relative to the safety arrival height, and distance. Click to choose a different waypoint (a task waypoint to skip to that leg, or any waypoint to set as Goto when no task is loaded).': 'Actief waypoint: toont het volgende taakwaypoint wanneer een bestelde taak wordt geladen, anders het Goto-waypoint. Toont de naam van het waypoint, het verschil in aankomsthoogte ten opzichte van de veiligheidsaankomsthoogte en de afstand. Klik om een \u200b\u200bander waypoint te kiezen (een taakwaypoint om naar dat traject te gaan, of een waypoint om in te stellen als Goto als er geen taak is geladen).',
        'FFVP Federal Cup (NetCoupe) on WeGlide. The scored path has at most three turnpoints between start and finish and at least 25 km total. Points are proportional to credited distance, 100 divided by the glider handicap (DAeC-style index), and a success factor of 1.0 for a free flight or 1.2 for a task declared electronically before takeoff. XCSoar live scoring uses a success factor of 1.0 only, not the 1.2 multiplier for declared tasks.': 'FFVP Federal Cup (NetCoupe) op WeGlide. Het gescoorde pad heeft maximaal drie keerpunten tussen start en finish en is in totaal minimaal 25 km. Punten zijn evenredig aan de toegekende afstand, 100 gedeeld door de zweefvliegtuighandicap (DAeC-stijl index), en een succesfactor van 1,0 voor een vrije vlucht of 1,2 voor een taak die vóór het opstijgen elektronisch wordt aangegeven. XCSoar live scoring gebruikt alleen een succesfactor van 1,0, niet de vermenigvuldiger van 1,2 voor aangegeven taken.',
        'Previous waypoint: when an ordered task is loaded, automatically tracks the task waypoint before the active leg (the start waypoint when on the first leg). Displays the waypoint name, arrival altitude difference relative to the safety arrival height, and distance. Click to choose a different waypoint to display (task waypoints when a task is loaded, otherwise the full waypoint list); selection is informational only and never advances the task or sets a Goto. With a task loaded, choose "Resume auto tracking" at the top of the list to revert to automatic tracking.': 'Vorig waypoint: wanneer een bestelde taak wordt geladen, wordt automatisch het taakwaypoint gevolgd vóór de actieve etappe (het startwaypoint tijdens de eerste etappe). Toont de naam van het waypoint, het verschil in aankomsthoogte ten opzichte van de veiligheidsaankomsthoogte en de afstand. Klik om een \u200b\u200bander waypoint te kiezen om weer te geven (taakwaypoints wanneer een taak is geladen, anders de volledige waypointlijst); selectie is alleen ter informatie en brengt nooit vooruitgang in de taak of stelt een Goto in. Terwijl een taak is geladen, kiest u "Automatische tracking hervatten" bovenaan de lijst om terug te keren naar automatische tracking.',
        'This parameter estimates the height%s at which the average dry updraft strength drops below 225 fpm and is expected to give better quantitative numbers for the maximum cloudless thermalling height than the BL Top height, especially when mixing results from vertical wind shear rather than thermals. (Note: the present assumptions tend to underpredict the max. thermalling height for dry conditions.) In the presence of clouds the maximum thermalling height may instead be limited by the cloud base. Being for "dry" thermals, this parameter omits the effect of "cloudsuck".': 'Deze parameter schat de hoogte%s waarop de gemiddelde droge opwaartse kracht onder de 225 fpm daalt en zal naar verwachting betere kwantitatieve cijfers opleveren voor de maximale wolkenloze thermische hoogte dan de BL Top-hoogte, vooral wanneer menging het gevolg is van verticale windschering in plaats van thermiek. (Opmerking: de huidige aannames hebben de neiging de maximale thermische hoogte voor droge omstandigheden te laag te voorspellen.) In de aanwezigheid van wolken kan de maximale thermische hoogte in plaats daarvan worden beperkt door de wolkenbasis. Omdat het om "droge" thermiek gaat, laat deze parameter het effect van "cloudsuck" achterwege.',
        '![](resource:IDB_WARNING_TRIANGLE)\n\n!!! warning\n# Important Safety Notice\n\nBy using XCSoar, you acknowledge and accept the following:\n\n## Limitations\n\n- XCSoar is for **situational awareness only**\n- XCSoar is **not** a FLARM display\n- XCSoar is **not** aviation certified in any way\n- The artificial horizon is **not** fit for any purpose\n- Databanks (airspace, waypoints) may contain errors, be incomplete, or **not** up to date\n- NOTAM display does **not** replace proper pre-flight NOTAM briefing\n- NOTAM data may be incomplete, delayed, filtered, or unavailable\n- XCSoar is **not** guaranteed to be error free\n\n## Pilot Responsibility\n\nThe **Pilot in Command** is always responsible for the safe operation of the aircraft. Never rely solely on XCSoar for navigation or situational awareness.\n\n': '![](resource:IDB_WARNING_TRIANGLE)\n\n!!! warning\n# Belangrijke veiligheidsmededeling\n\nDoor XCSoar te gebruiken, erkent en accepteert u het volgende:\n\n## Beperkingen\n\n- XCSoar is voor **alleen situationeel bewustzijn**\n- XCSoar is **niet** een FLARM-display\n- XCSoar is op welke manier dan ook **niet** luchtvaart gecertificeerd\n- De kunstmatige horizon is **niet** geschikt voor elk doel\n- Databanken (luchtruim, waypoints) kunnen fouten bevatten, onvolledig zijn of **niet** up-to-date zijn\n- NOTAM-weergave vervangt **niet** de juiste NOTAM-briefing vóór de vlucht\n- NOTAM-gegevens kunnen onvolledig, vertraagd, gefilterd of niet beschikbaar zijn\n- XCSoar is **niet** gegarandeerd foutloos\n\n## Verantwoordelijkheid van de piloot\n\nDe **Piloot in bevel** is altijd verantwoordelijk voor de veilige exploitatie van het vliegtuig. Vertrouw nooit uitsluitend op XCSoar voor navigatie of situationeel bewustzijn.\n\n',
        '# Getting Started\n\nTo use XCSoar effectively, configure the following:\n\n- [Restore from backup](xcsoar://dialog/backup) - Restore previous XCSoar data from a USB or SD card (optional)\n\n- [%s] [Map and data](xcsoar://config/site-files) - Download maps, waypoints, and airspace files for your region\n\n- [%s] [Aircraft polar](xcsoar://config/planes) - Set up your aircraft with the correct polar curve\n\n- [%s] [Pilot info](xcsoar://config/logger) - Enter your name and weight\n\n- [%s] [Devices](xcsoar://config/devices) - Connect your flight instruments\n\n- [%s] [WeGlide](xcsoar://config/weglide) - Upload flights automatically to WeGlide\n\n- [%s] [Thermal Information Map](xcsoar://config/weather) - Show thermal locations from thermalmap.info on the map\n\n- [%s] [Safety factors](xcsoar://config/safety) - Set arrival height, terrain clearance and polar degradation\n\n- [%s] [Terrain Display](xcsoar://config/terrain) - Choose terrain colors, shading and contour lines\n\n- [ ] [Live tracking](xcsoar://config/tracking) *(optional)* - Share your position via SkyLines or LiveTrack24\n\nThe easiest way to explore XCSoar is to [replay an existing IGC flight](xcsoar://dialog/replay).': '# Aan de slag\n\nOm XCSoar effectief te gebruiken, configureert u het volgende:\n\n- [Herstellen vanaf back-up](xcsoar://dialog/backup) - Herstel eerdere XCSoar-gegevens vanaf een USB- of SD-kaart (optioneel)\n\n- [%s] [Kaart en gegevens](xcsoar://config/site-files) - Download kaarten, waypoints en luchtruimbestanden voor uw regio\n\n- [%s] [Vliegtuigen polair](xcsoar://config/planes) - Stel uw vliegtuig in met de juiste polaire curve\n\n- [%s] [Pilootinformatie](xcsoar://config/logger) - Vul uw naam en gewicht in\n\n- [%s] [Apparaten](xcsoar://config/devices) - Sluit uw vlieginstrumenten aan\n\n- [%s] [WijGlide](xcsoar://config/weglide) - Upload vluchten automatisch naar WeGlide\n\n- [%s] [Thermische informatiekaart](xcsoar://config/weather) - Toon thermische locaties van thermalmap.info op de kaart\n\n- [%s] [Veiligheidsfactoren](xcsoar://config/safety) - Stel de aankomsthoogte, de terreinvrijheid en de polaire degradatie in\n\n- [%s] [Terreinweergave](xcsoar://config/terrain) - Kies terreinkleuren, schaduwen en contourlijnen\n\n- [ ] [Live volgen](xcsoar://config/tracking) *(optional)* - Deel uw positie via SkyLines of LiveTrack24\n\nDe eenvoudigste manier om XCSoar te verkennen is door [speel een bestaande IGC-vlucht opnieuw af](xcsoar://dialog/replay).',
        '# Gesture Navigation\n\nXCSoar supports touch gestures on the map:\n\n- ![U](resource:IDB_GESTURE_UP) **Swipe Up** (U): Zoom in\n- ![D](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DOWN) **Swipe Down** (D): Zoom out\n- ![R](resource:IDB_GESTURE_RIGHT) **Swipe Right** (R): Previous screen mode\n- ![L](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LEFT) **Swipe Left** (L): Next screen mode\n- ![UD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_UD) **Up-Down** (UD): Auto zoom\n- ![DU](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DU) **Down-Up** (DU): Menu\n- ![DR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DR) **Down-Right** (DR): Waypoint details\n- ![DL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DL) **Down-Left** (DL): Alternates\n- ![LU](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LU) **Left-Up** (LU): Recently used waypoints\n- ![RD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_RD) **Right-Down** (RD): Task manager\n- ![URD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_URD) **Up-Right-Down** (URD): Analysis\n- ![LDR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LDR) **Left-Down-Right** (LDR): Checklist\n- ![URDL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_URDL) **Up-Right-Down-Left** (URDL): Pan mode\n- ![LDRDL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LDRDL) **Left-Down-Right-Down-Left** (LDRDL): Status\n- ![ULDR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_ULDR) **Up-Left-Down-Right** (ULDR): Quick menu\n\nLong-press on the map to enter Pan mode. Tap while in Pan mode to see nearby waypoints.': '# Gebarennavigatie\n\nXCSoar ondersteunt aanraakgebaren op de kaart:\n\n- ![U](resource:IDB_GESTURE_UP) **Veeg omhoog** (U): Zoom in\n- ![D](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DOWN) **Veeg omlaag** (D): Uitzoomen\n- ![R](resource:IDB_GESTURE_RIGHT) **Veeg naar rechts** (R): Vorige schermmodus\n- ![L](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LEFT) **Veeg naar links** (L): Volgende schermmodus\n- ![UD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_UD) **Omhoog-omlaag** (UD): Automatische zoom\n- ![DU](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DU) **Omlaag-omhoog** (DU): Menu\n- ![DR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DR) **Rechtsonder** (DR): Waypoint-details\n- ![DL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DL) **Linksonder** (DL): Alternatieven\n- ![LU](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LU) **Links-boven** (LU): Recent gebruikte tussenpunten\n- ![RD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_RD) **Rechts-onder** (RD): Taakbeheer\n- ![URD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_URD) **Omhoog-Rechts-Omlaag** (URD): Analyse\n- ![LDR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LDR) **Links-onder-rechts** (LDR): Controlelijst\n- ![URDL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_URDL) **Boven-Rechts-Onder-Links** (URDL): Pan-modus\n- ![LDRDL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LDRDL) **Links-Onder-Rechts-Onder-Links** (LDRDL): Status\n- ![ULDR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_ULDR) **Boven-links-onder-rechts** (ULDR): Snelmenu\n\nDruk lang op de kaart om de Pan-modus te openen. Tik in de Pan-modus om nabijgelegen waypoints te bekijken.',
    },
    "pl": {
        'Size of waypoint symbols on the map as a percentage of the built-in artwork (list dialogs keep a fixed row icon size).': 'Rozmiar symboli punktów trasy na mapie jako procent wbudowanej grafiki (okna dialogowe list zachowują stały rozmiar ikon w rzędach).',
        'Home waypoint name, arrival altitude difference relative to the safety arrival height, and distance. Click to change the home waypoint.': 'Nazwa punktu startowego, różnica wysokości przybycia w stosunku do bezpiecznej wysokości przybycia i odległość. Kliknij, aby zmienić punkt orientacyjny domu.',
        'Current QNH pressure setting used for barometric altitude calculation. Tap the infobox to open the setup panel and adjust QNH manually.': 'Bieżące ustawienie ciśnienia QNH używane do obliczania wysokości barometrycznej. Naciśnij infobox, aby otworzyć panel ustawień i ręcznie dostosować QNH.',
        'This page shows WiFi status when NetworkManager or ConnMan is on D-Bus (e.g. Linux with Wayland or KMS). Open WiFi list to scan and connect when a service is available.': 'Ta strona pokazuje stan Wi-Fi, gdy NetworkManager lub ConnMan jest podłączony do D-Bus (np. Linux z Wayland lub KMS). Otwórz listę Wi-Fi, aby skanować i łączyć się, gdy usługa jest dostępna.',
        'The terrain can be shaded among slopes to indicate either wind direction, sun position, a geographically fixed shading from North-West, or a screen-relative fixed shading from top left.': 'Teren może być zacieniony pomiędzy zboczami, aby wskazać kierunek wiatru, położenie słońca, geograficzne zacienienie z północnego zachodu lub stałe zacienienie względem ekranu od lewego górnego rogu.',
        "Synchronize the glide polar between XCSoar and the device (LXNAV varios). 'Receive' adopts the polar from the device (e.g. for club gliders). 'Send' pushes XCSoar's polar to the device.": 'Zsynchronizuj polaryzację pomiędzy XCSoar a urządzeniem (vario LXNAV). „Odbierz” przejmuje polar z urządzenia (np. dla szybowców klubowych). „Wyślij” przesyła polaryzację XCSoar do urządzenia.',
        'List of active airspace files. Use the Add and Remove buttons to activate or deactivate airspace files respectively. Supported file types are: Openair (.openair /.txt /.air), and Tim Newport-Pearce (.sua).': 'Lista aktywnych plików przestrzeni powietrznej. Użyj przycisków Dodaj i Usuń, aby odpowiednio aktywować lub dezaktywować pliki przestrzeni powietrznej. Obsługiwane typy plików to: Openair (.openair /.txt /.air) i Tim Newport-Pearce (.sua).',
        'Signed countdown until the start gate opens or closes (now). Value colour and secondary line reflect gate state at the current time: Waiting (blue), Open (green), Closed (red). PEV window overrides task gate when set.': 'Podpisane odliczanie do momentu otwarcia lub zamknięcia bramki startowej (teraz). Kolor wartości i linia pomocnicza odzwierciedlają aktualny stan bramy: Oczekiwanie (niebieski), Otwarty (zielony), Zamknięty (czerwony). Okno PEV zastępuje bramę zadania, gdy jest ustawione.',
        'Tells XCSoar to send its current GPS position to the device as $GPGGA and $GPRMC sentences. Turn off when another GPS source is already feeding the device on the same line. Changes take effect after reconnecting the device.': 'Nakazuje XCSoarowi wysłanie swojej aktualnej pozycji GPS do urządzenia w postaci zdań $GPGGA i $GPRMC. Wyłącz, gdy inne źródło GPS już zasila urządzenie na tej samej linii. Zmiany zaczną obowiązywać po ponownym podłączeniu urządzenia.',
        'Logger pressure altitude when the device provides it (igc_pressure_altitude), otherwise ISA pressure altitude only (1013.25 hPa; not QNH-corrected). Does not show barometric AMSL or GPS height — use other InfoBoxes for navigation.': 'Rejestruj wysokość ciśnieniową, jeśli urządzenie ją udostępnia (igc_ Pressure_altitude), w przeciwnym razie tylko wysokość ciśnieniową ISA (1013,25 hPa; bez korekty QNH). Nie pokazuje wysokości barometrycznej AMSL ani GPS — do nawigacji użyj innych InfoBoxów.',
        'Same gate as Start open. Main value is estimated time to reach the start line (MacCready leg when available, else distance / ground speed). Value colour and secondary line reflect gate state at that ETA: Too early (blue), Can start (green), Too late (red).': 'Ta sama brama co Start otwarta. Główną wartością jest szacowany czas dotarcia do linii startu (odcinek MacCready’ego, jeśli jest dostępny, w przeciwnym razie odległość/prędkość względem ziemi). Kolor wartości i linia pomocnicza odzwierciedlają stan bramki w tym ETA: Za wcześnie (niebieski), Można rozpocząć (zielony), Za późno (czerwony).',
        'Active waypoint: shows the next task waypoint when an ordered task is loaded, otherwise the Goto waypoint. Displays the waypoint name, arrival altitude difference relative to the safety arrival height, and distance. Click to choose a different waypoint (a task waypoint to skip to that leg, or any waypoint to set as Goto when no task is loaded).': 'Aktywny punkt trasy: pokazuje następny punkt trasy zadania, gdy załadowane jest zamówione zadanie, w przeciwnym razie punkt trasy Goto. Wyświetla nazwę punktu trasy, różnicę wysokości przybycia w stosunku do bezpiecznej wysokości przybycia i odległość. Kliknij, aby wybrać inny punkt trasy (punkt trasy zadania, aby przejść do tego etapu lub dowolny punkt trasy, który można ustawić jako Goto, gdy nie jest załadowane żadne zadanie).',
        'FFVP Federal Cup (NetCoupe) on WeGlide. The scored path has at most three turnpoints between start and finish and at least 25 km total. Points are proportional to credited distance, 100 divided by the glider handicap (DAeC-style index), and a success factor of 1.0 for a free flight or 1.2 for a task declared electronically before takeoff. XCSoar live scoring uses a success factor of 1.0 only, not the 1.2 multiplier for declared tasks.': 'Puchar Federalny FFVP (NetCoupe) na WeGlide. Punktowana trasa ma co najwyżej trzy punkty zwrotne między startem a metą i ma łącznie co najmniej 25 km. Punkty są proporcjonalne do zaliczonego dystansu, 100 podzielone przez handicap szybowca (wskaźnik w stylu DAeC) oraz współczynnik sukcesu 1,0 w przypadku lotu swobodnego lub 1,2 w przypadku zadania zadeklarowanego elektronicznie przed startem. Punktacja na żywo XCSoar wykorzystuje tylko współczynnik sukcesu 1,0, a nie mnożnik 1,2 dla zadeklarowanych zadań.',
        'Previous waypoint: when an ordered task is loaded, automatically tracks the task waypoint before the active leg (the start waypoint when on the first leg). Displays the waypoint name, arrival altitude difference relative to the safety arrival height, and distance. Click to choose a different waypoint to display (task waypoints when a task is loaded, otherwise the full waypoint list); selection is informational only and never advances the task or sets a Goto. With a task loaded, choose "Resume auto tracking" at the top of the list to revert to automatic tracking.': 'Poprzedni punkt trasy: po załadowaniu zamówionego zadania automatycznie śledzi punkt trasy zadania przed aktywnym etapem (punkt początkowy w przypadku pierwszego etapu). Wyświetla nazwę punktu trasy, różnicę wysokości przybycia w stosunku do bezpiecznej wysokości przybycia i odległość. Kliknij, aby wybrać inny punkt trasy do wyświetlenia (punkty trasy zadania po załadowaniu zadania, w przeciwnym razie pełna lista punktów trasy); wybór ma charakter wyłącznie informacyjny i nigdy nie przyspiesza zadania ani nie ustawia Goto. Po załadowaniu zadania wybierz "Wznów automatyczne śledzenie" na górze listy, aby powrócić do automatycznego śledzenia.',
        'This parameter estimates the height%s at which the average dry updraft strength drops below 225 fpm and is expected to give better quantitative numbers for the maximum cloudless thermalling height than the BL Top height, especially when mixing results from vertical wind shear rather than thermals. (Note: the present assumptions tend to underpredict the max. thermalling height for dry conditions.) In the presence of clouds the maximum thermalling height may instead be limited by the cloud base. Being for "dry" thermals, this parameter omits the effect of "cloudsuck".': 'Parametr ten szacuje wysokość%s, przy której średnia siła suchego prądu wstępującego spada poniżej 225 stóp na minutę i oczekuje się, że da lepsze liczby ilościowe dla maksymalnej bezchmurnej wysokości termicznej niż wysokość BL Top, zwłaszcza gdy mieszanie wynika z pionowego uskoku wiatru, a nie z termiki. (Uwaga: obecne założenia zwykle nie przewidują maksymalnej wysokości termicznej w warunkach suchych.) W obecności chmur maksymalna wysokość termiczna może być ograniczona przez podstawę chmur. W przypadku termiki „suchej” parametr ten pomija efekt „zasysania chmur”.',
        '![](resource:IDB_WARNING_TRIANGLE)\n\n!!! warning\n# Important Safety Notice\n\nBy using XCSoar, you acknowledge and accept the following:\n\n## Limitations\n\n- XCSoar is for **situational awareness only**\n- XCSoar is **not** a FLARM display\n- XCSoar is **not** aviation certified in any way\n- The artificial horizon is **not** fit for any purpose\n- Databanks (airspace, waypoints) may contain errors, be incomplete, or **not** up to date\n- NOTAM display does **not** replace proper pre-flight NOTAM briefing\n- NOTAM data may be incomplete, delayed, filtered, or unavailable\n- XCSoar is **not** guaranteed to be error free\n\n## Pilot Responsibility\n\nThe **Pilot in Command** is always responsible for the safe operation of the aircraft. Never rely solely on XCSoar for navigation or situational awareness.\n\n': '![](resource:IDB_WARNING_TRIANGLE)\n\n!!! warning\n# Ważna uwaga dotycząca bezpieczeństwa\n\nKorzystając z XCSoar, potwierdzasz i akceptujesz, co następuje:\n\n## Ograniczenia\n\n- XCSoar jest dla **tylko świadomość sytuacyjna**\n- XCSoar to **nie** wyświetlacz FLARM\n- XCSoar posiada certyfikat lotniczy **nie** pod każdym względem\n- Sztuczny horyzont **nie** nadaje się do każdego celu\n- Banki danych (przestrzeń powietrzna, punkty orientacyjne) mogą zawierać błędy, być niekompletne lub **nie** aktualne\n- Wyświetlanie NOTAM **nie** zastępuje właściwą odprawę NOTAM przed lotem\n- Dane NOTAM mogą być niekompletne, opóźnione, przefiltrowane lub niedostępne\n- XCSoar to **nie**, które gwarantuje, że jest wolne od błędów\n\n## Odpowiedzialność pilota\n\nZa bezpieczną eksploatację statku powietrznego zawsze odpowiada **Pilot w dowództwie**. Nigdy nie polegaj wyłącznie na XCSoar w zakresie nawigacji lub świadomości sytuacyjnej.\n\n',
        '# Getting Started\n\nTo use XCSoar effectively, configure the following:\n\n- [Restore from backup](xcsoar://dialog/backup) - Restore previous XCSoar data from a USB or SD card (optional)\n\n- [%s] [Map and data](xcsoar://config/site-files) - Download maps, waypoints, and airspace files for your region\n\n- [%s] [Aircraft polar](xcsoar://config/planes) - Set up your aircraft with the correct polar curve\n\n- [%s] [Pilot info](xcsoar://config/logger) - Enter your name and weight\n\n- [%s] [Devices](xcsoar://config/devices) - Connect your flight instruments\n\n- [%s] [WeGlide](xcsoar://config/weglide) - Upload flights automatically to WeGlide\n\n- [%s] [Thermal Information Map](xcsoar://config/weather) - Show thermal locations from thermalmap.info on the map\n\n- [%s] [Safety factors](xcsoar://config/safety) - Set arrival height, terrain clearance and polar degradation\n\n- [%s] [Terrain Display](xcsoar://config/terrain) - Choose terrain colors, shading and contour lines\n\n- [ ] [Live tracking](xcsoar://config/tracking) *(optional)* - Share your position via SkyLines or LiveTrack24\n\nThe easiest way to explore XCSoar is to [replay an existing IGC flight](xcsoar://dialog/replay).': '# Pierwsze kroki\n\nAby efektywnie korzystać z XCSoar, skonfiguruj następujące opcje:\n\n- [Przywróć z kopii zapasowej](xcsoar://dialog/backup) - Przywróć poprzednie dane XCSoar z USB lub karty SD (opcjonalnie)\n\n- [%s] [Mapa i dane](xcsoar://config/site-files) - Pobierz mapy, punkty trasy i pliki przestrzeni powietrznej dla swojego regionu\n\n- [%s] [Polar samolotu](xcsoar://config/planes) - Ustaw swój samolot z poprawną krzywą biegunową\n\n- [%s] [Informacje pilotażowe](xcsoar://config/logger) - Podaj swoje imię i wagę\n\n- [%s] [Urządzenia](xcsoar://config/devices) - Podłącz swoje przyrządy pokładowe\n\n- [%s] [WeGlide](xcsoar://config/weglide) - Przesyłaj loty automatycznie do WeGlide\n\n- [%s] [Mapa informacji termicznych](xcsoar://config/weather) - Pokaż lokalizacje termalne z Thermalmap.info na mapie\n\n- [%s] [Czynniki bezpieczeństwa](xcsoar://config/safety) - Ustaw wysokość dotarcia, prześwit terenu i degradację polarną\n\n- [%s] [Wyświetlacz terenu](xcsoar://config/terrain) - Wybierz kolory terenu, cieniowanie i linie konturowe\n\n- [ ] [Śledzenie na żywo](xcsoar://config/tracking) *(optional)* - Udostępnij swoją pozycję za pośrednictwem SkyLines lub LiveTrack24\n\nNajprostszym sposobem na poznanie XCSoar jest [odtworzyć istniejący lot IGC](xcsoar://dialog/replay).',
        '# Gesture Navigation\n\nXCSoar supports touch gestures on the map:\n\n- ![U](resource:IDB_GESTURE_UP) **Swipe Up** (U): Zoom in\n- ![D](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DOWN) **Swipe Down** (D): Zoom out\n- ![R](resource:IDB_GESTURE_RIGHT) **Swipe Right** (R): Previous screen mode\n- ![L](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LEFT) **Swipe Left** (L): Next screen mode\n- ![UD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_UD) **Up-Down** (UD): Auto zoom\n- ![DU](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DU) **Down-Up** (DU): Menu\n- ![DR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DR) **Down-Right** (DR): Waypoint details\n- ![DL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DL) **Down-Left** (DL): Alternates\n- ![LU](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LU) **Left-Up** (LU): Recently used waypoints\n- ![RD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_RD) **Right-Down** (RD): Task manager\n- ![URD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_URD) **Up-Right-Down** (URD): Analysis\n- ![LDR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LDR) **Left-Down-Right** (LDR): Checklist\n- ![URDL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_URDL) **Up-Right-Down-Left** (URDL): Pan mode\n- ![LDRDL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LDRDL) **Left-Down-Right-Down-Left** (LDRDL): Status\n- ![ULDR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_ULDR) **Up-Left-Down-Right** (ULDR): Quick menu\n\nLong-press on the map to enter Pan mode. Tap while in Pan mode to see nearby waypoints.': '# Nawigacja gestami\n\nXCSoar obsługuje gesty dotykowe na mapie:\n\n- ![U](resource:IDB_GESTURE_UP) **Przesuń w górę** (U): Powiększ\n- ![D](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DOWN) **Przesuń w dół** (D): Pomniejsz\n- ![R](resource:IDB_GESTURE_RIGHT) **Przesuń w prawo** (R): Poprzedni tryb ekranu\n- ![L](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LEFT) **Przesuń w lewo** (L): Tryb następnego ekranu\n- ![UD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_UD) **Góra-dół** (UD): Automatyczne powiększanie\n- ![DU](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DU) **Dół-góra** (DU): Menu\n- ![DR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DR) **Szczery** (DR): Szczegóły punktu trasy\n- ![DL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DL) **Lewy dół** (DL): Alternatywy\n- ![LU](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LU) **Lewa góra** (LU): Ostatnio używane punkty trasy\n- ![RD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_RD) **Prawo w dół** (RD): Menedżer zadań\n- ![URD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_URD) **Góra-prawo-dół** (URD): Analiza\n- ![LDR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LDR) **Lewo-dół-prawo** (LDR): Lista kontrolna\n- ![URDL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_URDL) **Góra-prawo-dół-lewo** (URDL): Tryb panoramowania\n- ![LDRDL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LDRDL) **Lewo-dół-prawo-dół-lewo** (LDRDL): Status\n- ![ULDR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_ULDR) **Góra-lewo-dół-prawo** (ULDR): Szybkie menu\n\nNaciśnij i przytrzymaj mapę, aby przejść do trybu panoramowania. Stuknij w trybie Pan, aby zobaczyć pobliskie punkty trasy.',
    },
    "pt": {
        'Size of waypoint symbols on the map as a percentage of the built-in artwork (list dialogs keep a fixed row icon size).': 'Tamanho dos símbolos de waypoint no mapa como uma porcentagem da arte integrada (as caixas de diálogo de lista mantêm um tamanho de ícone de linha fixo).',
        'Home waypoint name, arrival altitude difference relative to the safety arrival height, and distance. Click to change the home waypoint.': 'Nome do waypoint inicial, diferença de altitude de chegada em relação à altura de chegada de segurança e distância. Clique para alterar o ponto de referência inicial.',
        'Current QNH pressure setting used for barometric altitude calculation. Tap the infobox to open the setup panel and adjust QNH manually.': 'Configuração atual de pressão QNH usada para cálculo de altitude barométrica. Toque na infobox para abrir o painel de configuração e ajustar o QNH manualmente.',
        'This page shows WiFi status when NetworkManager or ConnMan is on D-Bus (e.g. Linux with Wayland or KMS). Open WiFi list to scan and connect when a service is available.': 'Esta página mostra o status do WiFi quando o NetworkManager ou ConnMan está no D-Bus (por exemplo, Linux com Wayland ou KMS). Abra a lista WiFi para verificar e conectar-se quando um serviço estiver disponível.',
        'The terrain can be shaded among slopes to indicate either wind direction, sun position, a geographically fixed shading from North-West, or a screen-relative fixed shading from top left.': 'O terreno pode ser sombreado entre as encostas para indicar a direção do vento, a posição do sol, um sombreamento geograficamente fixo do Noroeste ou um sombreamento fixo relativo à tela no canto superior esquerdo.',
        "Synchronize the glide polar between XCSoar and the device (LXNAV varios). 'Receive' adopts the polar from the device (e.g. for club gliders). 'Send' pushes XCSoar's polar to the device.": "Sincronize o planeio polar entre o XCSoar e o dispositivo (LXNAV varios). 'Receber' adota a polar do dispositivo (por exemplo, para planadores de clube). 'Send' empurra a polar do XCSoar para o dispositivo.",
        'List of active airspace files. Use the Add and Remove buttons to activate or deactivate airspace files respectively. Supported file types are: Openair (.openair /.txt /.air), and Tim Newport-Pearce (.sua).': 'Lista de arquivos de espaço aéreo ativos. Use os botões Adicionar e Remover para ativar ou desativar arquivos de espaço aéreo respectivamente. Os tipos de arquivo suportados são: Openair (.openair /.txt /.air) e Tim Newport-Pearce (.sua).',
        'Signed countdown until the start gate opens or closes (now). Value colour and secondary line reflect gate state at the current time: Waiting (blue), Open (green), Closed (red). PEV window overrides task gate when set.': 'Contagem regressiva assinada até o portão de largada abrir ou fechar (agora). A cor do valor e a linha secundária refletem o estado do portão no momento: Aguardando (azul), Aberto (verde), Fechado (vermelho). A janela PEV substitui o portão de tarefas quando definida.',
        'Tells XCSoar to send its current GPS position to the device as $GPGGA and $GPRMC sentences. Turn off when another GPS source is already feeding the device on the same line. Changes take effect after reconnecting the device.': 'Diz ao XCSoar para enviar sua posição GPS atual para o dispositivo como sentenças $GPGGA e $GPRMC. Desligue quando outra fonte GPS já estiver alimentando o dispositivo na mesma linha. As alterações entram em vigor após reconectar o dispositivo.',
        'Logger pressure altitude when the device provides it (igc_pressure_altitude), otherwise ISA pressure altitude only (1013.25 hPa; not QNH-corrected). Does not show barometric AMSL or GPS height — use other InfoBoxes for navigation.': 'Registrar a altitude de pressão quando o dispositivo a fornecer (igc_pression_altitude), caso contrário, apenas a altitude de pressão ISA (1013,25 hPa; não corrigida por QNH). Não mostra AMSL barométrico ou altura GPS - use outras InfoBoxes para navegação.',
        'Same gate as Start open. Main value is estimated time to reach the start line (MacCready leg when available, else distance / ground speed). Value colour and secondary line reflect gate state at that ETA: Too early (blue), Can start (green), Too late (red).': 'O mesmo portão do Start aberto. O valor principal é o tempo estimado para alcançar a linha de partida (perna MacCready quando disponível, caso contrário, distância / velocidade de solo). A cor do valor e a linha secundária refletem o estado do portão naquele ETA: Muito cedo (azul), Pode começar (verde), Muito tarde (vermelho).',
        'Active waypoint: shows the next task waypoint when an ordered task is loaded, otherwise the Goto waypoint. Displays the waypoint name, arrival altitude difference relative to the safety arrival height, and distance. Click to choose a different waypoint (a task waypoint to skip to that leg, or any waypoint to set as Goto when no task is loaded).': 'Waypoint ativo: mostra o próximo waypoint da tarefa quando uma tarefa ordenada é carregada, caso contrário, o waypoint Goto. Exibe o nome do waypoint, a diferença de altitude de chegada relativa à altura de chegada de segurança e a distância. Clique para escolher um waypoint diferente (um waypoint de tarefa para pular para aquele trecho ou qualquer waypoint para definir como Goto quando nenhuma tarefa for carregada).',
        'FFVP Federal Cup (NetCoupe) on WeGlide. The scored path has at most three turnpoints between start and finish and at least 25 km total. Points are proportional to credited distance, 100 divided by the glider handicap (DAeC-style index), and a success factor of 1.0 for a free flight or 1.2 for a task declared electronically before takeoff. XCSoar live scoring uses a success factor of 1.0 only, not the 1.2 multiplier for declared tasks.': 'Copa Federal FFVP (NetCoupe) no WeGlide. O percurso pontuado tem no máximo três pontos de viragem entre a largada e a chegada e pelo menos 25 km no total. Os pontos são proporcionais à distância creditada, 100 divididos pelo handicap do planador (índice estilo DAeC) e um fator de sucesso de 1,0 para um voo livre ou 1,2 para uma tarefa declarada eletronicamente antes da decolagem. A pontuação ao vivo do XCSoar usa apenas um fator de sucesso de 1,0, não o multiplicador de 1,2 para tarefas declaradas.',
        'Previous waypoint: when an ordered task is loaded, automatically tracks the task waypoint before the active leg (the start waypoint when on the first leg). Displays the waypoint name, arrival altitude difference relative to the safety arrival height, and distance. Click to choose a different waypoint to display (task waypoints when a task is loaded, otherwise the full waypoint list); selection is informational only and never advances the task or sets a Goto. With a task loaded, choose "Resume auto tracking" at the top of the list to revert to automatic tracking.': 'Waypoint anterior: quando uma tarefa ordenada é carregada, rastreia automaticamente o waypoint da tarefa antes do trecho ativo (o waypoint inicial quando no primeiro trecho). Exibe o nome do waypoint, a diferença de altitude de chegada relativa à altura de chegada de segurança e a distância. Clique para escolher um waypoint diferente para exibir (waypoints de tarefas quando uma tarefa é carregada, caso contrário, a lista completa de waypoints); a seleção é apenas informativa e nunca avança a tarefa ou define um Goto. Com uma tarefa carregada, escolha "Retomar rastreamento automático" no topo da lista para reverter para o rastreamento automático.',
        'This parameter estimates the height%s at which the average dry updraft strength drops below 225 fpm and is expected to give better quantitative numbers for the maximum cloudless thermalling height than the BL Top height, especially when mixing results from vertical wind shear rather than thermals. (Note: the present assumptions tend to underpredict the max. thermalling height for dry conditions.) In the presence of clouds the maximum thermalling height may instead be limited by the cloud base. Being for "dry" thermals, this parameter omits the effect of "cloudsuck".': 'Este parâmetro estima a altura%s na qual a resistência média da corrente ascendente seca cai abaixo de 225 fpm e espera-se que forneça melhores números quantitativos para a altura térmica máxima sem nuvens do que a altura BL Top, especialmente ao misturar resultados de cisalhamento vertical do vento em vez de térmicos. (Nota: as presentes suposições tendem a subestimar a altura térmica máxima para condições secas.) Na presença de nuvens, a altura térmica máxima pode, em vez disso, ser limitada pela base da nuvem. Sendo para térmicas “secas”, este parâmetro omite o efeito de “cloudsuck”.',
        '![](resource:IDB_WARNING_TRIANGLE)\n\n!!! warning\n# Important Safety Notice\n\nBy using XCSoar, you acknowledge and accept the following:\n\n## Limitations\n\n- XCSoar is for **situational awareness only**\n- XCSoar is **not** a FLARM display\n- XCSoar is **not** aviation certified in any way\n- The artificial horizon is **not** fit for any purpose\n- Databanks (airspace, waypoints) may contain errors, be incomplete, or **not** up to date\n- NOTAM display does **not** replace proper pre-flight NOTAM briefing\n- NOTAM data may be incomplete, delayed, filtered, or unavailable\n- XCSoar is **not** guaranteed to be error free\n\n## Pilot Responsibility\n\nThe **Pilot in Command** is always responsible for the safe operation of the aircraft. Never rely solely on XCSoar for navigation or situational awareness.\n\n': '![](resource:IDB_WARNING_TRIANGLE)\n\n!!! warning\n# Aviso importante de segurança\n\nAo usar o XCSoar, você reconhece e aceita o seguinte:\n\n## Limitações\n\n- XCSoar é para **apenas consciência situacional**\n- XCSoar é **não** um display FLARM\n- XCSoar é certificado de aviação **não** de alguma forma\n- O horizonte artificial é **não** adequado para qualquer finalidade\n- Bancos de dados (espaço aéreo, waypoints) podem conter erros, estar incompletos ou **não** atualizados\n- A exibição NOTAM **não** substitui o briefing NOTAM pré-voo adequado\n- Os dados NOTAM podem estar incompletos, atrasados, filtrados ou indisponíveis\n- XCSoar é **não** garantido livre de erros\n\n## Responsabilidade do Piloto\n\nA **Piloto em Comando** é sempre responsável pela operação segura da aeronave. Nunca confie apenas no XCSoar para navegação ou consciência situacional.\n\n',
        '# Getting Started\n\nTo use XCSoar effectively, configure the following:\n\n- [Restore from backup](xcsoar://dialog/backup) - Restore previous XCSoar data from a USB or SD card (optional)\n\n- [%s] [Map and data](xcsoar://config/site-files) - Download maps, waypoints, and airspace files for your region\n\n- [%s] [Aircraft polar](xcsoar://config/planes) - Set up your aircraft with the correct polar curve\n\n- [%s] [Pilot info](xcsoar://config/logger) - Enter your name and weight\n\n- [%s] [Devices](xcsoar://config/devices) - Connect your flight instruments\n\n- [%s] [WeGlide](xcsoar://config/weglide) - Upload flights automatically to WeGlide\n\n- [%s] [Thermal Information Map](xcsoar://config/weather) - Show thermal locations from thermalmap.info on the map\n\n- [%s] [Safety factors](xcsoar://config/safety) - Set arrival height, terrain clearance and polar degradation\n\n- [%s] [Terrain Display](xcsoar://config/terrain) - Choose terrain colors, shading and contour lines\n\n- [ ] [Live tracking](xcsoar://config/tracking) *(optional)* - Share your position via SkyLines or LiveTrack24\n\nThe easiest way to explore XCSoar is to [replay an existing IGC flight](xcsoar://dialog/replay).': '# Começando\n\nPara usar o XCSoar efetivamente, configure o seguinte:\n\n- [Restaurar do backup](xcsoar://dialog/backup) - Restaure dados anteriores do XCSoar de um cartão USB ou SD (opcional)\n\n- [%s] [Mapa e dados](xcsoar://config/site-files) - Baixe mapas, pontos de referência e arquivos de espaço aéreo para sua região\n\n- [%s] [Aeronave polar](xcsoar://config/planes) - Configure sua aeronave com a curva polar correta\n\n- [%s] [Informações do piloto](xcsoar://config/logger) - Digite seu nome e peso\n\n- [%s] [Dispositivos](xcsoar://config/devices) - Conecte seus instrumentos de voo\n\n- [%s] [WeGlide](xcsoar://config/weglide) - Carregar voos automaticamente para WeGlide\n\n- [%s] [Mapa de informações térmicas](xcsoar://config/weather) - Mostrar localizações térmicas de Thermalmap.info no mapa\n\n- [%s] [Fatores de segurança](xcsoar://config/safety) - Defina a altura de chegada, a distância ao terreno e a degradação polar\n\n- [%s] [Exibição de terreno](xcsoar://config/terrain) - Escolha cores do terreno, sombreamento e linhas de contorno\n\n- [ ] [Rastreamento ao vivo](xcsoar://config/tracking) *(optional)* - Compartilhe sua posição via SkyLines ou LiveTrack24\n\nA maneira mais fácil de explorar o XCSoar é [reproduzir um voo IGC existente](xcsoar://dialog/replay).',
        '# Gesture Navigation\n\nXCSoar supports touch gestures on the map:\n\n- ![U](resource:IDB_GESTURE_UP) **Swipe Up** (U): Zoom in\n- ![D](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DOWN) **Swipe Down** (D): Zoom out\n- ![R](resource:IDB_GESTURE_RIGHT) **Swipe Right** (R): Previous screen mode\n- ![L](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LEFT) **Swipe Left** (L): Next screen mode\n- ![UD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_UD) **Up-Down** (UD): Auto zoom\n- ![DU](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DU) **Down-Up** (DU): Menu\n- ![DR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DR) **Down-Right** (DR): Waypoint details\n- ![DL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DL) **Down-Left** (DL): Alternates\n- ![LU](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LU) **Left-Up** (LU): Recently used waypoints\n- ![RD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_RD) **Right-Down** (RD): Task manager\n- ![URD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_URD) **Up-Right-Down** (URD): Analysis\n- ![LDR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LDR) **Left-Down-Right** (LDR): Checklist\n- ![URDL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_URDL) **Up-Right-Down-Left** (URDL): Pan mode\n- ![LDRDL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LDRDL) **Left-Down-Right-Down-Left** (LDRDL): Status\n- ![ULDR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_ULDR) **Up-Left-Down-Right** (ULDR): Quick menu\n\nLong-press on the map to enter Pan mode. Tap while in Pan mode to see nearby waypoints.': '# Navegação por gestos\n\nO XCSoar suporta gestos de toque no mapa:\n\n- ![U](resource:IDB_GESTURE_UP) **Deslize para cima** (U): Ampliar\n- ![D](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DOWN) **Deslize para baixo** (D): Diminuir zoom\n- ![R](resource:IDB_GESTURE_RIGHT) **Deslize para a direita** (R): Modo de tela anterior\n- ![L](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LEFT) **Deslize para a esquerda** (L): Modo de próxima tela\n- ![UD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_UD) **De cima para baixo** (UD): Zoom automático\n- ![DU](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DU) **Para baixo** (DU): Menu\n- ![DR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DR) **Abaixo à direita** (DR): Detalhes do ponto de referência\n- ![DL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DL) **Baixo-esquerda** (DL): Suplentes\n- ![LU](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LU) **Esquerda** (LU): Pontos de passagem usados \u200b\u200brecentemente\n- ![RD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_RD) **Direita para baixo** (RD): Gerenciador de tarefas\n- ![URD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_URD) **Cima-Direita-Baixo** (URD): Análise\n- ![LDR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LDR) **Esquerda-Baixo-Direita** (LDR): Lista de verificação\n- ![URDL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_URDL) **Cima-Direita-Baixo-Esquerda** (URDL): Modo panorâmico\n- ![LDRDL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LDRDL) **Esquerda-Baixo-Direita-Baixo-Esquerda** (LDRDL): Status\n- ![ULDR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_ULDR) **Cima-Esquerda-Baixo-Direita** (ULDR): Menu rápido\n\nPressione longamente no mapa para entrar no modo Pan. Toque no modo panorâmico para ver pontos de referência próximos.',
    },
    "pt_BR": {
        'Size of waypoint symbols on the map as a percentage of the built-in artwork (list dialogs keep a fixed row icon size).': 'Tamanho dos símbolos de waypoint no mapa como uma porcentagem da arte integrada (as caixas de diálogo de lista mantêm um tamanho de ícone de linha fixo).',
        'Home waypoint name, arrival altitude difference relative to the safety arrival height, and distance. Click to change the home waypoint.': 'Nome do waypoint inicial, diferença de altitude de chegada em relação à altura de chegada de segurança e distância. Clique para alterar o ponto de referência inicial.',
        'Current QNH pressure setting used for barometric altitude calculation. Tap the infobox to open the setup panel and adjust QNH manually.': 'Configuração atual de pressão QNH usada para cálculo de altitude barométrica. Toque na infobox para abrir o painel de configuração e ajustar o QNH manualmente.',
        'This page shows WiFi status when NetworkManager or ConnMan is on D-Bus (e.g. Linux with Wayland or KMS). Open WiFi list to scan and connect when a service is available.': 'Esta página mostra o status do WiFi quando o NetworkManager ou ConnMan está no D-Bus (por exemplo, Linux com Wayland ou KMS). Abra a lista WiFi para verificar e conectar-se quando um serviço estiver disponível.',
        'The terrain can be shaded among slopes to indicate either wind direction, sun position, a geographically fixed shading from North-West, or a screen-relative fixed shading from top left.': 'O terreno pode ser sombreado entre as encostas para indicar a direção do vento, a posição do sol, um sombreamento geograficamente fixo do Noroeste ou um sombreamento fixo relativo à tela no canto superior esquerdo.',
        "Synchronize the glide polar between XCSoar and the device (LXNAV varios). 'Receive' adopts the polar from the device (e.g. for club gliders). 'Send' pushes XCSoar's polar to the device.": "Sincronize o planeio polar entre o XCSoar e o dispositivo (LXNAV varios). 'Receber' adota a polar do dispositivo (por exemplo, para planadores de clube). 'Send' empurra a polar do XCSoar para o dispositivo.",
        'List of active airspace files. Use the Add and Remove buttons to activate or deactivate airspace files respectively. Supported file types are: Openair (.openair /.txt /.air), and Tim Newport-Pearce (.sua).': 'Lista de arquivos de espaço aéreo ativos. Use os botões Adicionar e Remover para ativar ou desativar arquivos de espaço aéreo respectivamente. Os tipos de arquivo suportados são: Openair (.openair /.txt /.air) e Tim Newport-Pearce (.sua).',
        'Signed countdown until the start gate opens or closes (now). Value colour and secondary line reflect gate state at the current time: Waiting (blue), Open (green), Closed (red). PEV window overrides task gate when set.': 'Contagem regressiva assinada até o portão de largada abrir ou fechar (agora). A cor do valor e a linha secundária refletem o estado do portão no momento: Aguardando (azul), Aberto (verde), Fechado (vermelho). A janela PEV substitui o portão de tarefas quando definida.',
        'Tells XCSoar to send its current GPS position to the device as $GPGGA and $GPRMC sentences. Turn off when another GPS source is already feeding the device on the same line. Changes take effect after reconnecting the device.': 'Diz ao XCSoar para enviar sua posição GPS atual para o dispositivo como sentenças $GPGGA e $GPRMC. Desligue quando outra fonte GPS já estiver alimentando o dispositivo na mesma linha. As alterações entram em vigor após reconectar o dispositivo.',
        'Logger pressure altitude when the device provides it (igc_pressure_altitude), otherwise ISA pressure altitude only (1013.25 hPa; not QNH-corrected). Does not show barometric AMSL or GPS height — use other InfoBoxes for navigation.': 'Registrar a altitude de pressão quando o dispositivo a fornecer (igc_pression_altitude), caso contrário, apenas a altitude de pressão ISA (1013,25 hPa; não corrigida por QNH). Não mostra AMSL barométrico ou altura GPS - use outras InfoBoxes para navegação.',
        'Same gate as Start open. Main value is estimated time to reach the start line (MacCready leg when available, else distance / ground speed). Value colour and secondary line reflect gate state at that ETA: Too early (blue), Can start (green), Too late (red).': 'O mesmo portão do Start aberto. O valor principal é o tempo estimado para alcançar a linha de partida (perna MacCready quando disponível, caso contrário, distância / velocidade de solo). A cor do valor e a linha secundária refletem o estado do portão naquele ETA: Muito cedo (azul), Pode começar (verde), Muito tarde (vermelho).',
        'Active waypoint: shows the next task waypoint when an ordered task is loaded, otherwise the Goto waypoint. Displays the waypoint name, arrival altitude difference relative to the safety arrival height, and distance. Click to choose a different waypoint (a task waypoint to skip to that leg, or any waypoint to set as Goto when no task is loaded).': 'Waypoint ativo: mostra o próximo waypoint da tarefa quando uma tarefa ordenada é carregada, caso contrário, o waypoint Goto. Exibe o nome do waypoint, a diferença de altitude de chegada relativa à altura de chegada de segurança e a distância. Clique para escolher um waypoint diferente (um waypoint de tarefa para pular para aquele trecho ou qualquer waypoint para definir como Goto quando nenhuma tarefa for carregada).',
        'FFVP Federal Cup (NetCoupe) on WeGlide. The scored path has at most three turnpoints between start and finish and at least 25 km total. Points are proportional to credited distance, 100 divided by the glider handicap (DAeC-style index), and a success factor of 1.0 for a free flight or 1.2 for a task declared electronically before takeoff. XCSoar live scoring uses a success factor of 1.0 only, not the 1.2 multiplier for declared tasks.': 'Copa Federal FFVP (NetCoupe) no WeGlide. O percurso pontuado tem no máximo três pontos de viragem entre a largada e a chegada e pelo menos 25 km no total. Os pontos são proporcionais à distância creditada, 100 divididos pelo handicap do planador (índice estilo DAeC) e um fator de sucesso de 1,0 para um voo livre ou 1,2 para uma tarefa declarada eletronicamente antes da decolagem. A pontuação ao vivo do XCSoar usa apenas um fator de sucesso de 1,0, não o multiplicador de 1,2 para tarefas declaradas.',
        'Previous waypoint: when an ordered task is loaded, automatically tracks the task waypoint before the active leg (the start waypoint when on the first leg). Displays the waypoint name, arrival altitude difference relative to the safety arrival height, and distance. Click to choose a different waypoint to display (task waypoints when a task is loaded, otherwise the full waypoint list); selection is informational only and never advances the task or sets a Goto. With a task loaded, choose "Resume auto tracking" at the top of the list to revert to automatic tracking.': 'Waypoint anterior: quando uma tarefa ordenada é carregada, rastreia automaticamente o waypoint da tarefa antes do trecho ativo (o waypoint inicial quando no primeiro trecho). Exibe o nome do waypoint, a diferença de altitude de chegada relativa à altura de chegada de segurança e a distância. Clique para escolher um waypoint diferente para exibir (waypoints de tarefas quando uma tarefa é carregada, caso contrário, a lista completa de waypoints); a seleção é apenas informativa e nunca avança a tarefa ou define um Goto. Com uma tarefa carregada, escolha "Retomar rastreamento automático" no topo da lista para reverter para o rastreamento automático.',
        'This parameter estimates the height%s at which the average dry updraft strength drops below 225 fpm and is expected to give better quantitative numbers for the maximum cloudless thermalling height than the BL Top height, especially when mixing results from vertical wind shear rather than thermals. (Note: the present assumptions tend to underpredict the max. thermalling height for dry conditions.) In the presence of clouds the maximum thermalling height may instead be limited by the cloud base. Being for "dry" thermals, this parameter omits the effect of "cloudsuck".': 'Este parâmetro estima a altura%s na qual a resistência média da corrente ascendente seca cai abaixo de 225 fpm e espera-se que forneça melhores números quantitativos para a altura térmica máxima sem nuvens do que a altura BL Top, especialmente ao misturar resultados de cisalhamento vertical do vento em vez de térmicos. (Nota: as presentes suposições tendem a subestimar a altura térmica máxima para condições secas.) Na presença de nuvens, a altura térmica máxima pode, em vez disso, ser limitada pela base da nuvem. Sendo para térmicas “secas”, este parâmetro omite o efeito de “cloudsuck”.',
        '![](resource:IDB_WARNING_TRIANGLE)\n\n!!! warning\n# Important Safety Notice\n\nBy using XCSoar, you acknowledge and accept the following:\n\n## Limitations\n\n- XCSoar is for **situational awareness only**\n- XCSoar is **not** a FLARM display\n- XCSoar is **not** aviation certified in any way\n- The artificial horizon is **not** fit for any purpose\n- Databanks (airspace, waypoints) may contain errors, be incomplete, or **not** up to date\n- NOTAM display does **not** replace proper pre-flight NOTAM briefing\n- NOTAM data may be incomplete, delayed, filtered, or unavailable\n- XCSoar is **not** guaranteed to be error free\n\n## Pilot Responsibility\n\nThe **Pilot in Command** is always responsible for the safe operation of the aircraft. Never rely solely on XCSoar for navigation or situational awareness.\n\n': '![](resource:IDB_WARNING_TRIANGLE)\n\n!!! warning\n# Aviso importante de segurança\n\nAo usar o XCSoar, você reconhece e aceita o seguinte:\n\n## Limitações\n\n- XCSoar é para **apenas consciência situacional**\n- XCSoar é **não** um display FLARM\n- XCSoar é certificado de aviação **não** de alguma forma\n- O horizonte artificial é **não** adequado para qualquer finalidade\n- Bancos de dados (espaço aéreo, waypoints) podem conter erros, estar incompletos ou **não** atualizados\n- A exibição NOTAM **não** substitui o briefing NOTAM pré-voo adequado\n- Os dados NOTAM podem estar incompletos, atrasados, filtrados ou indisponíveis\n- XCSoar é **não** garantido livre de erros\n\n## Responsabilidade do Piloto\n\nA **Piloto em Comando** é sempre responsável pela operação segura da aeronave. Nunca confie apenas no XCSoar para navegação ou consciência situacional.\n\n',
        '# Getting Started\n\nTo use XCSoar effectively, configure the following:\n\n- [Restore from backup](xcsoar://dialog/backup) - Restore previous XCSoar data from a USB or SD card (optional)\n\n- [%s] [Map and data](xcsoar://config/site-files) - Download maps, waypoints, and airspace files for your region\n\n- [%s] [Aircraft polar](xcsoar://config/planes) - Set up your aircraft with the correct polar curve\n\n- [%s] [Pilot info](xcsoar://config/logger) - Enter your name and weight\n\n- [%s] [Devices](xcsoar://config/devices) - Connect your flight instruments\n\n- [%s] [WeGlide](xcsoar://config/weglide) - Upload flights automatically to WeGlide\n\n- [%s] [Thermal Information Map](xcsoar://config/weather) - Show thermal locations from thermalmap.info on the map\n\n- [%s] [Safety factors](xcsoar://config/safety) - Set arrival height, terrain clearance and polar degradation\n\n- [%s] [Terrain Display](xcsoar://config/terrain) - Choose terrain colors, shading and contour lines\n\n- [ ] [Live tracking](xcsoar://config/tracking) *(optional)* - Share your position via SkyLines or LiveTrack24\n\nThe easiest way to explore XCSoar is to [replay an existing IGC flight](xcsoar://dialog/replay).': '# Começando\n\nPara usar o XCSoar efetivamente, configure o seguinte:\n\n- [Restaurar do backup](xcsoar://dialog/backup) - Restaure dados anteriores do XCSoar de um cartão USB ou SD (opcional)\n\n- [%s] [Mapa e dados](xcsoar://config/site-files) - Baixe mapas, pontos de referência e arquivos de espaço aéreo para sua região\n\n- [%s] [Aeronave polar](xcsoar://config/planes) - Configure sua aeronave com a curva polar correta\n\n- [%s] [Informações do piloto](xcsoar://config/logger) - Digite seu nome e peso\n\n- [%s] [Dispositivos](xcsoar://config/devices) - Conecte seus instrumentos de voo\n\n- [%s] [WeGlide](xcsoar://config/weglide) - Carregar voos automaticamente para WeGlide\n\n- [%s] [Mapa de informações térmicas](xcsoar://config/weather) - Mostrar localizações térmicas de Thermalmap.info no mapa\n\n- [%s] [Fatores de segurança](xcsoar://config/safety) - Defina a altura de chegada, a distância ao terreno e a degradação polar\n\n- [%s] [Exibição de terreno](xcsoar://config/terrain) - Escolha cores do terreno, sombreamento e linhas de contorno\n\n- [ ] [Rastreamento ao vivo](xcsoar://config/tracking) *(optional)* - Compartilhe sua posição via SkyLines ou LiveTrack24\n\nA maneira mais fácil de explorar o XCSoar é [reproduzir um voo IGC existente](xcsoar://dialog/replay).',
        '# Gesture Navigation\n\nXCSoar supports touch gestures on the map:\n\n- ![U](resource:IDB_GESTURE_UP) **Swipe Up** (U): Zoom in\n- ![D](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DOWN) **Swipe Down** (D): Zoom out\n- ![R](resource:IDB_GESTURE_RIGHT) **Swipe Right** (R): Previous screen mode\n- ![L](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LEFT) **Swipe Left** (L): Next screen mode\n- ![UD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_UD) **Up-Down** (UD): Auto zoom\n- ![DU](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DU) **Down-Up** (DU): Menu\n- ![DR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DR) **Down-Right** (DR): Waypoint details\n- ![DL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DL) **Down-Left** (DL): Alternates\n- ![LU](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LU) **Left-Up** (LU): Recently used waypoints\n- ![RD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_RD) **Right-Down** (RD): Task manager\n- ![URD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_URD) **Up-Right-Down** (URD): Analysis\n- ![LDR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LDR) **Left-Down-Right** (LDR): Checklist\n- ![URDL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_URDL) **Up-Right-Down-Left** (URDL): Pan mode\n- ![LDRDL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LDRDL) **Left-Down-Right-Down-Left** (LDRDL): Status\n- ![ULDR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_ULDR) **Up-Left-Down-Right** (ULDR): Quick menu\n\nLong-press on the map to enter Pan mode. Tap while in Pan mode to see nearby waypoints.': '# Navegação por gestos\n\nO XCSoar suporta gestos de toque no mapa:\n\n- ![U](resource:IDB_GESTURE_UP) **Deslize para cima** (U): Ampliar\n- ![D](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DOWN) **Deslize para baixo** (D): Diminuir zoom\n- ![R](resource:IDB_GESTURE_RIGHT) **Deslize para a direita** (R): Modo de tela anterior\n- ![L](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LEFT) **Deslize para a esquerda** (L): Modo de próxima tela\n- ![UD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_UD) **De cima para baixo** (UD): Zoom automático\n- ![DU](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DU) **Para baixo** (DU): Menu\n- ![DR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DR) **Abaixo à direita** (DR): Detalhes do ponto de referência\n- ![DL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DL) **Baixo-esquerda** (DL): Suplentes\n- ![LU](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LU) **Esquerda** (LU): Pontos de passagem usados \u200b\u200brecentemente\n- ![RD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_RD) **Direita para baixo** (RD): Gerenciador de tarefas\n- ![URD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_URD) **Cima-Direita-Baixo** (URD): Análise\n- ![LDR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LDR) **Esquerda-Baixo-Direita** (LDR): Lista de verificação\n- ![URDL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_URDL) **Cima-Direita-Baixo-Esquerda** (URDL): Modo panorâmico\n- ![LDRDL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LDRDL) **Esquerda-Baixo-Direita-Baixo-Esquerda** (LDRDL): Status\n- ![ULDR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_ULDR) **Cima-Esquerda-Baixo-Direita** (ULDR): Menu rápido\n\nPressione longamente no mapa para entrar no modo Pan. Toque no modo panorâmico para ver pontos de referência próximos.',
    },
    "ro": {
        'Size of waypoint symbols on the map as a percentage of the built-in artwork (list dialogs keep a fixed row icon size).': 'Dimensiunea simbolurilor punctelor de referință de pe hartă ca procent din opera de artă încorporată (ferestrele de dialog cu listă păstrează o dimensiune fixă \u200b\u200ba pictogramei de rând).',
        'Home waypoint name, arrival altitude difference relative to the safety arrival height, and distance. Click to change the home waypoint.': 'Numele punctului de trecere de acasă, diferența de altitudine de sosire în raport cu înălțimea de sosire de siguranță și distanță. Faceți clic pentru a schimba punctul de referință de acasă.',
        'Current QNH pressure setting used for barometric altitude calculation. Tap the infobox to open the setup panel and adjust QNH manually.': 'Setarea curentă a presiunii QNH utilizată pentru calculul altitudinii barometrice. Atingeți caseta de informații pentru a deschide panoul de configurare și ajustați manual QNH.',
        'This page shows WiFi status when NetworkManager or ConnMan is on D-Bus (e.g. Linux with Wayland or KMS). Open WiFi list to scan and connect when a service is available.': 'Această pagină arată starea WiFi atunci când NetworkManager sau ConnMan sunt pe D-Bus (de exemplu, Linux cu Wayland sau KMS). Deschideți lista WiFi pentru a scana și a vă conecta atunci când un serviciu este disponibil.',
        'The terrain can be shaded among slopes to indicate either wind direction, sun position, a geographically fixed shading from North-West, or a screen-relative fixed shading from top left.': 'Terenul poate fi umbrit printre versanți pentru a indica fie direcția vântului, poziția soarelui, o umbrire fixă \u200b\u200bdin punct de vedere geografic din nord-vest, fie o umbrire fixă \u200b\u200brelativ la ecran din stânga sus.',
        "Synchronize the glide polar between XCSoar and the device (LXNAV varios). 'Receive' adopts the polar from the device (e.g. for club gliders). 'Send' pushes XCSoar's polar to the device.": 'Sincronizați polara de alunecare între XCSoar și dispozitiv (LXNAV varios). „Receive” adoptă polarul de la dispozitiv (de exemplu, pentru planoare club). „Trimite” împinge polarul XCSoar către dispozitiv.',
        'List of active airspace files. Use the Add and Remove buttons to activate or deactivate airspace files respectively. Supported file types are: Openair (.openair /.txt /.air), and Tim Newport-Pearce (.sua).': 'Lista fișierelor de spațiu aerian activ. Utilizați butoanele Adăugare și Eliminare pentru a activa sau, respectiv, dezactiva fișierele din spațiul aerian. Tipurile de fișiere acceptate sunt: \u200b\u200bOpenair (.openair /.txt /.air) și Tim Newport-Pearce (.sua).',
        'Signed countdown until the start gate opens or closes (now). Value colour and secondary line reflect gate state at the current time: Waiting (blue), Open (green), Closed (red). PEV window overrides task gate when set.': 'Numărătoare inversă semnată până când poarta de start se deschide sau se închide (acum). Culoarea valorii și linia secundară reflectă starea porții la ora curentă: În așteptare (albastru), Deschis (verde), Închis (roșu). Fereastra PEV suprascrie poarta sarcinilor atunci când este setată.',
        'Tells XCSoar to send its current GPS position to the device as $GPGGA and $GPRMC sentences. Turn off when another GPS source is already feeding the device on the same line. Changes take effect after reconnecting the device.': 'Spune XCSoar să-și trimită poziția GPS curentă către dispozitiv ca propoziții $GPGGA și $GPRMC. Opriți când o altă sursă GPS alimentează deja dispozitivul pe aceeași linie. Modificările intră în vigoare după reconectarea dispozitivului.',
        'Logger pressure altitude when the device provides it (igc_pressure_altitude), otherwise ISA pressure altitude only (1013.25 hPa; not QNH-corrected). Does not show barometric AMSL or GPS height — use other InfoBoxes for navigation.': 'Înregistrați altitudinea presiunii atunci când dispozitivul o oferă (igc_pressure_altitude), în caz contrar, doar altitudinea presiunii ISA (1013,25 hPa; nu este corectată cu QNH). Nu afișează înălțimea barometrică AMSL sau GPS - utilizați alte InfoBoxes pentru navigare.',
        'Same gate as Start open. Main value is estimated time to reach the start line (MacCready leg when available, else distance / ground speed). Value colour and secondary line reflect gate state at that ETA: Too early (blue), Can start (green), Too late (red).': 'Aceeași poartă ca Start deschisă. Valoarea principală este timpul estimat pentru a ajunge la linia de start (picior MacCready când este disponibil, altfel distanța / viteza la sol). Culoarea valorii și linia secundară reflectă starea porții la acel ETA: Prea devreme (albastru), Poate începe (verde), Prea târziu (roșu).',
        'Active waypoint: shows the next task waypoint when an ordered task is loaded, otherwise the Goto waypoint. Displays the waypoint name, arrival altitude difference relative to the safety arrival height, and distance. Click to choose a different waypoint (a task waypoint to skip to that leg, or any waypoint to set as Goto when no task is loaded).': 'Punct de trecere activ: afișează următorul punct de trecere al sarcinii atunci când este încărcată o sarcină ordonată, în caz contrar, punctul de trecere. Afișează numele punctului de trecere, diferența de altitudine de sosire în raport cu înălțimea de sosire de siguranță și distanță. Faceți clic pentru a alege un alt punct de trecere (un punct de trecere al sarcinii pentru a trece la acel segment sau orice punct de referință pe care să îl setați ca Goto când nu este încărcată nicio sarcină).',
        'FFVP Federal Cup (NetCoupe) on WeGlide. The scored path has at most three turnpoints between start and finish and at least 25 km total. Points are proportional to credited distance, 100 divided by the glider handicap (DAeC-style index), and a success factor of 1.0 for a free flight or 1.2 for a task declared electronically before takeoff. XCSoar live scoring uses a success factor of 1.0 only, not the 1.2 multiplier for declared tasks.': 'Cupa Federală FFVP (NetCoupe) pe WeGlide. Traseul punctat are cel mult trei puncte de cotitură între start și sosire și cel puțin 25 km în total. Punctele sunt proporționale cu distanța creditată, 100 împărțit la handicapul planorului (indicele în stil DAeC) și un factor de succes de 1,0 pentru un zbor liber sau 1,2 pentru o sarcină declarată electronic înainte de decolare. Scorul live XCSoar folosește doar un factor de succes de 1,0, nu multiplicatorul de 1,2 pentru sarcinile declarate.',
        'Previous waypoint: when an ordered task is loaded, automatically tracks the task waypoint before the active leg (the start waypoint when on the first leg). Displays the waypoint name, arrival altitude difference relative to the safety arrival height, and distance. Click to choose a different waypoint to display (task waypoints when a task is loaded, otherwise the full waypoint list); selection is informational only and never advances the task or sets a Goto. With a task loaded, choose "Resume auto tracking" at the top of the list to revert to automatic tracking.': 'Punct de trecere anterior: atunci când o sarcină comandată este încărcată, urmărește automat punctul de referință al sarcinii înainte de etapa activă (punctul de pornire când se află pe primul pas). Afișează numele punctului de trecere, diferența de altitudine de sosire în raport cu înălțimea de sosire de siguranță și distanță. Faceți clic pentru a alege un alt punct de trecere de afișat (puncte de trecere a sarcinii atunci când o sarcină este încărcată, în caz contrar, lista completă a punctelor de trecere); selecția este doar informativă și nu avansează niciodată sarcina sau setează un Goto. Cu o sarcină încărcată, alegeți "Reluați urmărirea automată" în partea de sus a listei pentru a reveni la urmărirea automată.',
        'This parameter estimates the height%s at which the average dry updraft strength drops below 225 fpm and is expected to give better quantitative numbers for the maximum cloudless thermalling height than the BL Top height, especially when mixing results from vertical wind shear rather than thermals. (Note: the present assumptions tend to underpredict the max. thermalling height for dry conditions.) In the presence of clouds the maximum thermalling height may instead be limited by the cloud base. Being for "dry" thermals, this parameter omits the effect of "cloudsuck".': 'Acest parametru estimează înălțimea %s la care puterea medie a curentului ascendent uscat scade sub 225 fpm și este de așteptat să ofere numere cantitative mai bune pentru înălțimea termică maximă fără nori decât înălțimea BL Top, mai ales atunci când amestecul rezultate de la forfecarea verticală a vântului, mai degrabă decât de la termică. (Notă: ipotezele prezente au tendința de a subestima înălțimea maximă termică pentru condiții uscate.) În prezența norilor, înălțimea maximă termică poate fi limitată de baza norilor. Fiind pentru termice „uscate”, acest parametru omite efectul de „sugere de nori”.',
        '![](resource:IDB_WARNING_TRIANGLE)\n\n!!! warning\n# Important Safety Notice\n\nBy using XCSoar, you acknowledge and accept the following:\n\n## Limitations\n\n- XCSoar is for **situational awareness only**\n- XCSoar is **not** a FLARM display\n- XCSoar is **not** aviation certified in any way\n- The artificial horizon is **not** fit for any purpose\n- Databanks (airspace, waypoints) may contain errors, be incomplete, or **not** up to date\n- NOTAM display does **not** replace proper pre-flight NOTAM briefing\n- NOTAM data may be incomplete, delayed, filtered, or unavailable\n- XCSoar is **not** guaranteed to be error free\n\n## Pilot Responsibility\n\nThe **Pilot in Command** is always responsible for the safe operation of the aircraft. Never rely solely on XCSoar for navigation or situational awareness.\n\n': '![](resource:IDB_WARNING_TRIANGLE)\n\n!!! warning\n# Notă importantă de siguranță\n\nPrin utilizarea XCSoar, luați la cunoștință și acceptați următoarele:\n\n## Limitări\n\n- XCSoar este pentru **numai conștientizarea situației**\n- XCSoar este **nu** un afișaj FLARM\n- XCSoar este certificat de aviație **nu** în orice fel\n- Orizontul artificial este **nu** potrivit pentru orice scop\n- Băncile de date (spațiu aerian, puncte de trecere) pot conține erori, pot fi incomplete sau **nu** actualizate\n- Afișarea NOTAM-ului **nu** înlocuiește informarea NOTAM înainte de zbor\n- Datele NOTAM pot fi incomplete, întârziate, filtrate sau indisponibile\n- XCSoar este **nu** garantat a fi fără erori\n\n## Responsabilitatea pilotului\n\n**Pilot la comandă** este întotdeauna responsabil pentru operarea în siguranță a aeronavei. Nu vă bazați niciodată exclusiv pe XCSoar pentru navigare sau cunoașterea situației.\n\n',
        '# Getting Started\n\nTo use XCSoar effectively, configure the following:\n\n- [Restore from backup](xcsoar://dialog/backup) - Restore previous XCSoar data from a USB or SD card (optional)\n\n- [%s] [Map and data](xcsoar://config/site-files) - Download maps, waypoints, and airspace files for your region\n\n- [%s] [Aircraft polar](xcsoar://config/planes) - Set up your aircraft with the correct polar curve\n\n- [%s] [Pilot info](xcsoar://config/logger) - Enter your name and weight\n\n- [%s] [Devices](xcsoar://config/devices) - Connect your flight instruments\n\n- [%s] [WeGlide](xcsoar://config/weglide) - Upload flights automatically to WeGlide\n\n- [%s] [Thermal Information Map](xcsoar://config/weather) - Show thermal locations from thermalmap.info on the map\n\n- [%s] [Safety factors](xcsoar://config/safety) - Set arrival height, terrain clearance and polar degradation\n\n- [%s] [Terrain Display](xcsoar://config/terrain) - Choose terrain colors, shading and contour lines\n\n- [ ] [Live tracking](xcsoar://config/tracking) *(optional)* - Share your position via SkyLines or LiveTrack24\n\nThe easiest way to explore XCSoar is to [replay an existing IGC flight](xcsoar://dialog/replay).': '# Noțiuni de bază\n\nPentru a utiliza XCSoar eficient, configurați următoarele:\n\n- [Restaurați din backup](xcsoar://dialog/backup) - Restaurați datele XCSoar anterioare de pe un card USB sau SD (opțional)\n\n- [%s] [Hartă și date](xcsoar://config/site-files) - Descărcați hărți, puncte de referință și fișiere de spațiu aerian pentru regiunea dvs\n\n- [%s] [Avioane polare](xcsoar://config/planes) - Configurați-vă aeronava cu curba polară corectă\n\n- [%s] [Informații pilot](xcsoar://config/logger) - Introduceți numele și greutatea dvs\n\n- [%s] [Dispozitive](xcsoar://config/devices) - Conectați-vă instrumentele de zbor\n\n- [%s] [WeGlide](xcsoar://config/weglide) - Încărcați zboruri automat în WeGlide\n\n- [%s] [Harta Informatii Termice](xcsoar://config/weather) - Afișați locațiile termice de pe thermalmap.info pe hartă\n\n- [%s] [Factori de siguranță](xcsoar://config/safety) - Setați înălțimea de sosire, spațiul liber și degradarea polară\n\n- [%s] [Afișare teren](xcsoar://config/terrain) - Alegeți culorile terenului, umbrirea și liniile de contur\n\n- [ ] [Urmărire în direct](xcsoar://config/tracking) *(optional)* - Partajați-vă poziția prin SkyLines sau LiveTrack24\n\nCel mai simplu mod de a explora XCSoar este să [reluați un zbor IGC existent](xcsoar://dialog/replay).',
        '# Gesture Navigation\n\nXCSoar supports touch gestures on the map:\n\n- ![U](resource:IDB_GESTURE_UP) **Swipe Up** (U): Zoom in\n- ![D](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DOWN) **Swipe Down** (D): Zoom out\n- ![R](resource:IDB_GESTURE_RIGHT) **Swipe Right** (R): Previous screen mode\n- ![L](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LEFT) **Swipe Left** (L): Next screen mode\n- ![UD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_UD) **Up-Down** (UD): Auto zoom\n- ![DU](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DU) **Down-Up** (DU): Menu\n- ![DR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DR) **Down-Right** (DR): Waypoint details\n- ![DL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DL) **Down-Left** (DL): Alternates\n- ![LU](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LU) **Left-Up** (LU): Recently used waypoints\n- ![RD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_RD) **Right-Down** (RD): Task manager\n- ![URD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_URD) **Up-Right-Down** (URD): Analysis\n- ![LDR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LDR) **Left-Down-Right** (LDR): Checklist\n- ![URDL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_URDL) **Up-Right-Down-Left** (URDL): Pan mode\n- ![LDRDL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LDRDL) **Left-Down-Right-Down-Left** (LDRDL): Status\n- ![ULDR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_ULDR) **Up-Left-Down-Right** (ULDR): Quick menu\n\nLong-press on the map to enter Pan mode. Tap while in Pan mode to see nearby waypoints.': '# Navigare prin gesturi\n\nXCSoar acceptă gesturi tactile pe hartă:\n\n- ![U](resource:IDB_GESTURE_UP) **Glisați în sus** (U): Măriți\n- ![D](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DOWN) **Glisați în jos** (D): Micșorați\n- ![R](resource:IDB_GESTURE_RIGHT) **Glisați spre dreapta** (R): Modul ecran anterior\n- ![L](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LEFT) **Glisați spre stânga** (L): Următorul mod de ecran\n- ![UD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_UD) **Sus-Jos** (UD): Zoom automat\n- ![DU](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DU) **Jos-Sus** (DU): Meniu\n- ![DR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DR) **Jos-Dreapta** (DR): Detalii waypoint\n- ![DL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DL) **Jos-Stânga** (DL): supleanți\n- ![LU](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LU) **Stânga-Sus** (LU): Puncte de trecere utilizate recent\n- ![RD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_RD) **Dreapta-Jos** (RD): Manager de sarcini\n- ![URD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_URD) **Sus-Dreapta-Jos** (URD): Analiză\n- ![LDR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LDR) **Stânga-Jos-Dreapta** (LDR): Lista de verificare\n- ![URDL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_URDL) **Sus-Dreapta-Jos-Stânga** (URDL): Modul Pan\n- ![LDRDL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LDRDL) **Stânga-Jos-Dreapta-Jos-Stânga** (LDRDL): Stare\n- ![ULDR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_ULDR) **Sus-Stânga-Jos-Dreapta** (ULDR): Meniu rapid\n\nApăsați lung pe hartă pentru a intra în modul Pan. Atingeți în modul Pan pentru a vedea punctele de referință din apropiere.',
    },
    "ru": {
        'Size of waypoint symbols on the map as a percentage of the built-in artwork (list dialogs keep a fixed row icon size).': 'Размер символов путевых точек на карте в процентах от встроенного изображения (в диалоговых окнах списков сохраняется фиксированный размер значков строк).',
        'Home waypoint name, arrival altitude difference relative to the safety arrival height, and distance. Click to change the home waypoint.': 'Название домашней маршрутной точки, разница высот прибытия относительно безопасной высоты прибытия и расстояние. Нажмите, чтобы изменить домашнюю точку.',
        'Current QNH pressure setting used for barometric altitude calculation. Tap the infobox to open the setup panel and adjust QNH manually.': 'Текущая настройка давления QNH, используемая для расчета барометрической высоты. Коснитесь информационного окна, чтобы открыть панель настройки и настроить QNH вручную.',
        'This page shows WiFi status when NetworkManager or ConnMan is on D-Bus (e.g. Linux with Wayland or KMS). Open WiFi list to scan and connect when a service is available.': 'На этой странице отображается состояние Wi-Fi, когда NetworkManager или ConnMan подключены к D-Bus (например, Linux с Wayland или KMS). Откройте список Wi-Fi для сканирования и подключения, когда услуга будет доступна.',
        'The terrain can be shaded among slopes to indicate either wind direction, sun position, a geographically fixed shading from North-West, or a screen-relative fixed shading from top left.': 'Рельеф между склонами можно заштриховать, чтобы указать направление ветра, положение солнца, географически фиксированную затенение с северо-запада или фиксированную затенение относительно экрана сверху слева.',
        "Synchronize the glide polar between XCSoar and the device (LXNAV varios). 'Receive' adopts the polar from the device (e.g. for club gliders). 'Send' pushes XCSoar's polar to the device.": 'Синхронизируйте полярную полярку между XCSoar и устройством (варианты LXNAV). «Прием» принимает поляру устройства (например, для клубных планеров). «Отправить» отправляет поляру XCSoar на устройство.',
        'List of active airspace files. Use the Add and Remove buttons to activate or deactivate airspace files respectively. Supported file types are: Openair (.openair /.txt /.air), and Tim Newport-Pearce (.sua).': 'Список активных файлов воздушного пространства. Используйте кнопки «Добавить» и «Удалить», чтобы активировать или деактивировать файлы воздушного пространства соответственно. Поддерживаемые типы файлов: Openair (.openair/.txt/.air) и Тим Ньюпорт-Пирс (.sua).',
        'Signed countdown until the start gate opens or closes (now). Value colour and secondary line reflect gate state at the current time: Waiting (blue), Open (green), Closed (red). PEV window overrides task gate when set.': 'Подписанный обратный отсчет до открытия или закрытия стартовых ворот (сейчас). Цвет значения и дополнительная линия отражают состояние ворот в текущий момент: Ожидание (синий), Открыто (зеленое), Закрыто (красное). Окно PEV переопределяет ворота задачи, если оно установлено.',
        'Tells XCSoar to send its current GPS position to the device as $GPGGA and $GPRMC sentences. Turn off when another GPS source is already feeding the device on the same line. Changes take effect after reconnecting the device.': 'Указывает XCSoar отправить на устройство свою текущую позицию GPS в виде предложений $GPGGA и $GPRMC. Выключите, когда другой источник GPS уже передает сигнал устройству по той же линии. Изменения вступят в силу после переподключения устройства.',
        'Logger pressure altitude when the device provides it (igc_pressure_altitude), otherwise ISA pressure altitude only (1013.25 hPa; not QNH-corrected). Does not show barometric AMSL or GPS height — use other InfoBoxes for navigation.': 'Регистратор барометрической высоты, когда устройство предоставляет ее (igc_pressure_altitude), в противном случае только барометрическая высота ISA (1013,25 гПа; без поправки QNH). Не показывает барометрическую высоту AMSL или GPS — для навигации используйте другие информационные окна.',
        'Same gate as Start open. Main value is estimated time to reach the start line (MacCready leg when available, else distance / ground speed). Value colour and secondary line reflect gate state at that ETA: Too early (blue), Can start (green), Too late (red).': 'Те же ворота, что и Старт, открыты. Основное значение – это расчетное время достижения стартовой линии (участок Маккриди, если он доступен, иначе расстояние/путевая скорость). Цвет значения и дополнительная линия отражают состояние ворот в это расчетное время прибытия: слишком рано (синий), можно начать (зеленый), слишком поздно (красный).',
        'Active waypoint: shows the next task waypoint when an ordered task is loaded, otherwise the Goto waypoint. Displays the waypoint name, arrival altitude difference relative to the safety arrival height, and distance. Click to choose a different waypoint (a task waypoint to skip to that leg, or any waypoint to set as Goto when no task is loaded).': 'Активная путевая точка: показывает следующую путевую точку задачи при загрузке заказанной задачи, в противном случае — путевую точку «Перейти». Отображает название маршрутной точки, разницу высот прибытия относительно безопасной высоты прибытия и расстояние. Нажмите, чтобы выбрать другую путевую точку (путевую точку задачи, чтобы перейти к этому этапу, или любую путевую точку, которую можно установить как «Перейти», когда задача не загружена).',
        'FFVP Federal Cup (NetCoupe) on WeGlide. The scored path has at most three turnpoints between start and finish and at least 25 km total. Points are proportional to credited distance, 100 divided by the glider handicap (DAeC-style index), and a success factor of 1.0 for a free flight or 1.2 for a task declared electronically before takeoff. XCSoar live scoring uses a success factor of 1.0 only, not the 1.2 multiplier for declared tasks.': 'Федеральный кубок FFVP (NetCoupe) на WeGlide. Засчитанный маршрут имеет не более трех поворотных точек между стартом и финишем и имеет общую протяженность не менее 25 км. Очки пропорциональны зачисленному расстоянию, 100 делят на гандикап планера (индекс в стиле DAeC) и коэффициенту успеха 1,0 для свободного полета или 1,2 для задания, объявленного в электронном виде перед взлетом. Для оценки XCSoar в реальном времени используется только коэффициент успеха 1,0, а не множитель 1,2 для заявленных задач.',
        'Previous waypoint: when an ordered task is loaded, automatically tracks the task waypoint before the active leg (the start waypoint when on the first leg). Displays the waypoint name, arrival altitude difference relative to the safety arrival height, and distance. Click to choose a different waypoint to display (task waypoints when a task is loaded, otherwise the full waypoint list); selection is informational only and never advances the task or sets a Goto. With a task loaded, choose "Resume auto tracking" at the top of the list to revert to automatic tracking.': 'Предыдущая путевая точка: при загрузке заказанного задания автоматически отслеживается путевая точка задачи перед активным этапом (начальная путевая точка на первом этапе). Отображает название маршрутной точки, разницу высот прибытия относительно безопасной высоты прибытия и расстояние. Нажмите, чтобы выбрать другую путевую точку для отображения (путевые точки задачи, когда задача загружена, в противном случае — полный список путевых точек); выбор носит исключительно информационный характер и никогда не продвигает задачу и не устанавливает переход к шагу. Загрузив задачу, выберите "Возобновить автоматическое отслеживание" вверху списка, чтобы вернуться к автоматическому отслеживанию.',
        'This parameter estimates the height%s at which the average dry updraft strength drops below 225 fpm and is expected to give better quantitative numbers for the maximum cloudless thermalling height than the BL Top height, especially when mixing results from vertical wind shear rather than thermals. (Note: the present assumptions tend to underpredict the max. thermalling height for dry conditions.) In the presence of clouds the maximum thermalling height may instead be limited by the cloud base. Being for "dry" thermals, this parameter omits the effect of "cloudsuck".': 'Этот параметр оценивает высоту %s, на которой средняя сила сухого восходящего потока падает ниже 225 футов в минуту, и, как ожидается, даст лучшие количественные значения для максимальной высоты безоблачного термического процесса, чем высота BL Top, особенно когда смешивание происходит в результате вертикального сдвига ветра, а не термических потоков. (Примечание: существующие предположения имеют тенденцию занижать максимальную высоту термического образования для засушливых условий.) При наличии облаков максимальная высота термического образования может вместо этого ограничиваться нижней границей облака. Поскольку этот параметр предназначен для «сухих» термиков, он не учитывает эффект «засасывания облаков».',
        '![](resource:IDB_WARNING_TRIANGLE)\n\n!!! warning\n# Important Safety Notice\n\nBy using XCSoar, you acknowledge and accept the following:\n\n## Limitations\n\n- XCSoar is for **situational awareness only**\n- XCSoar is **not** a FLARM display\n- XCSoar is **not** aviation certified in any way\n- The artificial horizon is **not** fit for any purpose\n- Databanks (airspace, waypoints) may contain errors, be incomplete, or **not** up to date\n- NOTAM display does **not** replace proper pre-flight NOTAM briefing\n- NOTAM data may be incomplete, delayed, filtered, or unavailable\n- XCSoar is **not** guaranteed to be error free\n\n## Pilot Responsibility\n\nThe **Pilot in Command** is always responsible for the safe operation of the aircraft. Never rely solely on XCSoar for navigation or situational awareness.\n\n': '![](resource:IDB_WARNING_TRIANGLE)\n\n!!! warning\n# Важное уведомление о безопасности\n\nИспользуя XCSoar, вы признаете и принимаете следующее:\n\n## Ограничения\n\n- XCSoar для **только ситуационная осведомленность**\n- XCSoar — это **нет** дисплей FLARM.\n- XCSoar имеет авиационный сертификат **нет** в любом случае.\n- Искусственный горизонт **нет** пригоден для любых целей\n- Банки данных (воздушное пространство, путевые точки) могут содержать ошибки, быть неполными или неактуальными.\n- Дисплей NOTAM заменяет **нет** надлежащий предполетный инструктаж по NOTAM\n- Данные NOTAM могут быть неполными, задержанными, отфильтрованными или недоступными.\n- XCSoar - это **нет**, гарантированно безошибочный.\n\n## Ответственность пилота\n\n**Пилот в команде** всегда несет ответственность за безопасную эксплуатацию самолета. Никогда не полагайтесь исключительно на XCSoar в вопросах навигации или ситуационной осведомленности.\n\n',
        '# Getting Started\n\nTo use XCSoar effectively, configure the following:\n\n- [Restore from backup](xcsoar://dialog/backup) - Restore previous XCSoar data from a USB or SD card (optional)\n\n- [%s] [Map and data](xcsoar://config/site-files) - Download maps, waypoints, and airspace files for your region\n\n- [%s] [Aircraft polar](xcsoar://config/planes) - Set up your aircraft with the correct polar curve\n\n- [%s] [Pilot info](xcsoar://config/logger) - Enter your name and weight\n\n- [%s] [Devices](xcsoar://config/devices) - Connect your flight instruments\n\n- [%s] [WeGlide](xcsoar://config/weglide) - Upload flights automatically to WeGlide\n\n- [%s] [Thermal Information Map](xcsoar://config/weather) - Show thermal locations from thermalmap.info on the map\n\n- [%s] [Safety factors](xcsoar://config/safety) - Set arrival height, terrain clearance and polar degradation\n\n- [%s] [Terrain Display](xcsoar://config/terrain) - Choose terrain colors, shading and contour lines\n\n- [ ] [Live tracking](xcsoar://config/tracking) *(optional)* - Share your position via SkyLines or LiveTrack24\n\nThe easiest way to explore XCSoar is to [replay an existing IGC flight](xcsoar://dialog/replay).': '# Начиная\n\nЧтобы эффективно использовать XCSoar, настройте следующее:\n\n- [Восстановление из резервной копии](xcsoar://dialog/backup) - Восстановите предыдущие данные XCSoar с USB или SD-карты (необязательно)\n\n- [%s] [Карта и данные](xcsoar://config/site-files) - Загрузите карты, путевые точки и файлы воздушного пространства для вашего региона.\n\n- [%s] [Самолет полярный](xcsoar://config/planes) - Настройте свой самолет на правильную полярную кривую.\n\n- [%s] [Информация о пилоте](xcsoar://config/logger) - Введите свое имя и вес\n\n- [%s] [Устройства](xcsoar://config/devices) - Подключите свои летные приборы\n\n- [%s] [WeGlide](xcsoar://config/weglide) - Автоматическая загрузка рейсов в WeGlide\n\n- [%s] [Термальная информационная карта](xcsoar://config/weather) - Показать на карте термальные объекты с сайта Thermalmap.info.\n\n- [%s] [Факторы безопасности](xcsoar://config/safety) - Установите высоту прибытия, просвет и полярную деградацию.\n\n- [%s] [Отображение местности](xcsoar://config/terrain) - Выбирайте цвета местности, штриховку и контурные линии.\n\n- [ ] [Живое отслеживание](xcsoar://config/tracking) *(optional)* - Поделитесь своей позицией через SkyLines или LiveTrack24.\n\nСамый простой способ изучить XCSoar — это [воспроизвести существующий полет IGC](xcsoar://dialog/replay).',
        '# Gesture Navigation\n\nXCSoar supports touch gestures on the map:\n\n- ![U](resource:IDB_GESTURE_UP) **Swipe Up** (U): Zoom in\n- ![D](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DOWN) **Swipe Down** (D): Zoom out\n- ![R](resource:IDB_GESTURE_RIGHT) **Swipe Right** (R): Previous screen mode\n- ![L](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LEFT) **Swipe Left** (L): Next screen mode\n- ![UD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_UD) **Up-Down** (UD): Auto zoom\n- ![DU](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DU) **Down-Up** (DU): Menu\n- ![DR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DR) **Down-Right** (DR): Waypoint details\n- ![DL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DL) **Down-Left** (DL): Alternates\n- ![LU](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LU) **Left-Up** (LU): Recently used waypoints\n- ![RD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_RD) **Right-Down** (RD): Task manager\n- ![URD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_URD) **Up-Right-Down** (URD): Analysis\n- ![LDR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LDR) **Left-Down-Right** (LDR): Checklist\n- ![URDL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_URDL) **Up-Right-Down-Left** (URDL): Pan mode\n- ![LDRDL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LDRDL) **Left-Down-Right-Down-Left** (LDRDL): Status\n- ![ULDR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_ULDR) **Up-Left-Down-Right** (ULDR): Quick menu\n\nLong-press on the map to enter Pan mode. Tap while in Pan mode to see nearby waypoints.': '# Жестовая навигация\n\nXCSoar поддерживает сенсорные жесты на карте:\n\n- ![U](resource:IDB_GESTURE_UP) **Проведите пальцем вверх** (U): Увеличить масштаб\n- ![D](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DOWN) **Проведите пальцем вниз** (D): Уменьшить масштаб\n- ![R](resource:IDB_GESTURE_RIGHT) **Проведите пальцем вправо** (R): Предыдущий режим экрана\n- ![L](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LEFT) **Проведите пальцем влево** (L): Следующий режим экрана\n- ![UD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_UD) **Вверх-Вниз** (UD): Автоматическое масштабирование\n- ![DU](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DU) **Вниз-Вверх** (DU): Меню\n- ![DR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DR) **Вниз-вправо** (DR): Детали маршрутной точки\n- ![DL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DL) **Вниз-влево** (DL): Заместители\n- ![LU](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LU) **Левый вверх** (LU): Недавно использованные путевые точки\n- ![RD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_RD) **Вправо-вниз** (RD): Диспетчер задач\n- ![URD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_URD) **Вверх-Вправо-Вниз** (URD): Анализ\n- ![LDR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LDR) **Влево-вниз-вправо** (LDR): Контрольный список\n- ![URDL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_URDL) **Вверх-Вправо-Вниз-Влево** (URDL): Режим панорамирования\n- ![LDRDL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LDRDL) **Влево-вниз-вправо-вниз-влево** (LDRDL): Статус\n- ![ULDR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_ULDR) **Вверх-влево-вниз-вправо** (ULDR): Быстрое меню\n\nНажмите и удерживайте карту, чтобы войти в режим панорамирования. Нажмите в режиме панорамирования, чтобы увидеть ближайшие путевые точки.',
    },
    "sk": {
        'Size of waypoint symbols on the map as a percentage of the built-in artwork (list dialogs keep a fixed row icon size).': 'Veľkosť symbolov trasových bodov na mape ako percento vstavanej kresby (dialógové okná so zoznamom majú pevnú veľkosť ikon riadkov).',
        'Home waypoint name, arrival altitude difference relative to the safety arrival height, and distance. Click to change the home waypoint.': 'Názov trasového bodu domov, rozdiel nadmorskej výšky príletu vo vzťahu k bezpečnej výške príletu a vzdialenosť. Kliknutím zmeníte trasový bod domov.',
        'Current QNH pressure setting used for barometric altitude calculation. Tap the infobox to open the setup panel and adjust QNH manually.': 'Aktuálne nastavenie tlaku QNH používané na výpočet barometrickej nadmorskej výšky. Klepnutím na infobox otvoríte panel nastavení a manuálne upravíte QNH.',
        'This page shows WiFi status when NetworkManager or ConnMan is on D-Bus (e.g. Linux with Wayland or KMS). Open WiFi list to scan and connect when a service is available.': 'Táto stránka zobrazuje stav WiFi, keď je NetworkManager alebo ConnMan na D-Bus (napr. Linux s Wayland alebo KMS). Otvorte zoznam WiFi na skenovanie a pripojenie, keď je dostupná služba.',
        'The terrain can be shaded among slopes to indicate either wind direction, sun position, a geographically fixed shading from North-West, or a screen-relative fixed shading from top left.': 'Terén môže byť zatienený medzi svahmi, aby sa ukázal buď smer vetra, poloha slnka, geograficky fixné tienenie zo severozápadu, alebo relatívne fixné tienenie vľavo hore.',
        "Synchronize the glide polar between XCSoar and the device (LXNAV varios). 'Receive' adopts the polar from the device (e.g. for club gliders). 'Send' pushes XCSoar's polar to the device.": "Synchronizujte kĺzavú polárnu medzi XCSoar a zariadením (LXNAV varios). „Prijať“ preberá polárku zo zariadenia (napr. pre klubové vetrone). 'Odoslať' posunie polárku XCSoar do zariadenia.",
        'List of active airspace files. Use the Add and Remove buttons to activate or deactivate airspace files respectively. Supported file types are: Openair (.openair /.txt /.air), and Tim Newport-Pearce (.sua).': 'Zoznam aktívnych súborov vzdušného priestoru. Pomocou tlačidiel Pridať a Odstrániť môžete súbory vzdušného priestoru aktivovať alebo deaktivovať. Podporované typy súborov sú: Openair (.openair /.txt /.air) a Tim Newport-Pearce (.sua).',
        'Signed countdown until the start gate opens or closes (now). Value colour and secondary line reflect gate state at the current time: Waiting (blue), Open (green), Closed (red). PEV window overrides task gate when set.': 'Podpísané odpočítavanie do otvorenia alebo zatvorenia štartovacej brány (teraz). Farba hodnoty a sekundárna čiara odrážajú stav brány v aktuálnom čase: Čaká (modrá), Otvorená (zelená), Zatvorená (červená). Okno PEV prepíše bránu úlohy, keď je nastavené.',
        'Tells XCSoar to send its current GPS position to the device as $GPGGA and $GPRMC sentences. Turn off when another GPS source is already feeding the device on the same line. Changes take effect after reconnecting the device.': 'Povie XCSoar, aby odoslal svoju aktuálnu polohu GPS do zariadenia ako vety $GPGGA a $GPRMC. Vypnite, keď iný zdroj GPS už napája zariadenie na rovnakej linke. Zmeny sa prejavia po opätovnom pripojení zariadenia.',
        'Logger pressure altitude when the device provides it (igc_pressure_altitude), otherwise ISA pressure altitude only (1013.25 hPa; not QNH-corrected). Does not show barometric AMSL or GPS height — use other InfoBoxes for navigation.': 'Zaznamenáva tlakovú výšku, keď ju zariadenie poskytuje (igc_pressure_altitude), inak iba tlakovú výšku ISA (1013,25 hPa; bez korekcie QNH). Nezobrazuje barometrickú výšku AMSL ani GPS – na navigáciu použite iné informačné boxy.',
        'Same gate as Start open. Main value is estimated time to reach the start line (MacCready leg when available, else distance / ground speed). Value colour and secondary line reflect gate state at that ETA: Too early (blue), Can start (green), Too late (red).': 'Rovnaká brána ako Štart otvorený. Hlavná hodnota je odhadovaný čas na dosiahnutie štartovacej čiary (krok MacCready, ak je k dispozícii, inak vzdialenosť / rýchlosť voči zemi). Farba hodnoty a sekundárna čiara odrážajú stav brány v danom ETA: Príliš skoro (modrá), Môže začať (zelená), Príliš neskoro (červená).',
        'Active waypoint: shows the next task waypoint when an ordered task is loaded, otherwise the Goto waypoint. Displays the waypoint name, arrival altitude difference relative to the safety arrival height, and distance. Click to choose a different waypoint (a task waypoint to skip to that leg, or any waypoint to set as Goto when no task is loaded).': 'Aktívny trasový bod: zobrazuje trasový bod ďalšej úlohy, keď je načítaná objednaná úloha, inak trasový bod Prejsť na. Zobrazuje názov trasového bodu, rozdiel nadmorskej výšky príletu vo vzťahu k bezpečnej výške príletu a vzdialenosť. Kliknite, ak chcete vybrať iný trasový bod (traťový bod úlohy na preskočenie na túto časť alebo akýkoľvek trasový bod, ktorý chcete nastaviť ako Goto, keď nie je načítaná žiadna úloha).',
        'FFVP Federal Cup (NetCoupe) on WeGlide. The scored path has at most three turnpoints between start and finish and at least 25 km total. Points are proportional to credited distance, 100 divided by the glider handicap (DAeC-style index), and a success factor of 1.0 for a free flight or 1.2 for a task declared electronically before takeoff. XCSoar live scoring uses a success factor of 1.0 only, not the 1.2 multiplier for declared tasks.': 'Federálny pohár FFVP (NetCoupe) na WeGlide. Bodovaná trasa má najviac tri otočné body medzi štartom a cieľom a celkovo najmenej 25 km. Body sú úmerné pripísanej vzdialenosti, 100 delené hendikepom vetroňa (index v štýle DAeC) a faktorom úspechu 1,0 za voľný let alebo 1,2 za úlohu deklarovanú elektronicky pred vzletom. Živé skórovanie XCSoar používa iba faktor úspechu 1,0, nie multiplikátor 1,2 pre deklarované úlohy.',
        'Previous waypoint: when an ordered task is loaded, automatically tracks the task waypoint before the active leg (the start waypoint when on the first leg). Displays the waypoint name, arrival altitude difference relative to the safety arrival height, and distance. Click to choose a different waypoint to display (task waypoints when a task is loaded, otherwise the full waypoint list); selection is informational only and never advances the task or sets a Goto. With a task loaded, choose "Resume auto tracking" at the top of the list to revert to automatic tracking.': 'Predchádzajúci trasový bod: keď sa načíta objednaná úloha, automaticky sleduje trasový bod úlohy pred aktívnym úsekom (začiatočný trasový bod na prvom úseku). Zobrazuje názov trasového bodu, rozdiel nadmorskej výšky príletu vo vzťahu k bezpečnej výške príletu a vzdialenosť. Kliknutím vyberte iný trasový bod na zobrazenie (trasové body úlohy pri načítaní úlohy, inak úplný zoznam trasových bodov); výber je len informatívny a nikdy neposúva úlohu ani nenastavuje Goto. Po načítaní úlohy vyberte "Obnoviť automatické sledovanie" v hornej časti zoznamu, aby ste sa vrátili k automatickému sledovaniu.',
        'This parameter estimates the height%s at which the average dry updraft strength drops below 225 fpm and is expected to give better quantitative numbers for the maximum cloudless thermalling height than the BL Top height, especially when mixing results from vertical wind shear rather than thermals. (Note: the present assumptions tend to underpredict the max. thermalling height for dry conditions.) In the presence of clouds the maximum thermalling height may instead be limited by the cloud base. Being for "dry" thermals, this parameter omits the effect of "cloudsuck".': 'Tento parameter odhaduje výšku%s, pri ktorej priemerná sila suchého stúpavého prúdu klesne pod 225 fpm a očakáva sa, že poskytne lepšie kvantitatívne čísla pre maximálnu bezoblačnú stúpavú výšku ako BL Top výška, najmä keď zmiešavacie výsledky z vertikálneho strihu vetra a nie z termiky. (Poznámka: súčasné predpoklady majú tendenciu podpredpovedať maximálnu výšku stúpania pre suché podmienky.) V prítomnosti oblačnosti môže byť maximálna výška stúpania obmedzená základňou oblačnosti. Keďže ide o "suchú" termiku, tento parameter vynecháva efekt "cloudsuck".',
        '![](resource:IDB_WARNING_TRIANGLE)\n\n!!! warning\n# Important Safety Notice\n\nBy using XCSoar, you acknowledge and accept the following:\n\n## Limitations\n\n- XCSoar is for **situational awareness only**\n- XCSoar is **not** a FLARM display\n- XCSoar is **not** aviation certified in any way\n- The artificial horizon is **not** fit for any purpose\n- Databanks (airspace, waypoints) may contain errors, be incomplete, or **not** up to date\n- NOTAM display does **not** replace proper pre-flight NOTAM briefing\n- NOTAM data may be incomplete, delayed, filtered, or unavailable\n- XCSoar is **not** guaranteed to be error free\n\n## Pilot Responsibility\n\nThe **Pilot in Command** is always responsible for the safe operation of the aircraft. Never rely solely on XCSoar for navigation or situational awareness.\n\n': '![](resource:IDB_WARNING_TRIANGLE)\n\n!!! warning\n# Dôležité bezpečnostné upozornenie\n\nPoužívaním XCSoar beriete na vedomie a prijímate nasledovné:\n\n## Obmedzenia\n\n- XCSoar je pre **iba situačné povedomie**\n- XCSoar je **nie** FLARM displej\n- XCSoar je akýmkoľvek spôsobom certifikovaný pre letectvo **nie**\n- Umelý horizont je **nie** vhodný na akýkoľvek účel\n- Databanky (vzdušný priestor, trasové body) môžu obsahovať chyby, môžu byť neúplné alebo **nie** aktuálne\n- Displej NOTAM nahrádza **nie** riadnu predletovú inštruktáž NOTAM\n- Údaje NOTAM môžu byť neúplné, oneskorené, filtrované alebo nedostupné\n- XCSoar je **nie** zaručene bez chýb\n\n## Zodpovednosť pilota\n\nZa bezpečnú prevádzku lietadla je vždy zodpovedný **Veliteľský pilot**. Nikdy sa nespoliehajte iba na XCSoar pri navigácii alebo situačnej informovanosti.\n\n',
        '# Getting Started\n\nTo use XCSoar effectively, configure the following:\n\n- [Restore from backup](xcsoar://dialog/backup) - Restore previous XCSoar data from a USB or SD card (optional)\n\n- [%s] [Map and data](xcsoar://config/site-files) - Download maps, waypoints, and airspace files for your region\n\n- [%s] [Aircraft polar](xcsoar://config/planes) - Set up your aircraft with the correct polar curve\n\n- [%s] [Pilot info](xcsoar://config/logger) - Enter your name and weight\n\n- [%s] [Devices](xcsoar://config/devices) - Connect your flight instruments\n\n- [%s] [WeGlide](xcsoar://config/weglide) - Upload flights automatically to WeGlide\n\n- [%s] [Thermal Information Map](xcsoar://config/weather) - Show thermal locations from thermalmap.info on the map\n\n- [%s] [Safety factors](xcsoar://config/safety) - Set arrival height, terrain clearance and polar degradation\n\n- [%s] [Terrain Display](xcsoar://config/terrain) - Choose terrain colors, shading and contour lines\n\n- [ ] [Live tracking](xcsoar://config/tracking) *(optional)* - Share your position via SkyLines or LiveTrack24\n\nThe easiest way to explore XCSoar is to [replay an existing IGC flight](xcsoar://dialog/replay).': '# Začíname\n\nAk chcete efektívne používať XCSoar, nakonfigurujte nasledovné:\n\n- [Obnoviť zo zálohy](xcsoar://dialog/backup) - Obnovte predchádzajúce dáta XCSoar z USB alebo SD karty (voliteľné)\n\n- [%s] [Mapa a údaje](xcsoar://config/site-files) - Stiahnite si mapy, trasové body a súbory vzdušného priestoru pre váš región\n\n- [%s] [Polárne lietadlo](xcsoar://config/planes) - Nastavte svoje lietadlo so správnou polárnou krivkou\n\n- [%s] [Informácie o pilotovi](xcsoar://config/logger) - Zadajte svoje meno a váhu\n\n- [%s] [Zariadenia](xcsoar://config/devices) - Pripojte svoje letové prístroje\n\n- [%s] [WeGlide](xcsoar://config/weglide) - Nahrajte lety automaticky do WeGlide\n\n- [%s] [Termálna informačná mapa](xcsoar://config/weather) - Zobrazte na mape termálne miesta z thermalmap.info\n\n- [%s] [Bezpečnostné faktory](xcsoar://config/safety) - Nastavte výšku príchodu, svetlú výšku terénu a polárne zhoršenie\n\n- [%s] [Zobrazenie terénu](xcsoar://config/terrain) - Vyberte farby terénu, tieňovanie a vrstevnice\n\n- [ ] [Živé sledovanie](xcsoar://config/tracking) *(optional)* - Zdieľajte svoju pozíciu cez SkyLines alebo LiveTrack24\n\nNajjednoduchší spôsob, ako preskúmať XCSoar, je [prehrať existujúci let IGC](xcsoar://dialog/replay).',
        '# Gesture Navigation\n\nXCSoar supports touch gestures on the map:\n\n- ![U](resource:IDB_GESTURE_UP) **Swipe Up** (U): Zoom in\n- ![D](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DOWN) **Swipe Down** (D): Zoom out\n- ![R](resource:IDB_GESTURE_RIGHT) **Swipe Right** (R): Previous screen mode\n- ![L](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LEFT) **Swipe Left** (L): Next screen mode\n- ![UD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_UD) **Up-Down** (UD): Auto zoom\n- ![DU](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DU) **Down-Up** (DU): Menu\n- ![DR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DR) **Down-Right** (DR): Waypoint details\n- ![DL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DL) **Down-Left** (DL): Alternates\n- ![LU](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LU) **Left-Up** (LU): Recently used waypoints\n- ![RD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_RD) **Right-Down** (RD): Task manager\n- ![URD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_URD) **Up-Right-Down** (URD): Analysis\n- ![LDR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LDR) **Left-Down-Right** (LDR): Checklist\n- ![URDL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_URDL) **Up-Right-Down-Left** (URDL): Pan mode\n- ![LDRDL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LDRDL) **Left-Down-Right-Down-Left** (LDRDL): Status\n- ![ULDR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_ULDR) **Up-Left-Down-Right** (ULDR): Quick menu\n\nLong-press on the map to enter Pan mode. Tap while in Pan mode to see nearby waypoints.': '# Navigácia gestami\n\nXCSoar podporuje dotykové gestá na mape:\n\n- ![U](resource:IDB_GESTURE_UP) **Potiahnite nahor** (U): Priblížiť\n- ![D](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DOWN) **Potiahnite prstom nadol** (D): Oddialiť\n- ![R](resource:IDB_GESTURE_RIGHT) **Prejdite prstom doprava** (R): Predchádzajúci režim obrazovky\n- ![L](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LEFT) **Potiahnite prstom doľava** (L): Ďalší režim obrazovky\n- ![UD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_UD) **Hore-Dole** (UD): Automatické priblíženie\n- ![DU](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DU) **Down-Up** (DU): Menu\n- ![DR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DR) **Vpravo dole** (DR): Podrobnosti o trasovom bode\n- ![DL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DL) **Dolu-vľavo** (DL): Náhradníci\n- ![LU](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LU) **Zľava hore** (LU): Nedávno použité trasové body\n- ![RD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_RD) **Vpravo-dole** (RD): Správca úloh\n- ![URD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_URD) **Hore-vpravo-dole** (URD): Analýza\n- ![LDR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LDR) **Vľavo-dole-vpravo** (LDR): Kontrolný zoznam\n- ![URDL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_URDL) **Hore-vpravo-dole-vľavo** (URDL): Režim posúvania\n- ![LDRDL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LDRDL) **Vľavo-dole-vpravo-dole-vľavo** (LDRDL): Stav\n- ![ULDR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_ULDR) **Hore-vľavo-dole-vpravo** (ULDR): Rýchle menu\n\nDlhým stlačením na mape vstúpite do režimu posúvania. Klepnutím v režime Posunúť zobrazíte blízke trasové body.',
    },
    "sl": {
        'Size of waypoint symbols on the map as a percentage of the built-in artwork (list dialogs keep a fixed row icon size).': 'Velikost simbolov točk poti na zemljevidu kot odstotek vgrajene umetnine (pogovorna okna seznama ohranjajo fiksno velikost ikone vrstice).',
        'Home waypoint name, arrival altitude difference relative to the safety arrival height, and distance. Click to change the home waypoint.': 'Ime domače točke poti, razlika višine prihoda glede na višino varnega prihoda in razdalja. Kliknite, če želite spremeniti domačo točko poti.',
        'Current QNH pressure setting used for barometric altitude calculation. Tap the infobox to open the setup panel and adjust QNH manually.': 'Trenutna nastavitev tlaka QNH, ki se uporablja za izračun barometrične višine. Tapnite informacijsko polje, da odprete nastavitveno ploščo in ročno prilagodite QNH.',
        'This page shows WiFi status when NetworkManager or ConnMan is on D-Bus (e.g. Linux with Wayland or KMS). Open WiFi list to scan and connect when a service is available.': 'Ta stran prikazuje stanje WiFi, ko je NetworkManager ali ConnMan na D-Bus (npr. Linux z Waylandom ali KMS). Odprite seznam WiFi za skeniranje in povezavo, ko je storitev na voljo.',
        'The terrain can be shaded among slopes to indicate either wind direction, sun position, a geographically fixed shading from North-West, or a screen-relative fixed shading from top left.': 'Teren je lahko senčen med pobočji, da nakaže smer vetra, položaj sonca, geografsko fiksno senčenje s severozahoda ali fiksno senčenje glede na zaslon od zgoraj levo.',
        "Synchronize the glide polar between XCSoar and the device (LXNAV varios). 'Receive' adopts the polar from the device (e.g. for club gliders). 'Send' pushes XCSoar's polar to the device.": "Sinhronizirajte drsno polarno med XCSoar in napravo (LXNAV varios). 'Receive' prevzame polar iz naprave (npr. za klubska jadralna letala). »Pošlji« potisne polar XCSoar v napravo.",
        'List of active airspace files. Use the Add and Remove buttons to activate or deactivate airspace files respectively. Supported file types are: Openair (.openair /.txt /.air), and Tim Newport-Pearce (.sua).': 'Seznam aktivnih datotek zračnega prostora. Z gumboma Dodaj in Odstrani aktivirajte ali deaktivirajte datoteke zračnega prostora. Podprte vrste datotek so: Openair (.openair /.txt /.air) in Tim Newport-Pearce (.sua).',
        'Signed countdown until the start gate opens or closes (now). Value colour and secondary line reflect gate state at the current time: Waiting (blue), Open (green), Closed (red). PEV window overrides task gate when set.': 'Podpisano odštevanje do odpiranja ali zapiranja startnih vrat (zdaj). Barva vrednosti in sekundarna vrstica odražata stanje vrat v trenutnem času: čakanje (modra), odprta (zelena), zaprta (rdeča). Okno PEV preglasi vrata opravila, ko je nastavljeno.',
        'Tells XCSoar to send its current GPS position to the device as $GPGGA and $GPRMC sentences. Turn off when another GPS source is already feeding the device on the same line. Changes take effect after reconnecting the device.': 'Sporoči XCSoarju, naj pošlje svoj trenutni položaj GPS napravi kot stavka $GPGGA in $GPRMC. Izklopite, ko drug vir GPS že napaja napravo na isti liniji. Spremembe stopijo v veljavo po ponovni povezavi naprave.',
        'Logger pressure altitude when the device provides it (igc_pressure_altitude), otherwise ISA pressure altitude only (1013.25 hPa; not QNH-corrected). Does not show barometric AMSL or GPS height — use other InfoBoxes for navigation.': 'Zabeležite tlačno višino, ko jo zagotovi naprava (igc_pressure_altitude), sicer samo tlačno višino ISA (1013,25 hPa; ni popravljeno s QNH). Ne prikazuje barometrične višine AMSL ali GPS — za navigacijo uporabite druga informacijska polja.',
        'Same gate as Start open. Main value is estimated time to reach the start line (MacCready leg when available, else distance / ground speed). Value colour and secondary line reflect gate state at that ETA: Too early (blue), Can start (green), Too late (red).': 'Odprta ista vrata kot Start. Glavna vrednost je predvideni čas za dosego štartne črte (MacCready etapa, ko je na voljo, sicer razdalja/hitrost tal). Barva vrednosti in sekundarna vrstica odražata stanje vrat ob tem ETA: prezgodaj (modra), lahko začne (zelena), prepozno (rdeča).',
        'Active waypoint: shows the next task waypoint when an ordered task is loaded, otherwise the Goto waypoint. Displays the waypoint name, arrival altitude difference relative to the safety arrival height, and distance. Click to choose a different waypoint (a task waypoint to skip to that leg, or any waypoint to set as Goto when no task is loaded).': 'Aktivna točka poti: prikaže naslednjo točko poti opravila, ko je naloženo naročeno opravilo, sicer pa točko poti Goto. Prikaže ime točke poti, razliko višine prihoda glede na varno višino prihoda in razdaljo. Kliknite, da izberete drugo točko poti (točko naloge, ki jo želite preskočiti na to etapo, ali katero koli točko poti, ki jo nastavite kot Goto, ko ni naloženo nobeno opravilo).',
        'FFVP Federal Cup (NetCoupe) on WeGlide. The scored path has at most three turnpoints between start and finish and at least 25 km total. Points are proportional to credited distance, 100 divided by the glider handicap (DAeC-style index), and a success factor of 1.0 for a free flight or 1.2 for a task declared electronically before takeoff. XCSoar live scoring uses a success factor of 1.0 only, not the 1.2 multiplier for declared tasks.': 'Zvezni pokal FFVP (NetCoupe) na WeGlide. Točkovana pot ima največ tri obračališča med startom in ciljem in skupno najmanj 25 km. Točke so sorazmerne s pripisano razdaljo, 100 deljeno s hendikepom jadralnega letala (indeks v stilu DAeC) in faktorjem uspeha 1,0 za prosti let ali 1,2 za nalogo, prijavljeno elektronsko pred vzletom. Točkovanje XCSoar v živo uporablja samo faktor uspeha 1,0, ne pa množitelja 1,2 za prijavljene naloge.',
        'Previous waypoint: when an ordered task is loaded, automatically tracks the task waypoint before the active leg (the start waypoint when on the first leg). Displays the waypoint name, arrival altitude difference relative to the safety arrival height, and distance. Click to choose a different waypoint to display (task waypoints when a task is loaded, otherwise the full waypoint list); selection is informational only and never advances the task or sets a Goto. With a task loaded, choose "Resume auto tracking" at the top of the list to revert to automatic tracking.': 'Prejšnja točka poti: ko je naloženo naročeno opravilo, samodejno sledi točki poti opravila pred aktivno etapo (začetna točka poti, ko ste na prvi etapi). Prikaže ime točke poti, razliko višine prihoda glede na varno višino prihoda in razdaljo. Kliknite, da izberete drugo točko poti za prikaz (točke poti opravila, ko je opravilo naloženo, sicer celoten seznam točk poti); izbira je samo informativna in nikoli ne napreduje pri nalogi ali nastavi Goto. Z naloženo nalogo izberite "Nadaljevanje samodejnega sledenja" na vrhu seznama, da se vrnete na samodejno sledenje.',
        'This parameter estimates the height%s at which the average dry updraft strength drops below 225 fpm and is expected to give better quantitative numbers for the maximum cloudless thermalling height than the BL Top height, especially when mixing results from vertical wind shear rather than thermals. (Note: the present assumptions tend to underpredict the max. thermalling height for dry conditions.) In the presence of clouds the maximum thermalling height may instead be limited by the cloud base. Being for "dry" thermals, this parameter omits the effect of "cloudsuck".': 'Ta parameter ocenjuje višino %s, pri kateri povprečna jakost suhega navzgornjega toka pade pod 225 fpm in naj bi dal boljše kvantitativne številke za največjo višino toplote brez oblaka kot višina BL Top, zlasti če je mešanje rezultatov navpičnega strižnega vetra in ne termike. (Opomba: sedanje predpostavke ponavadi premalo napovedujejo največjo temperaturno višino za suhe razmere.) V prisotnosti oblakov je lahko največja toplotna višina namesto tega omejena z dno oblaka. Ker gre za "suho" termiko, ta parameter izpušča učinek "sesanja oblakov".',
        '![](resource:IDB_WARNING_TRIANGLE)\n\n!!! warning\n# Important Safety Notice\n\nBy using XCSoar, you acknowledge and accept the following:\n\n## Limitations\n\n- XCSoar is for **situational awareness only**\n- XCSoar is **not** a FLARM display\n- XCSoar is **not** aviation certified in any way\n- The artificial horizon is **not** fit for any purpose\n- Databanks (airspace, waypoints) may contain errors, be incomplete, or **not** up to date\n- NOTAM display does **not** replace proper pre-flight NOTAM briefing\n- NOTAM data may be incomplete, delayed, filtered, or unavailable\n- XCSoar is **not** guaranteed to be error free\n\n## Pilot Responsibility\n\nThe **Pilot in Command** is always responsible for the safe operation of the aircraft. Never rely solely on XCSoar for navigation or situational awareness.\n\n': '![](resource:IDB_WARNING_TRIANGLE)\n\n!!! warning\n# Pomembno varnostno obvestilo\n\nZ uporabo XCSoar potrjujete in sprejemate naslednje:\n\n## Omejitve\n\n- XCSoar je za **samo zavedanje situacije**\n- XCSoar je **ne** FLARM zaslon\n- XCSoar je na kakršen koli način certificiran za letalstvo **ne**\n- Umetni horizont je **ne** primeren za vse namene\n- Banke podatkov (zračni prostor, točke poti) lahko vsebujejo napake, so nepopolne ali **ne** posodobljene\n- Prikaz NOTAM ali **ne** nadomešča ustrezna navodila za NOTAM pred letom\n- Podatki NOTAM so lahko nepopolni, z zamudo, filtrirani ali nedostopni\n- XCSoar je **ne** zajamčeno brez napak\n\n## Odgovornost pilota\n\nZa varno delovanje letala je vedno odgovoren **Pilot v poveljstvu**. Nikoli se ne zanašajte samo na XCSoar za navigacijo ali zaznavanje situacije.\n\n',
        '# Getting Started\n\nTo use XCSoar effectively, configure the following:\n\n- [Restore from backup](xcsoar://dialog/backup) - Restore previous XCSoar data from a USB or SD card (optional)\n\n- [%s] [Map and data](xcsoar://config/site-files) - Download maps, waypoints, and airspace files for your region\n\n- [%s] [Aircraft polar](xcsoar://config/planes) - Set up your aircraft with the correct polar curve\n\n- [%s] [Pilot info](xcsoar://config/logger) - Enter your name and weight\n\n- [%s] [Devices](xcsoar://config/devices) - Connect your flight instruments\n\n- [%s] [WeGlide](xcsoar://config/weglide) - Upload flights automatically to WeGlide\n\n- [%s] [Thermal Information Map](xcsoar://config/weather) - Show thermal locations from thermalmap.info on the map\n\n- [%s] [Safety factors](xcsoar://config/safety) - Set arrival height, terrain clearance and polar degradation\n\n- [%s] [Terrain Display](xcsoar://config/terrain) - Choose terrain colors, shading and contour lines\n\n- [ ] [Live tracking](xcsoar://config/tracking) *(optional)* - Share your position via SkyLines or LiveTrack24\n\nThe easiest way to explore XCSoar is to [replay an existing IGC flight](xcsoar://dialog/replay).': '# Kako začeti\n\nČe želite učinkovito uporabljati XCSoar, konfigurirajte naslednje:\n\n- [Obnovi iz varnostne kopije](xcsoar://dialog/backup) - Obnovi prejšnje podatke XCSoar s kartice USB ali SD (izbirno)\n\n- [%s] [Zemljevid in podatki](xcsoar://config/site-files) - Prenesite zemljevide, točke poti in datoteke zračnega prostora za svojo regijo\n\n- [%s] [Letalo polar](xcsoar://config/planes) - Nastavite svoje letalo s pravilno polarno krivuljo\n\n- [%s] [Informacije o pilotu](xcsoar://config/logger) - Vnesite svoje ime in težo\n\n- [%s] [Naprave](xcsoar://config/devices) - Povežite svoje letalne instrumente\n\n- [%s] [WeGlide](xcsoar://config/weglide) - Samodejno naložite lete v WeGlide\n\n- [%s] [Toplotni informacijski zemljevid](xcsoar://config/weather) - Prikažite termalne lokacije iz termalmap.info na zemljevidu\n\n- [%s] [Varnostni faktorji](xcsoar://config/safety) - Nastavite višino prihoda, oddaljenost od terena in polarno degradacijo\n\n- [%s] [Prikaz terena](xcsoar://config/terrain) - Izberite barve terena, senčenje in obrise\n\n- [ ] [Sledenje v živo](xcsoar://config/tracking) *(optional)* - Delite svoj položaj prek SkyLines ali LiveTrack24\n\nNajlažji način za raziskovanje XCSoar je [ponovite obstoječi let IGC](xcsoar://dialog/replay).',
        '# Gesture Navigation\n\nXCSoar supports touch gestures on the map:\n\n- ![U](resource:IDB_GESTURE_UP) **Swipe Up** (U): Zoom in\n- ![D](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DOWN) **Swipe Down** (D): Zoom out\n- ![R](resource:IDB_GESTURE_RIGHT) **Swipe Right** (R): Previous screen mode\n- ![L](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LEFT) **Swipe Left** (L): Next screen mode\n- ![UD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_UD) **Up-Down** (UD): Auto zoom\n- ![DU](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DU) **Down-Up** (DU): Menu\n- ![DR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DR) **Down-Right** (DR): Waypoint details\n- ![DL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DL) **Down-Left** (DL): Alternates\n- ![LU](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LU) **Left-Up** (LU): Recently used waypoints\n- ![RD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_RD) **Right-Down** (RD): Task manager\n- ![URD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_URD) **Up-Right-Down** (URD): Analysis\n- ![LDR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LDR) **Left-Down-Right** (LDR): Checklist\n- ![URDL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_URDL) **Up-Right-Down-Left** (URDL): Pan mode\n- ![LDRDL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LDRDL) **Left-Down-Right-Down-Left** (LDRDL): Status\n- ![ULDR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_ULDR) **Up-Left-Down-Right** (ULDR): Quick menu\n\nLong-press on the map to enter Pan mode. Tap while in Pan mode to see nearby waypoints.': '# Navigacija s kretnjami\n\nXCSoar podpira poteze na dotik na zemljevidu:\n\n- ![U](resource:IDB_GESTURE_UP) **Povlecite navzgor** (U): Povečaj\n- ![D](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DOWN) **Povlecite navzdol** (D): Pomanjšaj\n- ![R](resource:IDB_GESTURE_RIGHT) **Povlecite desno** (R): Prejšnji način zaslona\n- ![L](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LEFT) **Povlecite v levo** (L): Naslednji način zaslona\n- ![UD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_UD) **Gor-Dol** (UD): Samodejni zoom\n- ![DU](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DU) **Dol-Gor** (DU): meni\n- ![DR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DR) **Dol-Desno** (DR): Podrobnosti o točki poti\n- ![DL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DL) **Dol-Levo** (DL): Namestniki\n- ![LU](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LU) **Levo-Gor** (LU): Nedavno uporabljene točke poti\n- ![RD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_RD) **Desno-dol** (RD): Upravitelj opravil\n- ![URD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_URD) **Gor-desno-dol** (URD): Analiza\n- ![LDR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LDR) **Levo-dol-desno** (LDR): Kontrolni seznam\n- ![URDL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_URDL) **Gor-desno-dol-levo** (URDL): Pan način\n- ![LDRDL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LDRDL) **Levo-dol-desno-dol-levo** (LDRDL): Stanje\n- ![ULDR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_ULDR) **Gor-levo-dol-desno** (ULDR): Hitri meni\n\nDolgo pritisnite na zemljevid, da vstopite v način Pan. Tapnite v načinu Pan, da vidite bližnje točke poti.',
    },
    "sr": {
        'Size of waypoint symbols on the map as a percentage of the built-in artwork (list dialogs keep a fixed row icon size).': 'Величина симбола путне тачке на мапи као проценат уграђеног уметничког дела (дијалози листе задржавају фиксну величину иконе реда).',
        'Home waypoint name, arrival altitude difference relative to the safety arrival height, and distance. Click to change the home waypoint.': 'Назив кућне путне тачке, разлика у висини доласка у односу на висину сигурносног доласка и удаљеност. Кликните да промените кућну тачку.',
        'Current QNH pressure setting used for barometric altitude calculation. Tap the infobox to open the setup panel and adjust QNH manually.': 'Тренутна поставка притиска КНХ која се користи за прорачун барометарске висине. Додирните инфокутију да отворите таблу за подешавање и ручно подесите КНХ.',
        'This page shows WiFi status when NetworkManager or ConnMan is on D-Bus (e.g. Linux with Wayland or KMS). Open WiFi list to scan and connect when a service is available.': 'Ова страница приказује ВиФи статус када је НетворкМанагер или ЦоннМан на Д-Бус-у (нпр. Линук са Ваиланд-ом или КМС-ом). Отворите ВиФи листу да бисте скенирали и повезали се када је услуга доступна.',
        'The terrain can be shaded among slopes to indicate either wind direction, sun position, a geographically fixed shading from North-West, or a screen-relative fixed shading from top left.': 'Терен се може засенчити међу падинама да би се означио или правац ветра, положај сунца, географски фиксирано сенчење са северозапада или фиксно сенчење у односу на екран одозго лево.',
        "Synchronize the glide polar between XCSoar and the device (LXNAV varios). 'Receive' adopts the polar from the device (e.g. for club gliders). 'Send' pushes XCSoar's polar to the device.": 'Синхронизујте поларно клизање између КСЦСоар-а и уређаја (ЛКСНАВ вариос). „Примање“ преузима поларност са уређаја (нпр. за клупске једрилице). „Пошаљи“ гура КСЦСоар-ов полар на уређај.',
        'List of active airspace files. Use the Add and Remove buttons to activate or deactivate airspace files respectively. Supported file types are: Openair (.openair /.txt /.air), and Tim Newport-Pearce (.sua).': 'Листа активних датотека ваздушног простора. Користите дугмад Додај и Уклони да бисте активирали или деактивирали датотеке ваздушног простора. Подржани типови датотека су: Опенаир (.опенаир /.ткт /.аир) и Тим Невпорт-Пеарце (.суа).',
        'Signed countdown until the start gate opens or closes (now). Value colour and secondary line reflect gate state at the current time: Waiting (blue), Open (green), Closed (red). PEV window overrides task gate when set.': 'Потписано одбројавање док се почетна капија не отвори или затвори (сада). Боја вредности и секундарна линија одражавају стање капије у тренутном времену: Чекање (плаво), Отворено (зелено), Затворено (црвено). ПЕВ прозор замењује капију задатака када је подешен.',
        'Tells XCSoar to send its current GPS position to the device as $GPGGA and $GPRMC sentences. Turn off when another GPS source is already feeding the device on the same line. Changes take effect after reconnecting the device.': 'Каже КСЦСоару да пошаље своју тренутну ГПС позицију уређају као $ГПГГА и $ГПРМЦ реченице. Искључите када други ГПС извор већ напаја уређај на истој линији. Промене ступају на снагу након поновног повезивања уређаја.',
        'Logger pressure altitude when the device provides it (igc_pressure_altitude), otherwise ISA pressure altitude only (1013.25 hPa; not QNH-corrected). Does not show barometric AMSL or GPS height — use other InfoBoxes for navigation.': 'Забележите висину притиска када је уређај обезбеди (игц_прессуре_алтитуде), иначе само ИСА висина притиска (1013,25 хПа; није исправљено КНХ). Не приказује барометарску АМСЛ или ГПС висину — користите друге ИнфоБоксове за навигацију.',
        'Same gate as Start open. Main value is estimated time to reach the start line (MacCready leg when available, else distance / ground speed). Value colour and secondary line reflect gate state at that ETA: Too early (blue), Can start (green), Too late (red).': 'Иста капија као Старт отворена. Главна вредност је процењено време за достизање стартне линије (МацЦреади нога када је доступна, у супротном удаљеност / брзина на терену). Боја вредности и секундарна линија одражавају стање капије у том ЕТА: Прерано (плаво), Може да почне (зелено), Прекасно (црвено).',
        'Active waypoint: shows the next task waypoint when an ordered task is loaded, otherwise the Goto waypoint. Displays the waypoint name, arrival altitude difference relative to the safety arrival height, and distance. Click to choose a different waypoint (a task waypoint to skip to that leg, or any waypoint to set as Goto when no task is loaded).': 'Активна путна тачка: приказује следећу међутачку задатка када се учита наручени задатак, у супротном Гото међутачку. Приказује назив путне тачке, разлику висине доласка у односу на висину сигурносног доласка и удаљеност. Кликните да бисте изабрали другу тачку пута (путну тачку задатка да прескочите на ту деоницу или било коју тачку пута коју ћете поставити као Гото када ниједан задатак није учитан).',
        'FFVP Federal Cup (NetCoupe) on WeGlide. The scored path has at most three turnpoints between start and finish and at least 25 km total. Points are proportional to credited distance, 100 divided by the glider handicap (DAeC-style index), and a success factor of 1.0 for a free flight or 1.2 for a task declared electronically before takeoff. XCSoar live scoring uses a success factor of 1.0 only, not the 1.2 multiplier for declared tasks.': 'ФФВП Федерал Цуп (НетЦоупе) на ВеГлиде-у. Освојена стаза има највише три окретне тачке између старта и циља и најмање 25 км укупно. Поени су пропорционални кредитираној удаљености, 100 подељено са хендикепом једрилице (индекс у стилу ДАеЦ), и фактор успеха од 1,0 за слободан лет или 1,2 за задатак који је електронски декларисан пре полетања. КСЦСоар ливе бодовање користи само фактор успеха 1,0, а не множилац 1,2 за декларисане задатке.',
        'Previous waypoint: when an ordered task is loaded, automatically tracks the task waypoint before the active leg (the start waypoint when on the first leg). Displays the waypoint name, arrival altitude difference relative to the safety arrival height, and distance. Click to choose a different waypoint to display (task waypoints when a task is loaded, otherwise the full waypoint list); selection is informational only and never advances the task or sets a Goto. With a task loaded, choose "Resume auto tracking" at the top of the list to revert to automatic tracking.': 'Претходна тачка пута: када се наручени задатак учита, аутоматски прати тачку задатка пре активне етапе (почетна тачка пута када је на првој деоници). Приказује назив путне тачке, разлику висине доласка у односу на висину сигурносног доласка и удаљеност. Кликните да бисте изабрали другу тачку пута за приказ (тачке задатка када је задатак учитан, у супротном цела листа путних тачака); избор је само информативног карактера и никада не унапређује задатак или поставља Гото. Са учитаним задатком, изаберите ЗЗРЕСУМЕЗЗ на врху листе да бисте се вратили на аутоматско праћење.',
        'This parameter estimates the height%s at which the average dry updraft strength drops below 225 fpm and is expected to give better quantitative numbers for the maximum cloudless thermalling height than the BL Top height, especially when mixing results from vertical wind shear rather than thermals. (Note: the present assumptions tend to underpredict the max. thermalling height for dry conditions.) In the presence of clouds the maximum thermalling height may instead be limited by the cloud base. Being for "dry" thermals, this parameter omits the effect of "cloudsuck".': 'Овај параметар процењује висину ЗЗПЦТЗЗ на којој просечна јачина сувог узлазног струјања пада испод 225 фпм и очекује се да ће дати боље квантитативне бројеве за максималну висину термализације без облака од висине БЛ Топ, посебно када је мешање резултат вертикалног смицања ветра, а не термалних. (Напомена: садашње претпоставке имају тенденцију да не предвиђају максималну висину термичке температуре за суве услове.) У присуству облака максимална висина термичке температуре може бити ограничена базом облака. Будући да се ради о "сувим" термикама, овај параметар изоставља ефекат "цлоудсуцк".',
        '![](resource:IDB_WARNING_TRIANGLE)\n\n!!! warning\n# Important Safety Notice\n\nBy using XCSoar, you acknowledge and accept the following:\n\n## Limitations\n\n- XCSoar is for **situational awareness only**\n- XCSoar is **not** a FLARM display\n- XCSoar is **not** aviation certified in any way\n- The artificial horizon is **not** fit for any purpose\n- Databanks (airspace, waypoints) may contain errors, be incomplete, or **not** up to date\n- NOTAM display does **not** replace proper pre-flight NOTAM briefing\n- NOTAM data may be incomplete, delayed, filtered, or unavailable\n- XCSoar is **not** guaranteed to be error free\n\n## Pilot Responsibility\n\nThe **Pilot in Command** is always responsible for the safe operation of the aircraft. Never rely solely on XCSoar for navigation or situational awareness.\n\n': '![](resource:IDB_WARNING_TRIANGLE)\n\n!!! warning\n# Важно обавештење о безбедности\n\nКоришћењем КСЦСоар-а, потврђујете и прихватате следеће:\n\n## Ограничења\n\n- КСЦСоар је за ЗЗСАЗЗ\n- КСЦСоар је ЗЗНОТЗЗ ФЛАРМ дисплеј\n- КСЦСоар је ЗЗНОТЗЗ сертификован за авијацију на било који начин\n- Вештачки хоризонт је ЗЗНОТЗЗ погодан за било коју намену\n- Банке података (ваздушни простор, путне тачке) могу садржати грешке, бити непотпуне или ЗЗНОТЗЗ ажурне\n- НОТАМ екран да ли ЗЗНОТЗЗ замењује правилан НОТАМ брифинг пре лета\n- НОТАМ подаци могу бити непотпуни, одложени, филтрирани или недоступни\n- КСЦСоар је ЗЗНОТЗЗ гарантовано без грешака\n\n## Одговорност пилота\n\nЗЗПИЦЗЗ је увек одговоран за безбедан рад авиона. Никада се не ослањајте само на КСЦСоар за навигацију или свест о ситуацији.\n\n',
        '# Getting Started\n\nTo use XCSoar effectively, configure the following:\n\n- [Restore from backup](xcsoar://dialog/backup) - Restore previous XCSoar data from a USB or SD card (optional)\n\n- [%s] [Map and data](xcsoar://config/site-files) - Download maps, waypoints, and airspace files for your region\n\n- [%s] [Aircraft polar](xcsoar://config/planes) - Set up your aircraft with the correct polar curve\n\n- [%s] [Pilot info](xcsoar://config/logger) - Enter your name and weight\n\n- [%s] [Devices](xcsoar://config/devices) - Connect your flight instruments\n\n- [%s] [WeGlide](xcsoar://config/weglide) - Upload flights automatically to WeGlide\n\n- [%s] [Thermal Information Map](xcsoar://config/weather) - Show thermal locations from thermalmap.info on the map\n\n- [%s] [Safety factors](xcsoar://config/safety) - Set arrival height, terrain clearance and polar degradation\n\n- [%s] [Terrain Display](xcsoar://config/terrain) - Choose terrain colors, shading and contour lines\n\n- [ ] [Live tracking](xcsoar://config/tracking) *(optional)* - Share your position via SkyLines or LiveTrack24\n\nThe easiest way to explore XCSoar is to [replay an existing IGC flight](xcsoar://dialog/replay).': '# Геттинг Стартед\n\nДа бисте ефикасно користили КСЦСоар, конфигуришите следеће:\n\n- [Вратите из резервне копије](xcsoar://dialog/backup) - Вратите претходне КСЦСоар податке са УСБ или СД картице (опционо)\n\n- [%s] [Мапа и подаци](xcsoar://config/site-files) - Преузмите мапе, путне тачке и датотеке ваздушног простора за свој регион\n\n- [%s] [Авион поларни](xcsoar://config/planes) - Подесите свој авион са исправном поларном кривом\n\n- [%s] [Информације о пилоту](xcsoar://config/logger) - Унесите своје име и тежину\n\n- [%s] [Уређаји](xcsoar://config/devices) - Повежите своје инструменте за летење\n\n- [%s] [ВеГлиде](xcsoar://config/weglide) - Аутоматски отпремајте летове у ВеГлиде\n\n- [%s] [Мапа термалних информација](xcsoar://config/weather) - Прикажи термалне локације са термалне мапе.инфо на мапи\n\n- [%s] [Фактори сигурности](xcsoar://config/safety) - Подесите висину доласка, клиренс терена и поларну деградацију\n\n- [%s] [Приказ терена](xcsoar://config/terrain) - Изаберите боје терена, сенчење и контурне линије\n\n- [ ] [Праћење уживо](xcsoar://config/tracking) *(optional)* - Поделите своју позицију преко СкиЛинес-а или ЛивеТрацк24\n\nНајлакши начин да истражите КСЦСоар је да [поновите постојећи ИГЦ лет](xcsoar://dialog/replay).',
        '# Gesture Navigation\n\nXCSoar supports touch gestures on the map:\n\n- ![U](resource:IDB_GESTURE_UP) **Swipe Up** (U): Zoom in\n- ![D](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DOWN) **Swipe Down** (D): Zoom out\n- ![R](resource:IDB_GESTURE_RIGHT) **Swipe Right** (R): Previous screen mode\n- ![L](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LEFT) **Swipe Left** (L): Next screen mode\n- ![UD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_UD) **Up-Down** (UD): Auto zoom\n- ![DU](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DU) **Down-Up** (DU): Menu\n- ![DR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DR) **Down-Right** (DR): Waypoint details\n- ![DL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DL) **Down-Left** (DL): Alternates\n- ![LU](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LU) **Left-Up** (LU): Recently used waypoints\n- ![RD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_RD) **Right-Down** (RD): Task manager\n- ![URD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_URD) **Up-Right-Down** (URD): Analysis\n- ![LDR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LDR) **Left-Down-Right** (LDR): Checklist\n- ![URDL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_URDL) **Up-Right-Down-Left** (URDL): Pan mode\n- ![LDRDL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LDRDL) **Left-Down-Right-Down-Left** (LDRDL): Status\n- ![ULDR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_ULDR) **Up-Left-Down-Right** (ULDR): Quick menu\n\nLong-press on the map to enter Pan mode. Tap while in Pan mode to see nearby waypoints.': '# Навигација покретима\n\nКСЦСоар подржава покрете додиром на мапи:\n\n- ![U](resource:IDB_GESTURE_UP) **Превуците нагоре** (U): Увећајте\n- ![D](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DOWN) **Превуците надоле** (D): Умањите\n- ![R](resource:IDB_GESTURE_RIGHT) **Превуците удесно** (R): Претходни режим екрана\n- ![L](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LEFT) **Превуците налево** (L): Следећи режим екрана\n- ![UD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_UD) **Горе-Доле** (UD): Аутоматско зумирање\n- ![DU](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DU) **Доле-горе** (DU): Мени\n- ![DR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DR) **Доле-десно** (DR): Детаљи путне тачке\n- ![DL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DL) **Доле-лево** (DL): Алтернатес\n- ![LU](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LU) **Лефт-Уп** (LU): Недавно коришћене путне тачке\n- ![RD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_RD) **Десно-доле** (RD): Менаџер задатака\n- ![URD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_URD) **Горе-Десно-Доле** (URD): Анализа\n- ![LDR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LDR) **Лево-Доле-Десно** (LDR): Контролна листа\n- ![URDL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_URDL) **Горе-десно-доле-лево** (URDL): Пан режим\n- ![LDRDL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LDRDL) **Лево-доле-десно-доле-лево** (LDRDL): Статус\n- ![ULDR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_ULDR) **Горе-Лево-Доле-Десно** (ULDR): Брзи мени\n\nДуго притисните на мапи да бисте ушли у режим Пан. Додирните док сте у режиму Пан да бисте видели оближње међутачке.',
    },
    "sv": {
        'Size of waypoint symbols on the map as a percentage of the built-in artwork (list dialogs keep a fixed row icon size).': 'Storleken på waypointsymboler på kartan i procent av det inbyggda konstverket (listdialoger har en fast radikonstorlek).',
        'Home waypoint name, arrival altitude difference relative to the safety arrival height, and distance. Click to change the home waypoint.': 'Hemvägpunktens namn, ankomsthöjdsskillnad i förhållande till säkerhetens ankomsthöjd och avstånd. Klicka för att ändra hemvägpunkten.',
        'Current QNH pressure setting used for barometric altitude calculation. Tap the infobox to open the setup panel and adjust QNH manually.': 'Aktuell QNH-tryckinställning som används för barometrisk höjdberäkning. Tryck på infoboxen för att öppna inställningspanelen och justera QNH manuellt.',
        'This page shows WiFi status when NetworkManager or ConnMan is on D-Bus (e.g. Linux with Wayland or KMS). Open WiFi list to scan and connect when a service is available.': 'Den här sidan visar WiFi-status när NetworkManager eller ConnMan är på D-Bus (t.ex. Linux med Wayland eller KMS). Öppna WiFi-listan för att skanna och ansluta när en tjänst är tillgänglig.',
        'The terrain can be shaded among slopes to indicate either wind direction, sun position, a geographically fixed shading from North-West, or a screen-relative fixed shading from top left.': 'Terrängen kan skuggas bland sluttningar för att indikera antingen vindriktning, solposition, en geografiskt fixerad skuggning från nordväst, eller en skärmrelativ fast skuggning uppifrån till vänster.',
        "Synchronize the glide polar between XCSoar and the device (LXNAV varios). 'Receive' adopts the polar from the device (e.g. for club gliders). 'Send' pushes XCSoar's polar to the device.": "Synkronisera glidpolaren mellan XCSoar och enheten (LXNAV varios). 'Receive' antar polaren från enheten (t.ex. för klubbglidare). 'Skicka' skjuter XCSoars polar till enheten.",
        'List of active airspace files. Use the Add and Remove buttons to activate or deactivate airspace files respectively. Supported file types are: Openair (.openair /.txt /.air), and Tim Newport-Pearce (.sua).': 'Lista över aktiva luftrumsfiler. Använd knapparna Lägg till och Ta bort för att aktivera respektive inaktivera luftrumsfiler. Filtyper som stöds är: Openair (.openair /.txt /.air) och Tim Newport-Pearce (.sua).',
        'Signed countdown until the start gate opens or closes (now). Value colour and secondary line reflect gate state at the current time: Waiting (blue), Open (green), Closed (red). PEV window overrides task gate when set.': 'Signerad nedräkning tills startgrinden öppnas eller stängs (nu). Värdefärg och sekundär linje reflekterar portens tillstånd vid den aktuella tiden: Väntar (blå), Öppen (grön), Stängd (röd). PEV-fönstret åsidosätter aktivitetsporten när den är inställd.',
        'Tells XCSoar to send its current GPS position to the device as $GPGGA and $GPRMC sentences. Turn off when another GPS source is already feeding the device on the same line. Changes take effect after reconnecting the device.': 'Ber XCSoar att skicka sin nuvarande GPS-position till enheten som $GPGGA- och $GPRMC-meningar. Stäng av när en annan GPS-källa redan matar enheten på samma linje. Ändringar träder i kraft efter att enheten återansluts.',
        'Logger pressure altitude when the device provides it (igc_pressure_altitude), otherwise ISA pressure altitude only (1013.25 hPa; not QNH-corrected). Does not show barometric AMSL or GPS height — use other InfoBoxes for navigation.': 'Loggertryckhöjd när enheten tillhandahåller det (igc_pressure_altitude), annars endast ISA tryckhöjd (1013,25 hPa; inte QNH-korrigerad). Visar inte barometrisk AMSL- eller GPS-höjd — använd andra infoboxar för navigering.',
        'Same gate as Start open. Main value is estimated time to reach the start line (MacCready leg when available, else distance / ground speed). Value colour and secondary line reflect gate state at that ETA: Too early (blue), Can start (green), Too late (red).': 'Samma grind som Start öppen. Huvudvärde är beräknad tid för att nå startlinjen (MacCready etapp när tillgängligt, annars distans / markhastighet). Värdefärg och sekundär linje reflekterar portens tillstånd vid den ETA: För tidigt (blå), Kan starta (grön), För sent (röd).',
        'Active waypoint: shows the next task waypoint when an ordered task is loaded, otherwise the Goto waypoint. Displays the waypoint name, arrival altitude difference relative to the safety arrival height, and distance. Click to choose a different waypoint (a task waypoint to skip to that leg, or any waypoint to set as Goto when no task is loaded).': 'Aktiv waypoint: visar nästa uppgifts waypoint när en beställd uppgift laddas, annars Goto waypoint. Visar waypointnamnet, ankomsthöjdsskillnaden i förhållande till säkerhetens ankomsthöjd och avstånd. Klicka för att välja en annan waypoint (en uppgiftswaypoint för att hoppa till det etappen, eller valfri waypoint att ställa in som Goto när ingen uppgift är laddad).',
        'FFVP Federal Cup (NetCoupe) on WeGlide. The scored path has at most three turnpoints between start and finish and at least 25 km total. Points are proportional to credited distance, 100 divided by the glider handicap (DAeC-style index), and a success factor of 1.0 for a free flight or 1.2 for a task declared electronically before takeoff. XCSoar live scoring uses a success factor of 1.0 only, not the 1.2 multiplier for declared tasks.': 'FFVP Federal Cup (NetCoupe) på WeGlide. Den poängsatta banan har högst tre vändpunkter mellan start och mål och minst 25 km totalt. Poäng är proportionella mot krediterad distans, 100 dividerat med gliderhandikapp (DAeC-stilsindex) och en framgångsfaktor på 1,0 för en fri flygning eller 1,2 för en uppgift som deklareras elektroniskt före start. XCSoar live scoring använder en framgångsfaktor på endast 1,0, inte multiplikatorn 1,2 för deklarerade uppgifter.',
        'Previous waypoint: when an ordered task is loaded, automatically tracks the task waypoint before the active leg (the start waypoint when on the first leg). Displays the waypoint name, arrival altitude difference relative to the safety arrival height, and distance. Click to choose a different waypoint to display (task waypoints when a task is loaded, otherwise the full waypoint list); selection is informational only and never advances the task or sets a Goto. With a task loaded, choose "Resume auto tracking" at the top of the list to revert to automatic tracking.': 'Föregående waypoint: när en beställd uppgift laddas, spårar automatiskt uppgiftens waypoint före den aktiva etappen (startwaypointen när den är på den första etappen). Visar waypointnamnet, ankomsthöjdsskillnaden i förhållande till säkerhetens ankomsthöjd och avstånd. Klicka för att välja en annan waypoint att visa (uppgiftswaypoints när en uppgift är laddad, annars hela waypointlistan); Valet är endast informativt och förflyttar aldrig uppgiften eller anger ett Goto. Med en uppgift laddad, välj "Återuppta automatisk spårning" överst i listan för att återgå till automatisk spårning.',
        'This parameter estimates the height%s at which the average dry updraft strength drops below 225 fpm and is expected to give better quantitative numbers for the maximum cloudless thermalling height than the BL Top height, especially when mixing results from vertical wind shear rather than thermals. (Note: the present assumptions tend to underpredict the max. thermalling height for dry conditions.) In the presence of clouds the maximum thermalling height may instead be limited by the cloud base. Being for "dry" thermals, this parameter omits the effect of "cloudsuck".': 'Denna parameter uppskattar höjden %s vid vilken den genomsnittliga torra uppströmsstyrkan faller under 225 fpm och förväntas ge bättre kvantitativa siffror för den maximala molnfria termiska höjden än BL Top-höjden, särskilt när blandningsresultat från vertikal vindskjuvning snarare än termik. (Notera: de nuvarande antagandena tenderar att underförutsäga den maximala termiska höjden för torra förhållanden.) I närvaro av moln kan den maximala termiska höjden istället begränsas av molnbasen. Eftersom den är för "torr" termik utelämnar denna parameter effekten av "molnsug".',
        '![](resource:IDB_WARNING_TRIANGLE)\n\n!!! warning\n# Important Safety Notice\n\nBy using XCSoar, you acknowledge and accept the following:\n\n## Limitations\n\n- XCSoar is for **situational awareness only**\n- XCSoar is **not** a FLARM display\n- XCSoar is **not** aviation certified in any way\n- The artificial horizon is **not** fit for any purpose\n- Databanks (airspace, waypoints) may contain errors, be incomplete, or **not** up to date\n- NOTAM display does **not** replace proper pre-flight NOTAM briefing\n- NOTAM data may be incomplete, delayed, filtered, or unavailable\n- XCSoar is **not** guaranteed to be error free\n\n## Pilot Responsibility\n\nThe **Pilot in Command** is always responsible for the safe operation of the aircraft. Never rely solely on XCSoar for navigation or situational awareness.\n\n': '![](resource:IDB_WARNING_TRIANGLE)\n\n!!! warning\n# Viktigt säkerhetsmeddelande\n\nGenom att använda XCSoar erkänner och accepterar du följande:\n\n## Begränsningar\n\n- XCSoar är för **endast situationsmedvetenhet**\n- XCSoar är **inte** en FLARM-skärm\n- XCSoar är **inte**-flygcertifierad på något sätt\n- Den konstgjorda horisonten är **inte** lämplig för alla ändamål\n- Databanker (luftrum, waypoints) kan innehålla fel, vara ofullständiga eller **inte** uppdaterade\n- NOTAM-skärmen ersätter **inte** korrekt NOTAM-briefing före flygning\n- NOTAM-data kan vara ofullständiga, försenade, filtrerade eller otillgängliga\n- XCSoar är **inte** garanterat felfritt\n\n## Pilotansvar\n\n**Befälhavande pilot** är alltid ansvarig för säker drift av flygplanet. Lita aldrig enbart på XCSoar för navigering eller situationsmedvetenhet.\n\n',
        '# Getting Started\n\nTo use XCSoar effectively, configure the following:\n\n- [Restore from backup](xcsoar://dialog/backup) - Restore previous XCSoar data from a USB or SD card (optional)\n\n- [%s] [Map and data](xcsoar://config/site-files) - Download maps, waypoints, and airspace files for your region\n\n- [%s] [Aircraft polar](xcsoar://config/planes) - Set up your aircraft with the correct polar curve\n\n- [%s] [Pilot info](xcsoar://config/logger) - Enter your name and weight\n\n- [%s] [Devices](xcsoar://config/devices) - Connect your flight instruments\n\n- [%s] [WeGlide](xcsoar://config/weglide) - Upload flights automatically to WeGlide\n\n- [%s] [Thermal Information Map](xcsoar://config/weather) - Show thermal locations from thermalmap.info on the map\n\n- [%s] [Safety factors](xcsoar://config/safety) - Set arrival height, terrain clearance and polar degradation\n\n- [%s] [Terrain Display](xcsoar://config/terrain) - Choose terrain colors, shading and contour lines\n\n- [ ] [Live tracking](xcsoar://config/tracking) *(optional)* - Share your position via SkyLines or LiveTrack24\n\nThe easiest way to explore XCSoar is to [replay an existing IGC flight](xcsoar://dialog/replay).': '# Komma igång\n\nFör att använda XCSoar effektivt, konfigurera följande:\n\n- [Återställ från säkerhetskopia](xcsoar://dialog/backup) - Återställ tidigare XCSoar-data från ett USB- eller SD-kort (valfritt)\n\n- [%s] [Karta och data](xcsoar://config/site-files) - Ladda ner kartor, waypoints och luftrumsfiler för din region\n\n- [%s] [Flygplan polar](xcsoar://config/planes) - Ställ in ditt flygplan med rätt polarkurva\n\n- [%s] [Pilotinformation](xcsoar://config/logger) - Ange ditt namn och vikt\n\n- [%s] [Enheter](xcsoar://config/devices) - Anslut dina flyginstrument\n\n- [%s] [WeGlide](xcsoar://config/weglide) - Ladda upp flyg automatiskt till WeGlide\n\n- [%s] [Termisk informationskarta](xcsoar://config/weather) - Visa termiska platser från thermalmap.info på kartan\n\n- [%s] [Säkerhetsfaktorer](xcsoar://config/safety) - Ställ in ankomsthöjd, terrängfrigång och polär nedbrytning\n\n- [%s] [Terrängdisplay](xcsoar://config/terrain) - Välj terrängfärger, skuggning och konturlinjer\n\n- [ ] [Livespårning](xcsoar://config/tracking) *(optional)* - Dela din position via SkyLines eller LiveTrack24\n\nDet enklaste sättet att utforska XCSoar är att [spela upp en befintlig IGC-flygning](xcsoar://dialog/replay).',
        '# Gesture Navigation\n\nXCSoar supports touch gestures on the map:\n\n- ![U](resource:IDB_GESTURE_UP) **Swipe Up** (U): Zoom in\n- ![D](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DOWN) **Swipe Down** (D): Zoom out\n- ![R](resource:IDB_GESTURE_RIGHT) **Swipe Right** (R): Previous screen mode\n- ![L](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LEFT) **Swipe Left** (L): Next screen mode\n- ![UD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_UD) **Up-Down** (UD): Auto zoom\n- ![DU](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DU) **Down-Up** (DU): Menu\n- ![DR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DR) **Down-Right** (DR): Waypoint details\n- ![DL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DL) **Down-Left** (DL): Alternates\n- ![LU](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LU) **Left-Up** (LU): Recently used waypoints\n- ![RD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_RD) **Right-Down** (RD): Task manager\n- ![URD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_URD) **Up-Right-Down** (URD): Analysis\n- ![LDR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LDR) **Left-Down-Right** (LDR): Checklist\n- ![URDL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_URDL) **Up-Right-Down-Left** (URDL): Pan mode\n- ![LDRDL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LDRDL) **Left-Down-Right-Down-Left** (LDRDL): Status\n- ![ULDR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_ULDR) **Up-Left-Down-Right** (ULDR): Quick menu\n\nLong-press on the map to enter Pan mode. Tap while in Pan mode to see nearby waypoints.': '# Gestnavigering\n\nXCSoar stöder beröringsgester på kartan:\n\n- ![U](resource:IDB_GESTURE_UP) **Svep uppåt** (U): Zooma in\n- ![D](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DOWN) **Svep nedåt** (D): Zooma ut\n- ![R](resource:IDB_GESTURE_RIGHT) **Svep åt höger** (R): Föregående skärmläge\n- ![L](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LEFT) **Svep åt vänster** (L): Nästa skärmläge\n- ![UD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_UD) **Upp-Ner** (UD): Autozoom\n- ![DU](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DU) **Ner-Upp** (DU): Meny\n- ![DR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DR) **Fullkomligt** (DR): Waypoint detaljer\n- ![DL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DL) **Ned-vänster** (DL): Ersätter\n- ![LU](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LU) **Vänster-Upp** (LU): Nyligen använda waypoints\n- ![RD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_RD) **Höger ner** (RD): Task manager\n- ![URD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_URD) **Upp-Höger-Ner** (URD): Analys\n- ![LDR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LDR) **Vänster-Ner-Höger** (LDR): Checklista\n- ![URDL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_URDL) **Upp-Höger-Ner-Vänster** (URDL): Panoreringsläge\n- ![LDRDL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LDRDL) **Vänster-Ner-Höger-Ner-Vänster** (LDRDL): Status\n- ![ULDR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_ULDR) **Upp-Vänster-Ner-Höger** (ULDR): Snabbmeny\n\nTryck länge på kartan för att gå in i panoreringsläget. Tryck i panoreringsläget för att se närliggande waypoints.',
    },
    "te": {
        'Size of waypoint symbols on the map as a percentage of the built-in artwork (list dialogs keep a fixed row icon size).': 'అంతర్నిర్మిత కళాకృతి యొక్క శాతంగా మ్యాప్\u200cలోని వే పాయింట్ చిహ్నాల పరిమాణం (జాబితా డైలాగ్\u200cలు స్థిర వరుస చిహ్నం పరిమాణాన్ని ఉంచుతాయి).',
        'Home waypoint name, arrival altitude difference relative to the safety arrival height, and distance. Click to change the home waypoint.': 'ఇంటి వే పాయింట్ పేరు, భద్రత రాక ఎత్తు మరియు దూరానికి సంబంధించి రాక ఎత్తు వ్యత్యాసం. హోమ్ వే పాయింట్\u200cని మార్చడానికి క్లిక్ చేయండి.',
        'Current QNH pressure setting used for barometric altitude calculation. Tap the infobox to open the setup panel and adjust QNH manually.': 'భారమితీయ ఎత్తు గణన కోసం ఉపయోగించబడుతుంది ప్రస్తుత QNH ఒత్తిడి సెట్టింగ్. సెటప్ ప్యానెల్\u200cను తెరవడానికి మరియు QNHని మాన్యువల్\u200cగా సర్దుబాటు చేయడానికి ఇన్ఫోబాక్స్\u200cను నొక్కండి.',
        'This page shows WiFi status when NetworkManager or ConnMan is on D-Bus (e.g. Linux with Wayland or KMS). Open WiFi list to scan and connect when a service is available.': 'NetworkManager లేదా ConnMan D-Busలో ఉన్నప్పుడు ఈ పేజీ WiFi స్థితిని చూపుతుంది (ఉదా. Linux with Wayland లేదా KMS). సేవ అందుబాటులో ఉన్నప్పుడు స్కాన్ చేయడానికి మరియు కనెక్ట్ చేయడానికి WiFi జాబితాను తెరవండి.',
        'The terrain can be shaded among slopes to indicate either wind direction, sun position, a geographically fixed shading from North-West, or a screen-relative fixed shading from top left.': 'గాలి దిశ, సూర్యుని స్థానం, వాయువ్యం నుండి భౌగోళికంగా స్థిరమైన షేడింగ్ లేదా ఎగువ ఎడమ నుండి స్క్రీన్-సంబంధిత స్థిరమైన షేడింగ్\u200cను సూచించడానికి వాలుల మధ్య భూభాగాన్ని షేడ్ చేయవచ్చు.',
        "Synchronize the glide polar between XCSoar and the device (LXNAV varios). 'Receive' adopts the polar from the device (e.g. for club gliders). 'Send' pushes XCSoar's polar to the device.": "XCSoar మరియు పరికరం (LXNAV వేరియోస్) మధ్య గ్లైడ్ పోలార్\u200cను సమకాలీకరించండి. 'రిసీవ్' పరికరం నుండి ధ్రువాన్ని స్వీకరిస్తుంది (ఉదా. క్లబ్ గ్లైడర్\u200cల కోసం). 'పంపు' XCSoar యొక్క ధ్రువాన్ని పరికరానికి నెట్టివేస్తుంది.",
        'List of active airspace files. Use the Add and Remove buttons to activate or deactivate airspace files respectively. Supported file types are: Openair (.openair /.txt /.air), and Tim Newport-Pearce (.sua).': 'యాక్టివ్ ఎయిర్\u200cస్పేస్ ఫైల్\u200cల జాబితా. ఎయిర్\u200cస్పేస్ ఫైల్\u200cలను వరుసగా యాక్టివేట్ చేయడానికి లేదా డియాక్టివేట్ చేయడానికి యాడ్ అండ్ రిమూవ్ బటన్\u200cలను ఉపయోగించండి. మద్దతు ఉన్న ఫైల్ రకాలు: Openair (.openair /.txt /.air), మరియు Tim Newport-Pearce (.sua).',
        'Signed countdown until the start gate opens or closes (now). Value colour and secondary line reflect gate state at the current time: Waiting (blue), Open (green), Closed (red). PEV window overrides task gate when set.': 'ప్రారంభ ద్వారం తెరుచుకునే లేదా మూసివేయబడే వరకు (ఇప్పుడు) కౌంట్\u200cడౌన్ సంతకం చేయబడింది. విలువ రంగు మరియు ద్వితీయ పంక్తి ప్రస్తుత సమయంలో గేట్ స్థితిని ప్రతిబింబిస్తాయి: వేచి ఉండటం (నీలం), ఓపెన్ (ఆకుపచ్చ), మూసివేయబడింది (ఎరుపు). సెట్ చేసినప్పుడు PEV విండో టాస్క్ గేట్\u200cను భర్తీ చేస్తుంది.',
        'Tells XCSoar to send its current GPS position to the device as $GPGGA and $GPRMC sentences. Turn off when another GPS source is already feeding the device on the same line. Changes take effect after reconnecting the device.': 'పరికరానికి దాని ప్రస్తుత GPS స్థానాన్ని $GPGGA మరియు $GPRMC వాక్యాల రూపంలో పంపమని XCSoarకి చెబుతుంది. మరొక GPS మూలం ఇప్పటికే అదే లైన్\u200cలో పరికరాన్ని ఫీడ్ చేస్తున్నప్పుడు ఆఫ్ చేయండి. పరికరాన్ని మళ్లీ కనెక్ట్ చేసిన తర్వాత మార్పులు ప్రభావం చూపుతాయి.',
        'Logger pressure altitude when the device provides it (igc_pressure_altitude), otherwise ISA pressure altitude only (1013.25 hPa; not QNH-corrected). Does not show barometric AMSL or GPS height — use other InfoBoxes for navigation.': 'పరికరం దానిని అందించినప్పుడు ఒత్తిడి ఎత్తును లాగర్ చేయండి (igc_pressure_altitude), లేకపోతే ISA పీడన ఎత్తు మాత్రమే (1013.25 hPa; QNH- సరిదిద్దబడలేదు). బారోమెట్రిక్ AMSL లేదా GPS ఎత్తు చూపదు - నావిగేషన్ కోసం ఇతర ఇన్ఫోబాక్స్\u200cలను ఉపయోగించండి.',
        'Same gate as Start open. Main value is estimated time to reach the start line (MacCready leg when available, else distance / ground speed). Value colour and secondary line reflect gate state at that ETA: Too early (blue), Can start (green), Too late (red).': 'స్టార్ట్ ఓపెన్ అయినప్పుడు అదే గేట్. ప్రధాన విలువ ప్రారంభ రేఖను చేరుకోవడానికి అంచనా వేసిన సమయం (అందుబాటులో ఉన్నప్పుడు MacCready లెగ్, లేకపోతే దూరం / గ్రౌండ్ వేగం). విలువ రంగు మరియు ద్వితీయ పంక్తి ఆ ETA వద్ద గేట్ స్థితిని ప్రతిబింబిస్తుంది: చాలా ముందుగానే (నీలం), ప్రారంభించవచ్చు (ఆకుపచ్చ), చాలా ఆలస్యం (ఎరుపు).',
        'Active waypoint: shows the next task waypoint when an ordered task is loaded, otherwise the Goto waypoint. Displays the waypoint name, arrival altitude difference relative to the safety arrival height, and distance. Click to choose a different waypoint (a task waypoint to skip to that leg, or any waypoint to set as Goto when no task is loaded).': 'యాక్టివ్ వే పాయింట్: ఆర్డర్ చేసిన టాస్క్ లోడ్ అయినప్పుడు తదుపరి టాస్క్ వే పాయింట్\u200cని చూపుతుంది, లేకపోతే గోటో వే పాయింట్. వే పాయింట్ పేరు, భద్రత రాక ఎత్తు మరియు దూరానికి సంబంధించి రాక ఎత్తు తేడాను ప్రదర్శిస్తుంది. వేరొక వే పాయింట్\u200cని ఎంచుకోవడానికి క్లిక్ చేయండి (ఆ లెగ్\u200cకి స్కిప్ చేయడానికి టాస్క్ వేపాయింట్ లేదా టాస్క్ లోడ్ కానప్పుడు గోటోగా సెట్ చేయడానికి ఏదైనా వే పాయింట్).',
        'FFVP Federal Cup (NetCoupe) on WeGlide. The scored path has at most three turnpoints between start and finish and at least 25 km total. Points are proportional to credited distance, 100 divided by the glider handicap (DAeC-style index), and a success factor of 1.0 for a free flight or 1.2 for a task declared electronically before takeoff. XCSoar live scoring uses a success factor of 1.0 only, not the 1.2 multiplier for declared tasks.': 'WeGlideలో FFVP ఫెడరల్ కప్ (NetCoupe). స్కోర్ చేసిన మార్గం ప్రారంభం మరియు ముగింపు మధ్య గరిష్టంగా మూడు టర్న్\u200cపాయింట్\u200cలను కలిగి ఉంటుంది మరియు మొత్తం కనీసం 25 కి.మీ. పాయింట్లు క్రెడిట్ చేయబడిన దూరానికి అనులోమానుపాతంలో ఉంటాయి, 100 గ్లైడర్ హ్యాండిక్యాప్ (DAeC-స్టైల్ ఇండెక్స్)తో భాగించబడతాయి మరియు ఉచిత విమానానికి 1.0 లేదా టేకాఫ్\u200cకు ముందు ఎలక్ట్రానిక్\u200cగా డిక్లేర్ చేయబడిన పనికి 1.2 సక్సెస్ ఫ్యాక్టర్. XCSoar ప్రత్యక్ష స్కోరింగ్ 1.0 విజయ కారకాన్ని మాత్రమే ఉపయోగిస్తుంది, డిక్లేర్డ్ టాస్క్\u200cల కోసం 1.2 గుణకం కాదు.',
        'Previous waypoint: when an ordered task is loaded, automatically tracks the task waypoint before the active leg (the start waypoint when on the first leg). Displays the waypoint name, arrival altitude difference relative to the safety arrival height, and distance. Click to choose a different waypoint to display (task waypoints when a task is loaded, otherwise the full waypoint list); selection is informational only and never advances the task or sets a Goto. With a task loaded, choose "Resume auto tracking" at the top of the list to revert to automatic tracking.': 'మునుపటి వే పాయింట్: ఆర్డర్ చేసిన టాస్క్ లోడ్ అయినప్పుడు, యాక్టివ్ లెగ్\u200cకి ముందు టాస్క్ వే పాయింట్\u200cని ఆటోమేటిక్\u200cగా ట్రాక్ చేస్తుంది (మొదటి లెగ్\u200cలో ఉన్నప్పుడు స్టార్ట్ వే పాయింట్). వే పాయింట్ పేరు, భద్రత రాక ఎత్తు మరియు దూరానికి సంబంధించి రాక ఎత్తు తేడాను ప్రదర్శిస్తుంది. ప్రదర్శించడానికి వేరొక వే పాయింట్\u200cని ఎంచుకోవడానికి క్లిక్ చేయండి (టాస్క్ లోడ్ అయినప్పుడు టాస్క్ వే పాయింట్\u200cలు, లేకపోతే పూర్తి వే పాయింట్ జాబితా); ఎంపిక అనేది సమాచారం మాత్రమే మరియు టాస్క్\u200cను ఎప్పటికీ ముందుకు తీసుకెళ్లదు లేదా గోటోను సెట్ చేయదు. టాస్క్ లోడ్ చేయబడినప్పుడు, ఆటోమేటిక్ ట్రాకింగ్\u200cకి తిరిగి రావడానికి జాబితా ఎగువన ఉన్న "ఆటో ట్రాకింగ్\u200cను పునఃప్రారంభించండి"ని ఎంచుకోండి.',
        'This parameter estimates the height%s at which the average dry updraft strength drops below 225 fpm and is expected to give better quantitative numbers for the maximum cloudless thermalling height than the BL Top height, especially when mixing results from vertical wind shear rather than thermals. (Note: the present assumptions tend to underpredict the max. thermalling height for dry conditions.) In the presence of clouds the maximum thermalling height may instead be limited by the cloud base. Being for "dry" thermals, this parameter omits the effect of "cloudsuck".': 'ఈ పరామితి %s ఎత్తును అంచనా వేస్తుంది, దీనిలో సగటు డ్రై అప్\u200cడ్రాఫ్ట్ బలం 225 fpm కంటే తక్కువగా పడిపోతుంది మరియు BL టాప్ ఎత్తు కంటే గరిష్ట క్లౌడ్\u200cలెస్ థర్మలింగ్ ఎత్తుకు మెరుగైన పరిమాణాత్మక సంఖ్యలను ఇస్తుందని అంచనా వేస్తుంది, ముఖ్యంగా థర్మల్\u200cల కంటే నిలువుగా ఉండే గాలి కోత నుండి ఫలితాలను కలపడం. (గమనిక: ప్రస్తుత అంచనాలు పొడి పరిస్థితుల కోసం గరిష్టంగా థర్మలింగ్ ఎత్తును తక్కువగా అంచనా వేస్తాయి.) మేఘాల సమక్షంలో గరిష్ట థర్మలింగ్ ఎత్తు బదులుగా క్లౌడ్ బేస్ ద్వారా పరిమితం చేయబడవచ్చు. "డ్రై" థర్మల్\u200cల కోసం, ఈ పరామితి "క్లౌడ్\u200cసక్" ప్రభావాన్ని వదిలివేస్తుంది.',
        '![](resource:IDB_WARNING_TRIANGLE)\n\n!!! warning\n# Important Safety Notice\n\nBy using XCSoar, you acknowledge and accept the following:\n\n## Limitations\n\n- XCSoar is for **situational awareness only**\n- XCSoar is **not** a FLARM display\n- XCSoar is **not** aviation certified in any way\n- The artificial horizon is **not** fit for any purpose\n- Databanks (airspace, waypoints) may contain errors, be incomplete, or **not** up to date\n- NOTAM display does **not** replace proper pre-flight NOTAM briefing\n- NOTAM data may be incomplete, delayed, filtered, or unavailable\n- XCSoar is **not** guaranteed to be error free\n\n## Pilot Responsibility\n\nThe **Pilot in Command** is always responsible for the safe operation of the aircraft. Never rely solely on XCSoar for navigation or situational awareness.\n\n': '![](resource:IDB_WARNING_TRIANGLE)\n\n!!! warning\n# ముఖ్యమైన భద్రతా నోటీసు\n\nXCSoarని ఉపయోగించడం ద్వారా, మీరు ఈ క్రింది వాటిని గుర్తించి, అంగీకరిస్తారు:\n\n## పరిమితులు\n\n- XCSoar **పరిస్థితుల అవగాహన మాత్రమే** కోసం\n- XCSoar అనేది **కాదు** ఒక FLARM డిస్ప్లే\n- XCSoar ఏ విధంగానైనా **కాదు** ఏవియేషన్ సర్టిఫికేట్ పొందింది\n- కృత్రిమ హోరిజోన్ ఏదైనా ప్రయోజనం కోసం **కాదు** సరిపోతుంది\n- డేటాబ్యాంక్\u200cలు (ఎయిర్\u200cస్పేస్, వే పాయింట్\u200cలు) లోపాలను కలిగి ఉండవచ్చు, అసంపూర్ణంగా ఉండవచ్చు లేదా **కాదు** తాజాగా ఉండవచ్చు\n- NOTAM ప్రదర్శన **కాదు** సరైన ప్రీ-ఫ్లైట్ NOTAM బ్రీఫింగ్\u200cను భర్తీ చేస్తుంది\n- NOTAM డేటా అసంపూర్ణంగా ఉండవచ్చు, ఆలస్యం కావచ్చు, ఫిల్టర్ చేయబడి ఉండవచ్చు లేదా అందుబాటులో ఉండకపోవచ్చు\n- XCSoar అనేది **కాదు** దోషరహితమని హామీ ఇవ్వబడింది\n\n## పైలట్ బాధ్యత\n\n**పైలట్ ఇన్ కమాండ్** ఎల్లప్పుడూ విమానం యొక్క సురక్షిత ఆపరేషన్\u200cకు బాధ్యత వహిస్తుంది. నావిగేషన్ లేదా పరిస్థితులపై అవగాహన కోసం XCSoarపై మాత్రమే ఆధారపడకండి.\n\n',
        '# Getting Started\n\nTo use XCSoar effectively, configure the following:\n\n- [Restore from backup](xcsoar://dialog/backup) - Restore previous XCSoar data from a USB or SD card (optional)\n\n- [%s] [Map and data](xcsoar://config/site-files) - Download maps, waypoints, and airspace files for your region\n\n- [%s] [Aircraft polar](xcsoar://config/planes) - Set up your aircraft with the correct polar curve\n\n- [%s] [Pilot info](xcsoar://config/logger) - Enter your name and weight\n\n- [%s] [Devices](xcsoar://config/devices) - Connect your flight instruments\n\n- [%s] [WeGlide](xcsoar://config/weglide) - Upload flights automatically to WeGlide\n\n- [%s] [Thermal Information Map](xcsoar://config/weather) - Show thermal locations from thermalmap.info on the map\n\n- [%s] [Safety factors](xcsoar://config/safety) - Set arrival height, terrain clearance and polar degradation\n\n- [%s] [Terrain Display](xcsoar://config/terrain) - Choose terrain colors, shading and contour lines\n\n- [ ] [Live tracking](xcsoar://config/tracking) *(optional)* - Share your position via SkyLines or LiveTrack24\n\nThe easiest way to explore XCSoar is to [replay an existing IGC flight](xcsoar://dialog/replay).': '# ప్రారంభించడం\n\nXCSoarను సమర్థవంతంగా ఉపయోగించడానికి, కింది వాటిని కాన్ఫిగర్ చేయండి:\n\n- [బ్యాకప్ నుండి పునరుద్ధరించండి](xcsoar://dialog/backup) - USB లేదా SD కార్డ్ నుండి మునుపటి XCSoar డేటాను పునరుద్ధరించండి (ఐచ్ఛికం)\n\n- [%s] [మ్యాప్ మరియు డేటా](xcsoar://config/site-files) - మీ ప్రాంతం కోసం మ్యాప్\u200cలు, వే పాయింట్\u200cలు మరియు ఎయిర్\u200cస్పేస్ ఫైల్\u200cలను డౌన్\u200cలోడ్ చేయండి\n\n- [%s] [విమానం ధ్రువ](xcsoar://config/planes) - సరైన ధ్రువ వక్రతతో మీ విమానాన్ని సెటప్ చేయండి\n\n- [%s] [పైలట్ సమాచారం](xcsoar://config/logger) - మీ పేరు మరియు బరువును నమోదు చేయండి\n\n- [%s] [పరికరాలు](xcsoar://config/devices) - మీ విమాన పరికరాలను కనెక్ట్ చేయండి\n\n- [%s] [WeGlide](xcsoar://config/weglide) - WeGlideకి స్వయంచాలకంగా విమానాలను అప్\u200cలోడ్ చేయండి\n\n- [%s] [థర్మల్ ఇన్ఫర్మేషన్ మ్యాప్](xcsoar://config/weather) - మ్యాప్\u200cలో thermalmap.info నుండి థర్మల్ స్థానాలను చూపండి\n\n- [%s] [భద్రతా కారకాలు](xcsoar://config/safety) - రాక ఎత్తు, భూభాగం క్లియరెన్స్ మరియు ధ్రువ క్షీణతను సెట్ చేయండి\n\n- [%s] [టెర్రైన్ డిస్ప్లే](xcsoar://config/terrain) - భూభాగం రంగులు, షేడింగ్ మరియు కాంటౌర్ లైన్లను ఎంచుకోండి\n\n- [ ] [ప్రత్యక్ష ట్రాకింగ్](xcsoar://config/tracking) *(optional)* - SkyLines లేదా LiveTrack24 ద్వారా మీ స్థానాన్ని పంచుకోండి\n\nXCSoarని అన్వేషించడానికి సులభమైన మార్గం [ఇప్పటికే ఉన్న IGC విమానాన్ని మళ్లీ ప్లే చేయండి](xcsoar://dialog/replay).',
        '# Gesture Navigation\n\nXCSoar supports touch gestures on the map:\n\n- ![U](resource:IDB_GESTURE_UP) **Swipe Up** (U): Zoom in\n- ![D](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DOWN) **Swipe Down** (D): Zoom out\n- ![R](resource:IDB_GESTURE_RIGHT) **Swipe Right** (R): Previous screen mode\n- ![L](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LEFT) **Swipe Left** (L): Next screen mode\n- ![UD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_UD) **Up-Down** (UD): Auto zoom\n- ![DU](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DU) **Down-Up** (DU): Menu\n- ![DR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DR) **Down-Right** (DR): Waypoint details\n- ![DL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DL) **Down-Left** (DL): Alternates\n- ![LU](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LU) **Left-Up** (LU): Recently used waypoints\n- ![RD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_RD) **Right-Down** (RD): Task manager\n- ![URD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_URD) **Up-Right-Down** (URD): Analysis\n- ![LDR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LDR) **Left-Down-Right** (LDR): Checklist\n- ![URDL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_URDL) **Up-Right-Down-Left** (URDL): Pan mode\n- ![LDRDL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LDRDL) **Left-Down-Right-Down-Left** (LDRDL): Status\n- ![ULDR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_ULDR) **Up-Left-Down-Right** (ULDR): Quick menu\n\nLong-press on the map to enter Pan mode. Tap while in Pan mode to see nearby waypoints.': '# సంజ్ఞ నావిగేషన్\n\nXCSoar మ్యాప్\u200cలో స్పర్శ సంజ్ఞలకు మద్దతు ఇస్తుంది:\n\n- ![U](resource:IDB_GESTURE_UP) **పైకి స్వైప్ చేయండి** (U): జూమ్ ఇన్ చేయండి\n- ![D](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DOWN) **క్రిందికి స్వైప్ చేయండి** (D): జూమ్ అవుట్ చేయండి\n- ![R](resource:IDB_GESTURE_RIGHT) **కుడివైపు స్వైప్ చేయండి** (R): మునుపటి స్క్రీన్ మోడ్\n- ![L](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LEFT) **ఎడమవైపు స్వైప్ చేయండి** (L): తదుపరి స్క్రీన్ మోడ్\n- ![UD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_UD) **అప్-డౌన్** (UD): ఆటో జూమ్\n- ![DU](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DU) **డౌన్-అప్** (DU): మెనూ\n- ![DR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DR) **దిగువ-కుడి** (DR): వే పాయింట్ వివరాలు\n- ![DL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DL) **దిగువ-ఎడమ** (DL): ప్రత్యామ్నాయాలు\n- ![LU](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LU) **ఎడమ-పైకి** (LU): ఇటీవల ఉపయోగించిన వే పాయింట్లు\n- ![RD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_RD) **కుడి-క్రిందికి** (RD): టాస్క్ మేనేజర్\n- ![URD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_URD) **అప్-రైట్-డౌన్** (URD): విశ్లేషణ\n- ![LDR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LDR) **ఎడమ-క్రింది-కుడి** (LDR): చెక్\u200cలిస్ట్\n- ![URDL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_URDL) **పైకి-కుడి-క్రిందికి-ఎడమ** (URDL): పాన్ మోడ్\n- ![LDRDL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LDRDL) **లెఫ్ట్-డౌన్-రైట్-డౌన్-ఎడమ** (LDRDL): స్థితి\n- ![ULDR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_ULDR) **పైకి-ఎడమ-క్రిందికి-కుడి** (ULDR): త్వరిత మెను\n\nపాన్ మోడ్\u200cలోకి ప్రవేశించడానికి మ్యాప్\u200cపై ఎక్కువసేపు నొక్కండి. సమీపంలోని వే పాయింట్\u200cలను చూడటానికి పాన్ మోడ్\u200cలో ఉన్నప్పుడు నొక్కండి.',
    },
    "tr": {
        'Size of waypoint symbols on the map as a percentage of the built-in artwork (list dialogs keep a fixed row icon size).': 'Yerleşik resmin yüzdesi olarak haritadaki yol noktası sembollerinin boyutu (liste iletişim kutuları sabit bir satır simgesi boyutunu korur).',
        'Home waypoint name, arrival altitude difference relative to the safety arrival height, and distance. Click to change the home waypoint.': 'Ana yol noktası adı, güvenli varış yüksekliğine göre varış yüksekliği farkı ve mesafe. Ana yol noktasını değiştirmek için tıklayın.',
        'Current QNH pressure setting used for barometric altitude calculation. Tap the infobox to open the setup panel and adjust QNH manually.': "Barometrik yükseklik hesaplaması için kullanılan mevcut QNH basınç ayarı. Kurulum panelini açmak ve QNH'yi manuel olarak ayarlamak için bilgi kutusuna dokunun.",
        'This page shows WiFi status when NetworkManager or ConnMan is on D-Bus (e.g. Linux with Wayland or KMS). Open WiFi list to scan and connect when a service is available.': 'Bu sayfa, NetworkManager veya ConnMan D-Bus üzerinde olduğunda WiFi durumunu gösterir (örn. Wayland veya KMS ile Linux). Bir hizmet mevcut olduğunda taramak ve bağlanmak için WiFi listesini açın.',
        'The terrain can be shaded among slopes to indicate either wind direction, sun position, a geographically fixed shading from North-West, or a screen-relative fixed shading from top left.': 'Arazi, rüzgar yönünü, güneşin konumunu, Kuzeybatıdan coğrafi olarak sabit bir gölgelemeyi veya sol üstten ekrana bağlı sabit bir gölgelemeyi belirtmek için eğimler arasında gölgelendirilebilir.',
        "Synchronize the glide polar between XCSoar and the device (LXNAV varios). 'Receive' adopts the polar from the device (e.g. for club gliders). 'Send' pushes XCSoar's polar to the device.": "XCSoar ve cihaz (LXNAV çeşitli) arasındaki kayma polaritesini senkronize edin. 'Al', cihazdaki polariteyi benimser (örn. kulüp planörleri için). 'Gönder', XCSoar'ın polarını cihaza iter.",
        'List of active airspace files. Use the Add and Remove buttons to activate or deactivate airspace files respectively. Supported file types are: Openair (.openair /.txt /.air), and Tim Newport-Pearce (.sua).': 'Aktif hava sahası dosyalarının listesi. Hava sahası dosyalarını sırasıyla etkinleştirmek veya devre dışı bırakmak için Ekle ve Kaldır düğmelerini kullanın. Desteklenen dosya türleri şunlardır: Openair (.openair /.txt /.air) ve Tim Newport-Pearce (.sua).',
        'Signed countdown until the start gate opens or closes (now). Value colour and secondary line reflect gate state at the current time: Waiting (blue), Open (green), Closed (red). PEV window overrides task gate when set.': 'Başlangıç \u200b\u200bkapısı açılana veya kapanana kadar (şimdi) imzalı geri sayım. Değer rengi ve ikincil çizgi, geçerli zamandaki kapı durumunu yansıtır: Bekliyor (mavi), Açık (yeşil), Kapalı (kırmızı). PEV penceresi ayarlandığında görev kapısını geçersiz kılar.',
        'Tells XCSoar to send its current GPS position to the device as $GPGGA and $GPRMC sentences. Turn off when another GPS source is already feeding the device on the same line. Changes take effect after reconnecting the device.': "XCSoar'a mevcut GPS konumunu cihaza $GPGGA ve $GPRMC cümleleri olarak göndermesini söyler. Başka bir GPS kaynağı aynı hat üzerinden cihazı besliyorsa kapatın. Değişiklikler cihaz yeniden bağlandıktan sonra geçerli olur.",
        'Logger pressure altitude when the device provides it (igc_pressure_altitude), otherwise ISA pressure altitude only (1013.25 hPa; not QNH-corrected). Does not show barometric AMSL or GPS height — use other InfoBoxes for navigation.': 'Cihaz sağladığında kaydedici basınç yüksekliği (igc_press_altitude), aksi takdirde yalnızca ISA basınç yüksekliği (1013,25 hPa; QNH düzeltmeli değil). Barometrik AMSL veya GPS yüksekliğini göstermez; navigasyon için diğer Bilgi Kutularını kullanın.',
        'Same gate as Start open. Main value is estimated time to reach the start line (MacCready leg when available, else distance / ground speed). Value colour and secondary line reflect gate state at that ETA: Too early (blue), Can start (green), Too late (red).': "Start açıkken aynı kapı. Ana değer, başlangıç \u200b\u200bçizgisine ulaşmak için tahmini süredir (varsa MacCready ayağı, aksi halde mesafe / yer hızı). Değer rengi ve ikincil çizgi, söz konusu ETA'daki kapı durumunu yansıtır: Çok erken (mavi), Başlayabilir (yeşil), Çok geç (kırmızı).",
        'Active waypoint: shows the next task waypoint when an ordered task is loaded, otherwise the Goto waypoint. Displays the waypoint name, arrival altitude difference relative to the safety arrival height, and distance. Click to choose a different waypoint (a task waypoint to skip to that leg, or any waypoint to set as Goto when no task is loaded).': 'Aktif yol noktası: sıralı bir görev yüklendiğinde bir sonraki görev geçiş noktasını gösterir, aksi halde Goto yol noktasını gösterir. Yol noktası adını, güvenli varış yüksekliğine göre varış yüksekliği farkını ve mesafeyi görüntüler. Farklı bir yol noktası seçmek için tıklayın (o ayağa atlamak için bir görev yol noktası veya hiçbir görev yüklenmediğinde Goto olarak ayarlanacak herhangi bir yol noktası).',
        'FFVP Federal Cup (NetCoupe) on WeGlide. The scored path has at most three turnpoints between start and finish and at least 25 km total. Points are proportional to credited distance, 100 divided by the glider handicap (DAeC-style index), and a success factor of 1.0 for a free flight or 1.2 for a task declared electronically before takeoff. XCSoar live scoring uses a success factor of 1.0 only, not the 1.2 multiplier for declared tasks.': "WeGlide'da FFVP Federal Kupası (NetCoupe). Puanlı yol, başlangıç \u200b\u200bve bitiş arasında en fazla üç dönüş noktasına sahiptir ve toplamda en az 25 km'dir. Puanlar, kredilendirilen mesafeyle orantılıdır, 100 puan planör handikapına (DAeC tarzı endeks) bölünür ve serbest uçuş için 1,0 veya kalkıştan önce elektronik olarak ilan edilen bir görev için 1,2 başarı faktörüdür. XCSoar canlı puanlama, beyan edilen görevler için 1,2 çarpanını değil, yalnızca 1,0 başarı faktörünü kullanır.",
        'Previous waypoint: when an ordered task is loaded, automatically tracks the task waypoint before the active leg (the start waypoint when on the first leg). Displays the waypoint name, arrival altitude difference relative to the safety arrival height, and distance. Click to choose a different waypoint to display (task waypoints when a task is loaded, otherwise the full waypoint list); selection is informational only and never advances the task or sets a Goto. With a task loaded, choose "Resume auto tracking" at the top of the list to revert to automatic tracking.': 'Önceki yol noktası: Sıralı bir görev yüklendiğinde, aktif ayaktan önceki görev ara noktasını otomatik olarak izler (ilk ayaktayken başlangıç \u200b\u200byol noktası). Yol noktası adını, güvenli varış yüksekliğine göre varış yüksekliği farkını ve mesafeyi görüntüler. Görüntülenecek farklı bir yol noktası seçmek için tıklayın (bir görev yüklendiğinde görev ara noktaları, aksi halde tam yol noktası listesi); seçim yalnızca bilgilendirme amaçlıdır ve hiçbir zaman görevi ilerletmez veya bir Git ayarlamaz. Bir görev yüklendiğinde, otomatik izlemeye geri dönmek için listenin en üstündeki "Otomatik takibi devam ettir"\'i seçin.',
        'This parameter estimates the height%s at which the average dry updraft strength drops below 225 fpm and is expected to give better quantitative numbers for the maximum cloudless thermalling height than the BL Top height, especially when mixing results from vertical wind shear rather than thermals. (Note: the present assumptions tend to underpredict the max. thermalling height for dry conditions.) In the presence of clouds the maximum thermalling height may instead be limited by the cloud base. Being for "dry" thermals, this parameter omits the effect of "cloudsuck".': 'Bu parametre, ortalama kuru yukarı çekiş kuvvetinin 225 fpm\'nin altına düştüğü %s yüksekliğini tahmin eder ve özellikle karıştırmanın termiklerden ziyade dikey rüzgar kesmesinden kaynaklandığı durumlarda, maksimum bulutsuz termiklenme yüksekliği için BL Top yüksekliğinden daha iyi niceliksel sayılar vermesi beklenir. (Not: mevcut varsayımlar, kuru koşullar için maksimum ısıllaşma yüksekliğini olduğundan düşük tahmin etme eğilimindedir.) Bulutlu durumlarda, maksimum ısıllaşma yüksekliği bunun yerine bulut tabanı tarafından sınırlanabilir. "Kuru" termikler için olan bu parametre, "bulut emme" etkisini göz ardı eder.',
        '![](resource:IDB_WARNING_TRIANGLE)\n\n!!! warning\n# Important Safety Notice\n\nBy using XCSoar, you acknowledge and accept the following:\n\n## Limitations\n\n- XCSoar is for **situational awareness only**\n- XCSoar is **not** a FLARM display\n- XCSoar is **not** aviation certified in any way\n- The artificial horizon is **not** fit for any purpose\n- Databanks (airspace, waypoints) may contain errors, be incomplete, or **not** up to date\n- NOTAM display does **not** replace proper pre-flight NOTAM briefing\n- NOTAM data may be incomplete, delayed, filtered, or unavailable\n- XCSoar is **not** guaranteed to be error free\n\n## Pilot Responsibility\n\nThe **Pilot in Command** is always responsible for the safe operation of the aircraft. Never rely solely on XCSoar for navigation or situational awareness.\n\n': "![](resource:IDB_WARNING_TRIANGLE)\n\n!!! warning\n# Önemli Güvenlik Uyarısı\n\nXCSoar'ı kullanarak aşağıdakileri onaylıyor ve kabul ediyorsunuz:\n\n## Sınırlamalar\n\n- XCSoar **yalnızca durumsal farkındalık** içindir\n- XCSoar bir **Olumsuz** FLARM ekranıdır\n- XCSoar herhangi bir şekilde **Olumsuz** havacılık sertifikasına sahiptir\n- Yapay ufuk her amaca uygun **Olumsuz**'dur\n- Veri bankaları (hava sahası, ara noktalar) hatalar içerebilir, eksik olabilir veya **Olumsuz** güncel olabilir\n- NOTAM ekranı **Olumsuz** uçuş öncesi uygun NOTAM brifinginin yerini alıyor\n- NOTAM verileri eksik, gecikmeli, filtrelenmiş veya kullanılamıyor olabilir\n- XCSoar'ın hatasız olduğu **Olumsuz** garantilidir\n\n## Pilot Sorumluluğu\n\n**Komuta Pilotu** her zaman uçağın güvenli işletiminden sorumludur. Navigasyon veya durumsal farkındalık için asla yalnızca XCSoar'a güvenmeyin.\n\n",
        '# Getting Started\n\nTo use XCSoar effectively, configure the following:\n\n- [Restore from backup](xcsoar://dialog/backup) - Restore previous XCSoar data from a USB or SD card (optional)\n\n- [%s] [Map and data](xcsoar://config/site-files) - Download maps, waypoints, and airspace files for your region\n\n- [%s] [Aircraft polar](xcsoar://config/planes) - Set up your aircraft with the correct polar curve\n\n- [%s] [Pilot info](xcsoar://config/logger) - Enter your name and weight\n\n- [%s] [Devices](xcsoar://config/devices) - Connect your flight instruments\n\n- [%s] [WeGlide](xcsoar://config/weglide) - Upload flights automatically to WeGlide\n\n- [%s] [Thermal Information Map](xcsoar://config/weather) - Show thermal locations from thermalmap.info on the map\n\n- [%s] [Safety factors](xcsoar://config/safety) - Set arrival height, terrain clearance and polar degradation\n\n- [%s] [Terrain Display](xcsoar://config/terrain) - Choose terrain colors, shading and contour lines\n\n- [ ] [Live tracking](xcsoar://config/tracking) *(optional)* - Share your position via SkyLines or LiveTrack24\n\nThe easiest way to explore XCSoar is to [replay an existing IGC flight](xcsoar://dialog/replay).': "# Başlarken\n\nXCSoar'ı etkili bir şekilde kullanmak için aşağıdakileri yapılandırın:\n\n- [Yedeklemeden geri yükle](xcsoar://dialog/backup) - Önceki XCSoar verilerini bir USB veya SD karttan geri yükleyin (isteğe bağlı)\n\n- [%s] [Harita ve veriler](xcsoar://config/site-files) - Bölgeniz için haritaları, ara noktaları ve hava sahası dosyalarını indirin\n\n- [%s] [Uçak kutup](xcsoar://config/planes) - Uçağınızı doğru kutup eğrisiyle ayarlayın\n\n- [%s] [Pilot bilgisi](xcsoar://config/logger) - Adınızı ve kilonuzu girin\n\n- [%s] [Cihazlar](xcsoar://config/devices) - Uçuş aletlerinizi bağlayın\n\n- [%s] [WeGlide](xcsoar://config/weglide) - Uçuşları WeGlide'a otomatik olarak yükle\n\n- [%s] [Termal Bilgi Haritası](xcsoar://config/weather) - Thermalmap.info'daki termal konumları haritada göster\n\n- [%s] [Güvenlik faktörleri](xcsoar://config/safety) - Varış yüksekliğini, arazi açıklığını ve kutup bozulmasını ayarlayın\n\n- [%s] [Arazi Gösterimi](xcsoar://config/terrain) - Arazi renklerini, gölgelemeyi ve kontur çizgilerini seçin\n\n- [ ] [Canlı izleme](xcsoar://config/tracking) *(optional)* - Konumunuzu SkyLines veya LiveTrack24 aracılığıyla paylaşın\n\nXCSoar'ı keşfetmenin en kolay yolu [mevcut bir IGC uçuşunu tekrar oynatma](xcsoar://dialog/replay).",
        '# Gesture Navigation\n\nXCSoar supports touch gestures on the map:\n\n- ![U](resource:IDB_GESTURE_UP) **Swipe Up** (U): Zoom in\n- ![D](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DOWN) **Swipe Down** (D): Zoom out\n- ![R](resource:IDB_GESTURE_RIGHT) **Swipe Right** (R): Previous screen mode\n- ![L](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LEFT) **Swipe Left** (L): Next screen mode\n- ![UD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_UD) **Up-Down** (UD): Auto zoom\n- ![DU](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DU) **Down-Up** (DU): Menu\n- ![DR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DR) **Down-Right** (DR): Waypoint details\n- ![DL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DL) **Down-Left** (DL): Alternates\n- ![LU](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LU) **Left-Up** (LU): Recently used waypoints\n- ![RD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_RD) **Right-Down** (RD): Task manager\n- ![URD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_URD) **Up-Right-Down** (URD): Analysis\n- ![LDR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LDR) **Left-Down-Right** (LDR): Checklist\n- ![URDL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_URDL) **Up-Right-Down-Left** (URDL): Pan mode\n- ![LDRDL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LDRDL) **Left-Down-Right-Down-Left** (LDRDL): Status\n- ![ULDR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_ULDR) **Up-Left-Down-Right** (ULDR): Quick menu\n\nLong-press on the map to enter Pan mode. Tap while in Pan mode to see nearby waypoints.': '# Hareketle Gezinme\n\nXCSoar haritada dokunma hareketlerini destekler:\n\n- ![U](resource:IDB_GESTURE_UP) **Yukarı Kaydır** (U): Yakınlaştır\n- ![D](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DOWN) **Aşağı Kaydır** (D): Uzaklaştır\n- ![R](resource:IDB_GESTURE_RIGHT) **Sağa Kaydır** (R): Önceki ekran modu\n- ![L](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LEFT) **Sola Kaydır** (L): Sonraki ekran modu\n- ![UD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_UD) **Yukarı-Aşağı** (UD): Otomatik yakınlaştırma\n- ![DU](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DU) **Aşağı-Yukarı** (DU): Menü\n- ![DR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DR) **Büsbütün** (DR): Yol noktası ayrıntıları\n- ![DL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DL) **Alt-Sol** (DL): Alternatifler\n- ![LU](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LU) **Sol Yukarı** (LU): Son kullanılan ara noktalar\n- ![RD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_RD) **Tam** (RD): Görev yöneticisi\n- ![URD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_URD) **Yukarı-Sağ-Aşağı** (URD): Analiz\n- ![LDR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LDR) **Sol-Aşağı-Sağ** (LDR): Kontrol listesi\n- ![URDL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_URDL) **Yukarı-Sağ-Aşağı-Sol** (URDL): Kaydırma modu\n- ![LDRDL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LDRDL) **Sol-Aşağı-Sağ-Aşağı-Sol** (LDRDL): Durum\n- ![ULDR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_ULDR) **Yukarı-Sol-Aşağı-Sağ** (ULDR): Hızlı menü\n\nPan moduna girmek için haritaya uzun basın. Yakındaki yol noktalarını görmek için Kaydırma modundayken dokunun.',
    },
    "uk": {
        'Size of waypoint symbols on the map as a percentage of the built-in artwork (list dialogs keep a fixed row icon size).': 'Розмір символів шляхових точок на карті у відсотках від вбудованої ілюстрації (діалогові вікна списків зберігають фіксований розмір піктограм рядка).',
        'Home waypoint name, arrival altitude difference relative to the safety arrival height, and distance. Click to change the home waypoint.': 'Назва маршрутної точки додому, різниця висоти прибуття відносно безпечної висоти прибуття та відстань. Натисніть, щоб змінити домашню маршрутну точку.',
        'Current QNH pressure setting used for barometric altitude calculation. Tap the infobox to open the setup panel and adjust QNH manually.': 'Поточне налаштування тиску QNH, яке використовується для розрахунку барометричної висоти. Торкніться інформаційного поля, щоб відкрити панель налаштування та налаштувати QNH вручну.',
        'This page shows WiFi status when NetworkManager or ConnMan is on D-Bus (e.g. Linux with Wayland or KMS). Open WiFi list to scan and connect when a service is available.': 'Ця сторінка показує статус WiFi, коли NetworkManager або ConnMan підключено до D-Bus (наприклад, Linux із Wayland або KMS). Відкрийте список Wi-Fi для сканування та підключення, коли послуга доступна.',
        'The terrain can be shaded among slopes to indicate either wind direction, sun position, a geographically fixed shading from North-West, or a screen-relative fixed shading from top left.': 'Ландшафт можна заштрихувати між схилами, щоб вказати напрямок вітру, положення сонця, географічно фіксоване затінення з північного заходу або фіксоване затінення відносно екрана з верхнього лівого боку.',
        "Synchronize the glide polar between XCSoar and the device (LXNAV varios). 'Receive' adopts the polar from the device (e.g. for club gliders). 'Send' pushes XCSoar's polar to the device.": 'Синхронізуйте полярність ковзання між XCSoar і пристроєм (різні LXNAV). «Прийом» приймає полярність пристрою (наприклад, для клубних планерів). «Надіслати» надсилає полярність XCSoar на пристрій.',
        'List of active airspace files. Use the Add and Remove buttons to activate or deactivate airspace files respectively. Supported file types are: Openair (.openair /.txt /.air), and Tim Newport-Pearce (.sua).': 'Список активних файлів повітряного простору. Використовуйте кнопки «Додати» та «Видалити», щоб активувати або деактивувати файли повітряного простору відповідно. Підтримувані типи файлів: Openair (.openair /.txt /.air) і Тім Ньюпорт-Пірс (.sua).',
        'Signed countdown until the start gate opens or closes (now). Value colour and secondary line reflect gate state at the current time: Waiting (blue), Open (green), Closed (red). PEV window overrides task gate when set.': 'Зворотний відлік із підписом до відкриття або закриття стартових воріт (зараз). Колір значення та вторинний рядок відображають поточний стан воріт: очікування (синій), відкритий (зелений), закритий (червоний). Вікно PEV замінює ворота завдання, якщо встановлено.',
        'Tells XCSoar to send its current GPS position to the device as $GPGGA and $GPRMC sentences. Turn off when another GPS source is already feeding the device on the same line. Changes take effect after reconnecting the device.': 'Вказує XCSoar надсилати на пристрій своє поточне положення GPS у вигляді речень $GPGGA і $GPRMC. Вимкніть, коли інше джерело GPS уже подає сигнал на пристрій на тій же лінії. Зміни вступають в силу після повторного підключення пристрою.',
        'Logger pressure altitude when the device provides it (igc_pressure_altitude), otherwise ISA pressure altitude only (1013.25 hPa; not QNH-corrected). Does not show barometric AMSL or GPS height — use other InfoBoxes for navigation.': 'Реєструвати барометричну висоту, коли її надає пристрій (igc_pressure_altitude), інакше – лише барометричну висоту ISA (1013,25 гПа; без коригування QNH). Не показує барометричну висоту AMSL або GPS — використовуйте інші інформаційні поля для навігації.',
        'Same gate as Start open. Main value is estimated time to reach the start line (MacCready leg when available, else distance / ground speed). Value colour and secondary line reflect gate state at that ETA: Too early (blue), Can start (green), Too late (red).': 'Ті самі ворота, що й Старт, відкриті. Основним значенням є приблизний час досягнення лінії старту (етап MacCready, якщо доступний, інакше відстань / швидкість руху). Колір значення та допоміжний рядок відображають стан воріт у цьому ETA: занадто рано (синій), можна почати (зелений), занадто пізно (червоний).',
        'Active waypoint: shows the next task waypoint when an ordered task is loaded, otherwise the Goto waypoint. Displays the waypoint name, arrival altitude difference relative to the safety arrival height, and distance. Click to choose a different waypoint (a task waypoint to skip to that leg, or any waypoint to set as Goto when no task is loaded).': 'Активна маршрутна точка: показує наступну маршрутну точку завдання, коли завантажено впорядковане завдання, інакше – маршрутну точку Goto. Відображає назву маршрутної точки, різницю висоти прибуття відносно безпечної висоти прибуття та відстань. Клацніть, щоб вибрати іншу маршрутну точку (проміжну точку завдання, щоб перейти до цього відрізка, або будь-яку точку, яку потрібно встановити як Goto, якщо завдання не завантажено).',
        'FFVP Federal Cup (NetCoupe) on WeGlide. The scored path has at most three turnpoints between start and finish and at least 25 km total. Points are proportional to credited distance, 100 divided by the glider handicap (DAeC-style index), and a success factor of 1.0 for a free flight or 1.2 for a task declared electronically before takeoff. XCSoar live scoring uses a success factor of 1.0 only, not the 1.2 multiplier for declared tasks.': 'Федеральний кубок FFVP (NetCoupe) на WeGlide. Зарахована траса має щонайбільше три поворотні точки між стартом і фінішом і загалом не менше 25 км. Бали пропорційні зарахованій відстані, 100 поділені на гандикап планера (індекс стилю DAeC) і коефіцієнт успішності 1,0 для вільного польоту або 1,2 для завдання, оголошеного в електронному вигляді перед зльотом. Підрахунок у реальному часі XCSoar використовує лише коефіцієнт успіху 1,0, а не множник 1,2 для заявлених завдань.',
        'Previous waypoint: when an ordered task is loaded, automatically tracks the task waypoint before the active leg (the start waypoint when on the first leg). Displays the waypoint name, arrival altitude difference relative to the safety arrival height, and distance. Click to choose a different waypoint to display (task waypoints when a task is loaded, otherwise the full waypoint list); selection is informational only and never advances the task or sets a Goto. With a task loaded, choose "Resume auto tracking" at the top of the list to revert to automatic tracking.': 'Попередня маршрутна точка: коли завантажується впорядковане завдання, автоматично відстежується маршрутна точка завдання перед активним відрізком (початкова маршрутна точка на першому етапі). Відображає назву маршрутної точки, різницю висоти прибуття відносно безпечної висоти прибуття та відстань. Натисніть, щоб вибрати іншу маршрутну точку для відображення (шляхові точки завдань, коли завдання завантажується, інакше повний список маршрутних точок); вибір є лише інформаційним і ніколи не просуває завдання та не встановлює Goto. Після завантаження завдання виберіть "Відновити автоматичне відстеження" у верхній частині списку, щоб повернутися до автоматичного відстеження.',
        'This parameter estimates the height%s at which the average dry updraft strength drops below 225 fpm and is expected to give better quantitative numbers for the maximum cloudless thermalling height than the BL Top height, especially when mixing results from vertical wind shear rather than thermals. (Note: the present assumptions tend to underpredict the max. thermalling height for dry conditions.) In the presence of clouds the maximum thermalling height may instead be limited by the cloud base. Being for "dry" thermals, this parameter omits the effect of "cloudsuck".': 'Цей параметр оцінює висоту %s, на якій середня сила сухого висхідного потоку падає нижче 225 футів на хвилину, і очікується, що він дасть кращі кількісні показники для максимальної безхмарної висоти термування, ніж висота BL Top, особливо якщо змішувати результати вертикального зсуву вітру, а не терміки. (Примітка: нинішні припущення, як правило, недопрогнозують максимальну висоту нагрівання для сухих умов.) За наявності хмар максимальна висота нагрівання може бути обмежена основою хмари. Для «сухих» термічних засобів цей параметр упускає ефект «затягування хмар».',
        '![](resource:IDB_WARNING_TRIANGLE)\n\n!!! warning\n# Important Safety Notice\n\nBy using XCSoar, you acknowledge and accept the following:\n\n## Limitations\n\n- XCSoar is for **situational awareness only**\n- XCSoar is **not** a FLARM display\n- XCSoar is **not** aviation certified in any way\n- The artificial horizon is **not** fit for any purpose\n- Databanks (airspace, waypoints) may contain errors, be incomplete, or **not** up to date\n- NOTAM display does **not** replace proper pre-flight NOTAM briefing\n- NOTAM data may be incomplete, delayed, filtered, or unavailable\n- XCSoar is **not** guaranteed to be error free\n\n## Pilot Responsibility\n\nThe **Pilot in Command** is always responsible for the safe operation of the aircraft. Never rely solely on XCSoar for navigation or situational awareness.\n\n': '![](resource:IDB_WARNING_TRIANGLE)\n\n!!! warning\n# Важливе повідомлення про безпеку\n\nВикористовуючи XCSoar, ви визнаєте та приймаєте наступне:\n\n## Обмеження\n\n- XCSoar для **лише ситуаційна обізнаність**\n- XCSoar – це **ні** FLARM дисплей\n- XCSoar має авіаційний сертифікат **ні**\n- Штучний горизонт **ні** підходить для будь-яких цілей\n- Банки даних (повітряний простір, шляхові точки) можуть містити помилки, бути неповними або **ні** актуальними\n- Дисплей NOTAM замінює **ні** правильний передпольотний брифінг NOTAM\n- Дані NOTAM можуть бути неповними, із затримкою, відфільтрованими або недоступними\n- XCSoar — це **ні**, який гарантовано не містить помилок\n\n## Відповідальність пілота\n\n**Командир пілота** завжди відповідає за безпечну експлуатацію літака. Ніколи не покладайтеся виключно на XCSoar для навігації чи визначення ситуації.\n\n',
        '# Getting Started\n\nTo use XCSoar effectively, configure the following:\n\n- [Restore from backup](xcsoar://dialog/backup) - Restore previous XCSoar data from a USB or SD card (optional)\n\n- [%s] [Map and data](xcsoar://config/site-files) - Download maps, waypoints, and airspace files for your region\n\n- [%s] [Aircraft polar](xcsoar://config/planes) - Set up your aircraft with the correct polar curve\n\n- [%s] [Pilot info](xcsoar://config/logger) - Enter your name and weight\n\n- [%s] [Devices](xcsoar://config/devices) - Connect your flight instruments\n\n- [%s] [WeGlide](xcsoar://config/weglide) - Upload flights automatically to WeGlide\n\n- [%s] [Thermal Information Map](xcsoar://config/weather) - Show thermal locations from thermalmap.info on the map\n\n- [%s] [Safety factors](xcsoar://config/safety) - Set arrival height, terrain clearance and polar degradation\n\n- [%s] [Terrain Display](xcsoar://config/terrain) - Choose terrain colors, shading and contour lines\n\n- [ ] [Live tracking](xcsoar://config/tracking) *(optional)* - Share your position via SkyLines or LiveTrack24\n\nThe easiest way to explore XCSoar is to [replay an existing IGC flight](xcsoar://dialog/replay).': "# Початок роботи\n\nЩоб ефективно використовувати XCSoar, налаштуйте наступне:\n\n- [Відновити з резервної копії](xcsoar://dialog/backup) - Відновлення попередніх даних XCSoar з USB або SD-карти (необов’язково)\n\n- [%s] [Карта і дані](xcsoar://config/site-files) - Завантажуйте карти, маршрутні точки та файли повітряного простору для вашого регіону\n\n- [%s] [Літак полярний](xcsoar://config/planes) - Налаштуйте свій літальний апарат за допомогою правильної полярної кривої\n\n- [%s] [Інформація про пілота](xcsoar://config/logger) - Введіть своє ім'я та вагу\n\n- [%s] [Пристрої](xcsoar://config/devices) - Підключіть свої пілотні прилади\n\n- [%s] [WeGlide](xcsoar://config/weglide) - Автоматично завантажуйте рейси в WeGlide\n\n- [%s] [Теплова інформаційна карта](xcsoar://config/weather) - Показати на карті термальні місця з heatmap.info\n\n- [%s] [Фактори безпеки](xcsoar://config/safety) - Встановіть висоту прибуття, кліренс місцевості та полярну деградацію\n\n- [%s] [Відображення місцевості](xcsoar://config/terrain) - Виберіть кольори рельєфу, затінення та контурні лінії\n\n- [ ] [Відстеження в реальному часі](xcsoar://config/tracking) *(optional)* - Поділіться своєю позицією через SkyLines або LiveTrack24\n\nНайпростіший спосіб дослідити XCSoar – це [відтворити існуючий рейс IGC](xcsoar://dialog/replay).",
        '# Gesture Navigation\n\nXCSoar supports touch gestures on the map:\n\n- ![U](resource:IDB_GESTURE_UP) **Swipe Up** (U): Zoom in\n- ![D](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DOWN) **Swipe Down** (D): Zoom out\n- ![R](resource:IDB_GESTURE_RIGHT) **Swipe Right** (R): Previous screen mode\n- ![L](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LEFT) **Swipe Left** (L): Next screen mode\n- ![UD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_UD) **Up-Down** (UD): Auto zoom\n- ![DU](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DU) **Down-Up** (DU): Menu\n- ![DR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DR) **Down-Right** (DR): Waypoint details\n- ![DL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DL) **Down-Left** (DL): Alternates\n- ![LU](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LU) **Left-Up** (LU): Recently used waypoints\n- ![RD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_RD) **Right-Down** (RD): Task manager\n- ![URD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_URD) **Up-Right-Down** (URD): Analysis\n- ![LDR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LDR) **Left-Down-Right** (LDR): Checklist\n- ![URDL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_URDL) **Up-Right-Down-Left** (URDL): Pan mode\n- ![LDRDL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LDRDL) **Left-Down-Right-Down-Left** (LDRDL): Status\n- ![ULDR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_ULDR) **Up-Left-Down-Right** (ULDR): Quick menu\n\nLong-press on the map to enter Pan mode. Tap while in Pan mode to see nearby waypoints.': '# Навігація жестами\n\nXCSoar підтримує сенсорні жести на карті:\n\n- ![U](resource:IDB_GESTURE_UP) **Проведіть пальцем вгору** (U): Збільшити\n- ![D](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DOWN) **Проведіть пальцем вниз** (D): Зменшити масштаб\n- ![R](resource:IDB_GESTURE_RIGHT) **Проведіть праворуч** (R): Попередній режим екрана\n- ![L](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LEFT) **Проведіть вліво** (L): Наступний режим екрану\n- ![UD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_UD) **Вгору-Вниз** (UD): Автоматичне масштабування\n- ![DU](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DU) **Вниз-Вгору** (DU): Меню\n- ![DR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DR) **Вниз-Праворуч** (DR): Деталі маршрутної точки\n- ![DL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DL) **Вниз-ліворуч** (DL): Альтернативні\n- ![LU](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LU) **Ліворуч-Вгору** (LU): Нещодавно використані маршрутні точки\n- ![RD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_RD) **Вправо-вниз** (RD): Диспетчер задач\n- ![URD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_URD) **Вгору-Вправо-Вниз** (URD): Аналіз\n- ![LDR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LDR) **Ліворуч-Вниз-Праворуч** (LDR): Контрольний список\n- ![URDL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_URDL) **Вгору-Вправо-Вниз-Вліво** (URDL): Режим панорамування\n- ![LDRDL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LDRDL) **Вліво-Вниз-Вправо-Вниз-Вліво** (LDRDL): Статус\n- ![ULDR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_ULDR) **Вгору-Вліво-Вниз-Вправо** (ULDR): Швидке меню\n\nУтримуйте карту, щоб перейти в режим панорамування. Торкніться в режимі панорамування, щоб побачити маршрутні точки поблизу.',
    },
    "vi": {
        'Size of waypoint symbols on the map as a percentage of the built-in artwork (list dialogs keep a fixed row icon size).': 'Kích thước của các ký hiệu điểm tham chiếu trên bản đồ theo tỷ lệ phần trăm của tác phẩm nghệ thuật tích hợp (hộp thoại danh sách giữ kích thước biểu tượng hàng cố định).',
        'Home waypoint name, arrival altitude difference relative to the safety arrival height, and distance. Click to change the home waypoint.': 'Tên điểm xuất phát, chênh lệch độ cao khi đến so với độ cao khi đến an toàn và khoảng cách. Bấm để thay đổi điểm về nhà.',
        'Current QNH pressure setting used for barometric altitude calculation. Tap the infobox to open the setup panel and adjust QNH manually.': 'Cài đặt áp suất QNH hiện tại được sử dụng để tính toán độ cao khí quyển. Nhấn vào hộp thông tin để mở bảng thiết lập và điều chỉnh QNH theo cách thủ công.',
        'This page shows WiFi status when NetworkManager or ConnMan is on D-Bus (e.g. Linux with Wayland or KMS). Open WiFi list to scan and connect when a service is available.': 'Trang này hiển thị trạng thái WiFi khi NetworkManager hoặc ConnMan trên D-Bus (ví dụ: Linux có Wayland hoặc KMS). Mở danh sách WiFi để quét và kết nối khi có dịch vụ.',
        'The terrain can be shaded among slopes to indicate either wind direction, sun position, a geographically fixed shading from North-West, or a screen-relative fixed shading from top left.': 'Địa hình có thể được tô bóng giữa các sườn dốc để biểu thị hướng gió, vị trí mặt trời, bóng cố định về mặt địa lý từ Tây Bắc hoặc bóng cố định tương đối trên màn hình từ trên cùng bên trái.',
        "Synchronize the glide polar between XCSoar and the device (LXNAV varios). 'Receive' adopts the polar from the device (e.g. for club gliders). 'Send' pushes XCSoar's polar to the device.": "Đồng bộ cực trượt giữa XCSoar và thiết bị (LXNAV varios). 'Nhận' sử dụng cực từ thiết bị (ví dụ: đối với tàu lượn của câu lạc bộ). 'Gửi' đẩy cực của XCSoar tới thiết bị.",
        'List of active airspace files. Use the Add and Remove buttons to activate or deactivate airspace files respectively. Supported file types are: Openair (.openair /.txt /.air), and Tim Newport-Pearce (.sua).': 'Danh sách các tập tin không phận đang hoạt động. Sử dụng các nút Thêm và Xóa để kích hoạt hoặc hủy kích hoạt các tệp không phận tương ứng. Các loại tệp được hỗ trợ là: Openair (.openair /.txt /.air) và Tim Newport-Pearce (.sua).',
        'Signed countdown until the start gate opens or closes (now). Value colour and secondary line reflect gate state at the current time: Waiting (blue), Open (green), Closed (red). PEV window overrides task gate when set.': 'Đã ký đếm ngược cho đến khi cổng bắt đầu mở hoặc đóng (bây giờ). Màu giá trị và dòng phụ phản ánh trạng thái cổng tại thời điểm hiện tại: Đang chờ (màu xanh), Mở (màu xanh lá cây), Đã đóng (màu đỏ). Cửa sổ PEV ghi đè cổng tác vụ khi được đặt.',
        'Tells XCSoar to send its current GPS position to the device as $GPGGA and $GPRMC sentences. Turn off when another GPS source is already feeding the device on the same line. Changes take effect after reconnecting the device.': 'Yêu cầu XCSoar gửi vị trí GPS hiện tại của nó tới thiết bị dưới dạng câu $GPGGA và $GPRMC. Tắt khi một nguồn GPS khác đang cấp nguồn cho thiết bị trên cùng một đường dây. Các thay đổi có hiệu lực sau khi kết nối lại thiết bị.',
        'Logger pressure altitude when the device provides it (igc_pressure_altitude), otherwise ISA pressure altitude only (1013.25 hPa; not QNH-corrected). Does not show barometric AMSL or GPS height — use other InfoBoxes for navigation.': 'Độ cao áp suất của bộ ghi khi thiết bị cung cấp (igc_ Pressure_altitude), nếu không thì chỉ độ cao áp suất ISA (1013,25 hPa; không hiệu chỉnh QNH). Không hiển thị chiều cao khí quyển AMSL hoặc GPS - sử dụng các Hộp thông tin khác để điều hướng.',
        'Same gate as Start open. Main value is estimated time to reach the start line (MacCready leg when available, else distance / ground speed). Value colour and secondary line reflect gate state at that ETA: Too early (blue), Can start (green), Too late (red).': 'Cổng tương tự như Bắt đầu mở. Giá trị chính là thời gian ước tính để đến vạch xuất phát (chặng MacCready nếu có, nếu không thì khoảng cách/tốc độ mặt đất). Màu giá trị và dòng phụ phản ánh trạng thái cổng tại ETA đó: Quá sớm (màu xanh), Có thể bắt đầu (màu xanh lá cây), Quá muộn (màu đỏ).',
        'Active waypoint: shows the next task waypoint when an ordered task is loaded, otherwise the Goto waypoint. Displays the waypoint name, arrival altitude difference relative to the safety arrival height, and distance. Click to choose a different waypoint (a task waypoint to skip to that leg, or any waypoint to set as Goto when no task is loaded).': 'Điểm tham chiếu hoạt động: hiển thị điểm tham chiếu của nhiệm vụ tiếp theo khi một nhiệm vụ được yêu cầu được tải, nếu không thì điểm tham chiếu Goto. Hiển thị tên điểm tham chiếu, chênh lệch độ cao khi đến so với độ cao đến an toàn và khoảng cách. Nhấp để chọn một điểm tham chiếu khác (một điểm tham chiếu của nhiệm vụ để chuyển sang chặng đó hoặc bất kỳ điểm tham chiếu nào để đặt làm Goto khi không có nhiệm vụ nào được tải).',
        'FFVP Federal Cup (NetCoupe) on WeGlide. The scored path has at most three turnpoints between start and finish and at least 25 km total. Points are proportional to credited distance, 100 divided by the glider handicap (DAeC-style index), and a success factor of 1.0 for a free flight or 1.2 for a task declared electronically before takeoff. XCSoar live scoring uses a success factor of 1.0 only, not the 1.2 multiplier for declared tasks.': 'Cúp Liên bang FFVP (NetCoupe) trên WeGlide. Đường đi được tính điểm có tối đa ba điểm rẽ giữa điểm xuất phát và điểm kết thúc và tổng chiều dài ít nhất là 25 km. Điểm tỷ lệ thuận với khoảng cách được ghi có, 100 chia cho điểm chấp của tàu lượn (chỉ số kiểu DAeC) và hệ số thành công là 1,0 cho chuyến bay miễn phí hoặc 1,2 cho nhiệm vụ được khai báo điện tử trước khi cất cánh. Tính điểm trực tiếp của XCSoar chỉ sử dụng hệ số thành công là 1,0 chứ không phải hệ số nhân 1,2 cho các nhiệm vụ đã khai báo.',
        'Previous waypoint: when an ordered task is loaded, automatically tracks the task waypoint before the active leg (the start waypoint when on the first leg). Displays the waypoint name, arrival altitude difference relative to the safety arrival height, and distance. Click to choose a different waypoint to display (task waypoints when a task is loaded, otherwise the full waypoint list); selection is informational only and never advances the task or sets a Goto. With a task loaded, choose "Resume auto tracking" at the top of the list to revert to automatic tracking.': 'Điểm tham chiếu trước: khi một nhiệm vụ theo thứ tự được tải, sẽ tự động theo dõi điểm tham chiếu của nhiệm vụ trước chặng hoạt động (điểm bắt đầu khi ở chặng đầu tiên). Hiển thị tên điểm tham chiếu, chênh lệch độ cao khi đến so với độ cao đến an toàn và khoảng cách. Bấm để chọn một điểm tham chiếu khác để hiển thị (các điểm tham chiếu của nhiệm vụ khi một tác vụ được tải, nếu không thì danh sách điểm tham chiếu đầy đủ); lựa chọn chỉ mang tính chất cung cấp thông tin và không bao giờ tiến hành nhiệm vụ hoặc đặt Goto. Khi một nhiệm vụ đã được tải, hãy chọn "Tiếp tục theo dõi tự động" ở đầu danh sách để hoàn nguyên về chế độ theo dõi tự động.',
        'This parameter estimates the height%s at which the average dry updraft strength drops below 225 fpm and is expected to give better quantitative numbers for the maximum cloudless thermalling height than the BL Top height, especially when mixing results from vertical wind shear rather than thermals. (Note: the present assumptions tend to underpredict the max. thermalling height for dry conditions.) In the presence of clouds the maximum thermalling height may instead be limited by the cloud base. Being for "dry" thermals, this parameter omits the effect of "cloudsuck".': 'Tham số này ước tính độ cao%s mà tại đó cường độ dòng thăng khô trung bình giảm xuống dưới 225 fpm và dự kiến \u200b\u200bsẽ đưa ra các con số định lượng tốt hơn cho độ cao tỏa nhiệt tối đa không mây so với độ cao BL Top, đặc biệt là khi trộn lẫn các kết quả từ lực cắt gió thẳng đứng thay vì nhiệt. (Lưu ý: các giả định hiện tại có xu hướng dự đoán thấp chiều cao tỏa nhiệt tối đa trong điều kiện khô ráo.) Khi có mây, chiều cao tỏa nhiệt tối đa có thể bị giới hạn bởi chân mây. Đối với bộ tản nhiệt "khô", thông số này bỏ qua hiệu ứng "hút mây".',
        '![](resource:IDB_WARNING_TRIANGLE)\n\n!!! warning\n# Important Safety Notice\n\nBy using XCSoar, you acknowledge and accept the following:\n\n## Limitations\n\n- XCSoar is for **situational awareness only**\n- XCSoar is **not** a FLARM display\n- XCSoar is **not** aviation certified in any way\n- The artificial horizon is **not** fit for any purpose\n- Databanks (airspace, waypoints) may contain errors, be incomplete, or **not** up to date\n- NOTAM display does **not** replace proper pre-flight NOTAM briefing\n- NOTAM data may be incomplete, delayed, filtered, or unavailable\n- XCSoar is **not** guaranteed to be error free\n\n## Pilot Responsibility\n\nThe **Pilot in Command** is always responsible for the safe operation of the aircraft. Never rely solely on XCSoar for navigation or situational awareness.\n\n': '![](resource:IDB_WARNING_TRIANGLE)\n\n!!! warning\n# Thông báo an toàn quan trọng\n\nBằng cách sử dụng XCSoar, bạn thừa nhận và chấp nhận những điều sau:\n\n## Hạn chế\n\n- XCSoar dành cho **chỉ nhận thức tình huống**\n- XCSoar là **không** một màn hình FLARM\n- XCSoar được chứng nhận hàng không **không** dưới mọi hình thức\n- Đường chân trời nhân tạo là **không** phù hợp cho mọi mục đích\n- Ngân hàng dữ liệu (vùng trời, điểm tham chiếu) có thể có lỗi, không đầy đủ hoặc **không** được cập nhật\n- Màn hình NOTAM **không** thay thế bản tóm tắt NOTAM trước chuyến bay thích hợp\n- Dữ liệu NOTAM có thể không đầy đủ, bị trì hoãn, bị lọc hoặc không có sẵn\n- XCSoar là **không** được đảm bảo không có lỗi\n\n## Trách nhiệm của phi công\n\n**Phi công chỉ huy** luôn chịu trách nhiệm về hoạt động an toàn của máy bay. Đừng bao giờ chỉ dựa vào XCSoar để điều hướng hoặc nhận biết tình huống.\n\n',
        '# Getting Started\n\nTo use XCSoar effectively, configure the following:\n\n- [Restore from backup](xcsoar://dialog/backup) - Restore previous XCSoar data from a USB or SD card (optional)\n\n- [%s] [Map and data](xcsoar://config/site-files) - Download maps, waypoints, and airspace files for your region\n\n- [%s] [Aircraft polar](xcsoar://config/planes) - Set up your aircraft with the correct polar curve\n\n- [%s] [Pilot info](xcsoar://config/logger) - Enter your name and weight\n\n- [%s] [Devices](xcsoar://config/devices) - Connect your flight instruments\n\n- [%s] [WeGlide](xcsoar://config/weglide) - Upload flights automatically to WeGlide\n\n- [%s] [Thermal Information Map](xcsoar://config/weather) - Show thermal locations from thermalmap.info on the map\n\n- [%s] [Safety factors](xcsoar://config/safety) - Set arrival height, terrain clearance and polar degradation\n\n- [%s] [Terrain Display](xcsoar://config/terrain) - Choose terrain colors, shading and contour lines\n\n- [ ] [Live tracking](xcsoar://config/tracking) *(optional)* - Share your position via SkyLines or LiveTrack24\n\nThe easiest way to explore XCSoar is to [replay an existing IGC flight](xcsoar://dialog/replay).': '# Bắt đầu\n\nĐể sử dụng XCSoar hiệu quả, hãy định cấu hình như sau:\n\n- [Khôi phục từ bản sao lưu](xcsoar://dialog/backup) - Khôi phục dữ liệu XCSoar trước đó từ USB hoặc thẻ SD (tùy chọn)\n\n- [%s] [Bản đồ và dữ liệu](xcsoar://config/site-files) - Tải xuống bản đồ, điểm tham chiếu và tệp không phận cho khu vực của bạn\n\n- [%s] [Máy bay vùng cực](xcsoar://config/planes) - Thiết lập máy bay của bạn với đường cong cực chính xác\n\n- [%s] [Thông tin phi công](xcsoar://config/logger) - Nhập tên và cân nặng của bạn\n\n- [%s] [Thiết bị](xcsoar://config/devices) - Kết nối dụng cụ bay của bạn\n\n- [%s] [WeGlide](xcsoar://config/weglide) - Tự động tải chuyến bay lên WeGlide\n\n- [%s] [Bản đồ thông tin nhiệt](xcsoar://config/weather) - Hiển thị các vị trí nhiệt từ Thermalmap.info trên bản đồ\n\n- [%s] [Yếu tố an toàn](xcsoar://config/safety) - Đặt độ cao đến, giải phóng địa hình và suy thoái cực\n\n- [%s] [Hiển thị địa hình](xcsoar://config/terrain) - Chọn màu sắc địa hình, bóng và đường đồng mức\n\n- [ ] [Theo dõi trực tiếp](xcsoar://config/tracking) *(optional)* - Chia sẻ vị trí của bạn thông qua SkyLines hoặc LiveTrack24\n\nCách dễ nhất để khám phá XCSoar là [phát lại chuyến bay IGC hiện có](xcsoar://dialog/replay).',
        '# Gesture Navigation\n\nXCSoar supports touch gestures on the map:\n\n- ![U](resource:IDB_GESTURE_UP) **Swipe Up** (U): Zoom in\n- ![D](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DOWN) **Swipe Down** (D): Zoom out\n- ![R](resource:IDB_GESTURE_RIGHT) **Swipe Right** (R): Previous screen mode\n- ![L](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LEFT) **Swipe Left** (L): Next screen mode\n- ![UD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_UD) **Up-Down** (UD): Auto zoom\n- ![DU](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DU) **Down-Up** (DU): Menu\n- ![DR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DR) **Down-Right** (DR): Waypoint details\n- ![DL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DL) **Down-Left** (DL): Alternates\n- ![LU](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LU) **Left-Up** (LU): Recently used waypoints\n- ![RD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_RD) **Right-Down** (RD): Task manager\n- ![URD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_URD) **Up-Right-Down** (URD): Analysis\n- ![LDR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LDR) **Left-Down-Right** (LDR): Checklist\n- ![URDL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_URDL) **Up-Right-Down-Left** (URDL): Pan mode\n- ![LDRDL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LDRDL) **Left-Down-Right-Down-Left** (LDRDL): Status\n- ![ULDR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_ULDR) **Up-Left-Down-Right** (ULDR): Quick menu\n\nLong-press on the map to enter Pan mode. Tap while in Pan mode to see nearby waypoints.': '# Điều hướng bằng cử chỉ\n\nXCSoar hỗ trợ cử chỉ chạm trên bản đồ:\n\n- ![U](resource:IDB_GESTURE_UP) **Vuốt lên** (U): Phóng to\n- ![D](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DOWN) **Vuốt xuống** (D): Thu nhỏ\n- ![R](resource:IDB_GESTURE_RIGHT) **Vuốt sang phải** (R): Chế độ màn hình trước\n- ![L](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LEFT) **Vuốt sang trái** (L): Chế độ màn hình tiếp theo\n- ![UD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_UD) **Lên xuống** (UD): Tự động thu phóng\n- ![DU](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DU) **Xuống-Lên** (DU): Thực đơn\n- ![DR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DR) **Xuống bên phải** (DR): Chi tiết điểm tham chiếu\n- ![DL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DL) **Xuống bên trái** (DL): Thay thế\n- ![LU](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LU) **trái lên** (LU): Điểm tham chiếu được sử dụng gần đây\n- ![RD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_RD) **Phải xuống** (RD): Trình quản lý tác vụ\n- ![URD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_URD) **Lên-Phải-Xuống** (URD): Phân tích\n- ![LDR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LDR) **Trái-Xuống-Phải** (LDR): Danh sách kiểm tra\n- ![URDL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_URDL) **Lên-Phải-Xuống-Trái** (URDL): Chế độ xoay\n- ![LDRDL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LDRDL) **Trái-Xuống-Phải-Xuống-Trái** (LDRDL): Trạng thái\n- ![ULDR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_ULDR) **Lên-Trái-Xuống-Phải** (ULDR): Trình đơn nhanh\n\nNhấn và giữ trên bản đồ để vào chế độ Pan. Nhấn khi đang ở chế độ Xoay để xem các điểm tham chiếu gần đó.',
    },
    "zh_CN": {
        'Size of waypoint symbols on the map as a percentage of the built-in artwork (list dialogs keep a fixed row icon size).': '地图上航路点符号的大小占内置图稿的百分比（列表对话框保持固定的行图标大小）。',
        'Home waypoint name, arrival altitude difference relative to the safety arrival height, and distance. Click to change the home waypoint.': '返航点名称、相对于安全到达高度的到达高度差以及距离。单击可更改起始航点。',
        'Current QNH pressure setting used for barometric altitude calculation. Tap the infobox to open the setup panel and adjust QNH manually.': '当前用于气压高度计算的 QNH 压力设置。点击信息框打开设置面板并手动调整 QNH。',
        'This page shows WiFi status when NetworkManager or ConnMan is on D-Bus (e.g. Linux with Wayland or KMS). Open WiFi list to scan and connect when a service is available.': '当 NetworkManager 或 ConnMan 在 D-Bus 上时（例如带有 Wayland 或 KMS 的 Linux），此页面显示 WiFi 状态。当服务可用时，打开 WiFi 列表进行扫描和连接。',
        'The terrain can be shaded among slopes to indicate either wind direction, sun position, a geographically fixed shading from North-West, or a screen-relative fixed shading from top left.': '地形可以在斜坡之间进行阴影来指示风向、太阳位置、来自西北的地理固定阴影或来自左上角的相对于屏幕的固定阴影。',
        "Synchronize the glide polar between XCSoar and the device (LXNAV varios). 'Receive' adopts the polar from the device (e.g. for club gliders). 'Send' pushes XCSoar's polar to the device.": '同步 XCSoar 和设备 (LXNAV varios) 之间的滑翔极坐标。 “接收”采用设备的极坐标（例如俱乐部滑翔机）。 “发送”将 XCSoar 的极轴推送到设备。',
        'List of active airspace files. Use the Add and Remove buttons to activate or deactivate airspace files respectively. Supported file types are: Openair (.openair /.txt /.air), and Tim Newport-Pearce (.sua).': '活动空域文件列表。使用“添加”和“删除”按钮分别激活或停用空域文件。支持的文件类型有：Openair (.openair /.txt /.air) 和 Tim Newport-Pearce (.sua)。',
        'Signed countdown until the start gate opens or closes (now). Value colour and secondary line reflect gate state at the current time: Waiting (blue), Open (green), Closed (red). PEV window overrides task gate when set.': '签名倒计时，直到开始门打开或关闭（现在）。数值颜色和副线反映当前时间的门状态：等待（蓝色）、打开（绿色）、关闭（红色）。设置后，PEV 窗口会覆盖任务门。',
        'Tells XCSoar to send its current GPS position to the device as $GPGGA and $GPRMC sentences. Turn off when another GPS source is already feeding the device on the same line. Changes take effect after reconnecting the device.': '告诉 XCSoar 将其当前 GPS 位置作为 $GPGGA 和 $GPRMC 语句发送到设备。当另一个 GPS 源已经在同一条线路上向设备供电时关闭。重新连接设备后更改生效。',
        'Logger pressure altitude when the device provides it (igc_pressure_altitude), otherwise ISA pressure altitude only (1013.25 hPa; not QNH-corrected). Does not show barometric AMSL or GPS height — use other InfoBoxes for navigation.': '当设备提供记录压力高度时 (igc_Pressure_altitude)，否则仅 ISA 压力高度（1013.25 hPa；未经 QNH 校正）。不显示气压 AMSL 或 GPS 高度 - 使用其他信息框进行导航。',
        'Same gate as Start open. Main value is estimated time to reach the start line (MacCready leg when available, else distance / ground speed). Value colour and secondary line reflect gate state at that ETA: Too early (blue), Can start (green), Too late (red).': '与开始打开的门相同。主要值是到达起跑线的估计时间（MacCready 航段可用时，否则距离/地面速度）。值颜色和辅助线反映了该 ETA 时的门状态：太早（蓝色）、可以开始（绿色）、太晚（红色）。',
        'Active waypoint: shows the next task waypoint when an ordered task is loaded, otherwise the Goto waypoint. Displays the waypoint name, arrival altitude difference relative to the safety arrival height, and distance. Click to choose a different waypoint (a task waypoint to skip to that leg, or any waypoint to set as Goto when no task is loaded).': '活动航点：加载有序任务时显示下一个任务航点，否则显示转到航点。显示航路点名称、相对于安全到达高度的到达高度差以及距离。单击可选择不同的航点（跳至该航段的任务航点，或在未加载任务时设置为转到的任何航点）。',
        'FFVP Federal Cup (NetCoupe) on WeGlide. The scored path has at most three turnpoints between start and finish and at least 25 km total. Points are proportional to credited distance, 100 divided by the glider handicap (DAeC-style index), and a success factor of 1.0 for a free flight or 1.2 for a task declared electronically before takeoff. XCSoar live scoring uses a success factor of 1.0 only, not the 1.2 multiplier for declared tasks.': 'WeGlide 上的 FFVP 联邦杯 (NetCoupe)。得分路径在起点和终点之间最多有 3 个转折点，总长度至少为 25 公里。积分与记入距离成正比，100 除以滑翔机障碍（DAeC 式指数），自由飞行的成功系数为 1.0，起飞前以电子方式声明的任务的成功系数为 1.2。 XCSoar 实时评分仅使用 1.0 的成功系数，而不是声明任务的 1.2 乘数。',
        'Previous waypoint: when an ordered task is loaded, automatically tracks the task waypoint before the active leg (the start waypoint when on the first leg). Displays the waypoint name, arrival altitude difference relative to the safety arrival height, and distance. Click to choose a different waypoint to display (task waypoints when a task is loaded, otherwise the full waypoint list); selection is informational only and never advances the task or sets a Goto. With a task loaded, choose "Resume auto tracking" at the top of the list to revert to automatic tracking.': '上一个航点：加载有序任务时，自动跟踪活动航段之前的任务航点（第一航段时的起始航点）。显示航路点名称、相对于安全到达高度的到达高度差以及距离。单击可选择要显示的不同航点（加载任务时的任务航点，否则显示完整航点列表）；选择仅供参考，不会推进任务或设置转到。加载任务后，选择列表顶部的 "恢复自动跟踪" 以恢复为自动跟踪。',
        'This parameter estimates the height%s at which the average dry updraft strength drops below 225 fpm and is expected to give better quantitative numbers for the maximum cloudless thermalling height than the BL Top height, especially when mixing results from vertical wind shear rather than thermals. (Note: the present assumptions tend to underpredict the max. thermalling height for dry conditions.) In the presence of clouds the maximum thermalling height may instead be limited by the cloud base. Being for "dry" thermals, this parameter omits the effect of "cloudsuck".': '该参数估计平均干燥上升气流强度降至 225 fpm 以下时的高度 %s，并且预计会为最大无云热气流高度提供比 BL 顶部高度更好的定量数字，特别是当混合是由垂直风切变而不是热气流产生时。 （注：目前的假设往往会低估干燥条件下的最大热力高度。）在存在云的情况下，最大热力高度可能反而受到云底的限制。对于“干”热气流，该参数忽略了“cloudsuck”的影响。',
        '![](resource:IDB_WARNING_TRIANGLE)\n\n!!! warning\n# Important Safety Notice\n\nBy using XCSoar, you acknowledge and accept the following:\n\n## Limitations\n\n- XCSoar is for **situational awareness only**\n- XCSoar is **not** a FLARM display\n- XCSoar is **not** aviation certified in any way\n- The artificial horizon is **not** fit for any purpose\n- Databanks (airspace, waypoints) may contain errors, be incomplete, or **not** up to date\n- NOTAM display does **not** replace proper pre-flight NOTAM briefing\n- NOTAM data may be incomplete, delayed, filtered, or unavailable\n- XCSoar is **not** guaranteed to be error free\n\n## Pilot Responsibility\n\nThe **Pilot in Command** is always responsible for the safe operation of the aircraft. Never rely solely on XCSoar for navigation or situational awareness.\n\n': '![](resource:IDB_WARNING_TRIANGLE)\n\n!!! warning\n# 重要安全注意事项\n\n使用 XCSoar，即表示您承认并接受以下条款：\n\n## 局限性\n\n- XCSoar 是为了 **仅态势感知**\n- XCSoar 是 **不是** FLARM 显示器\n- XCSoar 以任何方式获得 **不是** 航空认证\n- 人造地平线 **不是** 适合任何用途\n- 数据库（空域、航路点）可能包含错误、不完整或 **不是** 是最新的\n- NOTAM 显示 **不是** 是否取代了正确的飞行前 NOTAM 简报\n- NOTAM 数据可能不完整、延迟、经过过滤或不可用\n- XCSoar 是 **不是** 保证无错误\n\n## 飞行员的责任\n\n**机长** 始终对飞机的安全运行负责。切勿仅依赖 XCSoar 进行导航或态势感知。\n\n',
        '# Getting Started\n\nTo use XCSoar effectively, configure the following:\n\n- [Restore from backup](xcsoar://dialog/backup) - Restore previous XCSoar data from a USB or SD card (optional)\n\n- [%s] [Map and data](xcsoar://config/site-files) - Download maps, waypoints, and airspace files for your region\n\n- [%s] [Aircraft polar](xcsoar://config/planes) - Set up your aircraft with the correct polar curve\n\n- [%s] [Pilot info](xcsoar://config/logger) - Enter your name and weight\n\n- [%s] [Devices](xcsoar://config/devices) - Connect your flight instruments\n\n- [%s] [WeGlide](xcsoar://config/weglide) - Upload flights automatically to WeGlide\n\n- [%s] [Thermal Information Map](xcsoar://config/weather) - Show thermal locations from thermalmap.info on the map\n\n- [%s] [Safety factors](xcsoar://config/safety) - Set arrival height, terrain clearance and polar degradation\n\n- [%s] [Terrain Display](xcsoar://config/terrain) - Choose terrain colors, shading and contour lines\n\n- [ ] [Live tracking](xcsoar://config/tracking) *(optional)* - Share your position via SkyLines or LiveTrack24\n\nThe easiest way to explore XCSoar is to [replay an existing IGC flight](xcsoar://dialog/replay).': '# 入门\n\n要有效使用 XCSoar，请配置以下内容：\n\n- [从备份恢复](xcsoar://dialog/backup) - 从 USB 或 SD 卡恢复以前的 XCSoar 数据（可选）\n\n- [%s] [地图和数据](xcsoar://config/site-files) - 下载您所在地区的地图、航点和空域文件\n\n- [%s] [飞机极地](xcsoar://config/planes) - 使用正确的极曲线设置您的飞机\n\n- [%s] [飞行员信息](xcsoar://config/logger) - 输入您的姓名和体重\n\n- [%s] [设备](xcsoar://config/devices) - 连接您的飞行仪表\n\n- [%s] [威滑行](xcsoar://config/weglide) - 自动上传航班至 WeGlide\n\n- [%s] [热信息图](xcsoar://config/weather) - 在地图上显示来自 heatmap.info 的热位置\n\n- [%s] [安全系数](xcsoar://config/safety) - 设置到达高度、地形间隙和极地退化\n\n- [%s] [地形显示](xcsoar://config/terrain) - 选择地形颜色、阴影和等高线\n\n- [ ] [实时追踪](xcsoar://config/tracking) *(optional)* - 通过 SkyLines 或 LiveTrack24 分享您的位置\n\n探索 XCSoar 的最简单方法是 [重播现有的 IGC 航班](xcsoar://dialog/replay).',
        '# Gesture Navigation\n\nXCSoar supports touch gestures on the map:\n\n- ![U](resource:IDB_GESTURE_UP) **Swipe Up** (U): Zoom in\n- ![D](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DOWN) **Swipe Down** (D): Zoom out\n- ![R](resource:IDB_GESTURE_RIGHT) **Swipe Right** (R): Previous screen mode\n- ![L](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LEFT) **Swipe Left** (L): Next screen mode\n- ![UD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_UD) **Up-Down** (UD): Auto zoom\n- ![DU](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DU) **Down-Up** (DU): Menu\n- ![DR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DR) **Down-Right** (DR): Waypoint details\n- ![DL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DL) **Down-Left** (DL): Alternates\n- ![LU](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LU) **Left-Up** (LU): Recently used waypoints\n- ![RD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_RD) **Right-Down** (RD): Task manager\n- ![URD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_URD) **Up-Right-Down** (URD): Analysis\n- ![LDR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LDR) **Left-Down-Right** (LDR): Checklist\n- ![URDL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_URDL) **Up-Right-Down-Left** (URDL): Pan mode\n- ![LDRDL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LDRDL) **Left-Down-Right-Down-Left** (LDRDL): Status\n- ![ULDR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_ULDR) **Up-Left-Down-Right** (ULDR): Quick menu\n\nLong-press on the map to enter Pan mode. Tap while in Pan mode to see nearby waypoints.': '# 手势导航\n\nXCSoar支持地图上的触摸手势：\n\n- ![U](resource:IDB_GESTURE_UP) **向上滑动** (U): 放大\n- ![D](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DOWN) **向下滑动** (D): 缩小\n- ![R](resource:IDB_GESTURE_RIGHT) **向右滑动** (R): 上一屏幕模式\n- ![L](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LEFT) **向左滑动** (L): 下一屏模式\n- ![UD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_UD) **上下** (UD): 自动变焦\n- ![DU](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DU) **下-上** (DU): 菜单\n- ![DR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DR) **彻头彻尾** (DR): 航点详情\n- ![DL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DL) **左下** (DL): 替补\n- ![LU](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LU) **左上** (LU): 最近使用的航点\n- ![RD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_RD) **右下** (RD): 任务管理器\n- ![URD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_URD) **上-右-下** (URD): 分析\n- ![LDR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LDR) **左-下-右** (LDR): 清单\n- ![URDL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_URDL) **右上-左下** (URDL): 平移模式\n- ![LDRDL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LDRDL) **左下右下左下** (LDRDL): 地位\n- ![ULDR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_ULDR) **上-左-下-右** (ULDR): 快捷菜单\n\n长按地图即可进入平移模式。在平移模式下点击可查看附近的航点。',
    },
    "zh_Hant": {
        'Size of waypoint symbols on the map as a percentage of the built-in artwork (list dialogs keep a fixed row icon size).': '地圖上航路點符號的大小佔內建圖稿的百分比（清單對話方塊保持固定的行圖示大小）。',
        'Home waypoint name, arrival altitude difference relative to the safety arrival height, and distance. Click to change the home waypoint.': '返航點名稱、相對於安全到達高度的到達高度差以及距離。按一下可變更起始航點。',
        'Current QNH pressure setting used for barometric altitude calculation. Tap the infobox to open the setup panel and adjust QNH manually.': '目前用於氣壓高度計算的 QNH 壓力設定。點擊資訊框以開啟設定面板並手動調整 QNH。',
        'This page shows WiFi status when NetworkManager or ConnMan is on D-Bus (e.g. Linux with Wayland or KMS). Open WiFi list to scan and connect when a service is available.': '當 NetworkManager 或 ConnMan 在 D-Bus 上（例如有 Wayland 或 KMS 的 Linux），此頁面會顯示 WiFi 狀態。當服務可用時，開啟 WiFi 清單進行掃描和連線。',
        'The terrain can be shaded among slopes to indicate either wind direction, sun position, a geographically fixed shading from North-West, or a screen-relative fixed shading from top left.': '地形可以在斜坡之間進行陰影來指示風向、太陽位置、來自西北方的地理固定陰影或來自左上角的相對於螢幕的固定陰影。',
        "Synchronize the glide polar between XCSoar and the device (LXNAV varios). 'Receive' adopts the polar from the device (e.g. for club gliders). 'Send' pushes XCSoar's polar to the device.": '同步 XCSoar 和設備 (LXNAV varios) 之間的滑翔極座標。 「接收」採用裝置的極座標（例如俱樂部滑翔機）。 「發送」將 XCSoar 的極軸推送到裝置。',
        'List of active airspace files. Use the Add and Remove buttons to activate or deactivate airspace files respectively. Supported file types are: Openair (.openair /.txt /.air), and Tim Newport-Pearce (.sua).': '活動空域文件列表。使用「新增」和「刪除」按鈕分別啟用或停用空域檔案。支援的檔案類型有：Openair (.openair /.txt /.air) 和 Tim Newport-Pearce (.sua)。',
        'Signed countdown until the start gate opens or closes (now). Value colour and secondary line reflect gate state at the current time: Waiting (blue), Open (green), Closed (red). PEV window overrides task gate when set.': '簽名倒數計時，直到開始門打開或關閉（現在）。數值顏色和副線反映目前時間的門狀態：等待（藍色）、開啟（綠色）、關閉（紅色）。設定後，PEV 視窗會覆蓋任務門。',
        'Tells XCSoar to send its current GPS position to the device as $GPGGA and $GPRMC sentences. Turn off when another GPS source is already feeding the device on the same line. Changes take effect after reconnecting the device.': '告訴 XCSoar 將其目前 GPS 位置作為 $GPGGA 和 $GPRMC 語句傳送到裝置。當另一個 GPS 來源已經在同一條路線上向設備供電時關閉。重新連接裝置後更改生效。',
        'Logger pressure altitude when the device provides it (igc_pressure_altitude), otherwise ISA pressure altitude only (1013.25 hPa; not QNH-corrected). Does not show barometric AMSL or GPS height — use other InfoBoxes for navigation.': '當設備提供記錄壓力高度時 (igc_Pressure_altitude)，否則僅 ISA 壓力高度（1013.25 hPa；未經 QNH 校正）。不顯示氣壓 AMSL 或 GPS 高度 - 使用其他資訊框進行導航。',
        'Same gate as Start open. Main value is estimated time to reach the start line (MacCready leg when available, else distance / ground speed). Value colour and secondary line reflect gate state at that ETA: Too early (blue), Can start (green), Too late (red).': '與開始打開的門相同。主要值是到達起跑線的估計時間（MacCready 航段可用時，否則距離/地面速度）。值色和輔助線反映了該 ETA 時的門狀態：太早（藍色）、可以開始（綠色）、太晚（紅色）。',
        'Active waypoint: shows the next task waypoint when an ordered task is loaded, otherwise the Goto waypoint. Displays the waypoint name, arrival altitude difference relative to the safety arrival height, and distance. Click to choose a different waypoint (a task waypoint to skip to that leg, or any waypoint to set as Goto when no task is loaded).': '活動航點：載入有序任務時顯示下一個任務航點，否則顯示轉到航點。顯示航路點名稱、相對於安全到達高度的到達高度差、距離。點選可選擇不同的航點（跳至該航段的任務航點，或在未載入任務時設定為轉到的任何航點）。',
        'FFVP Federal Cup (NetCoupe) on WeGlide. The scored path has at most three turnpoints between start and finish and at least 25 km total. Points are proportional to credited distance, 100 divided by the glider handicap (DAeC-style index), and a success factor of 1.0 for a free flight or 1.2 for a task declared electronically before takeoff. XCSoar live scoring uses a success factor of 1.0 only, not the 1.2 multiplier for declared tasks.': 'WeGlide 上的 FFVP 聯邦盃 (NetCoupe)。得分路徑在起點和終點之間最多有 3 個轉折點，總長度至少為 25 公里。積分與記入距離成正比，100 除以滑翔機障礙（DAeC 式指數），自由飛行的成功係數為 1.0，起飛前以電子方式聲明的任務的成功係數為 1.2。 XCSoar 即時評分僅使用 1.0 的成功係數，而不是聲明任務的 1.2 乘數。',
        'Previous waypoint: when an ordered task is loaded, automatically tracks the task waypoint before the active leg (the start waypoint when on the first leg). Displays the waypoint name, arrival altitude difference relative to the safety arrival height, and distance. Click to choose a different waypoint to display (task waypoints when a task is loaded, otherwise the full waypoint list); selection is informational only and never advances the task or sets a Goto. With a task loaded, choose "Resume auto tracking" at the top of the list to revert to automatic tracking.': '上一個航點：載入有序任務時，自動追蹤活動航段之前的任務航點（第一航段時的起始航點）。顯示航路點名稱、相對於安全到達高度的到達高度差、距離。點選可選擇要顯示的不同航點（載入任務時的任務航點，否則顯示完整航點清單）；選擇僅供參考，不會推進任務或設定轉到。載入任務後，選擇清單頂部的 "恢復自動追蹤" 以恢復為自動追蹤。',
        'This parameter estimates the height%s at which the average dry updraft strength drops below 225 fpm and is expected to give better quantitative numbers for the maximum cloudless thermalling height than the BL Top height, especially when mixing results from vertical wind shear rather than thermals. (Note: the present assumptions tend to underpredict the max. thermalling height for dry conditions.) In the presence of clouds the maximum thermalling height may instead be limited by the cloud base. Being for "dry" thermals, this parameter omits the effect of "cloudsuck".': '此參數估計平均乾燥上升氣流強度降至 225 fpm 以下時的高度 %s，並且預計會為最大無雲熱氣流高度提供比 BL 頂部高度更好的定量數字，特別是當混合是由垂直風切變而不是熱氣流產生時。 （註：目前的假設往往會低估乾燥條件下的最大熱力高度。）在存在雲的情況下，最大熱力高度可能反而受到雲底的限制。對於「乾」熱氣流，此參數忽略了「cloudsuck」的影響。',
        '![](resource:IDB_WARNING_TRIANGLE)\n\n!!! warning\n# Important Safety Notice\n\nBy using XCSoar, you acknowledge and accept the following:\n\n## Limitations\n\n- XCSoar is for **situational awareness only**\n- XCSoar is **not** a FLARM display\n- XCSoar is **not** aviation certified in any way\n- The artificial horizon is **not** fit for any purpose\n- Databanks (airspace, waypoints) may contain errors, be incomplete, or **not** up to date\n- NOTAM display does **not** replace proper pre-flight NOTAM briefing\n- NOTAM data may be incomplete, delayed, filtered, or unavailable\n- XCSoar is **not** guaranteed to be error free\n\n## Pilot Responsibility\n\nThe **Pilot in Command** is always responsible for the safe operation of the aircraft. Never rely solely on XCSoar for navigation or situational awareness.\n\n': '![](resource:IDB_WARNING_TRIANGLE)\n\n!!! warning\n# 重要安全注意事項\n\n使用 XCSoar，即表示您承認並接受以下條款：\n\n## 限制\n\n- XCSoar 是為了 **僅態勢感知**\n- XCSoar 是 **不是** FLARM 顯示器\n- XCSoar 以任何方式獲得 **不是** 航空認證\n- 人造地平線 **不是** 適合任何用途\n- 資料庫（空域、航路點）可能包含錯誤、不完整或 **不是** 是最新的\n- NOTAM 顯示 **不是** 是否取代了正確的飛行前 NOTAM 簡報\n- NOTAM 資料可能不完整、延遲、過濾或無法使用\n- XCSoar 是 **不是** 保證無錯誤\n\n## 飛行員的責任\n\n**機長** 始終對飛機的安全運作負責。切勿僅依賴 XCSoar 進行導航或態勢感知。\n\n',
        '# Getting Started\n\nTo use XCSoar effectively, configure the following:\n\n- [Restore from backup](xcsoar://dialog/backup) - Restore previous XCSoar data from a USB or SD card (optional)\n\n- [%s] [Map and data](xcsoar://config/site-files) - Download maps, waypoints, and airspace files for your region\n\n- [%s] [Aircraft polar](xcsoar://config/planes) - Set up your aircraft with the correct polar curve\n\n- [%s] [Pilot info](xcsoar://config/logger) - Enter your name and weight\n\n- [%s] [Devices](xcsoar://config/devices) - Connect your flight instruments\n\n- [%s] [WeGlide](xcsoar://config/weglide) - Upload flights automatically to WeGlide\n\n- [%s] [Thermal Information Map](xcsoar://config/weather) - Show thermal locations from thermalmap.info on the map\n\n- [%s] [Safety factors](xcsoar://config/safety) - Set arrival height, terrain clearance and polar degradation\n\n- [%s] [Terrain Display](xcsoar://config/terrain) - Choose terrain colors, shading and contour lines\n\n- [ ] [Live tracking](xcsoar://config/tracking) *(optional)* - Share your position via SkyLines or LiveTrack24\n\nThe easiest way to explore XCSoar is to [replay an existing IGC flight](xcsoar://dialog/replay).': '# 入門\n\n若要有效使用 XCSoar，請設定以下內容：\n\n- [從備份中恢復](xcsoar://dialog/backup) - 從 USB 或 SD 卡恢復先前的 XCSoar 資料（可選）\n\n- [%s] [地圖和數據](xcsoar://config/site-files) - 下載您所在地區的地圖、航點和空域文件\n\n- [%s] [飛機極地](xcsoar://config/planes) - 使用正確的極曲線設定您的飛機\n\n- [%s] [飛行員資訊](xcsoar://config/logger) - 輸入您的姓名和體重\n\n- [%s] [裝置](xcsoar://config/devices) - 連接您的飛行儀表\n\n- [%s] [威滑行](xcsoar://config/weglide) - 自動上傳航班至 WeGlide\n\n- [%s] [熱資訊圖](xcsoar://config/weather) - 在地圖上顯示來自 heatmap.info 的熱位置\n\n- [%s] [安全係數](xcsoar://config/safety) - 設定到達高度、地形間隙和極地退化\n\n- [%s] [地形顯示](xcsoar://config/terrain) - 選擇地形顏色、陰影和等高線\n\n- [ ] [即時追蹤](xcsoar://config/tracking) *(optional)* - 透過 SkyLines 或 LiveTrack24 分享您的位置\n\n探索 XCSoar 最簡單的方法是 [重播現有的 IGC 航班](xcsoar://dialog/replay).',
        '# Gesture Navigation\n\nXCSoar supports touch gestures on the map:\n\n- ![U](resource:IDB_GESTURE_UP) **Swipe Up** (U): Zoom in\n- ![D](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DOWN) **Swipe Down** (D): Zoom out\n- ![R](resource:IDB_GESTURE_RIGHT) **Swipe Right** (R): Previous screen mode\n- ![L](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LEFT) **Swipe Left** (L): Next screen mode\n- ![UD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_UD) **Up-Down** (UD): Auto zoom\n- ![DU](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DU) **Down-Up** (DU): Menu\n- ![DR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DR) **Down-Right** (DR): Waypoint details\n- ![DL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DL) **Down-Left** (DL): Alternates\n- ![LU](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LU) **Left-Up** (LU): Recently used waypoints\n- ![RD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_RD) **Right-Down** (RD): Task manager\n- ![URD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_URD) **Up-Right-Down** (URD): Analysis\n- ![LDR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LDR) **Left-Down-Right** (LDR): Checklist\n- ![URDL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_URDL) **Up-Right-Down-Left** (URDL): Pan mode\n- ![LDRDL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LDRDL) **Left-Down-Right-Down-Left** (LDRDL): Status\n- ![ULDR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_ULDR) **Up-Left-Down-Right** (ULDR): Quick menu\n\nLong-press on the map to enter Pan mode. Tap while in Pan mode to see nearby waypoints.': '# 手勢導航\n\nXCSoar支援地圖上的觸控手勢：\n\n- ![U](resource:IDB_GESTURE_UP) **向上滑動** (U): 放大\n- ![D](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DOWN) **向下滑動** (D): 縮小\n- ![R](resource:IDB_GESTURE_RIGHT) **向右滑動** (R): 上一螢幕模式\n- ![L](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LEFT) **向左滑動** (L): 下一頁模式\n- ![UD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_UD) **上下** (UD): 自動變焦\n- ![DU](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DU) **下-上** (DU): 選單\n- ![DR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DR) **徹頭徹尾** (DR): 航點詳情\n- ![DL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DL) **左下** (DL): 替補\n- ![LU](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LU) **左上** (LU): 最近使用的航點\n- ![RD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_RD) **右下** (RD): 工作管理員\n- ![URD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_URD) **上-右-下** (URD): 分析\n- ![LDR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LDR) **左-下-右** (LDR): 清單\n- ![URDL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_URDL) **右上-左下** (URDL): 平移模式\n- ![LDRDL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LDRDL) **左下右下左下** (LDRDL): 地位\n- ![ULDR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_ULDR) **上-左-下-右** (ULDR): 快速選單\n\n長按圖即可進入平移模式。在平移模式下點選可查看附近的航點。',
    },
}
